#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:130
msgid ""
"When :ref:`connecting a bank to Odoo <accounting/bank-synchronization/first-"
"synchronization>`:"
msgstr ""
"Saat :ref:`menghubungkan bank ke Odoo <accounting/bank-synchronization/first-"
"synchronization>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:132
msgid ""
"Depending on your bank and country, change the default third-party provider "
"when selecting the bank, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung bank dan negara Anda, ubah penyedia pihak ketiga default saat "
