msgid "Invoice creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:30
msgid ""
"Draft invoices can be created directly from documents like sales orders or "
"purchase orders or manually from the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` journal "
"in the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Faktur draft dapat dibuat langsung dari dokumen seperti pesanan penjualan "
"atau pesanan pembelian atau secara manual dari jurnal :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` di :guilabel:`Dashboard` Akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:33
msgid ""
"An invoice must include the required information to enable the customer to "
"pay promptly for their goods and services. Make sure the following fields "
"are appropriately completed:"
msgstr ""
"Faktur harus mencakup informasi yang diperlukan agar pelanggan dapat segera "
"membayar barang dan layanan mereka. Pastikan kolom berikut diisi dengan "
"tepat:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer`: When a customer is selected, Odoo automatically pulls "
"information from the customer record like the invoice "
"address, :doc:`preferred payment terms <customer_invoices/"
"payment_terms>`, :doc:`fiscal positions <taxes/fiscal_positions>`, "
"receivable account, and more onto the invoice. To change these values for "
"this specific invoice, edit them directly on the invoice. To change them for "
"future invoices, change the values on the contact record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pelanggan`: Ketika pelanggan dipilih, Odoo secara otomatis "
"menarik informasi dari catatan pelanggan seperti alamat "
"faktur, :doc:`ketentuan pembayaran yang disukai <customer_invoices/"
"payment_terms>`, :doc:`posisi fiskal <taxes/fiscal_positions>`, akun "
"piutang, dan lainnya ke dalam faktur. Untuk mengubah nilai-nilai ini untuk "
"faktur tertentu, edit langsung pada faktur. Untuk mengubahnya untuk faktur "
"mendatang, ubah nilai pada catatan kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice Date`: If not set manually, this field is automatically "
"set as the current date upon confirmation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Faktur`: Jika tidak diatur secara manual, kolom ini "
"secara otomatis diatur sebagai tanggal saat ini saat konfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Due Date` or :doc:`payment terms <customer_invoices/"
"payment_terms>`: To specify when the customer has to pay the invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Jatuh Tempo` atau :doc:`ketentuan pembayaran "
"<customer_invoices/payment_terms>`: Untuk menentukan kapan pelanggan harus "
"membayar faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`: Automatically set and can be changed if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jurnal`: Diatur secara otomatis dan dapat diubah jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:47
msgid ""
":doc:`Currency <get_started/multi_currency>`. If the invoice's currency "
"differs from the company's currency, the currency exchange rate is "
"automatically displayed."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Mata Uang <get_started/multi_currency>`. Jika mata uang faktur berbeda "
"dari mata uang perusahaan, nilai tukar mata uang akan ditampilkan secara "
"otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:50
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:93
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab:"
msgstr "Pada tab :guilabel:`Baris Faktur`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:52
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: Click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then search for and "
"select the product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produk`: Klik :guilabel:`Tambah baris`, lalu cari dan pilih "
"produk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:53
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:96
msgid ":guilabel:`Quantity`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kuantitas`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:54
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:97
msgid ":guilabel:`Price`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Harga`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:55
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:98
msgid ":doc:`Taxes <taxes>` (if applicable)"
msgstr ":doc:`Pajak <taxes>` (jika berlaku)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:57
msgid ""
"To access the product catalog and view all items in an organized display, "
"click :doc:`Catalog </applications/essentials/product_catalog>`. When the "
"products and quantities are selected, click :guilabel:`Back to Invoice` to "
"return to the invoice; the selected catalog items will appear in the invoice "
"lines."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses katalog produk dan melihat semua item dalam tampilan yang "
"terorganisir, klik :doc:`Katalog </applications/essentials/"
"product_catalog>`. Ketika produk dan jumlahnya dipilih, "
"klik :guilabel:`Kembali ke Faktur` untuk kembali ke faktur; item katalog "
"yang dipilih akan muncul di baris faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:63
msgid ""
"To display the total amount of the invoice in words, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and activate "
"the :guilabel:`Total amount of invoice in letters` option."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan jumlah total faktur dalam kata-kata, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan aktifkan "
"opsi :guilabel:`Jumlah total faktur dalam huruf`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:67
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab displays the accounting entries created. "
"Additional invoice information such as the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Reference`, :guilabel:`Payment Reference`, :doc:`Fiscal Positions <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`, :doc:`Incoterms <customer_invoices/incoterms>`, and more "
"can be added or modified in the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Item Jurnal` menampilkan entri akuntansi yang dibuat. "
"Informasi faktur tambahan seperti :guilabel:`Referensi "
"Pelanggan`, :guilabel:`Referensi Pembayaran`, :doc:`Posisi Fiskal <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`, :doc:`Incoterms <customer_invoices/incoterms>`, dan "
"lainnya dapat ditambahkan atau diubah pada tab :guilabel:`Info Lain`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:73
msgid ""
"Odoo initially creates invoices in :guilabel:`Draft` status. Draft invoices "
"have no accounting impact until they are :ref:`confirmed <accounting/invoice/"
"confirmation>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo awalnya membuat faktur dalam status :guilabel:`Draf`. Faktur draf tidak "
"memiliki dampak akuntansi sampai :ref:`dikonfirmasi <accounting/invoice/"
"confirmation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/overview.rst:47
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:82
msgid "Invoice confirmation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:84
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` when the invoice is completed. The invoice's "
"status changes to :guilabel:`Posted`, and a journal entry is generated based "
"on the invoice configuration. On confirmation, Odoo assigns each invoice a "
"unique number from a defined :doc:`sequence <customer_invoices/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` ketika faktur selesai. Status faktur berubah "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Diposting`, dan entri jurnal dibuat berdasarkan "
"konfigurasi faktur. Saat konfirmasi, Odoo memberikan setiap faktur nomor "
"unik dari :doc:`urutan <customer_invoices/sequence>` yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, an invoice can no longer be updated. Click :guilabel:`Reset "
"to draft` if changes are needed."
msgstr ""
"Setelah dikonfirmasi, faktur tidak dapat lagi diperbarui. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Reset ke draf` jika diperlukan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:92
msgid ""
"If required, invoices and other journal entries can be locked once posted "
"using the :ref:`Secure posted entries with hash <data-inalterability/"
"restricted>` feature."
msgstr ""
"Jika diperlukan, faktur dan entri jurnal lainnya dapat dikunci setelah "
"diposting menggunakan fitur :ref:`Amankan entri yang diposting dengan hash "
"<data-inalterability/restricted>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:98
msgid "Invoice sending"
msgstr "Invoice sending"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:100
msgid ""
"To set a preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method for a customer, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers` and select the "
"customer. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab of the contact form, select the "
"preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method in the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur metode :guilabel:`Pengiriman faktur` yang disukai untuk "
"pelanggan, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Pelanggan` dan "
"pilih pelanggan. Pada tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi` formulir kontak, pilih "
"metode :guilabel:`Pengiriman faktur` yang disukai pada "
"bagian :guilabel:`Faktur Pelanggan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:106
msgid ""
"Sending letters in Odoo requires :doc:`In-App Purchase (IAP) <../../"
"essentials/in_app_purchase>` credit or tokens."
msgstr ""
"Mengirim surat di Odoo memerlukan kredit atau token :doc:`Pembelian Dalam "
"Aplikasi (IAP) <../../essentials/in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:109
msgid ""
"To send the invoice to the customer, navigate back to the invoice record and "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim faktur ke pelanggan, kembali ke catatan faktur dan ikuti "
"langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:441
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:163
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:180
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:130
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:324
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:367
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:112
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`default invoice layout <studio/pdf-reports/default-layout>` has "
"not been customized yet, a :guilabel:`Configure your document layout` pop-up "
"window appears. Configure the layout and click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Jika :ref:`tata letak faktur default <studio/pdf-reports/default-layout>` "
"belum disesuaikan, jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Konfigurasikan tata letak "
"dokumen Anda` akan muncul. Konfigurasikan tata letak dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Lanjutkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:117
msgid "The document layout can be changed at any time in the general settings."
msgstr "Tata letak dokumen dapat diubah kapan saja di pengaturan umum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:118
msgid ""
"To add a QR code for banking app payments to the invoice, enable "
"the :guilabel:`QR Code` option in the :guilabel:`Configure Your Document "
"Layout` window. To modify this option, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Payments` section, and enable/disable the :guilabel:`QR Codes` option."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan kode QR untuk pembayaran aplikasi perbankan ke faktur, "
"aktifkan opsi :guilabel:`Kode QR` di jendela :guilabel:`Konfigurasikan Tata "
"Letak Dokumen Anda`. Untuk mengubah opsi ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi "
"--> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, gulir ke bawah ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Pembayaran Pelanggan`, dan aktifkan/nonaktifkan "
"opsi :guilabel:`Kode QR`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:123
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Send` window:"
msgstr "Di jendela :guilabel:`Kirim`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:125
msgid ""
"If a preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method was set in the contact "
"form, it is selected by default. Select another one if needed."
msgstr ""
"Jika metode :guilabel:`Pengiriman faktur` yang disukai telah diatur di "
"formulir kontak, metode tersebut akan dipilih secara default. Pilih metode "
"lain jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:127
msgid ""
"If no preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method was set in the contact "
"form, select the method to use for sending the invoice to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Jika metode :guilabel:`Pengiriman faktur` yang disukai tidak diatur di "
"formulir kontak, pilih metode yang akan digunakan untuk mengirim faktur ke "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:130
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` if the :guilabel:`by Email` option is selected, or "
"click :guilabel:`Download`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kirim` jika opsi :guilabel:`melalui Email` dipilih, atau "
"klik :guilabel:`Unduh`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:136
msgid "Sending multiple invoices"
msgstr "Mengirim beberapa faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:138
msgid ""
"To send multiple invoices, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --"
"> Invoices`, select them in the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view and "
"click :guilabel:`Send`. The :guilabel:`Send` window displays the number of "
"selected invoice to send by email."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim beberapa faktur, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan "
"--> Faktur`, pilih dari tampilan daftar di :guilabel:`Faktur` dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Jendela :guilabel:`Kirim` menampilkan jumlah faktur "
"yang dipilih untuk dikirim melalui email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:142
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Send`, a banner is added to the selected invoices "
"to indicate they are part of an ongoing send batch. This helps prevent the "
"process from being triggered manually again, as it may take some time to "
"complete for exceptionally large batches."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik :guilabel:`Kirim`, spanduk ditambahkan ke faktur yang "
"dipilih untuk menunjukkan bahwa faktur tersebut merupakan bagian dari batch "
"pengiriman yang sedang berlangsung. Ini membantu mencegah proses dipicu "
"secara manual lagi, karena mungkin memerlukan waktu untuk menyelesaikan "
"batch yang sangat besar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:146
msgid ""
"To check all invoices that have not yet been sent, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, click into the search bar and filter "
"on :guilabel:`Not Sent`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa semua faktur yang belum dikirim, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Faktur`. Di tampilan "
"daftar :guilabel:`Faktur`, klik ke bilah pencarian dan filter "
"pada :guilabel:`Belum Dikirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:153
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:197
msgid "Payment and reconciliation"
msgstr "Pembayaran dan rekonsiliasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:155
msgid ""
"In Odoo, an invoice is considered :guilabel:`Paid` when the associated "
"accounting entry has been reconciled with a corresponding bank transaction."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, faktur dianggap :guilabel:`Dibayar` ketika entri akuntansi yang "
"terkait telah direkonsiliasi dengan transaksi bank yang sesuai."

