"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Pelanggan`, akses formulir "
"pelanggan, buka tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Format` yang "
"sesuai di bagian :guilabel:`Faktur pelanggan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:35
msgid "E-invoice generation"
msgstr "Pembuatan e-invoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:37
msgid ""
"From a confirmed invoice, click :guilabel:`Send`. In the :guilabel:`Print & "
"Send` window, enable the relevant e-invoicing format option "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`by Peppol`), then click :guilabel:`Send` to generate and "
"attach the corresponding e-invoicing XML file."
msgstr ""
"Dari faktur yang dikonfirmasi, klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Di "
"jendela :guilabel:`Cetak & Kirim`, aktifkan opsi format e-invoicing yang "
"relevan (misalnya, :guilabel:`melalui Peppol`), lalu klik :guilabel:`Kirim` "
"untuk menghasilkan dan melampirkan file XML e-invoicing yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:44
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:377
msgid "Peppol"
msgstr "Peppol"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:46
msgid ""
"The `Peppol <https://peppol.org/about/>`_ network ensures the exchange of "
"documents and information between companies and governmental authorities. It "
"is primarily used for electronic invoicing, and its access points "
"(connectors to the Peppol network) allow companies to send electronic "
"documents such as customer invoices and credit notes and receive documents "
"like vendor bills and refunds."
msgstr ""
"Jaringan `Peppol <https://peppol.org/about/>`_ memastikan pertukaran dokumen "
"dan informasi antara perusahaan dan otoritas pemerintah. Ini terutama "
"digunakan untuk faktur elektronik, dan access point-nya (konektor ke "
"jaringan Peppol) memungkinkan perusahaan untuk mengirim dokumen elektronik "
"seperti faktur pelanggan dan nota kredit serta menerima dokumen seperti "
"tagihan vendor dan pengembalian dana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:51
msgid ""
"In this case, Odoo acts as both an **access point** and an :abbr:`SMP "
"(Service Metadata Publisher)` and enables electronic invoicing transactions "
"without the need to send invoices or bills by email or post."
msgstr ""
"Dalam hal ini, Odoo bertindak sebagai **access point** dan :abbr:`SMP "
"(Service Metadata Publisher)` dan memungkinkan transaksi faktur elektronik "
"tanpa perlu mengirim faktur atau tagihan melalui email atau pos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:56
msgid "Peppol registration is **free** and available in Odoo Community."
msgstr "Pendaftaran Peppol **gratis** dan tersedia di Odoo Community."

