#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:307
msgid "Peppol deregistration from Odoo"
msgstr "Pembatalan registrasi Peppol dari Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:309
msgid ""
"Only one Peppol receiver registration can be active for each Peppol endpoint "
"identifier at a time. To stop using Odoo as the Peppol access point, e.g., "
"to switch to another provider or reconfigure the registration for a new "
"database, you must first deregister from Peppol. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`PEPPOL Electronic Invoicing` section, "
"click :guilabel:`Remove from Peppol`, and confirm."
msgstr ""
"Hanya satu registrasi penerima Peppol yang dapat aktif untuk setiap pengenal "
"endpoint Peppol pada satu waktu. Untuk berhenti menggunakan Odoo sebagai "
"titik akses Peppol, misalnya untuk beralih ke penyedia lain atau "
"mengkonfigurasi ulang registrasi untuk database baru, Anda harus terlebih "
"dahulu membatalkan registrasi dari Peppol. Untuk melakukannya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, gulir ke "
"bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`PEPPOL Electronic Invoicing`, "
"klik :guilabel:`Remove from Peppol`, dan konfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:315
msgid ""
"Once removed, the Peppol registration is deleted from the database, and "
"documents can no longer be sent or received via Peppol in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Setelah dihapus, registrasi Peppol dihapus dari database, dan dokumen tidak "
"dapat lagi dikirim atau diterima melalui Peppol di Odoo."

