"transactions. Additionally, Odoo enables seamless transmission of e-invoices "
"through platforms connected to the Peppol network, ensuring compliance with "
"Estonian and EU e-invoicing standards."
msgstr ""
"**Format yang didukung**: Odoo mendukung format faktur elektronik standar, "
"seperti XML dalam format :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)`, yang "
"sepenuhnya kompatibel dengan Sistem e-Invoicing Rik's Estonia untuk "
"transaksi pengadaan publik. Selain itu, Odoo memungkinkan transmisi faktur "
"elektronik yang mulus melalui platform yang terhubung ke jaringan Peppol, "
"memastikan kepatuhan terhadap standar e-invoicing Estonia dan UE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrival**: In accordance with Estonian regulations to "
