"portal.sat.gob.gt/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:12
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Guatemala"
msgstr "Kerangka hukum untuk faktur elektronik di Guatemala"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:14
msgid ""
"Guatemala has mandated electronic invoicing under the :abbr:`FEL (Factura "
"Electrónica en Línea)` system, which applies to most businesses to enhance "
"fiscal control and modernize tax administration. Key elements include:"
msgstr ""
"Guatemala telah mewajibkan faktur elektronik berdasarkan sistem :abbr:`FEL "
"(Factura Electrónica en Línea)`, yang berlaku untuk sebagian besar bisnis "
"guna meningkatkan kontrol fiskal dan memodernisasi administrasi pajak. "
"Elemen kunci meliputi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Factura Electrónica en Línea (FEL)**: A mandatory e-invoicing system "
"required for B2B, B2C, and :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` "
"transactions, regulated by the :abbr:`SAT (Superintendencia de "
"Administración Tributaria)`. Each authorized document must be digitally "
"signed and contain a unique certification code."
msgstr ""
"**Factura Electrónica en Línea (FEL)**: Sistem faktur elektronik wajib yang "
"diperlukan untuk transaksi B2B, B2C, dan :abbr:`B2G (bisnis-ke-pemerintah)`, "
"diatur oleh :abbr:`SAT (Superintendencia de Administración Tributaria)`. "
"Setiap dokumen resmi harus ditandatangani secara digital dan berisi kode "
"sertifikasi unik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Integration with SAT**: All electronic documents must be issued through a "
"certified certifier `(Proveedor de Certificación)` and validated by "
"the :abbr:`SAT (Superintendencia de Administración Tributaria)` before being "
"delivered to the customer. Once validated, the document receives a "
"certification date and unique UUID."
msgstr ""
"**Integrasi dengan SAT**: Semua dokumen elektronik harus diterbitkan melalui "
"sertifikator bersertifikat `(Proveedor de Certificación)` dan divalidasi "
"oleh :abbr:`SAT (Superintendencia de Administración Tributaria)` sebelum "
"dikirim ke pelanggan. Setelah divalidasi, dokumen menerima tanggal "
"sertifikasi dan UUID unik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:26
msgid ""
"**XML Format**: Guatemala mandates the use of XML for electronic documents, "
"following SAT's official XSD schema to ensure interoperability and "
"traceability."
msgstr ""
"**Format XML**: Guatemala mewajibkan penggunaan XML untuk dokumen "
"elektronik, mengikuti skema XSD resmi SAT untuk memastikan interoperabilitas "
"dan keterlacakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Adoption Timeline**: The transition to FEL has been implemented gradually "
"by economic activity and taxpayer profile, but it is now mandatory for most "
"business sectors in the country."
msgstr ""
"**Jadwal Adopsi**: Transisi ke FEL telah diterapkan secara bertahap "
"berdasarkan aktivitas ekonomi dan profil wajib pajak, tetapi sekarang wajib "
"untuk sebagian besar sektor bisnis di negara ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:32
msgid "Compliance with Guatemalan e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Kepatuhan terhadap peraturan faktur elektronik Guatemala"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:34
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing simplifies compliance with Guatemala's e-invoicing "
