"bersertifikat, termasuk representasi grafis XML dan PDF mereka, dengan akses "
"penuh untuk audit dan proses kontrol."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:44
msgid ""
"**Automatic tax calculation and reporting**: Odoo automates VAT (IVA) and "
