"click on the :guilabel:`Register Payment` payment button of your document "
"and, in the pop-up window, select a **currency** in the :guilabel:`Amount` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendaftarkan pembayaran dalam mata uang selain mata uang utama "
"perusahaan Anda, klik pada tombol :guilabel:`Daftarkan Pembayaran` di "
"dokumen Anda dan, di jendela pop-up, pilih **mata uang** di "
"field :guilabel:`Jumlah`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
