#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:28
msgid ""
"To export reports in PDF or XLSX format, click :guilabel:`PDF` at the top or "
"click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` (:guilabel:`down arrow`) icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`PDF` button and select :guilabel:`XLSX`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengekspor laporan dalam format PDF atau XLSX, klik :guilabel:`PDF` di "
"bagian atas atau klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-down` (:guilabel:`panah bawah`) "
"di sebelah tombol :guilabel:`PDF` dan pilih :guilabel:`XLSX`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:32
msgid ""
"To compare values across periods, click the :guilabel:`Comparison` menu and "
"select the periods you want to compare."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membandingkan nilai antar periode, klik menu :guilabel:`Perbandingan` "
"dan pilih periode yang ingin Anda bandingkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:None
msgid "Comparison menu to compare time periods."
msgstr "Menu Perbandingan untuk membandingkan periode waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:43
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Balance Sheet` shows a snapshot of your organization's "
"assets, liabilities, and equity at a particular date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Neraca Keuangan` menampilkan gambaran aset, kewajiban, dan "
"ekuitas organisasi Anda pada tanggal tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:51
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Profit and Loss` report (or **Income Statement**) shows your "
"company's net income by deducting expenses from revenue for the reporting "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`Laba Rugi` (atau **Laporan Laba Rugi**) menampilkan laba "
"bersih perusahaan Anda dengan mengurangi pengeluaran dari pendapatan untuk "
"periode pelaporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:57
msgid "Executive Summary"
msgstr "Ringkasan Eksekutif"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:59
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Executive Summary` provides an overview of all the important "
"figures for overseeing your company's performance."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ringkasan Eksekutif` menyediakan gambaran umum semua angka "
"penting untuk mengawasi kinerja perusahaan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:62
msgid "It includes the following items:"
msgstr "Ini mencakup item-item berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`Performance`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kinerja`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:66
msgid ":guilabel:`Gross profit margin`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Margin laba kotor`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:66
msgid ""
"The contribution of all sales your business makes **minus** any direct costs "
"needed to make those sales (labor, materials, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Kontribusi dari semua penjualan yang dilakukan bisnis Anda **dikurangi** "
"biaya langsung yang diperlukan untuk melakukan penjualan tersebut (tenaga "
"kerja, bahan, dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:70
msgid ":guilabel:`Net profit margin`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Margin laba bersih`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:69
msgid ""
"The contribution of all sales made by your business **minus** any direct "
"costs needed to make those sales *and* fixed overheads your company has "
"(electricity, rent, taxes to be paid as a result of those sales, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Kontribusi dari semua penjualan yang dilakukan oleh bisnis Anda "
"**dikurangi** biaya langsung yang diperlukan untuk melakukan penjualan "
"tersebut *dan* overhead tetap yang dimiliki perusahaan Anda (listrik, sewa, "
"pajak yang harus dibayar sebagai hasil dari penjualan tersebut, dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`Return on investment (per annum)`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Laba atas investasi (per tahun)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:73
msgid ""
"The ratio of the net profit to the amount of assets the company used to make "
"those profits."
msgstr ""
"Rasio laba bersih terhadap jumlah aset yang digunakan perusahaan untuk "
"menghasilkan laba tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:88
msgid ":guilabel:`Position`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Posisi`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:76
msgid ":guilabel:`Average debtors days`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rata-rata hari debitur`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:76
msgid ""
"The average number of days it takes your customers to (fully) pay you across "
"all your customer invoices."
msgstr ""
"Rata-rata jumlah hari yang dibutuhkan pelanggan Anda untuk membayar (secara "
"penuh) di semua faktur pelanggan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:78
msgid ":guilabel:`Average creditors days`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rata-rata hari kreditur`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:79
msgid ""
"The average number of days it takes you to (fully) pay your suppliers across "
"all your bills."
msgstr ""
"Rata-rata jumlah hari yang dibutuhkan Anda untuk membayar (secara penuh) "
"pemasok Anda di semua tagihan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Short-term cash forecast`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Prakiraan kas jangka pendek`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:81
msgid ""
"How much cash is expected in or out of your business in the next month, "
"i.e., the balance of your **Sales account** for the month **minus** the "
"balance of your **Purchases account** for the month."
msgstr ""
"Berapa banyak kas yang diharapkan masuk atau keluar dari bisnis Anda dalam "
"bulan berikutnya, yaitu saldo **akun Penjualan** Anda untuk bulan tersebut "
"**dikurangi** saldo **akun Pembelian** Anda untuk bulan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:88
msgid ":guilabel:`Current assets to liabilities`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Aset lancar terhadap liabilitas`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:85
msgid ""
"Also referred to as the **current ratio**, this is the ratio of current "
"assets (:dfn:`assets that could be turned into cash within a year`) to the "
"current liabilities (:dfn:`liabilities that will be due in the next year`). "
"It is typically used to measure a company's ability to service its debt."
msgstr ""
"Juga disebut sebagai **rasio lancar**, ini adalah rasio aset lancar "
"(:dfn:`aset yang dapat diubah menjadi kas dalam satu tahun`) terhadap "
"liabilitas lancar (:dfn:`liabilitas yang akan jatuh tempo dalam tahun "
"berikutnya`). Ini biasanya digunakan untuk mengukur kemampuan perusahaan "
"dalam melunasi utangnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:93
msgid "General Ledger"
msgstr "Buku Besar Umum"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:95
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`General Ledger` report shows all transactions from all "
"accounts for a selected date range. The initial summary report shows the "
"totals for each account. To expand an account and view its details, click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`right arrow`) on the left. This "
"report is useful for reviewing each transaction that occurred during a "
"specific period."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`Buku Besar` menampilkan semua transaksi dari semua akun "
"untuk rentang tanggal yang dipilih. Laporan ringkasan awal menampilkan total "
"untuk setiap akun. Untuk memperluas akun dan melihat detailnya, "
"klik :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`panah kanan`) di sebelah kiri. "
"Laporan ini berguna untuk meninjau setiap transaksi yang terjadi selama "
"periode tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:105
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Aged Receivable` report shows the sales invoices awaiting "
"payment during a selected month and several months prior."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`Piutang Jatuh Tempo` menampilkan faktur penjualan yang "
"menunggu pembayaran selama bulan yang dipilih dan beberapa bulan sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:113
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Aged Payable` report displays information on individual "
"bills, credit notes, and overpayments you owe and how long these have gone "
"unpaid."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`Utang Jatuh Tempo` menampilkan informasi tentang tagihan "
"individual, nota kredit, dan pembayaran berlebih yang Anda utang serta "
"berapa lama ini belum dibayar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:119
msgid "Cash Flow Statement"
msgstr "Laporan Alur Kas"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:121
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cash Flow Statement` shows how changes in balance sheet "
"accounts and income affect cash and cash equivalents and breaks the analysis "
"down to operating, investing, and financing activities."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Laporan Arus Kas` menunjukkan bagaimana perubahan akun neraca "
"keuangan dan pendapatan mempengaruhi kas dan setara kas serta memecah "
"analisis menjadi aktivitas operasi, investasi, dan pendanaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:128
msgid "Tax Report"
msgstr "Laporan Pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:130
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Report` shows the :guilabel:`NET` and :guilabel:`TAX` "
"amounts for all the taxes grouped by type "
"(:guilabel:`Sales`/:guilabel:`Purchases`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Laporan Pajak` menampilkan jumlah :guilabel:`NETO` "
"dan :guilabel:`PAJAK` untuk semua pajak yang dikelompokkan berdasarkan jenis "
"(:guilabel:`Penjualan`/:guilabel:`Pembelian`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:149
msgid "Audit Trail"
msgstr "Audit Trail"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:151
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Audit Trail` report tracks changes made to fields that have "
"an impact on accounting and includes the date and time of the changes, the "
"user who made the changes, the type of change, the previous value, and the "
"updated value."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`Audit Trail` melacak perubahan yang dilakukan pada field "
"yang memengaruhi akuntansi dan mencakup tanggal serta waktu perubahan, user "
"yang melakukan perubahan, jenis perubahan, nilai sebelumnya, dan nilai yang "
"diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:155
msgid ""
"Changes to records are generally recorded in the :doc:`chatter </"
"applications/productivity/discuss/chatter>`, but with the audit trail "
"setting enabled, users get a dedicated and detailed audit trail report that "
"is immutable for better tracking. The audit trail report is available for "
"audit checks, satisfying the requirements of the financial authorities and "
"auditors of various countries."
msgstr ""
"Perubahan pada catatan umumnya dicatat di :doc:`chatter </applications/"
"productivity/discuss/chatter>`, tetapi dengan pengaturan jejak audit "
"diaktifkan, pengguna mendapatkan laporan jejak audit khusus dan terperinci "
"yang tidak dapat diubah untuk pelacakan yang lebih baik. Laporan jejak audit "
"tersedia untuk pemeriksaan audit, memenuhi persyaratan otoritas keuangan dan "
"auditor di berbagai negara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:161
msgid ""
"To enable the audit trail setting, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Settings --> Configuration`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Audit Trail` "
"section, and tick the checkbox beside :guilabel:`Audit Trail`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan pengaturan jejak audit, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pengaturan --> Konfigurasi`, gulir ke bawah "
"ke bagian :guilabel:`Jejak Audit`, dan centang kotak di "
"samping :guilabel:`Jejak Audit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:166
msgid ""
"Once enabled, the audit trail setting cannot be disabled, ensuring a "
"immutable and reliable record for audit and compliance purposes. Journal "
"entries, including invoices and vendor bills, cannot be deleted once they "
"are posted; they can only be cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Setelah diaktifkan, pengaturan jejak audit tidak dapat dinonaktifkan, "
"memastikan catatan yang tidak dapat diubah dan andal untuk tujuan audit dan "
"kepatuhan. Entri jurnal, termasuk faktur dan tagihan vendor, tidak dapat "
"dihapus setelah diposting; mereka hanya dapat dibatalkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:170
msgid ""
"To access the audit trail after it has been enabled, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Audit Trail`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses jejak audit setelah diaktifkan, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Jejak Audit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:3
msgid "Analytic accounting"
msgstr "Akuntansi analiti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:5
msgid ""
"Analytic accounting helps track costs and revenues and analyze a project's "
"or service's profitability. When creating journal entries, costs can "
"be :ref:`distributed <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` "
"across one or more analytic accounts."
msgstr ""
"Akuntansi analitik membantu melacak biaya dan pendapatan serta menganalisis "
"profitabilitas proyek atau layanan. Saat membuat entri jurnal, biaya "
"dapat :ref:`didistribusikan <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-"
"distribution>` ke satu atau lebih akun analitik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:9
msgid ""
"To activate this feature, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings` and enable :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` in "
"the :guilabel:`Analytics` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan fitur ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi "
"--> Pengaturan` dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Akun Analitik` di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Analitik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:13
msgid ":doc:`Analytic budget <budget>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Anggaran analitik <budget>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:18
msgid "Analytic accounts"
msgstr "Akun-akun analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:20
msgid "Analytic accounts give an overview of costs and revenue."
msgstr "Akun analitik memberikan gambaran umum biaya dan pendapatan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:22
msgid ""
"To access analytic accounts, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Analytic Accounts`. To create a new analytic account, "
"click :guilabel:`New` and fill in the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses akun analitik, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Akun Analitik`. Untuk membuat akun analitik baru, "
"klik :guilabel:`Baru` dan isi informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:26
msgid ":guilabel:`Analytic Account`: Assign the name of the analytic account."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Akun Analitik`: Tetapkan nama akun analitik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:27
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer`: Select the customer linked to the project, if "
"applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pelanggan`: Pilih pelanggan yang terkait dengan project, jika ada."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:28
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reference`: Include a reference to make the account easier to "
"find if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Referensi`: Sertakan referensi untuk memudahkan pencarian akun "
"jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Plan`: Link the :guilabel:`Analytic Account` to an :ref:`analytic "
"plan <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rencana`: Tautkan :guilabel:`Akun Analitik` ke :ref:`rencana "
"analitik <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: In a :doc:`multi-company </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` environment, select the company using the analytic "
"account. To make the analytic account accessible to all companies, leave the "
"field empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`: Dalam lingkungan :doc:`multi-perusahaan </"
"applications/general/companies/multi_company>`, pilih perusahaan yang "
"menggunakan akun analitik. Untuk membuat akun analitik dapat diakses oleh "
"semua perusahaan, biarkan bidang kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: Update the currency of the analytic account if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mata Uang`: Perbarui mata uang akun analitik jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:36
msgid "Then, the :doc:`budget <budget>` information can be filled in."
msgstr "Kemudian, informasi :doc:`anggaran <budget>` dapat diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:41
msgid "Analytic plans"
msgstr "Rencana analiti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:43
msgid ""
"Analytic plans group :ref:`analytic accounts <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_accounts>`, allowing the company to analyze its accounting, such as "
"tracking costs and revenues by project or department."
msgstr ""
"Rencana analitik mengelompokkan :ref:`akun analitik <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`, memungkinkan perusahaan untuk "
"menganalisis akuntansinya, seperti melacak biaya dan pendapatan berdasarkan "
"project atau departemen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:47
msgid ""
"To access analytic plans, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Analytic Plans`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new plan, add a name, "
"and fill in the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses rencana analitik, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Rencana Analitik`. Klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk membuat "
"rencana baru, tambahkan nama, dan isi informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Parent`: Link the plan to another analytic plan if a hierarchy "
"between plans must be built."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Induk`: Tautkan rencana ke rencana analitik lain jika hierarki "
"antara rencana harus dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Applicability`: Define how the plan is applied when "
"creating a new journal entry:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penerapan Default`: Tentukan bagaimana rencana diterapkan saat "
"membuat entri jurnal baru:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:55
msgid ":guilabel:`Optional`: Adding the analytic plan is not mandatory."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opsional`: Menambahkan rencana analitik tidak wajib."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory`: The entry cannot be confirmed if no analytic account "
"is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Wajib`: Entri tidak dapat dikonfirmasi jika tidak ada akun "
"analitik yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:57
msgid ":guilabel:`Unavailable`: The plan is not available."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tidak Tersedia`: Rencana tidak tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Color`: Set a color for the tag related to this specific plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Warna`: Tetapkan warna untuk tag yang terkait dengan rencana "
"spesifik ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:61
msgid ""
"To fine-tune a plan's applicability, create a new line in "
"the :guilabel:`Applicability` tab and set the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyesuaikan penerapan rencana secara detail, buat baris baru di "
"tab :guilabel:`Penerapan` dan atur bidang berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Domain`: Choose the accounting documents to which the plan "
"applies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Domain`: Pilih dokumen akuntansi yang menjadi target penerapan "
"rencana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Financial Accounts Prefixes`: Enter the prefix(es) of the "
"account(s) to which the plan applies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Awalan Akun Keuangan`: Masukkan awalan akun yang menjadi target "
"penerapan rencana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Category`: Choose the product category to which the plan "
"applies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategori Produk`: Pilih kategori produk yang menjadi target "
"penerapan rencana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Applicability`: Define how the plan is applied when creating a "
"new journal entry. The applicability set here always overrides the default "
"applicability."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penerapan`: Tentukan bagaimana rencana diterapkan saat membuat "
"entri jurnal baru. Penerapan yang ditetapkan di sini selalu mengesampingkan "
"penerapan default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: In a :doc:`multi-company </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` environment, select the company using the plan. To "
"make the analytic plan accessible to all companies, leave the field empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`: Dalam lingkungan :doc:`multi-perusahaan </"
"applications/general/companies/multi_company>`, pilih perusahaan yang "
"menggunakan rencana tersebut. Untuk membuat rencana analitik dapat diakses "
"oleh semua perusahaan, biarkan kolom kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:74
msgid "Two smart buttons are available:"
msgstr "Dua tombol pintar tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subplans`: To have a more complex analytic structure. Click the "
"smart button, then click :guilabel:`New` to add a subplan. This creates a "
"parent-child relationship between the two plans, and the :guilabel:`Parent` "
"field of the subplan is automatically populated with the original plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Subrencana`: Untuk memiliki struktur analitik yang lebih "
"kompleks. Klik tombol pintar, lalu klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk menambahkan "
"subrencana. Ini menciptakan hubungan induk-anak antara kedua rencana, dan "
"kolom :guilabel:`Induk` dari subrencana secara otomatis terisi dengan "
"rencana awal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Accounts`: To access the :ref:`analytic accounts "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` linked to the plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Akun Analitik`: Untuk mengakses :ref:`akun analitik <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` yang terhubung dengan rencana "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:84
msgid "Each analytic plan must have at least one analytic account."
msgstr "Setiap rencana analitik harus memiliki setidaknya satu akun analitik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:89
msgid "Analytic distribution"
msgstr "Distribusi analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:91
msgid ""
"The distribution of costs in one or more analytic accounts can be set in "
"each :ref:`invoice/bill <accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-"
"invoices-bills>` or :ref:`en masse <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"distribution-mass>`."
msgstr ""
"Distribusi biaya dalam satu atau lebih akun analitik dapat diatur di "
"setiap :ref:`faktur/tagihan <accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-"
"invoices-bills>` atau :ref:`secara massal <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"distribution-mass>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:96
msgid ""
"The analytic distribution is prefilled based on the applicability and "
"the :ref:`analytic distribution models <accounting/"
"analytic_distribution_models>`."
msgstr ""
"Distribusi analitik terisi otomatis berdasarkan penerapan dan :ref:`model "
"distribusi analitik <accounting/analytic_distribution_models>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:102
msgid "Analytic distribution on invoices or bills"
msgstr "Distribusi analitik pada faktur atau tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:104
msgid ""
"To add analytic distribution, click the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` "
"column when creating an :ref:`invoice <accounting/invoice/creation>` "
"or :ref:`bill <accounting/vendor_bills/creation>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan distribusi analitik, klik kolom :guilabel:`Distribusi "
"Analitik` saat membuat :ref:`faktur <accounting/invoice/creation>` "
"atau :ref:`tagihan <accounting/vendor_bills/creation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:108
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field is mandatory only if "
"the :ref:`analytic plan <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` has "
"been set as :guilabel:`Mandatory` in either the :guilabel:`Default "
"Applicability` field on an analytic plan or the :guilabel:`Applicability` "
"field on an analytic plan line."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` wajib diisi hanya jika :ref:`rencana "
"analitik <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` telah diatur "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Wajib` baik di kolom :guilabel:`Penerapan Default` pada "
"rencana analitik atau kolom :guilabel:`Penerapan` pada baris rencana "
"analitik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:113
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Analytic` window, select the desired :guilabel:`Analytic "
"Accounts` in the different :guilabel:`Analytic Plans` displayed in columns. "
"Then, split the costs between the accounts by modifying the percentage."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela :guilabel:`Analitik`, pilih :guilabel:`Akun Analitik` yang "
"diinginkan di berbagai :guilabel:`Rencana Analitik` yang ditampilkan dalam "
"kolom. Kemudian, bagi biaya di antara akun dengan mengubah persentase."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:None
msgid "create a distribution template"
msgstr "buat templat distribusi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:123
msgid "Analytic distribution en masse"
msgstr "Distribusi analitik secara massal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:125
msgid ""
"To mass-edit analytic accounts in several entries simultaneously, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Journal items`, and select "
"the ones that need to be updated. Click the :guilabel:`Analytic "
"Distribution` column and add the required distribution in "
"the :guilabel:`Analytic` column, then click the :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(cross)` and :guilabel:`Confirm`. The analytic "
"distribution is then added to the selected journal items."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit akun analitik secara massal di beberapa entri sekaligus, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Item jurnal`, dan pilih "
"yang perlu diperbarui. Klik kolom :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` dan "
"tambahkan distribusi yang diperlukan di kolom :guilabel:`Analitik`, lalu "
"klik :icon:`oi-close` :guilabel:`(silang)` dan :guilabel:`Konfirmasi`. "
"Distribusi analitik kemudian ditambahkan ke item jurnal yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:134
msgid "Analytic distribution models"
msgstr "Model distribusi analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:136
msgid ""
"Analytic distribution models automatically apply a specific distribution "
"based on defined criteria."
msgstr ""
"Model distribusi analitik secara otomatis menerapkan distribusi tertentu "
"berdasarkan kriteria yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:138
msgid ""
"To create a new analytic distribution model, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Analytic Distribution "
"Models`, click :guilabel:`New`, and set the conditions the model has to meet "
"to apply automatically:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat model distribusi analitik baru, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi "
"--> Konfigurasi --> Model Distribusi Analitik`, klik :guilabel:`Baru`, dan "
"atur kondisi yang harus dipenuhi model agar diterapkan secara otomatis:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:143
msgid ""
"All specified conditions of an analytic distribution model must be met for "
"the model to be applied. To apply an analytic distribution model based on "
"individual conditions, create separate analytic distribution models for each "
"condition."
msgstr ""
"Semua kondisi yang ditentukan dari model distribusi analitik harus terpenuhi "
"agar model dapat diterapkan. Untuk menerapkan model distribusi analitik "
"berdasarkan kondisi individual, buat model distribusi analitik terpisah "
"untuk setiap kondisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:146
msgid ""
"Analytic distribution models can be combined and sequenced, allowing "
"distribution across multiple models if linked to different :ref:`analytic "
"plans <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>`. To adjust the order, "
"drag and drop the models using the :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(draggable)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Model distribusi analitik dapat digabungkan dan diurutkan, memungkinkan "
"distribusi di beberapa model jika terhubung dengan :ref:`rencana analitik "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` yang berbeda. Untuk "
"menyesuaikan urutan, seret dan lepas model menggunakan ikon :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(dapat diseret)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accounts Prefixes`: Apply the distribution model only to journal "
"items involving accounts that begin with specific prefixes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prefiks Akun`: Terapkan model distribusi hanya pada item jurnal "
"yang melibatkan akun yang dimulai dengan prefiks tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner`: Apply the distribution model only to journal items "
"involving a specific partner."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mitra`: Terapkan model distribusi hanya pada item jurnal yang "
"melibatkan mitra tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:155
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: Apply the distribution model only to journal items "
"involving a specific product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produk`: Terapkan model distribusi hanya pada item jurnal yang "
"melibatkan produk tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:157
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: In a :doc:`multi-company </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` environment, apply the distribution model only to "
"journal items involving a specific company. To apply it across all "
"companies, leave the field empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`: Dalam lingkungan :doc:`multi-perusahaan </"
"applications/general/companies/multi_company>`, terapkan model distribusi "
"hanya pada item jurnal yang melibatkan perusahaan tertentu. Untuk "
"menerapkannya di semua perusahaan, biarkan kolom kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:160
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`: :ref:`Analytic distribution <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` that will be applied when the "
"above conditions are met."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik`: :ref:`Distribusi analitik <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` yang akan diterapkan ketika "
"kondisi di atas terpenuhi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:165
msgid ""
"Any time a journal item is posted to the :guilabel:`Utilities (601000)` "
"account, it should be automatically distributed in "
"the :guilabel:`Departments` analytic plan as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Setiap kali item jurnal diposting ke akun :guilabel:`Utilitas (601000)`, "
"item tersebut harus secara otomatis didistribusikan dalam rencana "
"analitik :guilabel:`Departemen` sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:168
msgid "60% to the :guilabel:`Manufacturing` analytic account"
msgstr "60% ke akun analitik :guilabel:`Manufaktur`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:169
msgid "30% to the :guilabel:`Marketing` analytic account"
msgstr "30% ke akun analitik :guilabel:`Pemasaran`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:170
msgid "10% to the :guilabel:`Admin` analytic account"
msgstr "10% ke akun analitik :guilabel:`Admin`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:172
msgid ""
"To automate this distribution, the :guilabel:`Accounts Prefix` can be set to "
"`601`, as :guilabel:`Utilities (601000)` is the only account in the chart of "
"accounts that begins with `601`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengotomatiskan distribusi ini, :guilabel:`Awalan Akun` dapat diatur "
"ke `601`, karena :guilabel:`Utilitas (601000)` adalah satu-satunya akun "
"dalam bagan akun yang dimulai dengan `601`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:176
msgid ""
"If additional accounts such as :guilabel:`Electricity (601100)` "
"or :guilabel:`Gas (601200)` are available in the chart of accounts, the "
"distribution will also apply to both since they share the same prefix."
msgstr ""
"Jika akun tambahan seperti :guilabel:`Listrik (601100)` atau :guilabel:`Gas "
"(601200)` tersedia dalam bagan akun, distribusi juga akan berlaku untuk "
"keduanya karena memiliki awalan yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:180
msgid ""
"To define more criteria, use the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(adjust settings)` icon to reveal more columns or "
"click :guilabel:`View` on an individual analytic distribution model."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menentukan lebih banyak kriteria, gunakan ikon :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(sesuaikan pengaturan)` untuk menampilkan lebih banyak "
"kolom atau klik :guilabel:`Lihat` pada model distribusi analitik individual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner Category`: Apply this distribution model only to journal "
"items involving a partner in a specific category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategori Mitra`: Terapkan model distribusi ini hanya pada item "
"jurnal yang melibatkan mitra dalam kategori tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:185
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Category`: Apply this distribution model to journal items "
"involving a product in a specific category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategori Produk`: Terapkan model distribusi ini pada item jurnal "
"yang melibatkan produk dalam kategori tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:189
msgid ""
"Alternatively, it is possible to create an analytic distribution model from "
"the :guilabel:`Analytic` window by clicking :guilabel:`New Model`:"
msgstr ""
"Sebagai alternatif, dimungkinkan untuk membuat model distribusi analitik "
"dari jendela :guilabel:`Analitik` dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Model Baru`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:192
msgid ""
"either when creating an invoice/bill and filling in the :ref:`analytic "
"distribution <accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-invoices-bills>`;"
msgstr ""
"baik saat membuat faktur/tagihan dan mengisi :ref:`distribusi analitik "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-invoices-bills>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:194
msgid ""
"or when :ref:`mass-editing analytic accounts <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"distribution-mass>` in several entries simultaneously."
msgstr ""
"atau saat :ref:`mengedit massal akun analitik <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/distribution-mass>` dalam beberapa entri secara "
"bersamaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:3
msgid "Budgets"
msgstr "Anggaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:5
msgid ""
":ref:`Analytic budgets <accounting/budgets/analytic-budgets>` track specific "
"activities and projects using analytic accounts, helping businesses make "
"informed decisions about specific departments, projects, or other groups of "
"transactions. In contrast, :ref:`financial budgets <accounting/budgets/"
"financial>` are tied to the general ledger accounts that appear on the "
"profit and loss and focus on the company's overall economic position."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Anggaran analitik <accounting/budgets/analytic-budgets>` melacak "
"aktivitas dan proyek tertentu menggunakan akun analitik, membantu bisnis "
"membuat keputusan berdasarkan informasi tentang departemen, proyek, atau "
"kelompok transaksi tertentu. Sebaliknya, :ref:`anggaran keuangan <accounting/"
"budgets/financial>` terkait dengan akun buku besar yang muncul pada laba "
"rugi dan berfokus pada posisi ekonomi keseluruhan perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:14
msgid "Analytic budgets"
msgstr "Budget analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:16
msgid ""
"Analytic budgets allow for allocating and tracking income and expenses in "
"detail, breaking down costs and revenues by specific projects, departments, "
"or groups of transactions. Analytic budgets can be applied across various "
"departments or projects to measure profitability and performance. Odoo "
"manages analytic budgets using :doc:`analytic accounting "
"<analytic_accounting>`."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran analitik memungkinkan untuk mengalokasikan dan melacak pendapatan "
"dan pengeluaran secara rinci, merinci biaya dan pendapatan berdasarkan "
"proyek, departemen, atau kelompok transaksi tertentu. Anggaran analitik "
"dapat diterapkan di berbagai departemen atau proyek untuk mengukur "
"profitabilitas dan kinerja. Odoo mengelola anggaran analitik "
"menggunakan :doc:`akuntansi analitik <analytic_accounting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:21
msgid ""
"To activate the option for creating analytic budgets, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Budget Management` in the :guilabel:`Analytics` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan opsi pembuatan anggaran analitik, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Manajemen Anggaran` di bagian :guilabel:`Analitik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:26
msgid ""
"Odoo structures budgets using :ref:`plans <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_plans>` and :ref:`accounts <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_accounts>`, which must be configured *before* creating a budget."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menyusun anggaran menggunakan :ref:`rencana <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` dan :ref:`akun <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`, yang harus dikonfigurasi *sebelum* "
"membuat anggaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:33
msgid "Set an analytic budget"
msgstr "Tetapkan anggaran analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create a new budget, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> "
"Analytic Budgets` and click :guilabel:`New`. Make sure the following fields "
"are appropriately completed: :guilabel:`Budget Name`, :guilabel:`Period`, "
"and :guilabel:`Budget Type`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat anggaran baru, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --"
"> Anggaran Analitik` dan klik :guilabel:`Baru`. Pastikan field berikut diisi "
"dengan tepat: :guilabel:`Nama Anggaran`, :guilabel:`Periode`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Tipe Anggaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:39
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Budget Lines` tab to "
"structure the budget with the :ref:`analytic plans <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` and :ref:`accounts <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` previously created. While "
"the :ref:`analytic plans <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` "
"correspond to the column names, select the :ref:`analytic accounts "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` to define the budget "
"lines and set the amounts for each in the :guilabel:`Budgeted` column. Once "
"all the budget lines are settled, click :guilabel:`Open`. If changes need to "
"be made once the budget's status is :guilabel:`Open`, there are two options:"
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Tambah baris` di tab :guilabel:`Baris Anggaran` untuk "
"menyusun anggaran dengan :ref:`rencana analitik <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` dan :ref:`akun <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` yang telah dibuat sebelumnya. "
"Sementara :ref:`rencana analitik <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_plans>` sesuai dengan nama kolom, pilih :ref:`akun analitik "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` untuk menentukan baris "
"anggaran dan tetapkan jumlah untuk masing-masing di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Dianggarkan`. Setelah semua baris anggaran selesai, "
"klik :guilabel:`Buka`. Jika perubahan perlu dilakukan setelah status "
"anggaran :guilabel:`Buka`, ada dua opsi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reset to Draft`: To overwrite the data, then reopen the budget."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Setel Ulang ke Draf`: Untuk menimpa data, lalu buka kembali "
"anggaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Revise`: A new budget will be created. Once it "
"is :guilabel:`Open`, a :guilabel:`Rev` reference is added to "
"the :guilabel:`Budget Name`. The original budget is then :guilabel:`Revised`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Revisi`: Anggaran baru akan dibuat. Setelah :guilabel:`Terbuka`, "
"referensi :guilabel:`Rev` ditambahkan ke :guilabel:`Nama Anggaran`. Anggaran "
"asli kemudian :guilabel:`Direvisi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:56
msgid "Check an analytic budget"
msgstr "Periksa anggaran analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:58
msgid ""
"Once the budget is :guilabel:`Open`, two additional columns are "
"available: :guilabel:`Committed` and :guilabel:`Achieved`. These columns' "
"amounts are automatically calculated based on the related :ref:`analytic "
"distribution <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` of "
"journal items. When the :ref:`analytic distribution <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` of a journal item within the "
"budget's period is updated, the budget's columns for the analytic account(s) "
"selected in the distribution are automatically updated. "
"The :guilabel:`Achieved` amount reflects the current result according to the "
"items of confirmed journal entries for the associated :ref:`analytic account "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`. In contrast, "
"the :guilabel:`Committed` amount displays the full value of "
"the :guilabel:`Achieved` amount, plus any confirmed purchase orders that "
"have not yet been billed."
msgstr ""
"Setelah anggaran :guilabel:`Terbuka`, dua kolom tambahan "
"tersedia: :guilabel:`Berkomitmen` dan :guilabel:`Tercapai`. Jumlah kolom-"
"kolom ini dihitung secara otomatis berdasarkan :ref:`distribusi analitik "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` terkait dari item "
"jurnal. Ketika :ref:`distribusi analitik <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic-distribution>` dari item jurnal dalam periode anggaran diperbarui, "
"kolom anggaran untuk akun analitik yang dipilih dalam distribusi secara "
"otomatis diperbarui. Jumlah :guilabel:`Tercapai` mencerminkan hasil saat ini "
"sesuai dengan item dari entri jurnal yang dikonfirmasi untuk :ref:`akun "
"analitik <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` terkait. "
"Sebaliknya, jumlah :guilabel:`Berkomitmen` menampilkan nilai penuh dari "
"jumlah :guilabel:`Tercapai`, ditambah pesanan pembelian yang dikonfirmasi "
"yang belum ditagih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:70
msgid ""
"When a line in a request for quotation or purchase order includes an "
"analytic distribution, a :guilabel:`Budget` smart button appears, providing "
"a link to the :ref:`budget report <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-"
"reporting>` for more details."
msgstr ""
"Ketika baris dalam permintaan penawaran atau pesanan pembelian menyertakan "
"distribusi analitik, tombol pintar :guilabel:`Anggaran` muncul, memberikan "
"tautan ke :ref:`laporan anggaran <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-"
"reporting>` untuk detail lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:73
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Open` budgets, if a request for quotation or a purchase order "
"is created using the associated analytic distribution and exceeds the "
"allocated budget amount, the corresponding purchase order line is "
"highlighted in red."
msgstr ""
"Untuk anggaran :guilabel:`Terbuka`, jika permintaan penawaran atau pesanan "
"pembelian dibuat menggunakan distribusi analitik terkait dan melebihi jumlah "
"anggaran yang dialokasikan, baris pesanan pembelian yang sesuai disorot "
"dengan warna merah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:77
msgid ""
"To reveal the :guilabel:`Theoretical` amount or percentage, use "
"the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`adjust settings`) icon in "
"the :guilabel:`Budget Lines`' header. The :guilabel:`Theoretical` amount "
"represents the amount of money that could theoretically have been spent or "
"should have been received based on the current date relative to the start/"
"end dates. Click :guilabel:`Details` to open a filtered view of "
"the :ref:`budget report <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-reporting>` "
"related to that specific budget line."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan jumlah atau persentase :guilabel:`Teoritis`, gunakan "
"ikon :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`sesuaikan pengaturan`) di "
"header :guilabel:`Baris Anggaran`. Jumlah :guilabel:`Teoritis` mewakili "
"jumlah uang yang secara teoritis dapat dibelanjakan atau seharusnya diterima "
"berdasarkan tanggal saat ini relatif terhadap tanggal mulai/akhir. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Detail` untuk membuka tampilan terfilter dari :ref:`laporan "
"anggaran <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-reporting>` yang terkait dengan "
"baris anggaran spesifik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:None
msgid "open budget with committed, achieved, and theoretical amounts"
msgstr "anggaran terbuka dengan jumlah berkomitmen, tercapai, dan teoritis"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:88
msgid ""
"Deleting a budget is only allowed in the :guilabel:`Draft` "
"and :guilabel:`Cancelled` stages."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus anggaran hanya diperbolehkan pada tahap :guilabel:`Draf` "
"dan :guilabel:`Dibatalkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:90
msgid ""
"To view the budget lines of one or multiple budgets directly from "
"the :guilabel:`Budgets` list view, select the budget(s) and "
"click :guilabel:`Budget Lines`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat baris anggaran dari satu atau beberapa anggaran langsung dari "
"tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Anggaran`, pilih anggaran dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Baris Anggaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:96
msgid "Generate periodic budgets"
msgstr "Hasilkan anggaran periodik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:98
msgid ""
"To create periodic budgets (monthly, quarterly, and yearly) for the "
"selected :guilabel:`Analytic Plans`, click :guilabel:`Generate`. A new "
"budget is created for each :guilabel:`Period` between the start and end "
"dates:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat anggaran periodik (bulanan, kuartalan, dan tahunan) "
"untuk :guilabel:`Rencana Analitik` yang dipilih, klik :guilabel:`Hasilkan`. "
"Anggaran baru dibuat untuk setiap :guilabel:`Periode` antara tanggal mulai "
"dan akhir:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:102
msgid ""
"If a single analytic plan is selected, each budget includes a line for each "
"account in that analytic plan."
msgstr ""
"Jika satu rencana analitik dipilih, setiap anggaran mencakup baris untuk "
"setiap akun dalam rencana analitik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:104
msgid ""
"If multiple analytic plans are selected, each budget includes a line for "
"each account/analytic plan combination."
msgstr ""
"Jika beberapa rencana analitik dipilih, setiap anggaran mencakup baris untuk "
"setiap kombinasi akun/rencana analitik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:107
msgid "To generate periodic budgets, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk menghasilkan anggaran periodik, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:109
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Budgets` list view, click :guilabel:`Generate`."
msgstr "Dalam tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Anggaran`, klik :guilabel:`Hasilkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:110
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Generate Budget` window, set the dates and select "
"the :guilabel:`Period` and the :guilabel:`Analytic Plans`."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela :guilabel:`Hasilkan Anggaran`, atur tanggal dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Periode` serta :guilabel:`Rencana Analitik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:0
msgid "all the options to generate periodical budgets"
msgstr "semua opsi untuk menghasilkan anggaran periodik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:116
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Split` to create the periodic budgets."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Pisahkan` untuk membuat anggaran periodik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:117
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Budgets` in the top-left corner to return to "
"the :guilabel:`Budgets` list view."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Anggaran` di sudut kiri atas untuk kembali ke tampilan "
"daftar :guilabel:`Anggaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:118
msgid ""
"One by one, click on the different periodic budgets with "
"the :guilabel:`Draft` status to open them and set the amounts in "
"the :guilabel:`Budgeted` column for each analytic account linked to the "
"chosen analytic plans."
msgstr ""
"Satu per satu, klik pada anggaran periodik yang berbeda dengan "
"status :guilabel:`Draft` untuk membukanya dan mengatur jumlah di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Budgeted` untuk setiap akun analitik yang terhubung dengan "
"rencana analitik yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:121
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Open` for each periodic budget."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Open` untuk setiap anggaran periodik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:128
msgid ""
"To perform various reporting actions, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Budget Report`, then:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukan berbagai tindakan pelaporan, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi "
"--> Pelaporan --> Laporan Anggaran`, kemudian:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:131
msgid "Track, analyze, and compare budget data."
msgstr "Lacak, analisis, dan bandingkan data anggaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:132
msgid ""
"Filter and group data using the :icon:`fa-plus-square` (:guilabel:`plus-"
"square`) or :icon:`fa-minus-square` :guilabel:`(minus-square)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Filter dan kelompokkan data menggunakan ikon :icon:`fa-plus-square` "
"(:guilabel:`plus-square`) atau :icon:`fa-minus-square` :guilabel:`(minus-"
"square)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:134
msgid ""
"Drill down into the report to see more details on the actual amounts and "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Telusuri lebih detail laporan untuk melihat lebih banyak detail tentang "
"jumlah aktual dan transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:135
msgid "Export the data for further analysis or reporting needs."
msgstr "Ekspor data untuk analisis lebih lanjut atau kebutuhan pelaporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:140
msgid "Financial budgets"
msgstr "Budget keuangan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:142
msgid ""
"Financial budgets are structured around specific income and expense accounts "
"and transactions for official financial reporting and compliance purposes."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran keuangan disusun berdasarkan akun pendapatan dan beban tertentu "
"serta transaksi untuk tujuan pelaporan keuangan resmi dan kepatuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:146
msgid ""
"Financial budgets are available on the :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/"
"reporting/profit-and-loss>` report."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran keuangan tersedia di laporan :ref:`Laba Rugi <accounting/reporting/"
"profit-and-loss>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:152
msgid "Set a financial budget"
msgstr "Mengatur anggaran keuangan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:154
msgid "To create a new financial budget, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk membuat anggaran keuangan baru, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:156
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Profit and Loss` to open "
"the :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>` report."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Laba Rugi` untuk membuka "
"laporan :ref:`Laba Rugi <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:158
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` button to use the date "
"selector and choose a period."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` untuk menggunakan "
"pemilih tanggal dan pilih periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:160
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Budget` button and name the "
"budget. A new column labeled with the budget name will appear next to "
"the :guilabel:`Balance` column."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Budget` dan beri nama anggaran. "
"Kolom baru yang diberi label dengan nama anggaran akan muncul di sebelah "
"kolom :guilabel:`Balance`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:162
msgid "Assign amounts to each account requiring analysis."
msgstr "Tetapkan jumlah untuk setiap akun yang memerlukan analisis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:163
msgid ""
"A new :guilabel:`%` column will appear to the right of the new budget "
"column, indicating the current status."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`%` baru akan muncul di sebelah kanan kolom anggaran baru, "
"yang menunjukkan status saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:166
msgid ""
"Different financial budgets can be created using these steps for comparison "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran keuangan yang berbeda dapat dibuat menggunakan langkah-langkah ini "
"untuk tujuan perbandingan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:169
msgid ""
"The date selector enables the division of periods and navigation between "
"periods, automatically updating the amounts accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Pemilih tanggal memungkinkan pembagian periode dan navigasi antar periode, "
"secara otomatis memperbarui jumlah sesuai dengan itu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:3
msgid "Custom reports"
msgstr "Laporan kustom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo comes with a powerful and easy-to-use reporting framework. The engine "
"allows you to create new reports, such as **tax reports**, or **balance "
"sheets** and **income statements** with **specific groupings** and "
"**layouts**."
msgstr ""
"Odoo datang dengan framework pelaporan yang kuat dan gampang digunakan. "
"Engine Odoo memungkinkan Anda untuk membuat laporan baru, seperti **laporan "
"pajak**, atau **neraca keuangan** dan **laporan laba rugi** dengan "
"**pengelompokan spesifik** dan **layout**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:10
msgid ""
"Activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` to access the accounting "
"report creation interface."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan :ref:`mode developer <developer-mode>` untuk mengakses antarmuka "
"pembuatan laporan akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:13
msgid ""
"To create a new report, open the :guilabel:`Accounting` app and navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Accounting Reports`. From here, you can "
"either create a :ref:`root report <customize-reports/root>` or "
"a :ref:`variant <customize-reports/variants>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat laporan baru, buka aplikasi :guilabel:`Akuntansi` dan "
"buka :menuselection:`Konfigurasi --> Laporan Akuntansi`. Dari sini, Anda "
"dapat membuat :ref:`laporan root <customize-reports/root>` atau :ref:`varian "
"<customize-reports/variants>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:20
msgid "Root reports"
msgstr "Root reports"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:22
msgid ""
"Root reports can be regarded as generic, neutral accounting reports. They "
"serve as models on which local accounting versions are built. If a report "
"has no root report, it is considered to be a root report itself."
msgstr ""
"Root report dapat dianggap sebagai laporan akuntansi yang netral dan umum. "
"Mereka bertindak sebagai model pada mana versi akuntansi lokal akan "
"dibangun. Bila laporan tidak memiliki root report, maka akan dianggap "
"sebagai root report itu sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:27
msgid ""
"A tax report for Belgium and the US would both use the same generic version "
"as a base and adapt it for their domestic regulations."
msgstr ""
"Laporan pajak untuk Belgia dan AS akan masing-masing menggunakan versi umum "
"yang sama sebagai dasar dan mengadaptasikannya untuk regulasi domestik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:30
msgid ""
"When creating a new root report, you need to create a **menu item** for it. "
"To do so, open the report and, on that same report, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon, then select :guilabel:`Create Menu Item`. "
"Refresh the page; the report is now available "
"under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting`."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat laporan root baru, Anda perlu membuat **item menu** untuknya. "
"Untuk melakukannya, buka laporan dan, pada laporan yang sama, klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Tindakan)`, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Buat Item "
"Menu`. Segarkan halaman; laporan sekarang tersedia di "
"bawah :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:36
msgid ""
"Cases that require creating a new root report are rare, such as when a "
"country's tax authorities require a new and specific type of report."
msgstr ""
"Kasus yang memerlukan pembuatan root report baru itu langka, seperti pada "
"kasus di mana otoritas pajak negara memerlukan tipe laporan yang baru dan "
"khusus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:42
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:142
msgid "Variants"
msgstr "Varian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:44
msgid ""
"Variants are country-specific versions of root reports and, therefore, "
"always refer to a root report. To create a variant, select a generic (root) "
"report in the :guilabel:`Root Report` field when creating a new report."
msgstr ""
"Variant adalah versi khusus negara dari root report dan, oleh karena itu, "
"selalu merujuk ke root report. Untuk membuat variant, pilih root report umum "
"di field :guilabel:`Root Report` saat membuat laporan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:48
msgid ""
"When a root report is opened from one of the accounting app's main menus, "
"all its variants are displayed in the variant selector in the top right "
"corner of the view."
msgstr ""
"Saat root report dibuka dari satu menu utama app akuntansi, semua varian-nya "
"ditampilkan di pemilih variant di pojok kanan atas tampilan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:52
msgid ""
"In the following image, :guilabel:`VAT Report (BE)` is the variant of the "
"root :guilabel:`Generic Tax report`."
msgstr ""
"Di gambar berikut, :guilabel:`Laporan PPN (BE)` adalah varian dari root "
"report :guilabel:`Laporan Pajak Umum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:58
msgid "Report lines"
msgstr "Baris laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:60
msgid ""
"After having created a report (either root or variant), you need to fill it "
"with report lines. You can either create a new one by clicking "
"on :guilabel:`Add a line`, or modify an existing report line by clicking on "
"it. All report lines *require* a :guilabel:`Name`, and can have an optional "
"additional :guilabel:`Code` (of your choice) if you wish to use their value "
"in formulas."
msgstr ""
"Setelah membuat laporan (baik root atau varian), Anda perlu mengisinya "
"dengan baris laporan. Anda dapat membuat yang baru dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris`, atau mengubah baris laporan yang ada "
"dengan mengkliknya. Semua baris laporan *memerlukan* :guilabel:`Nama`, dan "
"dapat memiliki :guilabel:`Kode` tambahan opsional (pilihan Anda) jika Anda "
"ingin menggunakan nilainya dalam formula."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:None
msgid "Engine lines options."
msgstr "Opsi baris engine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:71
msgid "Expressions"
msgstr "Expression"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:73
msgid ""
"Each report line can contain one or multiple **expressions**. Expressions "
"can be seen as **sub-variables** needed by a report line. To create an "
"expression, click on :guilabel:`Add a line` *within* a report line."
msgstr ""
"Setiap baris laporan dapat berisi satu atau beberapa **ekspresi**. Ekspresi "
"dapat dilihat sebagai **sub-variabel** yang diperlukan oleh baris laporan. "
"Untuk membuat ekspresi, klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` *di dalam* baris "
"laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:77
msgid ""
"When creating an expression, you must attribute a :guilabel:`Label` used to "
"refer to that expression. Therefore, it has to be **unique** among the "
"expressions of each line. Both a :guilabel:`Computation Engine` and "
"a :guilabel:`Formula` must also be indicated. The **engine** defines how "
"your **formula(s)** and **subformula(s)** are interpreted. It is possible to "
"mix expressions using different computation engines under the same line if "
"you need to."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat ekspresi, Anda harus memberikan :guilabel:`Label` yang "
"digunakan untuk merujuk ekspresi tersebut. Oleh karena itu, harus **unik** "
"di antara ekspresi setiap baris. :guilabel:`Mesin Komputasi` "
"dan :guilabel:`Formula` juga harus ditunjukkan. **Mesin** menentukan "
"bagaimana **formula** dan **subformula** Anda diinterpretasikan. "
"Dimungkinkan untuk menggabungkan ekspresi menggunakan mesin komputasi yang "
"berbeda di bawah baris yang sama jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:84
msgid "Depending on the engine, :guilabel:`subformulas` may also be required."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada enginenya, :guilabel:`subformula` juga mungkin diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:89
msgid "'Odoo Domain' engine"
msgstr "Engine 'Odoo Domain'"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:91
msgid ""
"With this engine, a formula is interpreted as an :ref:`Odoo domain "
"<reference/orm/domains>` targeting `account.move.line` objects."
msgstr ""
"Dengan engine ini, formula yang diinterpretasikan sebagai :ref:`Odoo domain "
"<reference/orm/domains>` menarget `account.move.line` objects."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:94
msgid ""
"The subformula allows you to define how the move lines matching the domain "
"are used to compute the value of the expression:"
msgstr ""
"Subformula ini memungkinkan Anda untuk mendefinisikan bagaimana baris "
"pergerakkan yang cocok dengan domain digunakan untuk menghitung nilai dari "
"expression:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:98
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:270
msgid "`sum`"
msgstr "`sum`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:98
msgid "The result is the sum of all the balances of the matched move lines."
msgstr ""
"Hasilnya adalah jumlah dari semua saldo dari baris pergerakkan yang cocok."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:102
msgid "`sum_if_pos`"
msgstr "`sum_if_pos`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:101
msgid ""
"The result is the sum of all the balances of the matched move lines if this "
"amount is positive. Otherwise, it is `0`."
msgstr ""
"Hasilnya adalah jumlah dari semua saldo dari baris pergerakkan yang cocok "
"bila jumlahnya positif. Bila tidak, adalah `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:106
msgid "`sum_if_neg`"
msgstr "`sum_if_neg`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:105
msgid ""
"The result is the sum of all the balances of the matched move lines if this "
"amount is negative. Otherwise, it is `0`."
msgstr ""
"Hasilnya adalah jumlah dari semua saldo dari baris pergerakkan yang cocok "
"bila jumlahnya negatif. Bila tidak, adalah `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:111
msgid "`count_rows`"
msgstr "`count_rows`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:109
msgid ""
"The result is the number of sub-lines of this expression. If the report line "
"has a group-by value, this will correspond to the number of distinct "
"grouping keys in the matched move lines. Otherwise, it will be the number of "
"matched move lines."
msgstr ""
"Hasilnya adalah jumlah sub-baris dari ekspresi ini. Jika baris laporan "
"memiliki nilai group-by, ini akan sesuai dengan jumlah kunci pengelompokan "
"yang berbeda dalam baris jurnal yang cocok. Jika tidak, ini akan menjadi "
"jumlah baris jurnal yang cocok."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:113
msgid ""
"You can also put a `-` sign at the beginning of the subformula to "
"**reverse** the sign of the result."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menaruh tanda `-` di awal subformula untuk **memutarbalik** "
"tanda dari hasil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:None
msgid "Expression line within a line report"
msgstr "Baris expression dalam laporan baris"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:122
msgid "'Tax Tags' engine"
msgstr "Engine 'Tag Pajak'"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:124
msgid ""
"A formula made for this engine consists of a name used to match tax tags. If "
"such tags do not exist when creating the expression, they will be created."
msgstr ""
"Formula yang dibuat untuk engine ini terdiri dari nama yang digunakan untuk "
"mencocokkan tag pajak. Bila tag tersebut tidak ada saat membuat expression, "
"mereka akan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:127
msgid ""
"When evaluating the expression, the expression computation can roughly be "
"expressed as: **(amount of the move lines with** `+` **tag)** `-` **(amount "
"of the move lines with** `-` **tag)**."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengevaluasi expression, perhitungan expression dapat secara kasar "
"diekspresikan sebagai: **(jumlah baris pergerakkan dengan tag** `+` **)** `-"
"` **(jumlah baris pergerakkan dengan tag** `-` **)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:131
msgid ""
"If the formula is `tag_name`, the engine matches tax tags `+tag_name` and `-"
"tag_name`, creating them if necessary. To exemplify further: two tags are "
"matched by the formula. If the formula is `A`, it will require (and create, "
"if needed) tags `+A` and `-A`."
msgstr ""
"Bila formula adalah `tag_name`, engine mencocokkan tag pajak `+tag_name` dan "
"`-tag_name`, bila diperlukan membuat tag tersebut. Contoh lebih lanjut: dua "
"tag dicocokkan formula. Bila formula adalah `A`, formula akan memerlukan "
"(dan membuat, bila diperlukan) tag `+A` dan `-A`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:138
msgid "'Aggregate Other Formulas' engine"
msgstr "Engine 'Aggregat Formula Lain'"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:140
msgid ""
"Use this engine when you need to perform arithmetic operations on the "
"amounts obtained for other expressions. Formulas here are composed of "
"references to expressions separated by one of the four basic arithmetic "
"operators (addition `+`, subtraction `-`, division `/`, and multiplication "
"`*`). To refer to an expression, type in its report line's **code** followed "
"by a period `.` and the expression's **label** (ex. **code.label**)."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan mesin ini ketika Anda perlu melakukan operasi aritmatika pada jumlah "
"yang diperoleh untuk ekspresi lain. Formula di sini terdiri dari referensi "
"ke ekspresi yang dipisahkan oleh salah satu dari empat operator aritmatika "
"dasar (penjumlahan `+`, pengurangan `-`, pembagian `/`, dan perkalian `*`). "
"Untuk merujuk ke ekspresi, ketik **kode** baris laporannya diikuti dengan "
"titik `.` dan **label** ekspresinya (mis. **code.label**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:146
msgid "**Subformulas** can be one of the following:"
msgstr "**Subformula** dapat merupakan salah satu dari yang berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:150
msgid "`if_above(CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_above(CUR(amount))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:149
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if it is "
"greater than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Nilai dari ekspresi aritmetika akan dikembalikkan hanya bila lebih besar "
"dari nilai yang disediakan sebelumnya. Bila tidak, hasilnya akan menjadi `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:154
msgid "`if_below(CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_below(CUR(amount))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:153
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if it is lower "
"than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Nilai dari ekspresi aritmetika akan dikembalikkan hanya bila lebih kecil "
"dari nilai yang disediakan sebelumnya. Bila tidak, hasilnya akan menjadi `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:158
msgid "`if_between(CUR1(amount1), CUR2(amount2))`"
msgstr "`if_between(CUR1(amount1), CUR2(amount2))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:157
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if it is "
"strictly between the provided bounds. Otherwise, it will be brought back to "
"the closest bound."
msgstr ""
"Nilai dari ekspresi aritmetika akan dikembalikkan hanya bila di antara nilai "
"yang disediakan sebelumnya. Bila tidak, hasilnya akan menjadi `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:163
msgid "`if_other_expr_above(LINE_CODE.EXPRESSION_LABEL, CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_other_expr_above(LINE_CODE.EXPRESSION_LABEL, CUR(amount))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:161
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if the value of "
"the expression denoted by the provided line code and expression label is "
"greater than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Nilai dari ekspresi aritmetika akan dikembalikkan hanya bila nilai ekspresi "
"yang ditunjukkan oleh baris kode dan label expression lebih besar dari nilai "
"yang disediakan sebelumnya. Bila tidak, hasilnya akan menjadi `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:168
msgid "`if_other_expr_below(LINE_CODE.EXPRESSION_LABEL, CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_other_expr_below(LINE_CODE.EXPRESSION_LABEL, CUR(amount))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:166
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if the value of "
"the expression denoted by the provided line code and expression label is "
"lower than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Nilai dari ekspresi aritmetika akan dikembalikkan hanya bila nilai ekspresi "
"yang ditunjukkan oleh baris kode dan label expression lebih kecil dari nilai "
"yang disediakan sebelumnya. Bila tidak, hasilnya akan menjadi `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:170
msgid ""
"`CUR` is the currency code in capital letters, and `amount` is the amount of "
"the bound expressed in that currency."
msgstr ""
"`CUR` adalah kode mata uang yang huruf besar, dan `jumlah` adalah jumlah "
"nilai yang diekspresikan dalam mata uang tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:173
msgid ""
"You can also use the `cross_report` subformula to match an expression found "
"in another report."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menggunakan subformula `cross_report` untuk mencocokkan "
"expression yang ditemukan di laporan lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:178
msgid "'Prefix of Account Codes' engine"
msgstr "Engine 'Awalan Kode Akun'"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:180
msgid ""
"This engine is used to match amounts made on accounts using the prefixes of "
"these accounts' codes as variables in an arithmetic expression."
msgstr ""
"Engine ini digunakan untuk mencocokkan jumlah yang dibuat pada akun "
"menggunakan awalan dari kode akun-akun tersebut sebagai variabel di ekspresi "
"aritmetika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21`"
msgstr "`21`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "Arithmetic expressions can also be a single prefix, such as here."
msgstr "Ekspresi aritmetika juga dapat merupakan satu awalan, seperti di sini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21 + 10 - 5`"
msgstr "`21 + 10 - 5`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula adds the balances of the move lines made on accounts whose "
"codes start with `21` and `10`, and subtracts the balance of the ones on "
"accounts with the prefix `5`."
msgstr ""
"Formula ini menambahkan saldo dari baris-baris pergerakkan yang dibuat pada "
"akun yang kodenya dimulai dengan `21` dan `10`, dan mengurangi saldo dari "
"mereka yang akunnya dimulai dengan `5`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:192
msgid "It is also possible to ignore a selection of sub-prefixes."
msgstr "Anda juga dapat mengabaikan pilihan sub-awalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21 + 10\\\\(101, 102) - 5\\\\(57)`"
msgstr "`21 + 10\\\\(101, 102) - 5\\\\(57)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula works the same way as the previous example but ignores the "
"prefixes `101`, `102`, and `57`."
msgstr ""
"Formula ini juga bekerja dengan cara yang sama seperti contoh sebelumnya "
"tapi mengabaikan awalan `101`, `102`, dan `57`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:199
msgid ""
"You can apply 'sub-filtering' on **credits and debits** using the `C` and "
"`D` suffixes. In this case, an account will only be considered if its prefix "
"matches, *and* if the total balance of the move lines made on this account "
"is **credit/debit**."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menerapkan 'sub-filter` pada **kredit dan debit** menggunakan "
"akhiran `C` dan `D`. Pada kasus ini, akun hanya akan dianggap bila awalannya "
"cocok, *dan* bila total saldo baris pergerakkan yang dibuat pada akun adalah "
"**kredit/debit**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:204
msgid ""
"Account `210001` has a balance of -42 and account `210002` has a balance of "
"25. The formula `21D` only matches the account `210002`, and hence returns "
"25. `210001` is not matched, as its balance is *credit*."
msgstr ""
"Akun `210001` memiliki saldo -42 dan akun `210002` memiliki saldo 25. "
"Formula `21D` hanya cocok dengan akun `210002`, sehingga mengembalikkan 25. "
"`210001` tidak cocok, karena saldonya adalah *credit*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:208
msgid "Prefix exclusions can be mixed with the `C` and `D` suffixes."
msgstr "Pengecualian awalan dapat digabungkan dengan akhiran `C` dan `D`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21D + 10\\\\(101, 102)C - 5\\\\(57)`"
msgstr "`21D + 10\\\\(101, 102)C - 5\\\\(57)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula adds the balances of the move lines made on accounts whose code "
"starts with `21` *if* it is debit (`D`) and `10` *if* it is credit (`C`), "
"but ignores prefixes `101`, `102`, and subtracts the balance of the ones on "
"accounts with the prefix `5`, ignoring the prefix `57`."
msgstr ""
"Formula ini menambahkan saldo dari baris-baris pergerakkan yang dibuat pada "
"akun yang kodenya dimulai dengan `21` *bila* debit (`D`) dan menambahkan "
"`10` *bila* kredit (`C`), tapi mengabaikan awalan `101`, `102`, dan "
"mengurangi saldo dari akun dengan awalan `5`, tapi mengabaikan awalan `57`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:216
msgid ""
"To match the letter `C` or `D` in a prefix and not use it as a suffix, use "
"an empty exclusion `()`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencocokkan huruf `C` atau `D` di awalan dan tidak menggunakannya "
"sebagai akhiran, gunakan pengecualian kosong ()`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21D\\\\()`"
msgstr "`21D\\\\()`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts whose code starts with `21D`, regardless of "
"their balance sign."
msgstr ""
"Formula ini mencocokkan akun yang kodenya dimulai dengan `21D`, terlepas "
"dari tanda saldo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:222
msgid ""
"In addition to using code prefixes to include accounts, you can also match "
"them with **account tags**. This is especially useful, for example, if your "
"country lacks a standardized chart of accounts, where the same prefix might "
"be used for different purposes across companies."
msgstr ""
"Di atas menggunakan awalan kode untuk mengikutsertakan akun, Anda juga dapat "
"mencocokkan mereka dengan **tag akun**. Ini berguna terutama, sebagai "
"contoh, bila negara Anda tidak memiliki standarisasi bagan akun, di mana "
"awalan yang sama mungkin digunakan untuk tujuan yang berbeda di perusahaan. "

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(25)`"
msgstr "`tag(25)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts whose associated tags contain the one with id "
"*25*."
msgstr "Formula ini mencocokkan akun yang tag terkait memiliki id *25*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:230
msgid ""
"If the tag you reference is defined in a data file, an xmlid can be used "
"instead of the id."
msgstr ""
"Bila tag yang Anda referensikan didefinisikan di file data, xmlid dapat "
"digunakan alih-alih id."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag)`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts whose associated tags include the tag denoted "
"by *my_module.my_tag*."
msgstr ""
"Formula ini mencocokkan akun yang tag terkaitnya mencakup tag yang ditandai "
"dengan *my_module.my_tag*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:237
msgid ""
"You can also use arithmetic expressions with tags, possibly combining them "
"with prefix selections."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menggunakan ekspresi aritmatika dengan tag, mungkin "
"menggabungkannya dengan pemilihan awalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag) + tag(42) + 10`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag) + tag(42) + 10`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"The balances of accounts tagged as *my_module.my_tag* will be summed with "
"those of accounts linked to the tag with ID *42* and accounts with the code "
"prefix `10`"
msgstr ""
"Saldo akun yang ditandai sebagai *my_module.my_tag* akan dijumlahkan dengan "
"akun yang terhubung ke tag dengan ID *42* dan akun dengan awalan kode `10`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:244
msgid "`C` and `D` suffixes can be used in the same way with tags."
msgstr "Akhiran `C` dan `D` dapat digunakan dengan cara yang sama dengan tag."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag)C`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag)C`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts with the tag *my_module.my_tag* and a credit "
"balance."
msgstr ""
"Formula ini mencocokkan akun dengan tag *my_module.my_tag* dan saldo kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:250
msgid "Prefix exclusion also works with tags."
msgstr "Pengecualian awalan juga berfungsi dengan tag."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag)\\\\(10)`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag)\\\\(10)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts with the tag *my_module.my_tag* and a code not "
"starting with `10`."
msgstr ""
"Formula ini mencocokkan akun dengan tag *my_module.my_tag* dan kode yang "
"tidak dimulai dengan `10`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:260
msgid "'External Value' engine"
msgstr "Mesin 'External Value'"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:262
msgid ""
"The 'external value' engine is used to refer to **manual** and **carryover "
"values**. Those values are not stored using `account.move.line`, but with "
"`account.report.external.value`. Each of these objects directly points to "
"the expression it impacts, so very little needs to be done about their "
"selection here."
msgstr ""
"Mesin 'nilai eksternal' digunakan untuk merujuk pada **nilai manual** dan "
"**nilai bawa alih**. Nilai-nilai tersebut tidak disimpan menggunakan "
"`account.move.line`, tetapi dengan `account.report.external.value`. Setiap "
"objek ini langsung menunjuk ke ekspresi yang terpengaruh, sehingga hanya "
"sedikit yang perlu dilakukan terkait pemilihan mereka di sini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:267
msgid "**Formulas** can be one of the following:"
msgstr "**Formula** dapat berupa salah satu dari berikut ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:270
msgid "If the result must be the sum of all the external values in the period."
msgstr ""
"Jika hasilnya harus berupa jumlah dari semua nilai eksternal dalam periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:273
msgid "`most_recent`"
msgstr "`most_recent`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:273
msgid ""
"If the result must be the value of the latest external value in the period."
msgstr ""
"Jika hasilnya harus berupa nilai dari nilai eksternal terbaru dalam periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:275
msgid "In addition, **subformulas** can be used in two ways:"
msgstr "Selain itu, **subformula** dapat digunakan dengan dua cara:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:278
msgid "`rounding=X`"
msgstr "`rounding=X`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:278
msgid ""
"Replacing `X` with a number instructs to round the amount to X decimals."
msgstr "Mengganti `X` dengan angka akan membulatkan jumlah ke X desimal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:282
msgid "`editable`"
msgstr "`editable`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:281
msgid ""
"Indicates this expression can be edited manually, triggering the display of "
"an icon in the report, allowing the user to perform this action."
msgstr ""
"Menunjukkan bahwa ekspresi ini dapat diedit secara manual, memicu tampilan "
"ikon dalam laporan, yang memungkinkan user untuk melakukan tindakan ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:285
msgid ""
"Manual values are created at the `date_to` currently selected in the report."
msgstr ""
"Nilai manual dibuat pada `date_to` yang saat ini dipilih dalam laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:287
msgid "Both subformulas can be mixed by separating them with a `;`."
msgstr ""
"Kedua subformula dapat digabungkan dengan memisahkannya menggunakan `;`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`editable;rounding=2`"
msgstr "`editable;rounding=2`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "is a correct subformula mixing both behaviors."
msgstr "adalah subformula yang benar yang menggabungkan kedua perilaku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:296
msgid "'Custom Python Function' engine"
msgstr "Mesin 'Fungsi Python Kustom'"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:298
msgid ""
"This engine is a means for developers to introduce custom computation of "
"expressions on a case-by-case basis. The formula is the name of a **python "
"function** to call, and the subformula is a **key** to fetch in the "
"**dictionary** returned by this function. Use it only if you are making a "
"custom module of your own."
msgstr ""
"Mesin ini adalah sarana bagi pengembang untuk memperkenalkan komputasi "
"kustom dari ekspresi berdasarkan kasus per kasus. Formula adalah nama "
"**fungsi python** yang akan dipanggil, dan subformula adalah **kunci** untuk "
"diambil dalam **dictionary** yang dikembalikan oleh fungsi ini. Gunakan ini "
"hanya jika Anda membuat modul kustom sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:306
msgid "Columns"
msgstr "Kolom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:308
msgid ""
"Reports can have an **indefinite number** of columns to display. Each column "
"gets its values from the **expressions** declared on the **lines**. The "
"field :guilabel:`expression_label` of the column gives the label of the "
"expressions whose value is displayed. If a line has no **expression** in "
"that field, then nothing is displayed for it in this column. If multiple "
"columns are required, you must use different **expression** labels."
msgstr ""
"Laporan dapat memiliki **jumlah tidak terbatas** kolom untuk ditampilkan. "
"Setiap kolom mendapatkan nilainya dari **ekspresi** yang dideklarasikan pada "
"**baris**. Field :guilabel:`expression_label` dari kolom memberikan label "
"ekspresi yang nilainya ditampilkan. Jika sebuah baris tidak memiliki "
"**ekspresi** dalam field tersebut, maka tidak ada yang ditampilkan untuk "
"baris itu di kolom ini. Jika beberapa kolom diperlukan, Anda harus "
"menggunakan label **ekspresi** yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:None
msgid "Columns of report."
msgstr "Kolom laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:317
msgid ""
"When using the **period comparison** feature found under "
"the :guilabel:`Options` tab of an accounting report, all columns are "
"repeated in and for each period."
msgstr ""
"Ketika menggunakan fitur **perbandingan periode** yang ditemukan di bawah "
"tab :guilabel:`Options` dari laporan akuntansi, semua kolom diulang dalam "
"dan untuk setiap periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:323
msgid "Line grouping"
msgstr "Pengelompokan baris"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:325
msgid ""
"Non-standard grouping is possible by adding or using existing fields on the "
"*Journal Item* model, provided that the fields are related and non-stored."
msgstr ""
"Pengelompokan non-standar dimungkinkan dengan menambahkan atau menggunakan "
"field yang ada pada model *Journal Item*, asalkan field tersebut terkait dan "
"non-stored."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:329
msgid ""
"Grouping lines requires the report to have explicit report lines that can be "
"edited. The deferred reports, for example, do not support grouping lines as "
"they use dynamic lines that are generated."
msgstr ""
"Pengelompokan baris memerlukan laporan untuk memiliki baris laporan "
"eksplisit yang dapat diedit. Laporan yang ditangguhkan, misalnya, tidak "
"mendukung pengelompokan baris karena mereka menggunakan baris dinamis yang "
"dihasilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:333
