#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:354
msgid "Group lines"
msgstr "Kelompokkan baris"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:356
msgid ""
"To group lines, go to the :ref:`Lines <customize-reports/lines>` tab of the "
"desired report, click on the line you want to group, and edit "
"the :guilabel:`Group by` field. Enter the technical name (:guilabel:`Field "
"Name`) of the field to use as the grouping key."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelompokkan baris, buka tab :ref:`Baris <customize-reports/lines>` "
"dari laporan yang diinginkan, klik baris yang ingin Anda kelompokkan, dan "
"edit bidang :guilabel:`Kelompokkan berdasarkan`. Masukkan nama teknis "
"(:guilabel:`Nama Bidang`) dari bidang yang akan digunakan sebagai kunci "
"pengelompokan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:361
msgid ""
"To find a list of all the model's fields and their technical names, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Journal Items`, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"bug` :guilabel:`(bug)` icon, then click :guilabel:`Fields`. The technical "
"name of each field is listed in the :guilabel:`Field Name` column."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menemukan daftar semua bidang model dan nama teknisnya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Item Jurnal`, lalu klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"bug` :guilabel:`(bug)`, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Bidang`. Nama teknis dari "
"setiap bidang tercantum dalam kolom :guilabel:`Nama Bidang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:367
msgid ""
":ref:`Consolidation via grouping by account code "
"<consolidation_account_mapping>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Konsolidasi melalui pengelompokan berdasarkan kode akun "
"<consolidation_account_mapping>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:372
msgid "Custom tax report setup"
msgstr "Pengaturan laporan pajak kustom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:375
msgid "Report configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:378
msgid ""
"All technical terms and functions of Odoo's reports engine are explained in "
"the previous sections of this page. We strongly recommend reading these "
"sections before setting up a custom tax report."
msgstr ""
"Semua istilah teknis dan fungsi dari mesin laporan Odoo dijelaskan di bagian "
"sebelumnya dari halaman ini. Kami sangat merekomendasikan untuk membaca "
"bagian-bagian ini sebelum menyiapkan laporan pajak kustom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:381
msgid ""
"To create a custom **tax report**, open the :guilabel:`Accounting` app, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Accounting Reports`, then "
"click :guilabel:`New`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat **laporan pajak** kustom, buka aplikasi :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, "
"navigasi ke :menuselection:`Konfigurasi --> Laporan Akuntansi`, kemudian "
"klik :guilabel:`Baru`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:384
msgid "Enter a **name** for your report."
msgstr "Masukkan **nama** untuk laporan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:385
msgid "Select a :ref:`Root Report <customize-reports/root>`."
msgstr "Pilih :ref:`Laporan Dasar <customize-reports/root>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:386
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Availability` field, select :guilabel:`Country "
"Matches`, then select the :guilabel:`Country` matching your company."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah bidang :guilabel:`Ketersediaan`, pilih :guilabel:`Negara Cocok`, "
"kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Negara` yang sesuai dengan perusahaan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:389
msgid ""
"Next, create a report line by clicking the :guilabel:`Add a line`. Once "
"created, click that report line to configure it:"
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, buat baris laporan dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris`. "
"Setelah dibuat, klik baris laporan tersebut untuk mengonfigurasinya:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:392
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` again to create an :ref:`Expression <customize-"
"reports/expressions>` and name it."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` lagi untuk membuat :ref:`Ekspresi "
"<customize-reports/expressions>` dan beri nama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:394
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Definition` tab, select a :guilabel:`Computation Engine` "
"for that expression depending on the following scenarios:"
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Definisi`, pilih :guilabel:`Mesin Komputasi` untuk "
"ekspresi tersebut tergantung pada skenario berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:399
msgid "Scenario A (Tax grids)"
msgstr "Skenario A (Grid pajak)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:401
msgid "In this scenario, your company *uses* tax grids:"
msgstr "Dalam skenario ini, perusahaan Anda *menggunakan* grid pajak:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:403
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Tax Tags` as the computation engine. Odoo uses this field "
"to link the report line to your taxes."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Tag Pajak` sebagai mesin komputasi. Odoo menggunakan bidang "
"ini untuk menghubungkan baris laporan ke pajak Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:405
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Formula` field, type your short grid identifier (e.g., "
"`vat_sales_base`). Odoo automatically generates the `+` and `-` variants of "
"this tag for you to map inside :menuselection:`Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Formula`, ketik pengidentifikasi grid pendek Anda "
"(misalnya, `vat_sales_base`). Odoo secara otomatis menghasilkan varian `+` "
"dan `-` dari tag ini untuk Anda petakan di dalam :menuselection:`Konfigurasi "
"--> Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:408
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Subformula` field, enter either `base` to report the "
"untaxed amount, or `tax` to report the actual tax amount collected/paid."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Subformula`, masukkan `base` untuk melaporkan jumlah "
"sebelum pajak, atau `tax` untuk melaporkan jumlah pajak aktual yang "
"dikumpulkan/dibayar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:411
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:421
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:435
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:445
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:476
msgid "Repeat this process as necessary. Then, :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Ulangi proses ini sesuai kebutuhan. Kemudian, :guilabel:`Save & Close`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:413
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:437
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:458
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:468
msgid "Alternatively, you can:"
msgstr "Atau, Anda dapat:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:415
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Aggregate Other Formulas` as the computation engine. Odoo "
"uses this field to perform math on lines *already present* in the report "
"rather than scanning raw transactions."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Aggregate Other Formulas` sebagai mesin komputasi. Odoo "
"menggunakan bidang ini untuk melakukan perhitungan matematis pada baris yang "
"*sudah ada* di laporan, bukan memindai transaksi mentah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:418
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:442
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Formula` field, use basic algebra referencing your line "
"codes (e.g., `LINE_10 - LINE_20`)."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Formula`, gunakan aljabar dasar yang merujuk ke kode "
"baris Anda (misalnya, `LINE_10 - LINE_20`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:423
msgid "Scenario B (No tax grids)"
msgstr "Skenario B (Tanpa kisi pajak)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:425
msgid ""
"In this scenario, your company *does not* use tax grids. Instead, it tracks "
"everything strictly via General Ledger accounts:"
msgstr ""
"Dalam skenario ini, perusahaan Anda *tidak* menggunakan kisi pajak. "
"Sebaliknya, perusahaan melacak semuanya secara ketat melalui akun Buku Besar:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:428
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Prefix of Account Codes` as the computation engine: Odoo "
"uses this for lines that need to pull financial totals. Instead of looking "
"for transaction tags, Odoo pulls live balances directly from your chart of "
"accounts."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Prefix of Account Codes` sebagai mesin komputasi: Odoo "
"menggunakan ini untuk baris yang perlu menarik total keuangan. Alih-alih "
"mencari tag transaksi, Odoo menarik saldo langsung dari bagan akun Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:431
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Formula` field, type the starting digits of the accounts "
"you want to track, (e.g., `40` will pull the combined total of all revenue "
"accounts starting with `400000`, `401000`, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Formula`, ketik digit awal dari akun yang ingin Anda "
"lacak, (misalnya, `40` akan menarik total gabungan dari semua akun "
"pendapatan yang dimulai dengan `400000`, `401000`, dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:439
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Aggregate Other Formulas` as the computation engine. Odoo "
"uses this to calculate subtotals, net tax, or grand totals by adding or "
"subtracting your other report lines."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Aggregate Other Formulas` sebagai mesin komputasi. Odoo "
"menggunakan ini untuk menghitung subtotal, pajak bersih, atau total "
"keseluruhan dengan menambahkan atau mengurangkan baris laporan Anda yang "
"lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:447
msgid "Scenario C (Advanced Engines)"
msgstr "Skenario C (Mesin Lanjutan)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:449
msgid ""
"In this scenario, your company requires advanced filtering, manual user "
"overrides, or complex algorithmic logic that standard tags and account "
"prefixes cannot handle:"
msgstr ""
"Dalam skenario ini, perusahaan Anda memerlukan pemfilteran lanjutan, "
"penggantian manual oleh user, atau logika algoritmik kompleks yang tidak "
"dapat ditangani oleh tag standar dan awalan akun:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:452
msgid ""
"Select :ref:`Odoo Domain <customize-reports/domain-engine>` as the "
"computation engine: Odoo uses this to bypass tax tags entirely and filter "
"raw journal items (`account.move.line`) using standard Odoo search syntax."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :ref:`Odoo Domain <customize-reports/domain-engine>` sebagai mesin "
"komputasi: Odoo menggunakan ini untuk melewati tag pajak sepenuhnya dan "
"memfilter item jurnal mentah (`account.move.line`) menggunakan sintaks "
"pencarian Odoo standar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:455
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Formula` field, enter a valid domain starting with "
"brackets to isolate tax-exempt transactions for specific partner categories."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Formula`, masukkan domain yang valid yang dimulai "
"dengan tanda kurung untuk mengisolasi transaksi bebas pajak untuk kategori "
"partner tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:460
msgid ""
"Select :ref:`External Value <customize-reports/external-engine>` as the "
"computation engine. Odoo uses this to log manual overrides or historical "
"carryover values."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :ref:`External Value <customize-reports/external-engine>` sebagai "
"mesin komputasi. Odoo menggunakan ini untuk mencatat penggantian manual atau "
"nilai carryover historis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:462
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Formula` field, type either `sum` (to add all manual "
"values together over multi-period reports) or `most_recent` (to display only "
"the latest value)."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Formula`, ketik `sum` (untuk menjumlahkan semua nilai "
"manual dalam laporan multi-periode) atau `most_recent` (untuk menampilkan "
"hanya nilai terbaru)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:464
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Subformula` field, type `editable` to display an edit icon "
"on the live report, allowing users to modify the value manually. "
"Additionally, you can round numbers by typing `rounding=x`."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Subformula`, ketik `editable` untuk menampilkan ikon "
"edit pada laporan langsung, memungkinkan user untuk mengubah nilai secara "
"manual. Selain itu, Anda dapat membulatkan angka dengan mengetik "
"`rounding=x`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:470
msgid ""
"Select :ref:`Custom Python Function <customize-reports/python-engine>` as "
"the computation engine. Odoo uses this as an execution engine to run "
"specific calculations through backend coding when rules involve progressive "
"brackets, loops, or multi-tier thresholds."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :ref:`Custom Python Function <customize-reports/python-engine>` "
"sebagai mesin komputasi. Odoo menggunakan ini sebagai mesin eksekusi untuk "
"menjalankan perhitungan spesifik melalui coding backend ketika aturan "
"melibatkan bracket progresif, loop, atau ambang batas multi-tingkat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:473
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Formula` field, enter the exact technical name of the "
"Python method defined in your custom localization module."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Formula`, masukkan nama teknis yang tepat dari metode "
"Python yang didefinisikan dalam modul lokalisasi kustom Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:478
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Options` tab of an **Expression**, populate "
"the :guilabel:`Carry Over To` field with a formula to always carry over "
"balances or only carry them over when the amount is negative. Leave this "
"field blank if you do not want to use this feature."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Options` dari sebuah **Expression**, isi "
"bidang :guilabel:`Carry Over To` dengan formula untuk selalu membawa saldo "
"atau hanya membawanya saat jumlahnya negatif. Biarkan bidang ini kosong jika "
"Anda tidak ingin menggunakan fitur ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`if_below(EUR(0))`"
msgstr "`if_below(EUR(0))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "This formula will only carry over amounts below 0.00 EUR."
msgstr "Formula ini hanya akan membawa jumlah di bawah 0,00 EUR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:487
msgid "Tax configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:489
msgid ""
"Next, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Taxes` and "
"click :guilabel:`New` to create and :ref:`configure new taxes <taxes/"
"configuration>` for your custom tax report. Create your **Sales** and "
"**Purchases** taxes, and populate the :guilabel:`Tax Grids` for all taxes "
"using the matching tax grids you created earlier. Finally, make sure "
"to :ref:`specify both a tax payable and tax receivable account <customize-"
"reports/tax-reports/closing-entry>` for each tax."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, buka :menuselection:`Konfigurasi --> Pajak` dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk membuat dan :ref:`mengonfigurasi pajak baru "
"<taxes/configuration>` untuk laporan pajak kustom Anda. Buat pajak "
"**Penjualan** dan **Pembelian** Anda, dan isi :guilabel:`Kisi Pajak` untuk "
"semua pajak menggunakan kisi pajak yang cocok yang telah Anda buat "
"sebelumnya. Terakhir, pastikan untuk :ref:`menentukan akun pajak terutang "
"dan pajak yang dapat diterima <customize-reports/tax-reports/closing-entry>` "
"untuk setiap pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "Tax grids configuration."
msgstr "Konfigurasi kisi pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:502
msgid "Closing entry"
msgstr "Entri penutupan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:504
msgid ""
"To close taxes, a :ref:`tax group <taxes/computation/group-of-taxes>` must "
"be specified on each tax used in your custom tax report. To do this, open "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` app, navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration --"
"> Taxes`, open a tax that requires a tax group, click "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, and select a group in "
"the :guilabel:`Tax Group` field. Once assigned, click the :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon and set both a :guilabel:`Tax Payable "
"Account` and a :guilabel:`Tax Receivable Account`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menutup pajak, :ref:`grup pajak <taxes/computation/group-of-taxes>` "
"harus ditentukan pada setiap pajak yang digunakan dalam laporan pajak kustom "
"Anda. Untuk melakukan ini, buka aplikasi :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, navigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, buka pajak yang memerlukan grup "
"pajak, klik tab :guilabel:`Opsi Lanjutan`, dan pilih grup di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Grup Pajak`. Setelah ditetapkan, klik ikon :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(panah kanan)` dan atur :guilabel:`Akun Pajak Terutang` "
"dan :guilabel:`Akun Pajak yang Dapat Diterima`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:512
msgid ""
"When everything has been set up, make sure to test your report by creating "
"invoices, bills, and credit notes using the taxes specific to that report. "
"Finally, test the closing entry itself."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semuanya diatur, pastikan untuk menguji laporan Anda dengan membuat "
"faktur, tagihan, dan nota kredit menggunakan pajak yang khusus untuk laporan "
"tersebut. Terakhir, uji entri penutupan itu sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:514
msgid ""
"If you want to hide a specific account from displaying in the tax closing "
"entry, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Taxes`, select the tax, and "
"click the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings adjust)` icon. "
"From there, check the :guilabel:`Tax Closing Entry` box to adjust its "
"visibility."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda ingin menyembunyikan akun tertentu agar tidak ditampilkan dalam "
"entri penutupan pajak, buka :menuselection:`Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, pilih "
"pajak, dan klik ikon :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(pengaturan "
"sesuaikan)`. Dari sana, centang kotak :guilabel:`Entri Penutupan Pajak` "
"untuk menyesuaikan visibilitasnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:520
msgid ":ref:`Tax closing <tax-returns/close>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Penutupan pajak <tax-returns/close>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:3
msgid "Data inalterability check report"
msgstr "Laporan pemeriksaan ketidakberubahan data"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:5
msgid ""
"Tax authorities in some countries require companies to **prove their posted "
"accounting entries are unaltered**, meaning that once an entry has been "
"secured, it can no longer be changed."
msgstr ""
"Otoritas pajak di beberapa negara mengharuskan perusahaan untuk "
"**membuktikan entri akuntansi yang diposting tidak diubah**, yang berarti "
"setelah entri diamankan, entri tersebut tidak dapat lagi diubah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:8
msgid ""
"To do so, Odoo creates a unique fingerprint for each secured entry thanks to "
"the **SHA-256 algorithm**. This fingerprint is called a hash. The hash is "
"generated by taking an entry's essential data (the values of the `name`, "
"`date`, `journal_id`, `company_id`, `debit`, `credit`, `account_id`, and "
"`partner_id` fields), concatenating it, and inputting it to the SHA-256 hash "
"function, which then outputs a fixed size (256-bit) string of characters. "
"The hash function is deterministic (:dfn:`the same input always creates the "
"same output`): any minor modification to the original data would completely "
"change the resulting hash. Consequently, the SHA-256 algorithm is often "
"used, among others, for data integrity verification purposes."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, Odoo membuat sidik jari unik untuk setiap entri yang "
"diamankan berkat **algoritma SHA-256**. Sidik jari ini disebut hash. Hash "
"dihasilkan dengan mengambil data penting entri (nilai dari bidang `name`, "
"`date`, `journal_id`, `company_id`, `debit`, `credit`, `account_id`, dan "
"`partner_id`), menggabungkannya, dan memasukkannya ke fungsi hash SHA-256, "
"yang kemudian menghasilkan string karakter berukuran tetap (256-bit). Fungsi "
"hash bersifat deterministik (:dfn:`input yang sama selalu menghasilkan "
"output yang sama`): setiap modifikasi kecil pada data asli akan sepenuhnya "
"mengubah hash yang dihasilkan. Akibatnya, algoritma SHA-256 sering "
"digunakan, antara lain, untuk tujuan verifikasi integritas data."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:17
msgid ""
"In addition, the previous entry's hash is always added to the next entry to "
"form a **hash chain**. This is used to ensure a new entry is not added "
"afterward between two secured entries, as doing so would break the hash "
"chain."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, hash entri sebelumnya selalu ditambahkan ke entri berikutnya "
"untuk membentuk **rantai hash**. Ini digunakan untuk memastikan entri baru "
"tidak ditambahkan setelahnya di antara dua entri yang diamankan, karena "
"melakukannya akan memutus rantai hash."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:22
msgid ""
"Hashes generated by the SHA-256 algorithm are theoretically not unique, as "
"there is a finite number of possible values. However, this number is "
"exceptionally high: 2²⁵⁶, which is a lot bigger than the number of atoms in "
"the known universe. This is why hashes are considered unique in practice."
msgstr ""
"Hash yang dihasilkan oleh algoritma SHA-256 secara teoritis tidak unik, "
"karena ada jumlah nilai yang mungkin terbatas. Namun, jumlah ini sangat "
"tinggi: 2²⁵⁶, yang jauh lebih besar dari jumlah atom di alam semesta yang "
"diketahui. Inilah sebabnya mengapa hash dianggap unik dalam praktiknya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:30
msgid "Inalterability features"
msgstr "Fitur ketidakberubahan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:32
msgid ""
"Inalterability features can be enabled by activating the :ref:`secure posted "
"entries with hash <data-inalterability/restricted>` option on any journal or "
"using the :ref:`secure entries wizard <data-inalterability/wizard>`."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ketidakberubahan dapat diaktifkan dengan mengaktifkan "
"opsi :ref:`amankan entri yang diposting dengan hash <data-inalterability/"
"restricted>` pada jurnal mana pun atau menggunakan :ref:`wizard entri aman "
"<data-inalterability/wizard>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:36
msgid ""
"Two indicators are added to the journal entry's form view. They show whether "
"the entry is secured or not."
msgstr ""
"Dua indikator ditambahkan ke tampilan formulir entri jurnal. Mereka "
"menunjukkan apakah entri tersebut diamankan atau tidak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:39
msgid ""
"A :icon:`fa-lock` or :icon:`fa-unlock` (:guilabel:`lock icon`) next to "
"the :guilabel:`Posted` state."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-lock` atau :icon:`fa-unlock` (:guilabel:`ikon gembok`) di sebelah "
"status :guilabel:`Diposting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:40
msgid "A :guilabel:`Secured` checkbox in the :guilabel:`Other info` tab."
msgstr "Kotak centang :guilabel:`Diamankan` di tab :guilabel:`Info lainnya`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:42
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Not Secured` filter is available on journal entries and journal "
"items' list views. It can be used to find posted journal entries that are "
"not secured yet."
msgstr ""
"Filter :guilabel:`Not Secured` tersedia pada tampilan daftar entri jurnal "
"dan item jurnal. Filter ini dapat digunakan untuk menemukan entri jurnal "
"yang sudah diposting namun belum diamankan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:44
msgid ""
"The option to open the :ref:`secure entries wizard <data-inalterability/"
"wizard>` is displayed in the :guilabel:`Accounting` menu."
msgstr ""
"Opsi untuk membuka :ref:`wizard pengamanan entri <data-inalterability/"
"wizard>` ditampilkan di menu :guilabel:`Akuntansi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:50
msgid "Secure posted entries with hash"
msgstr "Amankan entri yang diposting dengan hash"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:52
msgid ""
"To activate the hashing function on a specific journal, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`. Open a sales, "
"purchase, or miscellaneous journal, go to the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` "
"tab, and enable :guilabel:`Secure Posted Entries with Hash`. Journals for "
"which the feature is activated are called \"restricted\"."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan fungsi hashing pada jurnal tertentu, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Jurnal`. Buka jurnal "
"penjualan, pembelian, atau serbaguna, buka tab :guilabel:`Pengaturan "
"Lanjutan`, dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Amankan Entri yang Diposting dengan "
"Hash`. Jurnal yang fiturnya diaktifkan disebut \"terbatas\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:57
msgid ""
"To compute the hash of an entry, Odoo retrieves the predecessor entries of "
"the chain (i.e., the entries with the same sequence prefix) and hashes them "
"in a continuous way from the last hashed entry to the new entry to hash."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghitung hash dari sebuah entri, Odoo mengambil entri pendahulu dari "
"rantai tersebut (yaitu, entri dengan awalan urutan yang sama) dan melakukan "
"hash secara berkesinambungan dari entri terakhir yang di-hash hingga entri "
"baru yang akan di-hash."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:62
msgid ""
"Once you post an entry in a restricted journal, you cannot disable the "
"feature anymore, nor edit any secured entry."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda memposting entri di jurnal terbatas, Anda tidak dapat "
"menonaktifkan fitur ini lagi, maupun mengedit entri yang sudah diamankan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:68
msgid "Secure entries wizard"
msgstr "Wizard pengamanan entri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:70
msgid ""
"You can also use the :guilabel:`Secure Entries` Wizard to secure all journal "
"entries, in **all** journals, up to a specific date."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menggunakan Wizard :guilabel:`Secure Entries` untuk "
"mengamankan semua entri jurnal, di **semua** jurnal, hingga tanggal tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:74
msgid ""
"The wizard operates independently of the journal settings and journal types."
msgstr ""
"Wizard beroperasi secara independen dari pengaturan jurnal dan jenis jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:76
msgid ""
"To open it, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting`, and click "
"on :guilabel:`Secure Entries`. If the :ref:`inalterability features <data-"
"inalterability/inalterability_features>` are activated, it is also visible "
"outside the debug mode."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membukanya, aktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>`, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi`, dan klik :guilabel:`Secure "
"Entries`. Jika :ref:`fitur ketidakterubahan <data-inalterability/"
"inalterability_features>` diaktifkan, wizard juga terlihat di luar mode "
"debug."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:81
msgid ""
"To secure entries, select a date up to which all entries should be secured "
"and press :guilabel:`Secure Entries`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengamankan entri, pilih tanggal hingga semua entri harus diamankan "
"dan tekan :guilabel:`Secure Entries`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:85
msgid "After securing the entries, you can no longer edit them."
msgstr "Setelah mengamankan entri, Anda tidak dapat lagi mengeditnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:88
msgid ""
"It can happen that entries that are past the selected date are secured. This "
"is possible since the hash chain corresponds to the sequence prefix, ordered "
"by sequence number."
msgstr ""
"Bisa terjadi entri yang melewati tanggal yang dipilih ikut diamankan. Hal "
"ini mungkin terjadi karena rantai hash sesuai dengan awalan urutan, "
"diurutkan berdasarkan nomor urutan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:95
msgid "Report download"
msgstr "Unduh laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:97
msgid ""
"To download the data inalterability check report, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> Reporting` "
"and click on :guilabel:`Download the Data Inalterability Check Report`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengunduh laporan pemeriksaan ketidakterubahan data, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan --> Pelaporan` "
"dan klik :guilabel:`Download the Data Inalterability Check Report`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:100
msgid ""
"The report's first section is an overview of all journal sequence prefixes "
"containing hashed entries. In the :guilabel:`Restricted` column, you can see "
"whether or not a journal has the :ref:`secure posted entries with hash <data-"
"inalterability/restricted>` option (V) activated or not (X). "
"The :guilabel:`Check` column tells you whether all entries are correctly "
"hashed."
msgstr ""
"Bagian pertama laporan adalah ringkasan semua awalan urutan jurnal yang "
"berisi entri yang di-hash. Di kolom :guilabel:`Restricted`, Anda dapat "
"melihat apakah sebuah jurnal memiliki opsi :ref:`amankan entri yang "
"diposting dengan hash <data-inalterability/restricted>` yang diaktifkan (V) "
"atau tidak (X). Kolom :guilabel:`Check` memberi tahu Anda apakah semua entri "
"sudah di-hash dengan benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:None
msgid "Configuration report for two journals"
msgstr "Laporan konfigurasi untuk dua jurnal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:109
msgid ""
"The second section gives a more detailed result of the data consistency "
"check for each hashed journal sequence prefix. You can view the first hashed "
"entry and its corresponding hash, as well as the last hashed entry and its "
"corresponding hash."
msgstr ""
"Bagian kedua memberikan hasil yang lebih rinci dari pemeriksaan konsistensi "
"data untuk setiap awalan urutan jurnal yang di-hash. Anda dapat melihat "
"entri pertama yang di-hash dan hash yang sesuai, serta entri terakhir yang "
"di-hash dan hash yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/data_inalterability.rst:None
msgid "Data consistency check report for a journal"
msgstr "Laporan pemeriksaan konsistensi data untuk sebuah jurnal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:31
msgid "Intrastat"
msgstr "INTRASTAT"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:5
msgid ""
"Intrastat is the data collection and statistics production system for goods "
"traded among EU member states. It collects data on:"
msgstr ""
"Intrastat adalah sistem pengumpulan data dan produksi statistik untuk barang "
"yang diperdagangkan di antara negara anggota UE. Sistem ini mengumpulkan "
"data tentang:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:8
msgid ""
"Commercial transactions of goods for use, consumption, investment, or resale "
"with ownership transfer;"
msgstr ""
"Transaksi komersial barang untuk digunakan, dikonsumsi, diinvestasikan, atau "
"dijual kembali dengan transfer kepemilikan;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:10
msgid ""
"Goods movements without transfer of ownership (e.g., stock relocations or "
"moves of goods before or after outsourced production or processing, and "
"after maintenance or repair);"
msgstr ""
"Perpindahan barang tanpa transfer kepemilikan (misalnya, relokasi stok atau "
"perpindahan barang sebelum atau setelah produksi atau pemrosesan yang di-"
"outsource, dan setelah maintenance atau perbaikan);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:12
msgid "Returns of goods."
msgstr "Pengembalian barang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:15
msgid ""
"Although the Intrastat system continues to be used, the term Intrastat is "
"not used in the `latest legislation <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/"
"2019/2152/2022-01-01>`_, referring instead to *intra-Union trade in goods "
"statistics*."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun sistem Intrastat terus digunakan, istilah Intrastat tidak digunakan "
"dalam `perundang-undangan terbaru <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/"
"2019/2152/2022-01-01>`_, melainkan merujuk pada *statistik perdagangan "
"barang intra-Uni*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Eurostat Statistics Explained - Glossary: Intrastat <https://ec.europa.eu/"
"eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php?title=Glossary:Intrastat>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Eurostat Statistics Explained - Glosarium: Intrastat <https://ec.europa.eu/"
"eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php?title=Glossary:Intrastat>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:26
msgid "General configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi umum"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:28
msgid ""
"Enable the Intrastat report by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` "
"section, tick :guilabel:`Intrastat` and then :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan laporan Intrastat dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Faktur Pelanggan`, "
"centang :guilabel:`Intrastat` kemudian :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:35
msgid "Default transaction codes: invoice and refund"
msgstr "Kode transaksi default: faktur dan pengembalian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:37
msgid ""
"You can set a default :ref:`transaction code <intrastat/transaction-code>` "
"for all newly created invoice and refund transactions. "
"Under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, select "
"a :guilabel:`Default invoice transaction code` and/or a :guilabel:`Default "
"refund transaction code` and then :guilabel:`Save`. The code will be set "
"automatically on all respective invoice lines."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menetapkan :ref:`kode transaksi <intrastat/transaction-code>` "
"default untuk semua transaksi faktur dan pengembalian yang baru dibuat. Di "
"bawah :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Kode transaksi faktur default` dan/atau :guilabel:`Kode "
"transaksi pengembalian default` kemudian :guilabel:`Simpan`. Kode akan "
"ditetapkan secara otomatis pada semua baris faktur terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:45
msgid "Region code"
msgstr "Kode wilayah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:47
msgid ""
"The region code is **only used by Belgian companies**. "
"Under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, select "
"the :guilabel:`Company Intrastat Region` where the company is located and "
"then :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Kode wilayah **hanya digunakan oleh perusahaan Belgia**. Di "
"bawah :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Wilayah Intrastat Perusahaan` tempat perusahaan berada "
"kemudian :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:52
msgid ""
"If your warehouses are located in more than one region, you can define the "
"region code at the level of each warehouse instead. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Warehouses`, select a "
"warehouse, set its :guilabel:`Intrastat region`, and then :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Jika gudang Anda terletak di lebih dari satu wilayah, Anda dapat menentukan "
"kode wilayah pada tingkat setiap gudang. Untuk melakukannya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Inventaris --> Konfigurasi --> Gudang`, pilih gudang, "
"atur :guilabel:`Wilayah Intrastat`, kemudian :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:0
msgid "Adding the Intrastat region to a warehouse"
msgstr "Menambahkan wilayah Intrastat ke gudang"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:63
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:694
msgid "Product configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi produk"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:65
msgid ""
"All products must be properly configured to be included in the Intrastat "
"report."
msgstr ""
"Semua produk harus dikonfigurasi dengan benar agar dapat disertakan dalam "
"laporan Intrastat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:70
msgid "Commodity code"
msgstr "Kode komoditas"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:72
msgid ""
"Commodity codes are internationally recognized reference numbers used to "
"classify goods depending on their **nature**. Intrastat uses the `Combined "
"Nomenclature <https://taxation-customs.ec.europa.eu/customs-4/calculation-"
"customs-duties/customs-tariff/combined-nomenclature_en>`_."
msgstr ""
"Kode komoditas adalah nomor referensi yang diakui secara internasional yang "
"digunakan untuk mengklasifikasikan barang berdasarkan **sifatnya**. "
"Intrastat menggunakan `Combined Nomenclature <https://taxation-"
"customs.ec.europa.eu/customs-4/calculation-customs-duties/customs-tariff/"
"combined-nomenclature_en>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:75
msgid ""
"To add a commodity code, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Products` and select a product. Under the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, set "
"the product's :guilabel:`Commodity Code`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan kode komoditas, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelanggan --> Produk` dan pilih produk. Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, "
"atur :guilabel:`Kode Komoditas` produk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:79
msgid ""
"`National Bank of Belgium - Intrastat commodity codes <https://www.nbb.be/en/"
"statistics/foreign-trade/nomenclature-and-codes>`_"
msgstr ""
"`National Bank of Belgium - Kode komoditas Intrastat <https://www.nbb.be/en/"
"statistics/foreign-trade/nomenclature-and-codes>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:85
msgid "Quantity: weight and supplementary unit"
msgstr "Kuantitas: berat dan unit tambahan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:87
msgid ""
"Depending on the nature of the goods, it is necessary to specify either the "
"product's weight in kilos (without packaging) or the product's supplementary "
"unit, such as square meter (`m2`), number of items (`p/st`), liter (`l`), or "
"gram (`g`)."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada sifat barang, perlu ditentukan berat produk dalam kilogram "
"(tanpa kemasan) atau unit tambahan produk, seperti meter persegi (`m2`), "
"jumlah item (`p/st`), liter (`l`), atau gram (`g`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:91
msgid ""
"To add a product's weight or supplementary unit, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Products` and select a "
"product. Under the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, depending on the commodity "
"code set, either fill in the product :guilabel:`Weight` or "
"its :guilabel:`Supplementary Units`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan berat produk atau unit tambahan, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Produk` dan pilih produk. "
"Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, tergantung pada kode komoditas yang "
"ditetapkan, isi :guilabel:`Berat` produk atau :guilabel:`Unit Tambahan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:98
msgid "Country of origin"
msgstr "Negara asal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:100
msgid ""
"To add the product's country of origin, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Products` and select a product. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, set the :guilabel:`Country of Origin`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan negara asal produk, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelanggan --> Produk` dan pilih produk. Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, "
"atur :guilabel:`Negara Asal`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:106
msgid "Invoices and bills configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi faktur dan tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:108
msgid ""
"Once products are properly configured, several settings must be configured "
"on the invoices and bills you create."
msgstr ""
"Setelah produk dikonfigurasi dengan benar, beberapa pengaturan harus "
"dikonfigurasi pada faktur dan tagihan yang Anda buat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:114
msgid "Transaction code"
msgstr "Kode transaksi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:116
msgid ""
"Transaction codes are used to identify a transaction's nature. :ref:`Default "
"transaction codes <intrastat/default-transaction-codes>` can be set for "
"invoice and refund transactions."
msgstr ""
"Kode transaksi digunakan untuk mengidentifikasi sifat transaksi. :ref:`Kode "
"transaksi default <intrastat/default-transaction-codes>` dapat diatur untuk "
"transaksi faktur dan pengembalian dana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:119
msgid ""
"To set a transaction code on an invoice line, create an invoice or a bill, "
"click the columns selection button, tick :guilabel:`Intrastat`, and use the "
"newly-added :guilabel:`Intrastat` column to select a transaction code."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur kode transaksi pada baris faktur, buat faktur atau tagihan, "
"klik tombol pemilihan kolom, centang :guilabel:`Intrastat`, dan gunakan "
"kolom :guilabel:`Intrastat` yang baru ditambahkan untuk memilih kode "
"transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:None
msgid "Adding the Intrastat column to an invoice or bill"
msgstr "Menambahkan kolom Intrastat ke faktur atau tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/intrastat.rst:128
msgid ""
"`National Bank of Belgium - Intrastat: Nature of transactions from January "
"2022 <https://www.nbb.be/doc/dd/onegate/data/"
"new_natures_of_transaction_2022_en.pdf>`_"
msgstr ""
"`National Bank of Belgium - Intrastat: Nature of transactions from January "
