msgid "Tax Return Periodicity"
msgstr "Periodisitas SPT"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:33
msgid ""
"The configuration of the **Tax Return Periodicity** allows Odoo to compute "
"your tax return correctly and also to send you a reminder to never miss a "
"tax return deadline."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi **Periodisitas Pengembalian Pajak** memungkinkan Odoo menghitung "
"pengembalian pajak Anda dengan benar dan juga mengirimkan pengingat agar "
"Anda tidak pernah melewatkan tenggat waktu pengembalian pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:36
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Under the :guilabel:`Tax Return Periodicity`, you can set:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`. Di bawah :guilabel:`Periodisitas Pengembalian Pajak`, Anda "
"dapat mengatur:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Periodicity`: define here whether you submit your tax return on a "
"monthly or quarterly basis;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Periodisitas`: tentukan di sini apakah Anda menyerahkan "
"pengembalian pajak setiap bulan atau kuartal;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminder`: define when Odoo should remind you to submit your tax "
"return;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pengingat`: tentukan kapan Odoo harus mengingatkan Anda untuk "
"menyerahkan pengembalian pajak;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: select the journal in which to record the tax return."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jurnal`: pilih jurnal untuk mencatat pengembalian pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:46
msgid ""
"This is usually configured during the :doc:`app's initial set up <../"
"get_started>`."
msgstr ""
"Ini biasanya dikonfigurasi selama :doc:`penyiapan awal aplikasi <../"
"get_started>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:51
msgid "Tax Grids"
msgstr "Tax Grids"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:53
msgid ""
"Odoo generates tax reports based on the :guilabel:`Tax Grids` settings that "
"are configured on your taxes. Therefore, it is crucial to make sure that all "
"recorded transactions use the right taxes. You can see the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Grids` by opening the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab of any invoice and bill."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menghasilkan laporan pajak berdasarkan pengaturan :guilabel:`Kisi "
"Pajak` yang dikonfigurasi pada pajak Anda. Oleh karena itu, sangat penting "
"untuk memastikan bahwa semua transaksi yang dicatat menggunakan pajak yang "
"benar. Anda dapat melihat :guilabel:`Kisi Pajak` dengan membuka "
"tab :guilabel:`Item Jurnal` dari faktur dan tagihan mana pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "see which tax grids are used to record transactions in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr ""
"lihat kisi pajak mana yang digunakan untuk mencatat transaksi di Odoo "
"Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure your tax grids, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, and open the tax you want to modify. There, you "
"can edit your tax settings, along with the tax grids that are used to record "
"invoices or refunds."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi kisi pajak Anda, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, dan buka pajak yang ingin Anda modifikasi. Di sana, "
"Anda dapat mengedit pengaturan pajak Anda, bersama dengan kisi pajak yang "
"digunakan untuk mencatat faktur atau pengembalian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:66
msgid ""
"Taxes and reports are usually already pre-configured in Odoo: a :ref:`fiscal "
"localization package <fiscal_localizations/packages>` is installed according "
"to the country you select at the creation of your database."
msgstr ""
"Pajak dan laporan biasanya sudah dikonfigurasikan sebelumnya di "
"Odoo: :ref:`paket lokalisasi fiskal <fiscal_localizations/packages>` "
"dipasang sesuai dengan negara yang Anda pilih saat pembuatan database Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:73
msgid "Close a tax period"
msgstr "Tutup periode pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:78
msgid "Tax lock date"
msgstr "Tanggal kunci pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:80
msgid ""
"Any new transaction whose accounting date prior to the :guilabel:`Lock Tax "
"Return` date has its tax values moved to the next open tax period. This is "
"useful to make sure that no change can be made to a report once its period "
"is closed."
msgstr ""
"Setiap transaksi baru yang tanggal akuntansinya sebelum "
"tanggal :guilabel:`Kunci Pengembalian Pajak` memiliki nilai pajaknya "
"dipindahkan ke periode pajak terbuka berikutnya. Ini berguna untuk "
"memastikan bahwa tidak ada perubahan yang dapat dilakukan pada laporan "
"setelah periodenya ditutup."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:84
msgid ""
"Therefore, we recommend locking your tax date before working on "
"your :guilabel:`Closing Journal Entry`. This way, other users cannot modify "
"or add transactions that would have an impact on the :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, which can help you avoid some tax declaration errors."
msgstr ""
"Oleh karena itu, kami merekomendasikan mengunci tanggal pajak Anda sebelum "
"mengerjakan :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal Penutup`. Dengan cara ini, pengguna lain "
"tidak dapat memodifikasi atau menambahkan transaksi yang akan berdampak "
"pada :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal Penutup`, yang dapat membantu Anda menghindari "
"beberapa kesalahan deklarasi pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:89
msgid ""
"To check the current :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` date, or to edit it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Lock Dates`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa tanggal :guilabel:`Kunci Pengembalian Pajak` saat ini, atau "
"untuk mengeditnya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Tanggal "
"Kunci`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:97
msgid ""
"Once all the transactions involving taxes have been posted for the period "
"you want to report, open the :guilabel:`Tax Return` report by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Return`. Select the "
"period you want to declare using the date filter to have an overview of the "
"tax return. Then, click :guilabel:`Closing Entry` to create a tax closing "
"journal entry. Odoo automatically proposes the details of the journal entry. "
"Make any necessary changes and click :guilabel:`Post`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua transaksi yang melibatkan pajak telah diposting untuk periode "
"yang ingin Anda laporkan, buka laporan :guilabel:`Pengembalian Pajak` dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Pengembalian Pajak`. "
"Pilih periode yang ingin Anda deklarasikan menggunakan filter tanggal untuk "
"melihat ikhtisar pengembalian pajak. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Entri "
"Penutup` untuk membuat entri jurnal penutup pajak. Odoo secara otomatis "
"menyarankan detail entri jurnal. Lakukan perubahan yang diperlukan dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Posting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:104
msgid ""
"From the report, click :guilabel:`PDF` to download a PDF of the tax return. "
"Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Download Excel` to download an XLSX of the tax return. To "
"save the report to the Documents app, click the :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then click :guilabel:`Copy to Documents`. Select "
"the format to :guilabel:`Export to`, the :guilabel:`Documents Name`, "
"the :guilabel:`Folder` to store it in, and add any :guilabel:`Tags`."
msgstr ""
"Dari laporan, klik :guilabel:`PDF` untuk mengunduh PDF pengembalian pajak. "
"Atau, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`roda gigi`), lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Unduh Excel` untuk mengunduh XLSX pengembalian pajak. Untuk "
"menyimpan laporan ke aplikasi Dokumen, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`roda gigi`), lalu klik :guilabel:`Salin ke Dokumen`. Pilih "
"format untuk :guilabel:`Ekspor ke`, :guilabel:`Nama "
"Dokumen`, :guilabel:`Folder` untuk menyimpannya, dan "
"tambahkan :guilabel:`Tag` apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:110
msgid ""
"The report includes all the values to report to the tax authorities, along "
"with the amount to be paid or refunded."
msgstr ""
"Laporan ini mencakup semua nilai yang harus dilaporkan kepada otoritas "
"pajak, beserta jumlah yang harus dibayar atau dikembalikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:114
msgid ""
"If you forgot to lock your tax date before clicking on :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, then Odoo automatically locks your fiscal period on the same "
"date as the accounting date of your entry. This safety mechanism can prevent "
"some fiscal errors, but it is advised to lock your tax date manually before, "
"as described above."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda lupa mengunci tanggal pajak sebelum mengklik :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, maka Odoo secara otomatis mengunci periode fiskal Anda pada "
"tanggal yang sama dengan tanggal akuntansi entri Anda. Mekanisme pengamanan "
"ini dapat mencegah beberapa kesalahan fiskal, tetapi disarankan untuk "
"mengunci tanggal pajak Anda secara manual sebelumnya, seperti yang "
"dijelaskan di atas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:120
msgid ""
"Once the tax report for a period has been generated but not yet posted, "
"additional invoices or bills from that same period can still be posted and "
"included in the closing entry. To do so, click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Refresh` in the :guilabel:`Proposition of tax closing "
"journal entry`, or click :guilabel:`Closing Entry` again from the tax report."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pajak untuk suatu periode telah dibuat tetapi belum "
"diposting, faktur atau tagihan tambahan dari periode yang sama masih dapat "
"diposting dan disertakan dalam entri penutupan. Untuk melakukannya, "
"klik :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Refresh` di :guilabel:`Proposition of "
"tax closing journal entry`, atau klik :guilabel:`Closing Entry` lagi dari "
"laporan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:124
msgid ""
"After the tax report has been posted for a period, Odoo locks the period and "
"prevents the creation of new journal entries involving VAT. Any corrections "
"to customer invoices or vendor bills must then be recorded in the following "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pajak diposting untuk suatu periode, Odoo mengunci periode "
"tersebut dan mencegah pembuatan entri jurnal baru yang melibatkan PPN. "
"Setiap koreksi terhadap faktur pelanggan atau tagihan vendor harus dicatat "
"pada periode berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:130
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:151
msgid ":doc:`../get_started`"
msgstr ":doc:`../get_started`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:3
msgid "Year-end closing"
msgstr "Penutupan akhir tahun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:5
msgid ""
"Year-end closing is vital for maintaining financial accuracy, complying with "
"regulations, making informed decisions, and ensuring transparency in "
"reporting."
msgstr ""
"Penutupan akhir tahun sangat penting untuk menjaga akurasi keuangan, "
"mematuhi peraturan, membuat keputusan yang tepat, dan memastikan "
"transparansi dalam pelaporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`Tax return <tax_returns>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Pengembalian pajak <tax_returns>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:14
msgid "Fiscal years"
msgstr "Tahun fiskal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:16
msgid ""
"By default, the fiscal year is set to last 12 months and ends on December "
"31st. However, its duration and end date can vary due to cultural, "
"administrative, and economic considerations."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, tahun fiskal diatur berlangsung 12 bulan dan berakhir pada "
"tanggal 31 Desember. Namun, durasi dan tanggal akhirnya dapat bervariasi "
"karena pertimbangan budaya, administratif, dan ekonomi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:19
msgid ""
"To modify these values, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Fiscal Periods` section, change "
"the :guilabel:`Last Day` field if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah nilai-nilai ini, masuk ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Periode Fiskal`, ubah "
"kolom :guilabel:`Hari Terakhir` jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:22
msgid ""
"If the period lasts *more* than or *less* than 12 months, "
"enable :guilabel:`Fiscal Years` and :guilabel:`Save`. Go back to "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Periods` section and click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Fiscal Years`. Then, click :guilabel:`New`, give it "
"a :guilabel:`Name` and both a :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End "
"Date`."
msgstr ""
"Jika periode berlangsung *lebih* dari atau *kurang* dari 12 bulan, "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Tahun Fiskal` dan :guilabel:`Simpan`. Kembali ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Periode Fiskal` dan klik :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Tahun Fiskal`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Baru`, "
"berikan :guilabel:`Nama` dan :guilabel:`Tanggal Mulai` "
"serta :guilabel:`Tanggal Akhir`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:28
msgid ""
"Once the set fiscal period is over, Odoo automatically reverts to the "
"default periodicity, considering the value specified in the :guilabel:`Last "
"Day` field."
msgstr ""
"Setelah periode fiskal yang ditetapkan berakhir, Odoo secara otomatis "
"kembali ke periodisitas default, dengan mempertimbangkan nilai yang "
"ditentukan di kolom :guilabel:`Hari Terakhir`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:34
msgid "Year-end checklist"
msgstr "Daftar periksa akhir tahun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:39
msgid "Before closure"
msgstr "Sebelum penutupan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:41
msgid ""
"Before closing a fiscal year, ensure that everything is accurate and up-to-"
"date:"
msgstr "Sebelum menutup tahun fiskal, pastikan semua sudah akurat dan terbaru:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:43
msgid ""
"Make sure all bank accounts are fully :doc:`reconciled <../bank/"
"reconciliation>` up to year-end, and confirm that the ending book balances "
"match the bank statement balances."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan semua rekening bank telah sepenuhnya :doc:`direkonsiliasi <../bank/"
"reconciliation>` hingga akhir tahun, dan konfirmasikan bahwa saldo buku "
"akhir sesuai dengan saldo laporan bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:45
msgid ""
"Verify that all :doc:`customer invoices <../customer_invoices>` have been "
"created and confirmed and that there are no draft invoices."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi bahwa semua :doc:`faktur pelanggan <../customer_invoices>` telah "
"dibuat dan dikonfirmasi serta tidak ada faktur draft."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:47
msgid ""
"Confirm that all :doc:`vendor bills  <../vendor_bills>` have been created "
"and confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Konfirmasikan bahwa semua :doc:`tagihan vendor  <../vendor_bills>` telah "
"dibuat dan dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:48
msgid ""
"Ensure the accuracy of all :doc:`expenses <../../expenses>` and validate "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan keakuratan semua :doc:`pengeluaran <../../expenses>` dan validasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:49
msgid ""
"Check that all :doc:`received payments <../payments>` have been encoded and "
"confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Periksa bahwa semua :doc:`pembayaran yang diterima <../payments>` telah "
"dikodekan dan dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:50
msgid "Close all :ref:`suspense accounts <accounting/journals/bank-cash-cc>`."
msgstr ""
"Tutup semua :ref:`akun penggantungan <accounting/journals/bank-cash-cc>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:51
msgid ""
"Book all :doc:`depreciation <../vendor_bills/assets>` and :doc:`deferred "
"revenue <../customer_invoices/deferred_revenues>` entries."
msgstr ""
"Catat semua entri :doc:`penyusutan <../vendor_bills/assets>` "
"dan :doc:`pendapatan ditangguhkan <../customer_invoices/deferred_revenues>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:57
msgid "Closing a fiscal year"
msgstr "Menutup tahun fiskal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:59
msgid "Then, to close the fiscal year:"
msgstr "Kemudian, untuk menutup tahun fiskal:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:61
msgid ""
"Run a :ref:`tax report <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`, and verify that "
"all tax information is correct."
msgstr ""
"Jalankan :ref:`laporan pajak <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`, dan "
"verifikasi bahwa semua informasi pajak sudah benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:63
msgid ""
"Reconcile all accounts on the :ref:`balance sheet <accounting/reporting/"
"balance-sheet>`:"
msgstr ""
"Rekonsiliasi semua akun pada :ref:`neraca keuangan <accounting/reporting/"
"balance-sheet>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:65
msgid ""
"Update the bank balances in Odoo according to the actual balances found on "
"the bank statements."
msgstr ""
"Perbarui saldo bank di Odoo sesuai dengan saldo aktual yang ditemukan pada "
"laporan bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:66
msgid ""
"Reconcile all transactions in the cash and bank accounts by running "
"the :ref:`aged receivables <accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>` "
"and :ref:`aged payables <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>` reports."
msgstr ""
"Rekonsiliasi semua transaksi di akun kas dan bank dengan menjalankan "
"laporan :ref:`piutang jatuh tempo <accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>` "
"dan :ref:`hutang jatuh tempo <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:69
msgid ""
"Audit all accounts, fully understanding all transactions and their nature, "
"including :doc:`loans <../bank/loans>` and :doc:`fixed assets <../"
"vendor_bills/assets>`."
msgstr ""
"Audit semua akun, pahami sepenuhnya semua transaksi dan sifatnya, "
"termasuk :doc:`pinjaman <../bank/loans>` dan :doc:`aset tetap <../"
"vendor_bills/assets>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:71
msgid ""
"Optionally, :ref:`match payments <accounting/payments/payments-matching>` to "
"validate any open vendor bills and customer invoices with their payments. "
"While this step is optional, it could assist the year-end closing process if "
"all outstanding payments and invoices are reconciled, potentially finding "
"errors or mistakes in the system."
msgstr ""
"Secara opsional, :ref:`cocokkan pembayaran <accounting/payments/payments-"
"matching>` untuk memvalidasi tagihan vendor dan faktur pelanggan yang "
"terbuka dengan pembayarannya. Meskipun langkah ini opsional, hal ini dapat "
"membantu proses penutupan akhir tahun jika semua pembayaran dan faktur yang "
"tertunda direkonsiliasi, berpotensi menemukan kesalahan dalam sistem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:76
msgid ""
"Next, the accountant likely verifies balance sheet items and book entries "
"for:"
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, akuntan kemungkinan memverifikasi item neraca keuangan dan "
"entri pembukuan untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:78
msgid "year-end manual adjustments,"
msgstr "penyesuaian manual akhir tahun,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:79
msgid "work in progress,"
msgstr "pekerjaan dalam proses,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:80
msgid "depreciation journal entries,"
msgstr "entri jurnal penyusutan,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:81
msgid "loans,"
msgstr "pinjaman,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:82
msgid "tax adjustments,"
msgstr "penyesuaian pajak,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:83
msgid "etc."
msgstr "dll."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:85
msgid ""
"During the year-end audit, the accountant may print paper copies of all "
"balance sheet items (e.g., loans, bank accounts, prepayments, sales tax "
"statements) to compare them against the balances recorded in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Selama audit akhir tahun, akuntan dapat mencetak salinan kertas dari semua "
"item neraca keuangan (misalnya pinjaman, rekening bank, pembayaran di muka, "
"laporan pajak penjualan) untuk membandingkannya dengan saldo yang tercatat "
"di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:90
msgid ""
"As part of this process, setting a :ref:`Lock Everything <year-end/lock-"
"everything-date>` date to the last day (inclusive) of the preceding fiscal "
"year is good practice. This ensures that journal entries with an accounting "
"date on or before the lock date cannot be created or modified during the "
"audit. Users with *administrator* access rights can still create and edit "
"entries if an exception is configured."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai bagian dari proses ini, menetapkan tanggal :ref:`Lock Everything "
"<year-end/lock-everything-date>` pada hari terakhir (inklusif) tahun fiskal "
"sebelumnya merupakan praktik yang baik. Ini memastikan bahwa entri jurnal "
"dengan tanggal akuntansi pada atau sebelum tanggal kunci tidak dapat dibuat "
"atau dimodifikasi selama audit. User dengan hak akses *administrator* masih "
"dapat membuat dan mengedit entri jika pengecualian dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:99
msgid "Lock everything date"
msgstr "Kunci semua tanggal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:101
msgid ""
"Setting a lock date prevents modifications to any posted journal entries "
"with an accounting date on or before the lock date. It also prevents posting "
"new entries with an accounting date on or before the lock date. In such "
"cases, the system automatically sets the accounting date to the day after "
"the lock date."
msgstr ""
"Menetapkan tanggal kunci mencegah modifikasi terhadap entri jurnal yang "
"telah diposting dengan tanggal akuntansi pada atau sebelum tanggal kunci. "
"Ini juga mencegah posting entri baru dengan tanggal akuntansi pada atau "
"sebelum tanggal kunci. Dalam kasus seperti itu, sistem secara otomatis "
"menetapkan tanggal akuntansi ke hari setelah tanggal kunci."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:106
msgid ""
"To set a :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Accounting --> Lock Dates`. In the :guilabel:`Lock Journal Entries` "
"window, set the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menetapkan tanggal :guilabel:`Kunci Semua`, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Tanggal Kunci`. Di "
"jendela :guilabel:`Kunci Entri Jurnal`, tetapkan tanggal :guilabel:`Kunci "
"Semua` dan :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:111
msgid ""
"Users with :guilabel:`Administrator` access rights to the Accounting app can "
"create exceptions. To do so:"
msgstr ""
"User dengan hak akses :guilabel:`Administrator` ke aplikasi Akuntansi dapat "
"membuat pengecualian. Untuk melakukannya:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:114
msgid ""
"After setting the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date, reopen "
"the :guilabel:`Lock Journal Entries` window and remove the :guilabel:`Lock "
"Everything` date."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menetapkan tanggal :guilabel:`Lock Everything`, buka kembali "
"jendela :guilabel:`Lock Journal Entries` dan hapus tanggal :guilabel:`Lock "
"Everything`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:116
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Exception` banner, choose if this exception should be "
"set :guilabel:`for me` (the current user) or :guilabel:`for everyone` and "
"how long it should last."
msgstr ""
"Di banner :guilabel:`Exception`, pilih apakah pengecualian ini harus "
"ditetapkan :guilabel:`for me` (user saat ini) atau :guilabel:`for everyone` "
"dan berapa lama pengecualian tersebut harus berlaku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:118
msgid "A :guilabel:`Reason` for this exception can be added."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Alasan` untuk pengecualian ini dapat ditambahkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:119
msgid ""
"All of this information is logged in the chatter of the :doc:`company record "
"</applications/general/companies>`."
msgstr ""
"Semua informasi ini dicatat dalam chatter dari :doc:`catatan perusahaan </"
"applications/general/companies>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:123
msgid ""
"To remove the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date after it has been saved, "
"configure the exception to apply :guilabel:`for everyone` and set the "
"duration to :guilabel:`forever`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus tanggal :guilabel:`Lock Everything` setelah disimpan, "
"konfigurasikan pengecualian untuk diterapkan :guilabel:`for everyone` dan "
"atur durasi menjadi :guilabel:`forever`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:129
msgid "Current year's earnings"
msgstr "Laba tahun berjalan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:131
msgid ""
"Odoo uses a unique account type called **current year's earnings** to "
"display the difference between the **income** and **expense** accounts."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menggunakan tipe akun unik yang disebut **laba tahun berjalan** untuk "
"menampilkan selisih antara akun **pendapatan** dan **beban**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:135
msgid ""
"The chart of accounts can only contain one account of this type. By default, "
"it is a 999999 account named :guilabel:`Undistributed Profits/Losses`."
msgstr ""
"Bagan Akun hanya dapat berisi satu akun dengan tipe ini. Secara default, ini "
"adalah akun 999999 bernama :guilabel:`Undistributed Profits/Losses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:138
msgid ""
"To allocate the current year's earnings, create a new miscellaneous entry "
"with a date set to the end of the fiscal year to book them to any equity "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengalokasikan laba tahun berjalan, buat entri miscellaneous baru "
"dengan tanggal yang ditetapkan pada akhir tahun fiskal untuk membukukannya "
"ke akun ekuitas mana pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:141
msgid ""
"Then, verify whether the current year's earnings on the **balance sheet** "
"correctly show a zero balance. If so, a :guilabel:`Hard Lock date` can be "
"set to the last day of the fiscal year in :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Accounting --> Lock Dates`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, verifikasi apakah laba tahun berjalan pada **neraca keuangan** "
"dengan benar menunjukkan saldo nol. Jika ya, :guilabel:`Hard Lock date` "
"dapat ditetapkan pada hari terakhir tahun fiskal "
"di :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Lock Dates`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:146
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Hard Lock date` field is irreversible and is intended to "
"ensure data inalterability required to comply with accounting regulations in "
"certain countries. If such compliance is not applicable, setting this field "
"may not be necessary. However, if required, the date should only be set once "
"it is confirmed to be correct, as it **cannot be changed or overridden**, "
"regardless of access rights."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Hard Lock date` bersifat tidak dapat dibatalkan dan "
"dimaksudkan untuk memastikan ketidakberubahan data yang diperlukan untuk "
"mematuhi peraturan akuntansi di negara-negara tertentu. Jika kepatuhan "
"tersebut tidak berlaku, menetapkan bidang ini mungkin tidak diperlukan. "
"Namun, jika diperlukan, tanggal hanya boleh ditetapkan setelah dipastikan "
"benar, karena **tidak dapat diubah atau ditimpa**, terlepas dari hak akses."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:7
msgid ""
"Tax regulations generally require companies to compute tax amounts on sales, "
"keep a record of accumulated tax debit and credit, and periodically file "
"this information in tax returns."
msgstr ""
"Peraturan perpajakan umumnya mengharuskan perusahaan untuk menghitung jumlah "
"pajak atas penjualan, menyimpan catatan akumulasi debit dan kredit pajak, "
"dan secara berkala melaporkan informasi ini dalam laporan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:11
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Gambaran Umum"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:13
msgid "In general, managing taxes in Odoo involves the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Secara umum, mengelola pajak di Odoo melibatkan langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:15
msgid ""
"Taxes are added on individual lines of documents created via the Sales, "
"Purchase, Accounting, and Point of Sale apps."
msgstr ""
"Pajak ditambahkan pada baris individual dokumen yang dibuat melalui aplikasi "
"Penjualan, Pembelian, Akuntansi, dan POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:17
msgid "Odoo automatically computes tax amounts on the documents."
msgstr "Odoo secara otomatis menghitung jumlah pajak pada dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:18
msgid ""
"On accounting documents, Odoo generates journal items to keep track of tax "
"debit and tax credit."
msgstr ""
"Pada dokumen akuntansi, Odoo menghasilkan item jurnal untuk melacak debit "
"pajak dan kredit pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:19
msgid ""
"The total base, tax debit, and tax credit for a period can be viewed in the "
"tax return report and used to file a tax return."
msgstr ""
"Total dasar, debit pajak, dan kredit pajak untuk suatu periode dapat dilihat "
"di laporan pengembalian pajak dan digunakan untuk mengajukan pengembalian "
"pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:23
msgid "Taxes on sales and purchases"
msgstr "Pajak atas penjualan dan pembelian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:25
msgid ""
"Most sales and purchase documents have a :guilabel:`Taxes` field where taxes "
"can be applied to individual lines. This includes :doc:`invoices "
"<customer_invoices>` and :doc:`vendor bills <vendor_bills>` in the "
"Accounting app, :doc:`sales quotations <../../sales/sales/sales_quotations>` "
"in the Sales app, and :doc:`purchase orders <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` in the Purchase app."
msgstr ""
"Sebagian besar dokumen penjualan dan pembelian memiliki "
"kolom :guilabel:`Taxes` di mana pajak dapat diterapkan pada baris "
"individual. Ini termasuk :doc:`faktur <customer_invoices>` dan :doc:`tagihan "
"vendor <vendor_bills>` di aplikasi Akuntansi, :doc:`penawaran penjualan "
"<../../sales/sales/sales_quotations>` di aplikasi Penjualan, "
"dan :doc:`pesanan pembelian <../../inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/"
"rfq>` di aplikasi Pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Adding a 21% tax on an invoice line."
msgstr "Menambahkan pajak 21% pada baris faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:35
msgid ""
"When adding a product to a sale or purchase line, the taxes :ref:`assigned "
"to the product <taxes/product>` are automatically applied to the line."
msgstr ""
"Saat menambahkan produk ke baris penjualan atau pembelian, pajak "
"yang :ref:`ditetapkan ke produk <taxes/product>` secara otomatis diterapkan "
"ke baris tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:38
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`Point of Sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>` app, the "
"taxes :ref:`assigned to the products <taxes/product>` are applied directly "
"to the order and cannot be changed except by a :doc:`fiscal position <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"Di aplikasi :doc:`POS <../../sales/point_of_sale>`, pajak "
"yang :ref:`ditetapkan ke produk <taxes/product>` diterapkan langsung ke "
"pesanan dan tidak dapat diubah kecuali oleh :doc:`posisi fiskal <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:43
msgid "Automatic computation of tax amounts"
msgstr "Perhitungan otomatis jumlah pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:45
msgid ""
"Applying a tax to a sale or purchase line allows Odoo to automatically "
"compute the tax amount based on the sale or purchase line's subtotal and the "
"tax's configuration. The details of the computation are explained in "
"the :doc:`Tax computation documentation <taxes/tax_computation>`."
msgstr ""
"Menerapkan pajak ke baris penjualan atau pembelian memungkinkan Odoo untuk "
"secara otomatis menghitung jumlah pajak berdasarkan subtotal baris penjualan "
"atau pembelian dan konfigurasi pajak. Detail perhitungan dijelaskan "
"dalam :doc:`dokumentasi perhitungan pajak <taxes/tax_computation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Odoo automatically computes a tax amount for the 21% tax."
msgstr "Odoo secara otomatis menghitung jumlah pajak untuk pajak 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:53
msgid "Automatic generation of tax journal items"
msgstr "Pembuatan otomatis item jurnal pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:55
msgid ""
"Upon applying a tax on an :doc:`invoice <customer_invoices>` or :doc:`vendor "
"bill <vendor_bills>`, a tax payable journal item is automatically generated "
"with the tax amount. This keeps track of the tax debit or credit associated "
"with the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Saat menerapkan pajak pada :doc:`faktur <customer_invoices>` "
"atau :doc:`tagihan vendor <vendor_bills>`, item jurnal pajak terutang dibuat "
"secara otomatis dengan jumlah pajak. Ini melacak debit atau kredit pajak "
"yang terkait dengan transaksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:59
msgid ""
"Furthermore, the tax amount is added to the amount due on the receivable or "
"payable journal item."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, jumlah pajak ditambahkan ke jumlah yang harus dibayar pada item "
"jurnal piutang atau utang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:61
msgid ""
"Finally, :ref:`Tax Grids <tax-returns/tax-grids>` are added both to the "
"automatically created tax payable journal item and to the invoice line on "
"which the tax is applied. These tags are used to retrieve the journal items "
"corresponding to the tax's base and tax amount in the :doc:`Tax Return "
"<reporting/tax_returns>` report."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, :ref:`Kisi Pajak <tax-returns/tax-grids>` ditambahkan baik ke item "
"jurnal pajak terutang yang dibuat secara otomatis maupun ke baris faktur di "
"mana pajak diterapkan. Tag ini digunakan untuk mengambil item jurnal yang "
"sesuai dengan dasar pajak dan jumlah pajak dalam laporan :doc:`Laporan Pajak "
"<reporting/tax_returns>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically generates a tax payable journal item for the 21% tax."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis membuat item jurnal pajak terutang untuk pajak 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:70
msgid ""
"If :doc:`Cash Basis <taxes/cash_basis>` is enabled, upon reconciling the "
"invoice or vendor bill with the payment, an additional journal entry is "
"created to represent the creation of the tax debit or credit at that point "
"in time."
msgstr ""
"Jika :doc:`Basis Kas <taxes/cash_basis>` diaktifkan, saat merekonsiliasi "
"faktur atau tagihan vendor dengan pembayaran, entri jurnal tambahan dibuat "
"untuk mewakili pembuatan debit atau kredit pajak pada waktu tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:75
msgid "Filing tax returns"
msgstr "Pengajuan pengembalian pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:77
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Tax Return <reporting/tax_returns>` report aggregates the base and "
"tax amounts from invoices and vendor bills over a given period and presents "
"it in a format tailored to the :doc:`fiscal localization <../"
"fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :doc:`Pengembalian Pajak <reporting/tax_returns>` mengagregasi "
"jumlah dasar dan pajak dari faktur dan tagihan vendor selama periode "
"tertentu dan menyajikannya dalam format yang disesuaikan "
"dengan :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:81
msgid ""
"The amounts presented in the tax return report can be used to complete tax "
"declarations that need to be periodically submitted to the government. In "
"most cases, there is a one-to-one correspondence between the lines of the "
"tax return and the official tax declaration, allowing amounts to simply be "
"copied from one to the other."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah yang disajikan dalam laporan pengembalian pajak dapat digunakan untuk "
"melengkapi deklarasi pajak yang perlu diajukan secara berkala kepada "
"pemerintah. Dalam sebagian besar kasus, ada korespondensi satu-ke-satu "
"antara baris pengembalian pajak dan deklarasi pajak resmi, sehingga jumlah "
"dapat langsung disalin dari satu ke yang lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The base section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Bagian dasar dari laporan pengembalian pajak untuk Belgia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The tax section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Bagian pajak dari laporan pengembalian pajak untuk Belgia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:95
msgid "Basic tax configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi pajak dasar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:97
msgid "Follow these basic steps to set up taxes:"
msgstr "Ikuti langkah-langkah dasar berikut untuk mengatur pajak:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:99
msgid ""
"Enable any relevant :ref:`company-wide options <taxes/configuration/"
"company>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan semua :ref:`opsi perusahaan <taxes/configuration/company>` yang "
"relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:100
msgid ""
"Activate any needed :ref:`pre-configured taxes <taxes/list_activation>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan semua :ref:`pajak yang telah dikonfigurasi <taxes/list_activation>` "
"yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:101
msgid "Assign taxes on your :ref:`products <taxes/product>`."
msgstr "Tetapkan pajak pada :ref:`produk <taxes/product>` Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:106
msgid "Company-wide options"
msgstr "Opsi seluruh perusahaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:108
msgid ""
"To access these configuration options, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and scroll down to :guilabel:`Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses opsi konfigurasi ini, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan gulir ke bawah ke :guilabel:`Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:116
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Sales Tax` and :guilabel:`Purchase Tax` are "
"automatically set on products when creating new products."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan` dan :guilabel:`Pajak Pembelian` default secara "
"otomatis ditetapkan pada produk saat membuat produk baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:119
msgid ""
"If :ref:`Accounting Firms <accounting/fiduciaries>` mode is enabled, the "
"default sales tax is automatically set on new invoice lines, and the default "
"purchase tax is automatically set on new vendor bill lines."
msgstr ""
"Jika mode :ref:`Accounting Firms <accounting/fiduciaries>` diaktifkan, pajak "
"penjualan default secara otomatis ditetapkan pada baris invoice baru, dan "
"pajak pembelian default secara otomatis ditetapkan pada baris tagihan vendor "
"baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prices` can be changed to :guilabel:`Tax Included` to treat all "
"taxes as :ref:`tax included <taxes/included-in-price>` by default. This "
"would be appropriate if all of a company's pricing is done tax-included. If "
"only some of a company's pricing is tax-included, individual taxes can be "
"set as :guilabel:`Tax Included`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Harga` dapat diubah menjadi :guilabel:`Termasuk Pajak` untuk "
"memperlakukan semua pajak sebagai :ref:`tax included <taxes/included-in-"
"price>` secara default. Ini akan sesuai jika semua penetapan harga "
"perusahaan dilakukan termasuk pajak. Jika hanya beberapa penetapan harga "
"perusahaan yang termasuk pajak, pajak individual dapat ditetapkan "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Termasuk Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:129
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:3
msgid "EU intra-community distance selling"
msgstr "Penjualan jarak jauh intra-komunitas EU"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:131
msgid ""
"Activate this option if you are based in the EU and sell to consumers in "
"other EU countries to apply local VAT rates."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan opsi ini jika Anda berbasis di UE dan menjual kepada konsumen di "
"negara UE lainnya untuk menerapkan tarif PPN lokal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:135
msgid ":doc:`EU intra-community distance selling<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Penjualan jarak jauh intra-komunitas UE<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:138
msgid "Cash basis"
msgstr "Basis kas"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:140
msgid ""
"Activate this option if taxes must be accounted for on a cash rather than "
"accruals basis. Some countries mandate cash basis accounting; in that case, "
"this option will be activated by default by the :doc:`fiscal localization "
"package <../fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan opsi ini jika pajak harus dicatat berdasarkan kas daripada akrual. "
"Beberapa negara mewajibkan akuntansi basis kas; dalam kasus tersebut, opsi "
"ini akan diaktifkan secara default oleh :doc:`paket lokalisasi fiskal <../"
"fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`Cash basis <taxes/cash_basis>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Basis kas <taxes/cash_basis>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:150
msgid "Activate pre-configured taxes"
msgstr "Aktifkan pajak yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:152
msgid ""
"The list of taxes can be accessed by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Daftar pajak dapat diakses dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:155
msgid ""
"Generally, inactive taxes are created for most sales tax rates by "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../fiscal_localizations>` package, but only "
"the main tax rate is active by default. To activate an inactive tax, click "
"the toggle in the :guilabel:`Active` column."
msgstr ""
"Umumnya, pajak tidak aktif dibuat untuk sebagian besar tarif pajak penjualan "
"oleh paket :doc:`lokalisasi fiskal <../fiscal_localizations>`, tetapi hanya "
"tarif pajak utama yang aktif secara default. Untuk mengaktifkan pajak yang "
"tidak aktif, klik toggle di kolom :guilabel:`Aktif`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:162
msgid "Assign taxes on products"
msgstr "Tetapkan pajak pada produk"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:164
msgid ""
"To configure the taxes used for each product, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Products`, select the "
"product to configure, and fill the :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` "
"and :guilabel:`Purchase Taxes` fields. These taxes are automatically applied "
"when adding the product to an invoice, vendor bill, sales order, purchase "
"order, or point of sale order."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi pajak yang digunakan untuk setiap produk, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> Produk`, pilih produk yang "
"akan dikonfigurasi, dan isi kolom :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan` "
"dan :guilabel:`Pajak Pembelian`. Pajak ini secara otomatis diterapkan saat "
"menambahkan produk ke invoice, tagihan vendor, sales order, purchase order, "
"atau order POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:170
msgid ""
"Use the :ref:`Default Taxes <taxes/default>` company-wide setting to "
"automatically fill these fields on new products."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan pengaturan :ref:`Default Taxes <taxes/default>` seluruh perusahaan "
"untuk secara otomatis mengisi kolom ini pada produk baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:176
msgid "Advanced tax configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi pajak lanjutan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:178
msgid "The following aspects of a tax can be customized:"
msgstr "Aspek berikut dari pajak dapat disesuaikan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:180
msgid ""
"How the tax :ref:`appears in the backend <taxes/configuration/back-end>`"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana pajak :ref:`muncul di backend <taxes/configuration/back-end>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:181
msgid "How the tax :ref:`appears to customers <taxes/configuration/customer>`"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana pajak :ref:`muncul kepada pelanggan <taxes/configuration/customer>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:182
msgid "The details of the :doc:`tax computation <taxes/tax_computation>`"
msgstr "Detail dari :doc:`perhitungan pajak <taxes/tax_computation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:183
msgid "How tax payable journal items are :ref:`created <taxes/definition-tab>`"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana item jurnal pajak terutang :ref:`dibuat <taxes/definition-tab>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:184
msgid ""
":doc:`Fiscal positions <taxes/fiscal_positions>` (how to replace a tax by "
"another tax under certain conditions)"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Posisi fiskal <taxes/fiscal_positions>` (cara mengganti pajak dengan "
"pajak lain dalam kondisi tertentu)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:187
msgid ""
"To open a tax's configuration, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, then click the tax name."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuka konfigurasi pajak, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, kemudian klik nama pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:193
msgid "Configure backend appearance and availability"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan tampilan dan ketersediaan backend"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:195
msgid ""
"The following options determine how a tax is displayed to users in the Odoo "
"back-end."
msgstr ""
"Opsi berikut menentukan bagaimana pajak ditampilkan kepada pengguna di "
"backend Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:158
msgid "Tax name"
msgstr "Nama pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:202
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Name` appears for backend users in the :guilabel:`Taxes` "
