"> License and API Keys`. Klik :guilabel:`Generate License Key`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:89
msgid ""
"A warning appears stating: `If your business app is connected to Avalara "
"solutions, the connection will be broken until you update the app with the "
"new license key. This action cannot be undone.`"
msgstr ""
"Peringatan muncul yang menyatakan: `If your business app is connected to "
"Avalara solutions, the connection will be broken until you update the app "
"with the new license key. This action cannot be undone.`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:93
msgid ""
"Generating a new license key breaks the connection with existing business "
"apps using the *AvaTax* integration. Make sure to update these apps with the "
"new license key."
msgstr ""
"Menghasilkan license key baru akan memutuskan koneksi dengan aplikasi bisnis "
"yang ada yang menggunakan integrasi *AvaTax*. Pastikan untuk memperbarui "
"aplikasi ini dengan license key yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:96
msgid ""
"If this will be the first :abbr:`API (application programming interface)` "
"integration being made with *AvaTax* and Odoo, then "
"click :guilabel:`Generate license key`."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini adalah integrasi :abbr:`application programming interface` pertama "
"yang dibuat dengan *AvaTax* dan Odoo, maka klik :guilabel:`Generate license "
"key`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:99
msgid ""
"If this is an additional license key, ensure the previous connection can be "
"broken. There is **only** one license key associated with each of the "
"Avalara sandbox and production accounts."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini adalah license key tambahan, pastikan koneksi sebelumnya dapat "
"diputuskan. Hanya ada **satu** license key yang terkait dengan masing-masing "
"akun sandbox dan production Avalara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:103
msgid ""
"Copy this key to a safe place. It is strongly encouraged to back up the "
"license key for future reference. This key **cannot** be retrieved after "
"leaving this screen."
msgstr ""
"Salin kunci ini ke tempat yang aman. Sangat disarankan untuk membuat "
"cadangan license key untuk referensi di masa mendatang. Kunci ini **tidak "
"dapat** diambil kembali setelah meninggalkan layar ini."

