#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:39
msgid "Automatically"
msgstr "Secara Otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:41
msgid ""
"Vendor bills can be automatically created by sending an email to "
"an :ref:`email alias <accounting/bill-digitization/email-alias>` associated "
"with the purchase journal, or by :ref:`uploading a PDF <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/manual-upload>`."
msgstr ""
"Tagihan vendor dapat dibuat secara otomatis dengan mengirim email "
"ke :ref:`alias email <accounting/bill-digitization/email-alias>` yang "
"terkait dengan jurnal pembelian, atau dengan :ref:`mengunggah PDF "
"<accounting/bill-digitization/manual-upload>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once the bill is uploaded, the PDF document appears on the right side of the "
"screen, making it easy to fill in the bill information."
msgstr ""
"Setelah tagihan diunggah, dokumen PDF muncul di sisi kanan layar, memudahkan "
"pengisian informasi tagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:48
msgid ""
"Bills can be :doc:`digitized <vendor_bills/invoice_digitization>` for "
"automatic completion and :ref:`matched with purchase orders <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/vendor-bills-matching-po>` to replace OCR-detected data with "
"the existing purchase order's details."
msgstr ""
"Tagihan dapat :doc:`didigitalisasi <vendor_bills/invoice_digitization>` "
"untuk penyelesaian otomatis dan :ref:`dicocokkan dengan pesanan pembelian "
"<accounting/bill-digitization/vendor-bills-matching-po>` untuk mengganti "
"data yang terdeteksi OCR dengan detail pesanan pembelian yang ada."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:52
msgid ""
"Services such as digitizing scanned or PDF vendor bills in Odoo "
"require :doc:`In-App Purchase (IAP) </applications/essentials/"
"in_app_purchase>` credits."
msgstr ""
"Layanan seperti digitalisasi tagihan vendor yang dipindai atau PDF di Odoo "
"memerlukan kredit :doc:`Pembelian Dalam Aplikasi (IAP) </applications/"
"essentials/in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:55
msgid ""
"To automatically post bills from selected vendors, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors` and select the "
"relevant vendor. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, under "
"the :guilabel:`Automation` section, update the :guilabel:`Auto-post bills` "
"field  with one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting tagihan secara otomatis dari vendor yang dipilih, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Vendor --> Vendor` dan pilih vendor yang "
"relevan. Di tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Otomasi`, "
"perbarui kolom :guilabel:`Posting otomatis tagihan` dengan salah satu opsi "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:105
msgid ":guilabel:`Always`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Selalu`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`Ask after 3 validations without edits`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanyakan setelah 3 validasi tanpa perubahan`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:110
msgid ":guilabel:`Never`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tidak Pernah`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:65
msgid ""
":ref:`Vendor bills matching with purchase orders <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/vendor-bills-matching-po>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pencocokan tagihan vendor dengan pesanan pembelian <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/vendor-bills-matching-po>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:71
msgid "Bill completion"
msgstr "Penyelesaian tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:73
msgid ""
"Whether the bill is created manually or automatically, make sure the "
"following fields are appropriately completed:"
msgstr ""
"Baik tagihan dibuat secara manual atau otomatis, pastikan kolom berikut "
"diisi dengan tepat:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`: Odoo automatically fills in some information based on "
"the information on the vendor's contact record as well as previous purchase "
"orders and bills."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`: Odoo secara otomatis mengisi beberapa informasi "
"berdasarkan informasi pada catatan kontak vendor serta pesanan pembelian dan "
"tagihan sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill Reference`: Add the sales order reference provided by the "
"vendor. This field is used to :ref:`match <accounting/payments/payments-"
"matching>` the products when they are received."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Referensi Tagihan`: Tambahkan referensi sales order yang "
"diberikan oleh vendor. Kolom ini digunakan untuk :ref:`mencocokkan "
"<accounting/payments/payments-matching>` produk saat diterima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto-Complete`: Select a past bill/purchase order to complete the "
"document automatically. The :guilabel:`Vendor` field should be completed "
"before completing this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lengkapi Otomatis`: Pilih tagihan/pesanan pembelian sebelumnya "
"untuk melengkapi dokumen secara otomatis. Kolom :guilabel:`Vendor` harus "
"diisi sebelum melengkapi kolom ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Bill Date`: Select the document's issuance date."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal Tagihan`: Pilih tanggal penerbitan dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accounting Date`: Update the document's accounting registration "
"date if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Akuntansi`: Perbarui tanggal pencatatan akuntansi dokumen "
"jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Reference`: The :guilabel:`Memo` field automatically "
"includes the payment reference once the payment is registered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Referensi Pembayaran`: Kolom :guilabel:`Memo` secara otomatis "
"menyertakan referensi pembayaran setelah pembayaran dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recipient Bank`: Indicates the account number to which the "
"payment will be made. This field is required when paying via batch payment "
"files (such as :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-transfers>` "
"and :doc:`SEPA Direct Debit <payments/sepa_payments>`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bank Penerima`: Menunjukkan nomor rekening ke mana pembayaran "
"akan dilakukan. Bidang ini diperlukan saat membayar melalui file pembayaran "
"batch (seperti :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-transfers>` "
"dan :doc:`SEPA Direct Debit <payments/sepa_payments>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Due Date` or :guilabel:`Payment Terms` must be specified for the "
"bill payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Jatuh Tempo` atau :guilabel:`Ketentuan Pembayaran` harus "
"ditentukan untuk pembayaran tagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select which journal should record the bill and in "
"which :doc:`currency <get_started/multi_currency>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jurnal`: Pilih jurnal mana yang harus mencatat tagihan dan "
"dalam :doc:`mata uang <get_started/multi_currency>` apa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:101
msgid ""
"If the bill line does not correspond to an existing product in the database, "
"click the :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(bars)` icon to enter a "
"description for the bill line without linking it to a product."
msgstr ""
"Jika baris tagihan tidak sesuai dengan produk yang ada di database, klik "
"ikon :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(garis)` untuk memasukkan deskripsi "
"untuk baris tagihan tanpa menautkannya ke produk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:105
msgid ""
"To access the product catalog and view all items in an organized display, "
"click :doc:`Catalog </applications/essentials/product_catalog>`. When the "
"products and quantities are selected, click :guilabel:`Back to Bill` to "
"return to the vendor bill; the selected catalog items will appear in the "
"vendor bill lines."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses katalog produk dan melihat semua item dalam tampilan yang "
"terorganisir, klik :doc:`Katalog </applications/essentials/"
"product_catalog>`. Ketika produk dan jumlahnya dipilih, "
"klik :guilabel:`Kembali ke Tagihan` untuk kembali ke tagihan vendor; item "
"katalog yang dipilih akan muncul di baris tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:111
msgid ""
"Multiple bills for the same purchase order may be issued if the vendor is on "
"back-order and sends invoices as products are shipped or if the vendor sends "
"partial bills or requests a deposit. In this case, multiple bills may have "
"the same :guilabel:`Bill Reference`."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa tagihan untuk pesanan pembelian yang sama dapat diterbitkan jika "
"vendor melakukan back-order dan mengirim faktur saat produk dikirim atau "
"jika vendor mengirim tagihan parsial atau meminta uang muka. Dalam hal ini, "
"beberapa tagihan dapat memiliki :guilabel:`Referensi Tagihan` yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:118
msgid "Bill confirmation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:120
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` when the document is completed. The status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Posted`, and a journal entry is generated based on the vendor "
"bill information. On confirmation, Odoo assigns each vendor bill a unique "
"number from a defined :doc:`sequence <vendor_bills/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` ketika dokumen selesai. Status berubah "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Diposting`, dan entri jurnal dibuat berdasarkan informasi "
"tagihan vendor. Saat konfirmasi, Odoo menetapkan setiap tagihan vendor nomor "
"unik dari :doc:`urutan <vendor_bills/sequence>` yang telah ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:125
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, a vendor bill can no longer be updated. "
"Click :guilabel:`Reset to draft` if changes are required."
msgstr ""
"Setelah dikonfirmasi, tagihan vendor tidak dapat lagi diperbarui. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Reset ke draft` jika diperlukan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:131
msgid "Self-billing"
msgstr "Self-billing"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:133
msgid ""
"Self-billing is a workflow where a customer generates a vendor bill on the "
"supplier's behalf and sends a copy to the supplier for their records. It "
"removes the need for the supplier to send the customer a vendor bill and is "
"common in industries where the customer has more reliable transaction data. "
"It also reduces payment time as the customer does not have to wait for the "
"supplier to issue a vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"Self-billing adalah alur kerja di mana pelanggan membuat tagihan vendor atas "
"nama pemasok dan mengirimkan salinan kepada pemasok untuk catatan mereka. "
"Ini menghilangkan kebutuhan pemasok untuk mengirim tagihan vendor kepada "
"pelanggan dan umum di industri di mana pelanggan memiliki data transaksi "
"yang lebih dapat diandalkan. Ini juga mengurangi waktu pembayaran karena "
"pelanggan tidak perlu menunggu pemasok menerbitkan tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:139
msgid ""
"Odoo supports the generation of self-billing vendor bills and self-billing "
"credit notes, both of which can be sent both by email and via Peppol."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mendukung pembuatan tagihan vendor self-billing dan nota kredit self-"
"billing, yang keduanya dapat dikirim melalui email dan via Peppol."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:147
msgid ""
"To configure self-billing in Odoo, first create a separate purchase journal "
"specifically for self-billing:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi self-billing di Odoo, pertama buat jurnal pembelian "
"terpisah khusus untuk self-billing:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:150
msgid "Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Jurnal`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:151
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr "Klik tombol :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:152
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Journal Name` and set the :guilabel:`Type` "
"to :guilabel:`Purchase`."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan :guilabel:`Journal Name` dan atur :guilabel:`Type` "
"ke :guilabel:`Purchase`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:153
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, set a :guilabel:`Default Expense "
"Account` and enter a :guilabel:`Short Code`."
msgstr ""
"Pada tab :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal`, atur :guilabel:`Akun Beban Default` dan "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Kode Singkat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:155
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab, enable :guilabel:`Self Billing`."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Advanced Settings`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Self Billing`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:158
msgid ":doc:`get_started/journals`"
msgstr ":doc:`get_started/journals`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:163
msgid "Create a self-bill"
msgstr "Buat self-bill"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:165
msgid ""
"Self-bills can be created both :ref:`manually <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"creation-manual>` and :ref:`automatically <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"automatic>`. When creating self-bills, be sure to either create them "
"directly from the :ref:`self-billing purchase journal <accounting/"
"vendor_bills/self-billing-config>` on the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` "
"or manually set the :guilabel:`Journal` of the self-bill to the self-billing "
"purchase journal."
msgstr ""
"Self-bill dapat dibuat baik :ref:`secara manual <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"creation-manual>` maupun :ref:`secara otomatis <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"automatic>`. Saat membuat self-bill, pastikan untuk membuatnya langsung "
"dari :ref:`jurnal pembelian self-billing <accounting/vendor_bills/self-"
"billing-config>` di :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` atau secara manual "
"atur :guilabel:`Journal` dari self-bill ke jurnal pembelian self-billing."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:172
msgid ""
"The sequence of self-bills contains the :ref:`database ID "
"<export_import_data/different-ids>` (also known as the internal ID) of the "
"partner, making the sequence unique per partner."
msgstr ""
"Urutan self-bill berisi :ref:`database ID <export_import_data/different-"
"ids>` (juga dikenal sebagai ID internal) dari partner, membuat urutan unik "
"per partner."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:178
msgid "Send a self-bill"
msgstr "Kirim self-bill"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:180
msgid ""
"To send a self-bill after :ref:`creating <accounting/vendor_bills/self-"
"billing-create>` and confirming it, click :guilabel:`Send`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Send` popup window, select the sending methods "
"(i.e., :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`By Post`, and/or the appropriate Peppol "
"format), and click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim self-bill setelah :ref:`membuatnya <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"self-billing-create>` dan mengonfirmasinya, klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Di "
"jendela popup :guilabel:`Kirim`, pilih metode pengiriman "
"(yaitu :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`Melalui Pos`, dan/atau format Peppol "
"yang sesuai), lalu klik :guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:186
msgid ""
"If sending self-bills via :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`, "
"first :ref:`configure your Peppol registration <accounting/e-invoicing/"
"peppol-registration>`, then verify that the vendor is registered with "
"Peppol. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors`, "
"then go through the :ref:`contact verification process <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/contact-verification>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika mengirim self-bill via :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`, "
"pertama :ref:`konfigurasikan pendaftaran Peppol Anda <accounting/e-invoicing/"
"peppol-registration>`, lalu verifikasi bahwa vendor terdaftar dengan Peppol. "
"Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> "
"Vendors`, kemudian lakukan :ref:`proses verifikasi kontak <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/contact-verification>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:191
msgid ""
"Not every Peppol access point supports self-billing. Check with your "
"suppliers to ensure that theirs does."
msgstr ""
"Tidak setiap access point Peppol mendukung self-billing. Periksa dengan "
"pemasok Anda untuk memastikan bahwa mereka mendukungnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:199
msgid ""
"To register a payment, click on :guilabel:`Pay`. In the :guilabel:`Pay` "
"window, select the :guilabel:`Journal`, the :guilabel:`Payment Method`, "
"the :guilabel:`Amount`, and the :guilabel:`Currency`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat pembayaran, klik :guilabel:`Bayar`. Di "
"jendela :guilabel:`Bayar`, pilih :guilabel:`Jurnal`, :guilabel:`Metode "
"Pembayaran`, :guilabel:`Jumlah`, dan :guilabel:`Mata Uang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:203
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Amount` paid is less than the total remaining amount on "
"the vendor bill, the payment is :ref:`partial <accounting/payments/partial-"
"payment>`, and the :guilabel:`Payment Difference` field displays the "
"outstanding balance."
msgstr ""
"Ketika :guilabel:`Jumlah` yang dibayarkan kurang dari total sisa jumlah pada "
"tagihan vendor, pembayaran tersebut :ref:`parsial <accounting/payments/"
"partial-payment>`, dan kolom :guilabel:`Selisih Pembayaran` menampilkan "
"saldo yang belum dibayar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:207
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Memo` field is filled automatically if the :guilabel:`Payment "
"Reference` has been set correctly on the vendor bill. If the field is empty, "
"select the vendor invoice number as a reference."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Memo` diisi secara otomatis jika :guilabel:`Referensi "
"Pembayaran` telah diatur dengan benar pada tagihan vendor. Jika kolom "
"kosong, pilih nomor faktur vendor sebagai referensi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:211
msgid ""
"Then click :guilabel:`Create payment`. An :guilabel:`In "
"Payment`/:guilabel:`Partial` banner appears on the bill until it "
"is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` and its status updates "
"to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian klik :guilabel:`Buat pembayaran`. Spanduk :guilabel:`Dalam "
"Pembayaran`/:guilabel:`Parsial` muncul pada tagihan "
"hingga :doc:`direkonsiliasi <bank/reconciliation>` dan statusnya diperbarui "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Dibayar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:222
msgid "Aged payable report"
msgstr "Laporan utang jatuh tempo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:224
msgid ""
"To get an overview of the open vendor bills and their due dates, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged payable`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendapatkan gambaran umum tentang tagihan vendor yang belum dibayar "
"dan tanggal jatuh temponya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> "
"Utang Jatuh Tempo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:227
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-caret-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon next to a "
"vendor to view the details of all their outstanding bills, including the due "
"dates and amounts."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-right` :guilabel:`(panah kanan)` di sebelah vendor "
"untuk melihat detail semua tagihan terutang mereka, termasuk tanggal jatuh "
"tempo dan jumlahnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:3
msgid "Non-current assets and fixed assets"
msgstr "Aset tidak lancar dan aset tetap"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Non-current Assets**, also known as **long-term assets**, are investments "
"that are expected to be realized after one year. They are capitalized rather "
"than being expensed and appear on the company's balance sheet. Depending on "
"their nature, they may undergo **depreciation**."
msgstr ""
"**Aset Tidak Lancar**, juga dikenal sebagai **aset jangka panjang**, adalah "
"investasi yang diharapkan direalisasikan setelah satu tahun. Aset ini "
"dikapitalisasi daripada dibebankan dan muncul di neraca keuangan perusahaan. "
"Tergantung pada sifatnya, aset ini mungkin mengalami **penyusutan**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Fixed Assets** are a type of Non-current Assets and include the properties "
"bought for their productive aspects, such as buildings, vehicles, equipment, "
"land, and software."
msgstr ""
"**Aset Tetap** adalah jenis Aset Tidak Lancar dan mencakup properti yang "
"dibeli untuk aspek produktifnya, seperti bangunan, kendaraan, peralatan, "
"tanah, dan perangkat lunak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:12
msgid ""
"For example, let's say we buy a car for $ 27,000. We plan to amortize it "
"over five years, and we will sell it for $ 7,000 afterward. Using the "
"linear, or straight-line, depreciation method, $ 4,000 are expensed each "
"year as **depreciation expenses**. After five years, the **Accumulated "
"Depreciation** amount reported on the balance sheet equals $ 20,000, leaving "
"us with $ 7,000 of **Not Depreciable Value**, or Salvage value."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai contoh, katakanlah kita membeli mobil seharga $27.000. Kita "
"berencana untuk mengamortisasinya selama lima tahun, dan kita akan "
"menjualnya seharga $7.000 setelahnya. Menggunakan metode penyusutan linier, "
"atau garis lurus, $4.000 dibebankan setiap tahun sebagai **beban "
"penyusutan**. Setelah lima tahun, jumlah **Akumulasi Penyusutan** yang "
"dilaporkan di neraca keuangan sama dengan $20.000, meninggalkan kita dengan "
"$7.000 **Nilai Tidak Dapat Disusutkan**, atau nilai sisa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:18
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting handles depreciation by creating all depreciation entries "
"automatically in *draft mode*. They are then posted periodically."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Akuntansi menangani penyusutan dengan membuat semua entri penyusutan "
"secara otomatis dalam *mode draft*. Entri tersebut kemudian diposting secara "
"berkala."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:21
msgid "Odoo supports the following **Depreciation Methods**:"
msgstr "Odoo mendukung **Metode Penyusutan** berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:23
msgid "Straight Line"
msgstr "Garis Lurus"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:24
msgid "Declining"
msgstr "Declining"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:25
msgid "Declining Then Straight Line"
msgstr "Menurun Kemudian Garis Lurus"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:28
msgid ""
"The server checks once a day if an entry must be posted. It might then take "
"up to 24 hours before you see a change from *draft* to *posted*."
msgstr ""
"Server memeriksa sekali sehari apakah entri harus diposting. Mungkin "
"diperlukan hingga 24 jam sebelum Anda melihat perubahan dari *draft* ke "
"*posted*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:34
msgid ""
"Such transactions must be posted on an **Assets Account** rather than on the "
"default expense account."
msgstr ""
"Transaksi semacam itu harus diposting di **Akun Aset** daripada di akun "
"pengeluaran default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:38
msgid "Configure an Assets Account"
msgstr "Konfigurasi Akun Aset"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:40
msgid ""
"To configure your account in the **Chart of Accounts**, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Chart of Accounts`, "
"click on *Create*, and fill out the form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi akun Anda di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi "
"--> Bagan Akun`, klik *Buat*, dan isi formulir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Configuration of an Assets Account in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Konfigurasi Akun Aset di Odoo Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:48
msgid ""
"This account's type must be either *Fixed Assets* or *Non-current Assets*."
msgstr "Jenis akun ini harus berupa *Aset Tetap* atau *Aset Tidak Lancar*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:51
msgid "Post an expense to the right account"
msgstr "Post pengeluaran ke akun yang tepat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:54
msgid "Select the account on a draft bill"
msgstr "Pilih akun pada draft tagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:56
msgid ""
"On a draft bill, select the right account for all the assets you are buying."
msgstr ""
"Pada draft tagihan, pilih akun yang tepat untuk semua aset yang Anda beli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Selection of an Assets Account on a draft bill in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Pemilihan Akun Aset pada draft tagihan di Odoo Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:65
msgid "Choose a different Expense Account for specific products"
msgstr "Pilih Akun Pengeluaran yang berbeda untuk produk tertentu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:67
msgid ""
"Start editing the product, go to the *Accounting* tab, select the right "
"**Expense Account**, and save."
msgstr ""
"Mulai edit produk, buka tab *Akuntansi*, pilih **Akun Pengeluaran** yang "
"tepat, dan simpan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Change of the Assets Account for a product in Odoo"
msgstr "Perubahan Akun Aset untuk produk di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:75
msgid ""
"It is possible to :ref:`automate the creation of assets entries <assets-"
"automation>` for these products."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk :ref:`mengotomatisasi pembuatan entri aset <assets-"
"automation>` untuk produk-produk ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:81
msgid "Change the account of a posted journal item"
msgstr "Mengubah akun item jurnal yang telah diposting"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:83
msgid ""
"To do so, open your Purchases Journal by going to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Accounting --> Purchases`, select the journal item you want to modify, "
"click on the account, and select the right one."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka Jurnal Pembelian Anda dengan pergi "
"ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Pembelian`, pilih item jurnal "
"yang ingin Anda ubah, klik pada akun, dan pilih yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Modification of a posted journal item's account in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Modifikasi akun item jurnal yang telah diposting di Odoo Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:92
msgid "Assets entries"
msgstr "Entri Aset"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:97
msgid "Create a new entry"
msgstr "Buat entri baru"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:99
msgid ""
"An **Asset entry** automatically generates all journal entries in *draft "
"mode*. They are then posted one by one at the right time."
msgstr ""
"**Entri Aset** secara otomatis menghasilkan semua entri jurnal dalam *mode "
"draft*. Kemudian entri tersebut diposting satu per satu pada waktu yang "
"tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:102
msgid ""
"To create a new entry, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> "
"Assets`, click on *Create*, and fill out the form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat entri baru, pergi ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --"
"> Aset`, klik *Buat*, dan isi formulir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:105
msgid ""
"Click on **select related purchases** to link an existing journal item to "
"this new entry. Some fields are then automatically filled out, and the "
"journal item is now listed under the **Related Purchase** tab."
msgstr ""
"Klik **pilih pembelian terkait** untuk menautkan item jurnal yang ada ke "
"entri baru ini. Beberapa field kemudian terisi secara otomatis, dan item "
"jurnal sekarang terdaftar di bawah tab **Pembelian Terkait**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Assets entry in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Entri aset di Odoo Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:113
msgid ""
"Once done, you can click on *Compute Depreciation* (next to the *Confirm* "
"button) to generate all the values of the **Depreciation Board**. This board "
"shows you all the entries that Odoo will post to depreciate your asset, and "
"at which date."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, Anda dapat mengklik *Hitung Penyusutan* (di sebelah tombol "
"*Konfirmasi*) untuk menghasilkan semua nilai **Daftar Penyusutan**. Daftar "
"ini menunjukkan kepada Anda semua entri yang akan diposting Odoo untuk "
"menyusutkan aset Anda, dan pada tanggal berapa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Depreciation Board in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Daftar Penyusutan di Odoo Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:122
msgid "What does \"Prorata Temporis\" mean?"
msgstr "Apa arti \"Prorata Temporis\"?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:124
msgid ""
"The **Prorata Temporis** feature is useful to depreciate your assets the "
"most accurately possible."
msgstr ""
"Fitur **Prorata Temporis** berguna untuk menyusutkan aset Anda seakurat "
"mungkin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:126
msgid ""
"With this feature, the first entry on the Depreciation Board is computed "
"based on the time left between the *Prorata Date* and the *First "
"Depreciation Date* rather than the default amount of time between "
"depreciations."
msgstr ""
"Dengan fitur ini, entri pertama pada Daftar Penyusutan dihitung berdasarkan "
"waktu yang tersisa antara *Tanggal Prorata* dan *Tanggal Penyusutan Pertama* "
"daripada jumlah waktu default antara penyusutan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:130
msgid ""
"For example, the Depreciation Board above has its first depreciation with an "
"amount of $ 241.10 rather than $ 4,000.00. Consequently, the last entry is "
"also lower and has an amount of $ 3758.90."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, Daftar Penyusutan di atas memiliki penyusutan pertama dengan "
"jumlah $ 241,10 daripada $ 4.000,00. Akibatnya, entri terakhir juga lebih "
"rendah dan memiliki jumlah $ 3.758,90."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:134
msgid "What are the different Depreciation Methods"
msgstr "Apa saja Metode Penyusutan yang berbeda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:136
msgid ""
"The **Straight Line Depreciation Method** divides the initial Depreciable "
"Value by the number of depreciations planned. All depreciation entries have "
"the same amount."
msgstr ""
"**Metode Penyusutan Garis Lurus** membagi Nilai yang Dapat Disusutkan awal "
"dengan jumlah penyusutan yang direncanakan. Semua entri penyusutan memiliki "
"jumlah yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:139
msgid ""
"The **Declining Depreciation Method** multiplies the Depreciable Value by "
"the **Declining Factor** for each entry. Each depreciation entry has a lower "
"amount than the previous entry. The last depreciation entry doesn't use the "
"declining factor but instead has an amount corresponding to the balance of "
"the depreciable value so that it reaches $0 by the end of the specified "
"duration."
msgstr ""
"**Metode Penyusutan Menurun** mengalikan Nilai yang Dapat Disusutkan dengan "
"**Faktor Menurun** untuk setiap entri. Setiap entri penyusutan memiliki "
"jumlah yang lebih rendah dari entri sebelumnya. Entri penyusutan terakhir "
"tidak menggunakan faktor menurun tetapi memiliki jumlah yang sesuai dengan "
"saldo nilai yang dapat disusutkan sehingga mencapai $0 pada akhir durasi "
"yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:144
msgid ""
"The **Declining Then Straight Line Depreciation Method** uses the Declining "
"Method, but with a minimum Depreciation equal to the Straight Line Method. "
"This method ensures a fast depreciation at the beginning, followed by a "
"constant one afterward."
msgstr ""
"**Metode Penyusutan Menurun Kemudian Garis Lurus** menggunakan Metode "
"Menurun, tetapi dengan Penyusutan minimum sama dengan Metode Garis Lurus. "
"Metode ini memastikan penyusutan cepat di awal, diikuti dengan penyusutan "
"konstan setelahnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:149
msgid "Assets from the Purchases Journal"
msgstr "Aset dari Jurnal Pembelian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:151
msgid ""
"You can create an asset entry from a specific journal item in your "
"**Purchases Journal**."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membuat entri aset dari item jurnal tertentu di **Jurnal "
"Pembelian** Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:153
msgid ""
"To do so, open your Purchases Journal by going to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Accounting --> Purchases`, and select the journal item you want to "
"record as an asset. Make sure that it is posted in the right account "
"(see: :ref:`journal-assets-account`)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka Jurnal Pembelian Anda dengan masuk "
"ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Pembelian`, dan pilih item "
"jurnal yang ingin Anda catat sebagai aset. Pastikan item tersebut telah "
"diposting ke akun yang benar (lihat: :ref:`journal-assets-account`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:157
msgid ""
"Then, click on *Action*, select **Create Asset**, and fill out the form the "
"same way you would do to :ref:`create a new entry <create-assets-entry>`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, klik *Tindakan*, pilih **Buat Aset**, dan isi formulir dengan cara "
"yang sama seperti saat Anda :ref:`membuat entri baru <create-assets-entry>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Create Asset Entry from a journal item in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Buat Entri Aset dari item jurnal di Odoo Accounting"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:165
msgid "Modification of an Asset"
msgstr "Modifikasi Aset"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:167
msgid ""
"You can modify the values of an asset to increase or decrease its value."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memodifikasi nilai aset untuk menambah atau mengurangi nilainya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:169
msgid ""
"To do so, open the asset you want to modify, and click on *Modify "
"Depreciation*. Then, fill out the form with the new depreciation values and "
"click on *Modify*."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka aset yang ingin Anda modifikasi, dan klik "
"*Modifikasi Penyusutan*. Kemudian, isi formulir dengan nilai penyusutan baru "
"dan klik *Modifikasi*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:172
msgid ""
"A **decrease in value** posts a new Journal Entry for the **Value Decrease** "
"and modifies all the future *unposted* Journal Entries listed in the "
"Depreciation Board."
msgstr ""
"**Penurunan nilai** akan memposting Entri Jurnal baru untuk **Penurunan "
"Nilai** dan memodifikasi semua Entri Jurnal *yang belum diposting* di masa "
"mendatang yang tercantum dalam Papan Penyusutan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:175
msgid ""
"An **increase in value** requires you to fill out additional fields related "
"to the account movements and creates a new Asset entry with the **Value "
"Increase**. The Gross Increase Asset Entry can be accessed with a Smart "
"Button."
msgstr ""
"**Peningkatan nilai** mengharuskan Anda mengisi bidang tambahan yang terkait "
"dengan pergerakan akun dan membuat entri Aset baru dengan **Peningkatan "
"Nilai**. Entri Aset Peningkatan Bruto dapat diakses dengan Tombol Pintar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Gross Increase smart button in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Tombol pintar Peningkatan Bruto di Odoo Accounting"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:184
msgid "Disposal of Fixed Assets"
msgstr "Penghapusan Aset Tetap"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:186
msgid ""
"To **sell** an asset or **dispose** of it implies that it must be removed "
"from the Balance Sheet."
msgstr ""
"**Menjual** aset atau **membuangnya** berarti aset tersebut harus dihapus "
"dari Neraca Keuangan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:188
msgid ""
"To do so, open the asset you want to dispose of, click on *Sell or Dispose*, "
"and fill out the form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka aset yang ingin Anda buang, klik *Jual atau Buang*, "
"dan isi formulir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Disposal of Assets in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Penghapusan Aset di Odoo Accounting"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:194
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting then generates all the journal entries necessary to dispose "
"of the asset, including the gain or loss on sale, which is based on the "
"difference between the asset's book value at the time of the sale and the "
"amount it is sold for."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Accounting kemudian menghasilkan semua entri jurnal yang diperlukan "
"untuk membuang aset, termasuk keuntungan atau kerugian dari penjualan, yang "
"didasarkan pada selisih antara nilai buku aset pada saat penjualan dan "
"jumlah yang diperoleh dari penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:199
msgid ""
"To record the sale of an asset, you must first post the related Customer "
"Invoice so you can link the sale of the asset with it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat penjualan aset, Anda harus terlebih dahulu memposting Faktur "
"Pelanggan terkait sehingga Anda dapat menghubungkan penjualan aset dengan "
"faktur tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:205
msgid "Assets Models"
msgstr "Model Aset"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:207
msgid ""
"You can create **Assets Models** to create your Asset entries faster. It is "
"particularly useful if you recurrently buy the same kind of assets."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membuat **Model Aset** untuk membuat entri Aset Anda lebih cepat. "
"Ini sangat berguna jika Anda sering membeli jenis aset yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:210
msgid ""
"To create a model, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Assets Models`, click on *Create*, and fill out the form the same way you "
"would do to create a new entry."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat model, masuk ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Model Aset`, klik *Buat*, dan isi formulir dengan cara yang sama seperti "
"saat Anda membuat entri baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:214
msgid ""
"You can also convert a *confirmed Asset entry* into a model by opening it "
"from :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Assets` and then, by "
"clicking on the button *Save Model*."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat mengonversi *entri Aktiva yang dikonfirmasi* menjadi model "
"dengan membukanya dari :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Aktiva` "
"dan kemudian, dengan mengklik tombol *Simpan Model*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:219
msgid "Apply an Asset Model to a new entry"
msgstr "Terapkan Model Aktiva ke entri baru"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:221
msgid ""
"When you create a new Asset entry,  fill out the **Fixed Asset Account** "
"with the right asset account."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda membuat entri Aktiva baru, isi **Akun Aktiva Tetap** dengan akun "
"aktiva yang tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:224
msgid ""
"New buttons with all the models linked to that account appear at the top of "
"the form. Clicking on a model button fills out the form according to that "
"model."
msgstr ""
"Tombol baru dengan semua model yang terkait dengan akun tersebut muncul di "
"bagian atas formulir. Mengklik tombol model akan mengisi formulir sesuai "
"dengan model tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Assets model button in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Tombol model aktiva di Odoo Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:234
msgid "Automate the Assets"
msgstr "Otomatiskan Aktiva"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:236
msgid ""
"When you create or edit an account of which the type is either *Non-current "
"Assets* or *Fixed Assets*, you can configure it to create assets for the "
"expenses that are credited on it automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda membuat atau mengedit akun yang tipenya adalah *Aktiva Tidak "
"Lancar* atau *Aktiva Tetap*, Anda dapat mengonfigurasinya untuk membuat "
"aktiva secara otomatis untuk pengeluaran yang dikreditkan padanya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:240
msgid "You have three choices for the **Automate Assets** field:"
msgstr "Anda memiliki tiga pilihan untuk bidang **Otomatiskan Aktiva**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:242
msgid "**No:** this is the default value. Nothing happens."
msgstr "**Tidak:** ini adalah nilai default. Tidak terjadi apa-apa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:243
msgid ""
"**Create in draft:** whenever a transaction is posted on the account, a "
"draft *Assets entry* is created, but not validated. You must first fill out "
"the form in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Assets`."
msgstr ""
"**Buat dalam draf:** setiap kali transaksi diposting pada akun, *entri "
"Aktiva* draf dibuat, tetapi tidak divalidasi. Anda harus mengisi formulir "
"terlebih dahulu di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Akuntansi --> Aktiva`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:246
msgid ""
"**Create and validate:** you must also select an Asset Model (see: `Assets "
"Models`_). Whenever a transaction is posted on the account, an *Assets "
"entry* is created and immediately validated."
msgstr ""
"**Buat dan validasi:** Anda juga harus memilih Model Aktiva (lihat: `Model "
"Aktiva`_). Setiap kali transaksi diposting pada akun, *entri Aktiva* dibuat "
"dan langsung divalidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:None
msgid "Automate Assets on an account in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Otomatiskan Aktiva pada akun di Odoo Akuntansi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:254
msgid ""
"You can, for example, select this account as the default **Expense Account** "
"of a product to fully automate its purchase. (see: :ref:`product-assets-"
"account`)."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat, misalnya, memilih akun ini sebagai **Akun Pengeluaran** default "
"dari produk untuk sepenuhnya mengotomatiskan pembeliannya. "
"(lihat: :ref:`product-assets-account`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:258
msgid ":doc:`../get_started/chart_of_accounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../get_started/chart_of_accounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Deferred expenses"
msgstr "Beban dibayar di muka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Deferred expenses** and **prepayments** (also known as **prepaid "
"expenses**) are both costs that have already occurred for products or "
"services yet to be received."
msgstr ""
"**Beban dibayar di muka** dan **pembayaran di muka** (juga dikenal sebagai "
"**pengeluaran dibayar di muka**) adalah biaya yang telah terjadi untuk "
"produk atau layanan yang belum diterima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:8
msgid ""
"Such costs are **assets** for the company that pays them since it already "
"paid for products and services but has either not yet received them or not "
"yet used them. The company cannot report them on the current **profit and "
"loss statement**, or *income statement*, since the payments will be "
"effectively expensed in the future."
msgstr ""
"Biaya tersebut merupakan **aktiva** bagi perusahaan yang membayarnya karena "
"telah membayar produk dan layanan tetapi belum menerimanya atau belum "
"menggunakannya. Perusahaan tidak dapat melaporkannya pada **laporan laba "
"rugi** saat ini, atau *laporan pendapatan*, karena pembayaran akan efektif "
"dibebankan di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:13
msgid ""
"These future expenses must be deferred on the company's balance sheet until "
"the moment in time they can be **recognized**, at once or over a defined "
"period, on the profit and loss statement."
msgstr ""
"Pengeluaran masa depan ini harus ditangguhkan pada neraca keuangan "
"perusahaan sampai saat dapat **diakui**, sekaligus atau selama periode yang "
"ditentukan, pada laporan laba rugi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:16
msgid ""
"For example, let's say we pay $1200 at once for one year of insurance. We "
"already pay the cost now but haven't used the service yet. Therefore, we "
"post this new expense in a *prepayment account* and decide to recognize it "
"on a monthly basis. Each month, for the next 12 months, $100 will be "
"recognized as an expense."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, katakanlah kita membayar $1200 sekaligus untuk asuransi satu "
"tahun. Kita sudah membayar biayanya sekarang tetapi belum menggunakan "
"layanannya. Oleh karena itu, kita memposting pengeluaran baru ini di *akun "
"pembayaran di muka* dan memutuskan untuk mengakuinya secara bulanan. Setiap "
"bulan, selama 12 bulan ke depan, $100 akan diakui sebagai pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:21
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting handles deferred expenses by spreading them across multiple "
"entries that are posted periodically."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Akuntansi menangani beban dibayar di muka dengan menyebarkannya ke "
"beberapa entri yang diposting secara berkala."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:36
msgid "Deferred Expense"
msgstr "Penangguhan Pengeluaran "

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:37
msgid ""
"Expenses are deferred on this Current Asset account until they are "
"recognized."
msgstr "Pengeluaran didefer pada akun Aset Lancar sampai mereka direkam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:39
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo :ref:`automatically generates <vendor_bills/deferred/"
"generate_on_validation>` the deferral entries when you post a vendor bill. "
"However, you can also choose to :ref:`generate them manually <vendor_bills/"
"deferred/generate_manually>` by selecting the :guilabel:`Manually & Grouped` "
"option instead."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, Odoo :ref:`secara otomatis menghasilkan <vendor_bills/"
"deferred/generate_on_validation>` entri penangguhan ketika Anda memposting "
"tagihan vendor. Namun, Anda juga dapat memilih untuk :ref:`menghasilkannya "
"secara manual <vendor_bills/deferred/generate_manually>` dengan memilih "
"opsi :guilabel:`Manually & Grouped`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:44
msgid "Suppose a bill of $1200 must be deferred over 12 months."
msgstr "Misalkan tagihan sebesar $1200 harus ditangguhkan selama 12 bulan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:65
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` fields are "
"visible in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. In most cases, "
"the :guilabel:`Start Date` should be in the same month as "
"the :guilabel:`Bill Date`. Deferred expense entries are posted from the bill "
"date and are displayed in the report accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan kolom :guilabel:`Tanggal Mulai` dan :guilabel:`Tanggal Akhir` "
"terlihat di tab :guilabel:`Baris Invoice`. Dalam kebanyakan "
"kasus, :guilabel:`Tanggal Mulai` harus berada di bulan yang sama "
"dengan :guilabel:`Tanggal Tagihan`. Entri beban ditangguhkan diposting dari "
"tanggal tagihan dan ditampilkan dalam laporan sesuai dengan itu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:70
msgid ""
"For each line of the bill that should be deferred, specify the start and end "
"dates of the deferral period."
msgstr ""
"Untuk setiap baris tagihan yang harus ditangguhkan, tentukan tanggal mulai "
"dan tanggal akhir periode penangguhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:73
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Generate Entries` field is set to :guilabel:`On invoice/"
"bill validation`, Odoo automatically generates the deferral entries when the "
"bill is validated. Click on the :guilabel:`Deferred Entries` smart button to "
"see them."
msgstr ""
"Jika bidang :guilabel:`Generate Entries` diatur ke :guilabel:`On invoice/"
"bill validation`, Odoo secara otomatis menghasilkan entri penangguhan ketika "
"tagihan divalidasi. Klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Deferred Entries` untuk "
"melihatnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:77
msgid ""
"One entry, dated on the same day as the bill's accounting date, moves the "
"bill amounts from the expense account to the deferred account. The other "
"entries are deferral entries which will, month after month, move the bill "
"amounts from the deferred account to the expense account to recognize the "
"expense."
msgstr ""
"Satu entri, tertanggal pada hari yang sama dengan tanggal akuntansi tagihan, "
"memindahkan jumlah tagihan dari akun pengeluaran ke akun penangguhan. Entri "
"lainnya adalah entri penangguhan yang akan, bulan demi bulan, memindahkan "
"jumlah tagihan dari akun penangguhan ke akun pengeluaran untuk mengakui "
"pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:83
msgid ""
"You can defer a January bill of $1200 over 12 months by specifying a start "
"date of 01/01/2023 and an end date of 12/31/2023. At the end of August, $800 "
"is recognized as an expense, whereas $400 remains on the deferred account."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menangguhkan tagihan Januari sebesar $1200 selama 12 bulan dengan "
"menentukan tanggal mulai 01/01/2023 dan tanggal akhir 12/31/2023. Pada akhir "
"Agustus, $800 diakui sebagai pengeluaran, sedangkan $400 tetap berada di "
"akun penangguhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:90
msgid ""
"The deferred expense report computes an overview of the necessary deferral "
"entries for each account. To access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Deferred Expense`."
msgstr ""
"Laporan beban dibayar di muka menghitung ringkasan entri penangguhan yang "
"diperlukan untuk setiap akun. Untuk mengaksesnya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Beban Dibayar di Muka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Deferred expense report"
msgstr "Laporan beban dibayar di muka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:100
msgid ""
"Only bills whose accounting date is before the end of the period of the "
"report are taken into account."
msgstr ""
"Hanya tagihan yang tanggal akuntansinya sebelum akhir periode laporan yang "
"diperhitungkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:113
msgid ""
"At the end of each month, go to the Deferred Expenses report and click "
"the :guilabel:`Generate Entries` button. This generates two deferral entries:"
msgstr ""
"Pada akhir setiap bulan, buka laporan Beban Dibayar di Muka dan klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Generate Entries`. Ini menghasilkan dua entri penangguhan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:116
msgid ""
"One dated at the end of the month which aggregates, for each account, all "
"the deferred amounts of that month. This means that at the end of that "
"period, a part of the deferred expense is recognized."
msgstr ""
"Satu tertanggal pada akhir bulan yang mengagregasi, untuk setiap akun, semua "
"jumlah yang ditangguhkan pada bulan tersebut. Ini berarti pada akhir periode "
"tersebut, sebagian dari beban yang ditangguhkan diakui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:124
msgid "There are two bills:"
msgstr "Terdapat dua tagihan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:126
msgid "Bill A: $1200 to be deferred from 01/01/2023 to 12/31/2023"
msgstr ""
"Tagihan A: $1200 yang akan ditangguhkan dari 01/01/2023 hingga 12/31/2023"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:127
msgid "Bill B: $600 to be deferred from 01/01/2023 to 12/31/2023"
msgstr ""
"Tagihan B: $600 yang akan ditangguhkan dari 01/01/2023 hingga 12/31/2023"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:135
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:152
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:168
msgid ""
"Line 1: Expense account -1200 -600 = **-1800** (cancelling the total of both "
"bills)"
msgstr ""
"Baris 1: Akun pengeluaran -1200 -600 = **-1800** (membatalkan total kedua "
"tagihan)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:136
msgid ""
"Line 2: Expense account 100 + 50 = **150** (recognizing 1/12 of bill A and "
"bill B)"
msgstr ""
"Baris 2: Akun pengeluaran 100 + 50 = **150** (mengakui 1/12 dari tagihan A "
"dan tagihan B)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:153
msgid ""
"Line 2: Expense account 200 + 100 = **300** (recognizing 2/12 of bill A and "
"bill B)"
msgstr ""
"Baris 2: Akun pengeluaran 200 + 100 = **300** (mengakui 2/12 dari tagihan A "
"dan tagihan B)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:169
msgid ""
"Line 2: Expense account 1100 + 550 = **1650** (recognizing 11/12 of bill A "
"and bill B)"
msgstr ""
"Baris 2: Akun pengeluaran 1100 + 550 = **1650** (mengakui 11/12 dari tagihan "
"A dan tagihan B)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:176
msgid ""
"There is no need to generate entries in December. Indeed, if we do the "
"computation for December, we will have an amount of 0 to be deferred."
msgstr ""
"Tidak perlu membuat entri pada bulan Desember. Memang, jika kita melakukan "
"perhitungan untuk bulan Desember, kita akan memiliki jumlah 0 yang akan "
"ditangguhkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:182
msgid "bill A and bill B"
msgstr "tagihan A dan tagihan B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:186
msgid ""
"Therefore, at the end of December, bills A and B are fully recognized as "
"expense only once in spite of all the created entries thanks to the reversal "
"mechanism."
msgstr ""
"Oleh karena itu, pada akhir Desember, tagihan A dan B sepenuhnya diakui "
"sebagai pengeluaran hanya sekali meskipun ada banyak entri yang dibuat "
"berkat mekanisme pembalikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:3
msgid "Document digitization"
msgstr "Digitalisasi dokumen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:5
msgid ""
"Document digitization refers to the process of converting paper or digital "
"documents into records in a database. Using :abbr:`OCR (optical character "
"recognition)` and artificial intelligence technologies, Odoo reads the "
"content and automatically creates and fills in the record's details. This "
"process is mainly used for vendor bills (or refunds)."
msgstr ""
"Digitalisasi dokumen merujuk pada proses mengonversi dokumen kertas atau "
"digital menjadi catatan dalam database. Menggunakan :abbr:`OCR (optical "
"character recognition)` dan teknologi kecerdasan buatan, Odoo membaca konten "
"dan secara otomatis membuat serta mengisi detail catatan. Proses ini "
"terutama digunakan untuk tagihan vendor (atau pengembalian dana)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:11
msgid ""
"Although less common, this digitization process can also be applied to "
"customer invoices and credit notes. The :ref:`settings <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/configuration>` need to be adjusted accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun kurang umum, proses digitalisasi ini juga dapat diterapkan pada "
"faktur pelanggan dan nota kredit. :ref:`Pengaturan <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/configuration>` perlu disesuaikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:16
msgid ""
"`Test Odoo's invoice digitization <https://www.odoo.com/app/invoice-"
"automation>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Uji digitalisasi faktur Odoo <https://www.odoo.com/app/invoice-automation>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:17
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Vendor Bill Digitization <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"vendor-bill-digitization-7065>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Tutorial Odoo: Digitalisasi Tagihan Vendor <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/vendor-bill-digitization-7065>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:26
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"navigate to the :guilabel:`Digitization` section. Enable "
"the :guilabel:`Document Digitization` option and choose "
"whether :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` should be processed automatically or on "
"demand."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan navigasi "
"ke bagian :guilabel:`Digitalisasi`. Aktifkan opsi :guilabel:`Digitalisasi "
"Dokumen` dan pilih apakah :guilabel:`Tagihan Vendor` harus diproses secara "
"otomatis atau sesuai permintaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:31
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Single Invoice Line Per Tax` option is enabled, only one "
"line is created per tax in the new vendor bill, regardless of the number of "
"lines on it."
msgstr ""
"Jika opsi :guilabel:`Satu Baris Faktur Per Pajak` diaktifkan, hanya satu "
"baris yang dibuat per pajak dalam tagihan vendor baru, terlepas dari jumlah "
"baris di dalamnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:37
msgid "Vendor bills upload"
msgstr "Pengunggahan tagihan vendor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:39
msgid ""
"Vendor bills are :ref:`uploaded manually <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"manual-upload>` or sent to a :ref:`designated email alias <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/email-alias>` to be digitized. They can also "
"be :ref:`automatically posted <accounting/bill-digitization/auto-post-"
"bills>` for selected vendors."
msgstr ""
"Tagihan vendor :ref:`diunggah secara manual <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"manual-upload>` atau dikirim ke :ref:`alias email yang ditentukan "
"<accounting/bill-digitization/email-alias>` untuk didigitalisasi. Tagihan "
"juga dapat :ref:`diposting secara otomatis <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"auto-post-bills>` untuk vendor terpilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:45
msgid ""
"Once the bill is uploaded, the document preview appears on the right side of "
"the screen."
msgstr ""
"Setelah tagihan diunggah, pratinjau dokumen muncul di sisi kanan layar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:48
msgid ":doc:`Vendor bills <../vendor_bills>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Tagihan vendor <../vendor_bills>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:53
msgid "Manual upload"
msgstr "Pengunggahan manual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:55
msgid ""
"In the Accounting dashboard, drag and drop vendor bills into the desired "
"purchase journal or click :guilabel:`Upload` on the purchase journal."
msgstr ""
"Di Dashboard Akuntansi, seret dan lepaskan tagihan vendor ke jurnal "
"pembelian yang diinginkan atau klik :guilabel:`Unggah` pada jurnal pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:61
msgid "Upload via email alias"
msgstr "Unggah melalui alias email"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:63
msgid ""
"Vendor bills can be uploaded via an email alias associated with the relevant "
"journal in two ways:"
msgstr ""
"Tagihan vendor dapat diunggah melalui alias email yang terkait dengan jurnal "
"yang relevan dengan dua cara:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:65
msgid ""
"scanned from a connected scanner configured to send email to an email alias;"
msgstr ""
"dipindai dari pemindai terhubung yang dikonfigurasi untuk mengirim email ke "
"alias email;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:66
msgid "sent directly to an email alias."
msgstr "dikirim langsung ke alias email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:68
msgid ""
"Each PDF attached to the email is automatically converted into a new draft "
"vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"Setiap PDF yang dilampirkan pada email secara otomatis dikonversi menjadi "
"draf tagihan vendor baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:71
msgid ""
"Only PDF and XML formats are processed via an email alias associated with a "
"journal."
msgstr ""
"Hanya format PDF dan XML yang diproses melalui alias email yang terkait "
"dengan jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:72
msgid ""
"JPEG files must be processed via :ref:`email alias in the Documents app "
"<documents/email-aliases>`."
msgstr ""
"File JPEG harus diproses melalui :ref:`alias email di aplikasi Dokumen "
"<documents/email-aliases>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:75
msgid "To add an email alias to a journal, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan alias email ke jurnal, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:77
msgid ""
"Make sure an :doc:`alias domain <../../../websites/website/configuration/"
"domain_names>` has been configured."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :doc:`domain alias <../../../websites/website/configuration/"
"domain_names>` telah dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:79
msgid ""
"The default email alias `vendor-bills@` followed by the alias domain is "
"automatically created and available in the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab "
"of the :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` journal."
msgstr ""
"Alias email default `vendor-bills@` diikuti oleh domain alias secara "
"otomatis dibuat dan tersedia di tab :guilabel:`Pengaturan Lanjutan` dari "
"jurnal :guilabel:`Tagihan Vendor`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:81
msgid ""
"To change a default email alias, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals`, select the corresponding journal, and edit "
"the :guilabel:`Email Alias` in the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah alias email default, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Jurnal`, pilih jurnal yang sesuai, dan edit :guilabel:`Alias "
"Email` di tab :guilabel:`Pengaturan Lanjutan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:84
msgid ""
"Configure the connected scanner to send scanned documents to the email "
"alias, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasikan pemindai yang terhubung untuk mengirim dokumen yang dipindai "
"ke alias email, jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:87
msgid ""
"Alternatively, an :ref:`email alias in the Documents app <documents/email-"
"aliases>` can be used to automatically send vendor bills to "
"the :guilabel:`Finance` :ref:`folder <documents/folders>` (e.g., `inbox-"
"financial@example.odoo.com`)."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai alternatif, :ref:`alias email di aplikasi Dokumen <documents/email-"
"aliases>` dapat digunakan untuk mengirim tagihan vendor secara otomatis "
"ke :guilabel:`Finance` :ref:`folder <documents/folders>` (misalnya, `inbox-"
"financial@example.odoo.com`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:94
msgid "Automatic vendor bill posting"
msgstr "Posting tagihan vendor otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:97
msgid ""
"To use the :guilabel:`Auto-post bills` option, the :guilabel:`Digitize "
"automatically` setting in the :ref:`Document Digitization <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/configuration>` section must be enabled for vendor bills."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan opsi :guilabel:`Auto-post bills`, "
"pengaturan :guilabel:`Digitize automatically` di bagian :ref:`Document "
"Digitization <accounting/bill-digitization/configuration>` harus diaktifkan "
"untuk tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:101
msgid ""
"To automatically post digitized vendor bills for specific vendors, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors` and click the desired "
"vendor. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab of the contact form, select "
"an :guilabel:`Auto-post bills` option in the :guilabel:`Automation` section:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting tagihan vendor yang didigitalisasi secara otomatis untuk "
"vendor tertentu, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Vendors --> Vendors` dan "
"klik vendor yang diinginkan. Di tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi` pada formulir "
"kontak, pilih opsi :guilabel:`Auto-post bills` di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Automation`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Ask after 3 validations without edits`: When the third uploaded "
"bill is confirmed without any edits, an :guilabel:`Autopost Bills` window "
"appears. The following options can be chosen: :guilabel:`Activate auto-"
"validation`, :guilabel:`Ask me later`, or :guilabel:`Never for this vendor`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ask after 3 validations without edits`: Ketika tagihan ketiga "
"yang diunggah dikonfirmasi tanpa ada pengeditan, jendela :guilabel:`Autopost "
"Bills` muncul. Opsi berikut dapat dipilih: :guilabel:`Activate auto-"
"validation`, :guilabel:`Ask me later`, atau :guilabel:`Never for this "
"vendor`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:113
msgid ""
"Since automation is triggered after three validated bills without edits, the "
"contact name must already exist in the database, and each uploaded vendor "
"bill must include a bill date."
msgstr ""
"Karena otomatisasi dipicu setelah tiga tagihan divalidasi tanpa pengeditan, "
"nama kontak harus sudah ada di database, dan setiap tagihan vendor yang "
"diunggah harus menyertakan tanggal tagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:119
msgid "Digitization and data recognition with AI"
msgstr "Digitalisasi dan pengenalan data dengan AI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:121
msgid ""
"Depending on the :ref:`settings <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"configuration>`, documents are either automatically digitized or require "
"manual processing if digitization is set to on-demand only."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada :ref:`pengaturan <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"configuration>`, dokumen didigitalisasi secara otomatis atau memerlukan "
"pemrosesan manual jika digitalisasi diatur hanya berdasarkan permintaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:124
msgid ""
"To manually digitize an :ref:`uploaded document <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/vendor-bills-upload>`, click :guilabel:`Digitize document`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendigitalisasi :ref:`dokumen yang diunggah <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/vendor-bills-upload>` secara manual, klik :guilabel:`Digitize "
"document`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:127
msgid ""
"Once the document has been digitized, a blue banner appears; click :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Refresh`. Review and correct any information "
"uploaded during digitization: click on the related field(s) to edit them, or "
"click :guilabel:`Reload AI data` to refresh the data."
msgstr ""
"Setelah dokumen didigitalisasi, spanduk biru muncul; klik :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Refresh`. Tinjau dan perbaiki informasi apa pun yang "
"diunggah selama digitalisasi: klik pada bidang terkait untuk mengeditnya, "
"atau klik :guilabel:`Reload AI data` untuk menyegarkan data."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:131
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to post the document."
msgstr "Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk memposting dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:134
msgid ""
"Once a document has been digitized, the :guilabel:`Vendor` field remains "
"empty if the vendor doesn't exist in the database. To add it, click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` in the :guilabel:`Vendor` "
"field; the vendor name appears highlighted in the document preview on the "
"right. Click it to open a new vendor form with the name pre-filled."
msgstr ""
"Setelah dokumen didigitalisasi, bidang :guilabel:`Vendor` tetap kosong jika "
"vendor tidak ada di database. Untuk menambahkannya, klik :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(panah bawah)` di bidang :guilabel:`Vendor`; nama vendor "
"muncul disorot dalam pratinjau dokumen di sebelah kanan. Klik untuk membuka "
"formulir vendor baru dengan nama yang telah terisi sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:140
msgid "The following vendor bill fields are recognized by OCR:"
msgstr "Bidang tagihan vendor berikut dikenali oleh OCR:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:142
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`, :guilabel:`Bill Reference`, :guilabel:`Bill "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Payment Reference` (only in the Belgian +++xxx/xxxx/xxxxx++"
"+ format), :guilabel:`Recipient Bank`, :guilabel:`Due Date`, and the "
"currency (in a :doc:`multi-currency <../get_started/multi_currency>` "
"environment and if the currency is activated)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`, :guilabel:`Bill Reference`, :guilabel:`Bill "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Payment Reference` (hanya dalam format +++xxx/xxxx/xxxxx++"
"+ Belgia), :guilabel:`Recipient Bank`, :guilabel:`Due Date`, dan mata uang "
"(dalam lingkungan :doc:`multi-currency <../get_started/multi_currency>` dan "
"jika mata uang diaktifkan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:146
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Invoices Lines` tab: :guilabel:`Product` description/"
"label, :guilabel:`Quantity`, unit :guilabel:`Price`, :guilabel:`Taxes` (if "
"the :ref:`tax is activated <taxes/list_activation>`; this field is not "
"recognized by OCR for the :doc:`Indian localization <../../"
"fiscal_localizations/india>`), :guilabel:`Untaxed Amount`, "
"and :guilabel:`Total`."
msgstr ""
"Dari tab :guilabel:`Invoices Lines`: deskripsi/"
"label :guilabel:`Product`, :guilabel:`Quantity`, :guilabel:`Price` per "
"unit, :guilabel:`Taxes` (jika :ref:`pajak diaktifkan <taxes/"
"list_activation>`; bidang ini tidak dikenali oleh OCR untuk :doc:`lokalisasi "
"India <../../fiscal_localizations/india>`), :guilabel:`Untaxed Amount`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Total`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:155
msgid "Purchase order matching"
msgstr "Pencocokkan purchase order"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:157
msgid ""
"When a digitized vendor bill is recognized by :abbr:`OCR (optical character "
"recognition)`, Odoo searches the database for a matching purchase order. If "
"found, the vendor bill can be manually matched with the existing open "
"purchase order lines."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tagihan vendor yang didigitalisasi dikenali oleh :abbr:`OCR (optical "
"character recognition)`, Odoo mencari database untuk pesanan pembelian yang "
"cocok. Jika ditemukan, tagihan vendor dapat dicocokkan secara manual dengan "
"baris pesanan pembelian terbuka yang ada."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:161
msgid ""
"Once a vendor bill has been :ref:`uploaded <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"vendor-bills-upload>` and :ref:`digitized <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"digitization>`, click the :guilabel:`Purchase matching` smart button to "
"access the :guilabel:`Purchase matching` list view, displaying all purchase "
"order lines linked to the vendor assigned to the vendor bill. Then, select "
"the relevant purchase order lines and the draft vendor bill (shown in grey), "
"and click :guilabel:`Match`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah tagihan vendor :ref:`diunggah <accounting/bill-digitization/vendor-"
"bills-upload>` dan :ref:`didigitalisasi <accounting/bill-digitization/"
"digitization>`, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Purchase matching` untuk "
"mengakses tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Purchase matching`, yang menampilkan "
"semua baris pesanan pembelian yang terkait dengan vendor yang ditetapkan ke "
"tagihan vendor. Kemudian, pilih baris pesanan pembelian yang relevan dan "
"tagihan vendor draft (ditampilkan dalam warna abu-abu), dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Match`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:168
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Purchase Matching` list view, update "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` and :guilabel:`Price` in the purchase order lines, "
"if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Dalam tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Purchase Matching`, "
"perbarui :guilabel:`Quantity` dan :guilabel:`Price` di baris pesanan "
"pembelian, jika perlu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:171
msgid ""
"If there is no existing purchase order related to the vendor of the uploaded "
"vendor bill, a new purchase order can be directly created from the vendor "
"bill lines. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak ada pesanan pembelian yang terkait dengan vendor dari tagihan "
"vendor yang diunggah, pesanan pembelian baru dapat dibuat langsung dari "
"baris tagihan vendor. Untuk melakukannya, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:174
msgid ""
"Once the vendor bill is uploaded, make sure the :guilabel:`Vendor` field is "
"filled in with the correct vendor."
msgstr ""
"Setelah tagihan vendor diunggah, pastikan bidang :guilabel:`Vendor` diisi "
"dengan vendor yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:176
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Purchase matching` smart button, select the draft "
"vendor bill in the list (shown in grey), and click :guilabel:`Add to PO`."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Purchase matching`, pilih draf tagihan vendor "
"dalam daftar (ditampilkan dalam warna abu-abu), dan klik :guilabel:`Add to "
"PO`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:178
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Add to Purchase Order` window, start typing in "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase Order` field and select :guilabel:`Create and edit`."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela :guilabel:`Add to Purchase Order`, mulai mengetik di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Purchase Order` dan pilih :guilabel:`Create and edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:180
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Create Purchase Order` window, select the vendor assigned "
"to the vendor bill, then complete all :ref:`required fields <purchase/"
"manage_deals/create-new-rfq>` and click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela :guilabel:`Create Purchase Order`, pilih vendor yang ditetapkan "
"untuk tagihan vendor, lalu lengkapi semua :ref:`bidang yang diperlukan "
"<purchase/manage_deals/create-new-rfq>` dan klik :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:183
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Purchase Matching` list view, select the relevant purchase "
"order lines and the draft vendor bill (shown in grey), and "
"click :guilabel:`Match`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam tampilan daftar :guilabel:`Purchase Matching`, pilih baris pesanan "
"pembelian yang relevan dan draf tagihan vendor (ditampilkan dalam warna abu-"
"abu), dan klik :guilabel:`Match`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:187
msgid ""
"If any information required for the purchase order fields is missing, "
"click :guilabel:`Save and Close` in the :guilabel:`Create Purchase Order` "
"window. Then, open the Purchase app to fill in the fields and :ref:`confirm "
"the purchase order <purchase/manage_deals/confirm-order>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada informasi yang diperlukan untuk bidang pesanan pembelian yang "
"hilang, klik :guilabel:`Save and Close` di jendela :guilabel:`Create "
"Purchase Order`. Kemudian, buka aplikasi Pembelian untuk mengisi bidang "
"dan :ref:`konfirmasi pesanan pembelian <purchase/manage_deals/confirm-"
"order>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:192
msgid ""
"Electronic vendor bills with embedded XML ensure more accurate and efficient "
"processing."
msgstr ""
"Tagihan vendor elektronik dengan XML tertanam memastikan pemrosesan yang "
"lebih akurat dan efisien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:193
msgid ""
"Alternatively, the :ref:`Auto-complete <accounting/vendor_bills/bill-"
"completion>` feature can transfer information from the purchase order to the "
"vendor bill, without requiring OCR."
msgstr ""
"Atau, fitur :ref:`Auto-complete <accounting/vendor_bills/bill-completion>` "
"dapat mentransfer informasi dari pesanan pembelian ke tagihan vendor, tanpa "
"memerlukan OCR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:201
msgid ""
"The document digitization feature is an In-App Purchase (IAP) service "
"requiring prepaid credits. Digitizing one document uses one credit."
msgstr ""
"Fitur digitalisasi dokumen adalah layanan In-App Purchase (IAP) yang "
"memerlukan kredit prabayar. Mendigitalkan satu dokumen menggunakan satu "
"kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:204
msgid ""
"To buy credits, :ref:`go to the Settings app <iap/buying_credits>` "
"or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Digitization` section, and click :guilabel:`Buy credits`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membeli kredit, :ref:`buka aplikasi Pengaturan <iap/buying_credits>` "
"atau :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, navigasi ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Digitization`, dan klik :guilabel:`Buy credits`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:209
msgid ""
"Odoo Enterprise users with a valid subscription get free credits to test IAP "
"features before purchasing more credits for the database. This includes demo/"
"training databases, educational databases, and one-app-free databases."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna Odoo Enterprise dengan langganan yang valid mendapatkan kredit "
"gratis untuk menguji fitur IAP sebelum membeli lebih banyak kredit untuk "
"database. Ini termasuk database demo/pelatihan, database pendidikan, dan "
"database satu aplikasi gratis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:212
msgid ""
"XML files don't require OCR credits because they contain structured data "
"that can be processed directly, without OCR."
msgstr ""
"File XML tidak memerlukan kredit OCR karena berisi data terstruktur yang "
"dapat diproses langsung, tanpa OCR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:216
msgid ""
"`Odoo In-App Purchase Privacy Policy <https://iap.odoo.com/"
"privacy#header_6>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo In-App Purchase Privacy Policy <https://iap.odoo.com/"
"privacy#header_6>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:3
msgid "Vendor bill sequence"
msgstr "Urutan tagihan vendor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:5
msgid ""
"When confirming a vendor bill, Odoo generates a unique vendor bill reference "
"number. By default, it uses the sequence format `BILL/year/month/"
"incrementing-number` (e.g., `BILL/2025/01/00001`), which restarts from "
"`00001` each year."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengonfirmasi tagihan vendor, Odoo menghasilkan nomor referensi tagihan "
"vendor yang unik. Secara default, menggunakan format urutan `BILL/year/month/"
"incrementing-number` (misalnya, `BILL/2025/01/00001`), yang dimulai ulang "
"dari `00001` setiap tahun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:9
msgid ""
"However, it is possible to :ref:`change the sequence format <accounting/"
"vendor_bills/resequencing>` and its periodicity, and to :ref:`mass-"
"resequence vendor bills <accounting/vendor_bills/mass-resequencing>`."
msgstr ""
"Namun, dimungkinkan untuk :ref:`mengubah format urutan <accounting/"
"vendor_bills/resequencing>` dan periodisitasnya, dan untuk :ref:`mengurutkan "
"ulang tagihan vendor secara massal <accounting/vendor_bills/mass-"
"resequencing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:21
msgid ""
"To customize the default sequence, open the last confirmed vendor bill, "
"click :guilabel:`Reset to Draft`, and edit the vendor bill's reference "
"number."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyesuaikan urutan default, buka tagihan vendor yang terakhir "
"dikonfirmasi, klik :guilabel:`Reset to Draft`, dan edit nomor referensi "
"tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:None
msgid "Editing the reference number of a vendor bill."
msgstr "Mengedit nomor referensi tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:27
msgid ""
"Odoo then explains how the detected format will be applied to all future "
"vendor bills. For example, if the current vendor bill's month is withdrawn, "
"the sequence's periodicity will change to every year instead of every month."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kemudian menjelaskan bagaimana format yang terdeteksi akan diterapkan "
"ke semua tagihan vendor di masa mendatang. Misalnya, jika bulan tagihan "
"vendor saat ini ditarik, periodisitas urutan akan berubah menjadi setiap "
"tahun daripada setiap bulan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:35
msgid ""
"The sequence format can be edited directly when creating the first vendor "
"bill of a given sequence period."
msgstr ""
"Format urutan dapat diedit secara langsung saat membuat tagihan vendor "
"pertama dari periode urutan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:41
msgid "Mass-resequencing vendor bills"
msgstr "Penomoran ulang massal tagihan vendor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:43
msgid ""
"It can be helpful to resequence multiple vendor bill numbers. For example, "
"when importing vendor bills from another accounting system and the reference "
"originates from the previous software, continuity for the current year must "
"be maintained without restarting from the beginning."
msgstr ""
"Akan sangat membantu untuk menomori ulang beberapa nomor tagihan vendor. "
"Misalnya, ketika mengimpor tagihan vendor dari sistem akuntansi lain dan "
"referensi berasal dari perangkat lunak sebelumnya, kontinuitas untuk tahun "
"berjalan harus dipertahankan tanpa memulai dari awal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:50
msgid "Follow these steps to resequence vendor bill numbers:"
msgstr ""
"Ikuti langkah-langkah berikut untuk menomori ulang nomor tagihan vendor:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:53
msgid ""
"In the vendor bills list view, select the vendor bills that need a new "
"sequence."
msgstr ""
"Dalam tampilan daftar tagihan vendor, pilih tagihan vendor yang memerlukan "
"urutan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:67
msgid ""
"To indicate where the sequence change began, the first vendor bill in the "
"new sequence is highlighted in red in the :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` list. "
"This visual marker is permanent and purely informational."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menunjukkan di mana perubahan urutan dimulai, tagihan vendor pertama "
"dalam urutan baru ditandai dengan warna merah dalam "
"daftar :guilabel:`Tagihan Vendor`. Penanda visual ini bersifat permanen dan "
"hanya untuk informasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:70
msgid ""
"If there are any irregularities in the new sequence, such as gaps, "
"cancelled, or deleted entries within the open period, a :guilabel:`Gaps in "
"the sequence` message appears in the :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` journal on the "
"Accounting dashboard. To view more details about the related vendor bill(s), "
"click :guilabel:`Gaps in the sequence`. This visual marker is temporary and "
"will disappear once the entry's accounting date is on or after the lock date."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada ketidakteraturan dalam urutan baru, seperti celah, entri yang "
"dibatalkan, atau dihapus dalam periode terbuka, pesan :guilabel:`Celah dalam "
"urutan` muncul di jurnal :guilabel:`Tagihan Vendor` pada Dashboard "
"Akuntansi. Untuk melihat detail lebih lanjut tentang tagihan vendor terkait, "
"klik :guilabel:`Celah dalam urutan`. Penanda visual ini bersifat sementara "
"dan akan hilang setelah tanggal akuntansi entri berada pada atau setelah "
"tanggal kunci."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/sequence.rst:81
msgid ""
"When the range is invalid. For example, if the :guilabel:`Bill Date` doesn't "
"align with the date in the new sequence, such as using a 2024 sequence (BILL/"
"2024/MM/XXXX) for an vendor bill dated in 2025."
msgstr ""
"Ketika rentang tidak valid. Misalnya, jika :guilabel:`Tanggal Tagihan` tidak "
"sesuai dengan tanggal dalam urutan baru, seperti menggunakan urutan 2024 "
"(BILL/2024/MM/XXXX) untuk tagihan vendor yang bertanggal tahun 2025."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:108
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:114
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:117
msgid "Expenses"
msgstr "Pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Approve expenses"
msgstr "Setujui pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo, most users cannot approve expense reports; only users with the "
"necessary access rights or permissions can. This means that a user **must** "
"have at least *Team Approver* rights for the **Expenses** app. Employees "
"with the necessary rights can review expense reports, approve or refuse "
"them, and provide feedback with an integrated :ref:`Refuse Expense <expenses/"
"refuse-report>` communication tool."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, sebagian besar user tidak dapat menyetujui laporan pengeluaran; "
"hanya user dengan hak akses atau izin yang diperlukan yang dapat "
"melakukannya. Ini berarti bahwa user **harus** memiliki setidaknya hak *Team "
"Approver* untuk aplikasi **Pengeluaran**. Karyawan dengan hak yang "
"diperlukan dapat meninjau laporan pengeluaran, menyetujui atau menolaknya, "
"dan memberikan umpan balik dengan alat komunikasi :ref:`Refuse Expense "
"<expenses/refuse-report>` yang terintegrasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:11
msgid ""
"Please refer to the :doc:`access rights documentation </applications/general/"
"users>` to learn more about managing users and their access rights."
msgstr ""
"Silakan merujuk ke :doc:`dokumentasi hak akses </applications/general/"
"users>` untuk mempelajari lebih lanjut tentang mengelola pengguna dan hak "
"akses mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:15
msgid "View expense reports"
msgstr "Lihat laporan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:17
msgid ""
"Users who are able to approve expense reports (typically managers) have "
"an :guilabel:`Expense Reports` main navigation button at the top of the "
"**Expenses** app. This allows managers to view all expense reports they have "
"access rights for. Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense "
"Reports`, to view the :guilabel:`All Reports` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"User yang dapat menyetujui laporan pengeluaran (biasanya manajer) memiliki "
"tombol navigasi utama :guilabel:`Expense Reports` di bagian atas aplikasi "
"**Pengeluaran**. Ini memungkinkan manajer untuk melihat semua laporan "
"pengeluaran yang mereka miliki hak aksesnya. Navigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense Reports`, untuk melihat "
"dashboard :guilabel:`All Reports`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:22
msgid ""
"A list of all expense reports with a status of either :guilabel:`To "
"Submit`, :guilabel:`Submitted`, :guilabel:`Approved`, :guilabel:`Posted`, "
"or :guilabel:`Done` appears. Expense reports with a status "
"of :guilabel:`Refused` are hidden, by default."
msgstr ""
"Daftar semua laporan pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Untuk "
"Dikirim`, :guilabel:`Dikirim`, :guilabel:`Disetujui`, :guilabel:`Diposting`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Selesai` muncul. Laporan pengeluaran dengan "
"status :guilabel:`Ditolak` disembunyikan secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Reports to validate are found on the Reports to Approve page."
msgstr ""
"Laporan yang perlu divalidasi ditemukan di halaman Laporan untuk Disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:30
msgid "Approve expense reports"
msgstr "Setujui laporan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:32
msgid ""
"Expense reports can be approved in two ways: :ref:`individually <expenses/"
"individual>` or :ref:`in bulk <expenses/multiple>`."
msgstr ""
"Laporan pengeluaran dapat disetujui dengan dua cara: :ref:`secara individual "
"<expenses/individual>` atau :ref:`secara massal <expenses/multiple>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:36
msgid "Only reports with a status of :guilabel:`Submitted` can be approved."
msgstr ""
"Hanya laporan dengan status :guilabel:`Submitted` yang dapat disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:38
msgid ""
"It is recommended to display only :guilabel:`Submitted` reports by ticking "
"the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Submitted` filter, in the left column, "
"under the :guilabel:`Status` section."
msgstr ""
"Disarankan untuk menampilkan hanya laporan :guilabel:`Dikirim` dengan "
"mencentang kotak di samping filter :guilabel:`Dikirim`, di kolom kiri, di "
"bawah bagian :guilabel:`Status`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:41
msgid ""
"If a report is **not** able to be approved, the :guilabel:`Approve Report` "
"button **does not** appear on the :guilabel:`All Reports` page."
msgstr ""
"Jika laporan **tidak** dapat disetujui, tombol :guilabel:`Setujui Laporan` "
"**tidak** muncul di halaman :guilabel:`Semua Laporan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:47
msgid "Approve individual reports"
msgstr "Setujui laporan individual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:49
msgid ""
"To approve an individual report, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --"
"> Expense Reports`, and click on an individual report to view the detailed "
"report form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyetujui laporan individual, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> Expense Reports`, dan klik pada laporan individual untuk melihat "
"formulir laporan detail."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:52
msgid ""
"From here, several options are "
"presented: :guilabel:`Approve`,  :guilabel:`Refuse`, and :guilabel:`Reset to "
"draft`. Click :guilabel:`Approve` to approve the report."
msgstr ""
"Dari sini, beberapa opsi disajikan: :guilabel:`Approve`, :guilabel:`Refuse`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Reset to draft`. Klik :guilabel:`Approve` untuk menyetujui "
"laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:0
msgid "An individual expense report that can be approved or refused."
msgstr "Laporan pengeluaran individual yang dapat disetujui atau ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:61
msgid "Approve multiple reports"
msgstr "Setujui beberapa laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:63
msgid ""
"To approve multiple expense reports at once, first navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense Reports` to view a list of "
"expense reports. Next, select the reports to approve by ticking the checkbox "
"next to each report being approved, or tick the checkbox next to "
"the :guilabel:`Employee` column title to select all the reports in the list."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyetujui beberapa laporan pengeluaran sekaligus, pertama navigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Laporan Pengeluaran` untuk "
"melihat daftar laporan pengeluaran. Selanjutnya, pilih laporan yang akan "
"disetujui dengan mencentang kotak di samping setiap laporan yang disetujui, "
"atau centang kotak di samping judul kolom :guilabel:`Karyawan` untuk memilih "
"semua laporan dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:68
msgid "Next, click the :guilabel:`Approve Report` button."
msgstr "Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Setujui Laporan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:0
msgid "Select multiple expense reports at once."
msgstr "Pilih beberapa laporan pengeluaran sekaligus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:74
msgid ""
"Team managers can view all the expense reports for their team members only. "
"While on the :guilabel:`All Reports` page, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` to the right of the search bar, then "
"click :guilabel:`My Team` in the :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Filters` "
"section. This presents all the reports for only the manager's team."
msgstr ""
"Manajer tim dapat melihat semua laporan pengeluaran untuk anggota tim mereka "
"saja. Saat berada di halaman :guilabel:`All Reports`, klik :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` di sebelah kanan bilah pencarian, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`My Team` di bagian :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Filters`. "
"Ini menampilkan semua laporan hanya untuk tim manajer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:82
msgid "Refuse expense reports"
msgstr "Tolak laporan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:84
msgid ""
"Expense reports can **only** be refused on the individual expense report, "
"and **not** from the :guilabel:`All Reports` dashboard. To open an "
"individual expense report, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Expense Reports`, then click on an individual expense report to view the "
"detailed expense report form."
msgstr ""
"Laporan pengeluaran **hanya** dapat ditolak pada laporan pengeluaran "
"individual, dan **bukan** dari dashboard :guilabel:`All Reports`. Untuk "
"membuka laporan pengeluaran individual, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> Expense Reports`, lalu klik pada laporan pengeluaran individual "
"untuk melihat formulir laporan pengeluaran detail."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:89
msgid ""
"If more information is needed, such as a missing receipt, communicate any "
"necessary information requests in the *chatter* of the report form. On the "
"individual expense report, click either :guilabel:`Send message` "
"or :guilabel:`Log note` to open a message text box."
msgstr ""
"Jika informasi lebih lanjut diperlukan, seperti tanda terima yang hilang, "
"sampaikan permintaan informasi yang diperlukan di *chatter* formulir "
"laporan. Pada laporan pengeluaran individual, klik :guilabel:`Send message` "
"atau :guilabel:`Log note` untuk membuka kotak teks pesan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:93
msgid ""
"Type in a message, tagging the proper people, and post it to the *chatter* "
"by clicking :guilabel:`Send` or :guilabel:`Log`, depending on the method of "
"communication. The message is posted in the chatter, and the tagged people "
"are notified via email."
msgstr ""
"Ketik pesan, tandai orang yang tepat, dan posting ke *chatter* dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Send` atau :guilabel:`Log`, tergantung pada metode "
"komunikasi. Pesan diposting di chatter, dan orang yang ditandai akan "
"diberitahu melalui email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:98
msgid ""
"The only people that can be tagged in a message are *followers* of the "
"specific report. To see who is a follower, click the :icon:`fa-user-"
"o` :guilabel:`(Show Followers)` icon to display the followers of the expense "
"report."
msgstr ""
"Satu-satunya orang yang dapat ditandai dalam pesan adalah *followers* dari "
"laporan spesifik. Untuk melihat siapa yang menjadi follower, klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-user-o` :guilabel:`(Show Followers)` untuk menampilkan "
"follower dari laporan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:0
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Send messages in the chatter."
msgstr "Kirim pesan di chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:105
msgid ""
"To refuse an expense report, click :guilabel:`Refuse`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Refuse Expense` pop-up window loads. Enter a brief explanation "
"for the refusal on the :guilabel:`Reason` line, then "
"click :guilabel:`Refuse`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menolak laporan pengeluaran, klik :guilabel:`Refuse`, dan jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Refuse Expense` dimuat. Masukkan penjelasan singkat untuk "
"penolakan pada baris :guilabel:`Reason`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Refuse`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:112
msgid ""
"Once the expense report is refused, the status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Refused`, and the only button that appears is :guilabel:`Reset "
"to Draft`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengeluaran ditolak, status berubah "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Refused`, dan satu-satunya tombol yang muncul "
"adalah :guilabel:`Reset to Draft`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:3
msgid "Expense categories"
msgstr "Kategori pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **Expenses** streamlines the management of expenses. After an "
"employee :doc:`logs their expenses <../expenses/log_expenses>` "
"and :doc:`submits their expense report <../expenses/expense_reports>` in "
"Odoo, expenses are reviewed by management and accounting teams. "
"Once :doc:`approved <../expenses/approve_expenses>`, payments can be "
"processed and :doc:`disbursed back to the employee <../expenses/reimburse>` "
"for reimbursement."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Pengeluaran** menyederhanakan pengelolaan pengeluaran. Setelah "
"seorang karyawan :doc:`mencatat pengeluaran mereka <../expenses/"
"log_expenses>` dan :doc:`mengirimkan laporan pengeluaran mereka <../expenses/"
"expense_reports>` di Odoo, pengeluaran ditinjau oleh tim manajemen dan "
"akuntansi. Setelah :doc:`disetujui <../expenses/approve_expenses>`, "
"pembayaran dapat diproses dan :doc:`dibayarkan kembali kepada karyawan <../"
"expenses/reimburse>` untuk penggantian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:12
msgid "`Odoo Expenses: product page <https://www.odoo.com/app/expenses>`_"
msgstr "`Odoo Expenses: halaman produk <https://www.odoo.com/app/expenses>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:15
msgid "View expense categories"
msgstr "Lihat kategori pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:17
msgid ""
"The first step to track expenses is configuring the different types of "
"expenses for the company (managed as *expense categories* in Odoo). Each "
"category can be as specific or generalized as needed. Additionally, expense "
"categories can be configured to repay expenses at either a set price or "
"allow for specific prices to be reported."
msgstr ""
"Langkah pertama untuk melacak pengeluaran adalah mengonfigurasi berbagai "
"jenis pengeluaran untuk perusahaan (dikelola sebagai *kategori pengeluaran* "
"di Odoo). Setiap kategori dapat dibuat sespesifik atau seumum yang "
"diperlukan. Selain itu, kategori pengeluaran dapat dikonfigurasi untuk "
"mengganti pengeluaran dengan harga yang ditetapkan atau mengizinkan harga "
"tertentu untuk dilaporkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:22
msgid ""
"To view the default expense categories, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat kategori pengeluaran default, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> Kategori "
"Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:25
msgid ""
"The default expense categories allow creating expenses for common expenses, "
"including communication costs, meals, gifts, miles driven, and other travel "
"expenses. For expenses outside these default categories, the general "
"expenses category, :guilabel:`EXP_GEN`, is used. If a company has specific "
"expenses it commonly reimburses, and wants to track them "
"separately, :ref:`new expense categories can be made <expenses/new-"
"category>` or existing expense categories can be modified."
msgstr ""
"Kategori pengeluaran default memungkinkan pembuatan pengeluaran untuk "
"pengeluaran umum, termasuk biaya komunikasi, makanan, hadiah, jarak tempuh "
"berkendara, dan pengeluaran perjalanan lainnya. Untuk pengeluaran di luar "
"kategori default ini, kategori pengeluaran umum, :guilabel:`EXP_GEN`, "
"digunakan. Jika perusahaan memiliki pengeluaran tertentu yang biasa diganti "
"dan ingin melacaknya secara terpisah, :ref:`kategori pengeluaran baru dapat "
"dibuat <expenses/new-category>` atau kategori pengeluaran yang ada dapat "
"dimodifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:None
msgid "Set expense costs on products."
msgstr "Tetapkan biaya pengeluaran pada produk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:37
msgid "Create new expense categories"
msgstr "Buat kategori pengeluaran baru"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:39
msgid ""
"Some companies require more expense categories than the **Expenses** app "
"includes. For these situations, new expense categories can be created."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa perusahaan memerlukan lebih banyak kategori pengeluaran daripada "
"yang disertakan aplikasi **Pengeluaran**. Untuk situasi ini, kategori "
"pengeluaran baru dapat dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:43
msgid ""
"A company that trains car mechanics allows its technicians to purchase $500 "
"worth of tools in a year. In this situation, the company creates a new "
"category called `TOOLS` to track all tool expenses."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan yang melatih mekanik mobil mengizinkan teknisinya membeli alat "
"senilai $500 dalam setahun. Dalam situasi ini, perusahaan membuat kategori "
"baru bernama `TOOLS` untuk melacak semua pengeluaran alat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:47
msgid ""
"To create a new expense category, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --"
"> Configuration --> Expense Categories`. Click :guilabel:`New`, and a new "
"expense category form loads."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat kategori pengeluaran baru, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> Kategori "
"Pengeluaran`. Klik :guilabel:`Baru`, dan formulir kategori pengeluaran baru "
"akan dimuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:51
msgid ""
"Expense *categories* are managed like *products* in Odoo. The expense "
"category form follows the standard product form in Odoo, and the information "
"entered is similar. Expense *products* are referred to as expense "
"*categories* throughout this document since the main menu refers to these "
"as :guilabel:`Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""
"Kategori *pengeluaran* dikelola seperti *produk* di Odoo. Formulir kategori "
"pengeluaran mengikuti formulir produk standar di Odoo, dan informasi yang "
"dimasukkan serupa. *Produk* pengeluaran disebut sebagai *kategori* "
"pengeluaran di seluruh dokumen ini karena menu utama menyebutnya "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Kategori Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:56
msgid "Enter the following fields on the form:"
msgstr "Masukkan kolom berikut pada formulir:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Name`: Enter a name for the category that is short and "
"informative."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nama Produk`: Masukkan nama untuk kategori yang singkat dan "
"informatif."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cost`: If employees can report the actual cost of an expense, and "
"are reimbursed the reported amount, leave the field set to `0.00`. If the "
"expense should **always** be reimbursed for a specific price, enter the "
"amount in this field. If a price is entered, a :guilabel:`per` field appears "
"with :guilabel:`Unit` populated by default. :guilabel:`Unit` covers most "
"expense situations, but if the reimbursement is based on weight, length, "
"volume, etc., choose the corresponding type of unit using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Biaya`: Jika karyawan dapat melaporkan biaya aktual dari "
"pengeluaran, dan diganti sesuai jumlah yang dilaporkan, biarkan kolom diatur "
"ke `0.00`. Jika pengeluaran harus **selalu** diganti dengan harga tertentu, "
"masukkan jumlahnya di kolom ini. Jika harga dimasukkan, "
"kolom :guilabel:`per` akan muncul dengan :guilabel:`Unit` yang diisi secara "
"default. :guilabel:`Unit` mencakup sebagian besar situasi pengeluaran, "
"tetapi jika penggantian didasarkan pada berat, panjang, volume, dll., pilih "
"jenis unit yang sesuai menggunakan menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:67
msgid ""
"Here are some examples for when to set a specific :guilabel:`Cost` on a "
"product vs. leaving the :guilabel:`Cost` at `0.00`:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut adalah beberapa contoh kapan harus menetapkan :guilabel:`Cost` "
"tertentu pada produk versus membiarkan :guilabel:`Cost` pada `0.00`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:70
msgid ""
"**Meals**: If employees are reimbursed for their full meal cost, set "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` to `0.00`. When an employee logs an expense for a meal, "
"they enter the actual amount of the bill and are reimbursed for that amount. "
"An expense for a meal costing $95.23 would equal a reimbursement of $95.23."
msgstr ""
"**Makanan**: Jika karyawan diganti untuk biaya makanan penuh mereka, "
"atur :guilabel:`Biaya` ke `0.00`. Ketika karyawan mencatat pengeluaran untuk "
"makanan, mereka memasukkan jumlah tagihan yang sebenarnya dan diganti untuk "
"jumlah tersebut. Pengeluaran untuk makanan seharga $95,23 akan sama dengan "
"penggantian sebesar $95,23."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:74
msgid ""
"**Mileage**: If employees receive a flat rate for each mile they drive, set "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` to `1.00`. When an employee logs an expense for the "
"miles driven, they enter the number of miles driven in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` field, and are reimbursed $1.00 per mile they "
"reported. An expense for 100 miles would equal a reimbursement of $100.00."
msgstr ""
"**Jarak Tempuh**: Jika karyawan menerima tarif tetap untuk setiap mil yang "
"mereka kendarai, atur :guilabel:`Biaya` ke `1.00`. Ketika karyawan mencatat "
"pengeluaran untuk jarak yang ditempuh, mereka memasukkan jumlah mil yang "
"ditempuh di kolom :guilabel:`Kuantitas`, dan diganti $1,00 per mil yang "
"dilaporkan. Pengeluaran untuk 100 mil akan sama dengan penggantian sebesar "
"$100,00."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:78
msgid ""
"**Per Diem**: If employees receive a daily flat rate of $125.00 when "
"traveling, set the :guilabel:`Cost` to `125.00`. An expense for three days "
"of per diem costs (meals, incidentals, taxi fare, etc.) would equal a "
"reimbursement of $375.00."
msgstr ""
"**Per Diem**: Jika karyawan menerima tarif harian tetap sebesar $125,00 saat "
"bepergian, atur :guilabel:`Biaya` ke `125.00`. Pengeluaran untuk tiga hari "
"biaya per diem (makanan, kebutuhan insidental, ongkos taksi, dll.) akan sama "
"dengan penggantian sebesar $375,00."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:83
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cost` field is always visible on the expense category form, "
"but the :guilabel:`Sales Price` field is *only* visible if "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Price` is selected under the :guilabel:`Re-Invoice "
"Expenses` section. Otherwise, the :guilabel:`Sales Price` field is hidden."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Cost` selalu terlihat pada formulir kategori pengeluaran, "
"tetapi kolom :guilabel:`Sales Price` *hanya* terlihat jika :guilabel:`Sales "
"Price` dipilih di bagian :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Expenses`. Jika tidak, "
"kolom :guilabel:`Sales Price` akan disembunyikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reference`: Enter a short reference for the expense, such as "
"`FOOD` or `TRAVEL`. This reference is used when :ref:`emailing expenses "
"<expenses/email_expense>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Referensi`: Masukkan referensi singkat untuk pengeluaran, seperti "
"`FOOD` atau `TRAVEL`. Referensi ini digunakan saat :ref:`mengirim email "
"pengeluaran <expenses/email_expense>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Category`: Using the drop-down menu, select the category the "
"expense falls under. It is recommended to use the default category `All / "
"Expenses`, but another category can be selected if the accounting department "
"requires it."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategori`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih kategori di mana "
"pengeluaran termasuk. Disarankan untuk menggunakan kategori default `All / "
"Expenses`, tetapi kategori lain dapat dipilih jika departemen akuntansi "
"memerlukannya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If in a multi-company database, select the company the "
"expense category applies to. If the expense category applies to *all* "
"companies, leave this field blank."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`: Jika dalam database multi-perusahaan, pilih "
"perusahaan yang berlaku untuk kategori pengeluaran. Jika kategori "
"pengeluaran berlaku untuk *semua* perusahaan, biarkan kolom ini kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Guideline`: Enter some rules or important information for the "
"expense category. This is visible in the :guilabel:`Note` column on "
"the :guilabel:`Expense Category` dashboard."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pedoman`: Masukkan beberapa aturan atau informasi penting untuk "
"kategori pengeluaran. Ini terlihat di kolom :guilabel:`Catatan` pada "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Kategori Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:99
msgid ""
"An expense category for expenses related to working from home may have "
"a :guilabel:`Name` of `WFH`, and the :guilabel:`Guideline` may say "
"`Monitors, Chairs, & Other Home Working Costs`."
msgstr ""
"Kategori pengeluaran untuk pengeluaran terkait bekerja dari rumah mungkin "
"memiliki :guilabel:`Nama` `WFH`, dan :guilabel:`Pedoman` mungkin mengatakan "
"`Monitor, Kursi, & Biaya Bekerja dari Rumah Lainnya`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expense Account`: If using the Odoo **Accounting** app, select "
"the :abbr:`CoA (Chart of Accounts)` the expense should be logged on."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Akun Pengeluaran`: Jika menggunakan aplikasi **Akuntansi** Odoo, "
"pilih :abbr:`Bagan Akun (Chart of Accounts)` tempat pengeluaran harus "
"dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:106
msgid ""
"Check with the accounting department to determine the correct account to "
"reference in this field as it affects various reports."
msgstr ""
"Periksa dengan departemen akuntansi untuk menentukan akun yang tepat untuk "
"dirujuk di bidang ini karena mempengaruhi berbagai laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Purchase Taxes` and :guilabel:`Sales Taxes`: Enter the default "
"taxes that are applied when purchasing or selling this product, if "
"applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pajak Pembelian` dan :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan`: Masukkan pajak "
"default yang diterapkan saat membeli atau menjual produk ini, jika berlaku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:113
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` field is **only** visible if the **Sales** app "
"is installed, and either the :guilabel:`At cost` or :guilabel:`Sales Price` "
"options are selected in the :ref:`invoicing section <expenses/invoicing>`."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan` **hanya** terlihat jika aplikasi "
"**Penjualan** diinstal, dan salah satu opsi :guilabel:`Sesuai biaya` "
"atau :guilabel:`Harga Jual` dipilih di :ref:`bagian penagihan <expenses/"
"invoicing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:118
msgid ""
"It is considered good practice to use a tax that is configured "
"with :ref:`Tax Included in Price <taxes/included-in-price>`. Taxes are "
"automatically configured if these are set."
msgstr ""
"Dianggap sebagai praktik yang baik untuk menggunakan pajak yang "
"dikonfigurasi dengan :ref:`Pajak Termasuk dalam Harga <taxes/included-in-"
"price>`. Pajak secara otomatis dikonfigurasi jika ini diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:None
msgid "A new expense category for tools."
msgstr "Kategori pengeluaran baru untuk alat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:127
msgid "Invoicing section"
msgstr "Bagian Penagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:129
msgid ""
"If the **Sales** app is installed, an invoicing section is visible. This "
"section allows the expense to be reinvoiced to customers on sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Jika aplikasi **Penjualan** diinstal, bagian penagihan akan terlihat. Bagian "
"ini memungkinkan pengeluaran untuk ditagihkan kembali kepada pelanggan pada "
"pesanan penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:132
msgid ""
"If the expense **cannot** be reinvoiced, enable the :guilabel:`No` option. "
"If the expense category **can** be reinvoiced, enable either of these "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran **tidak dapat** ditagihkan kembali, aktifkan "
"opsi :guilabel:`Tidak`. Jika kategori pengeluaran **dapat** ditagihkan "
"kembali, aktifkan salah satu dari opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:135
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At cost`: Select this option to have the expense item reinvoiced "
"at the price set in the :guilabel:`Cost` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sesuai biaya`: Pilih opsi ini untuk memiliki item pengeluaran "
"ditagihkan kembali pada harga yang ditetapkan di bidang :guilabel:`Biaya`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Price`: Select this option to have the expense item "
"reinvoiced at the sales price. When enabled, a :guilabel:`Sales Price` field "
"appears beneath the :guilabel:`Product Name` field. Enter the sales price in "
"the new field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Harga Jual`: Pilih opsi ini untuk memiliki item pengeluaran "
"ditagihkan kembali pada harga jual. Saat diaktifkan, bidang :guilabel:`Harga "
"Jual` muncul di bawah bidang :guilabel:`Nama Produk`. Masukkan harga jual di "
"bidang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:142
msgid ""
"A heating and cooling company offers at-home repairs on the furnaces and "
"central air units it sells. Their technicians are sub-contracted, and use "
"their own vans, tools, and parts."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan pemanas dan pendingin menawarkan perbaikan di rumah untuk "
"tungku dan unit pendingin sentral yang dijualnya. Teknisi mereka dikontrak, "
"dan menggunakan van, alat, dan suku cadang mereka sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:145
msgid ""
"As part of their contracts, technicians are reimbursed for their travel. "
"They receive $1.00 for every mile they drive. Additionally, the customer "
"must pay for the travel as part of their service contract. The customer pays "
"$1.50 for every mile the technician drives to their location."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai bagian dari kontrak mereka, teknisi mendapat penggantian untuk "
"perjalanan mereka. Mereka menerima $1,00 untuk setiap mil yang mereka "
"tempuh. Selain itu, pelanggan harus membayar untuk perjalanan sebagai bagian "
"dari kontrak layanan mereka. Pelanggan membayar $1,50 untuk setiap mil yang "
"ditempuh teknisi ke lokasi mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:149
msgid ""
"To configure this expense, the :guilabel:`Sales Price` is set to `1.50` and "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` is set to `1.00`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi pengeluaran ini, :guilabel:`Harga Jual` diatur ke "
"`1.50` dan :guilabel:`Biaya` diatur ke `1.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_categories.rst:0
msgid "An expense category to reinvoice customers and pay technicians."
msgstr ""
"Kategori pengeluaran untuk menagihkan kembali pelanggan dan membayar teknisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:3
msgid "Expense reports"
msgstr "Laporan biaya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:5
msgid ""
"When expenses are ready to submit (such as at the end of a business trip, or "
"once a month), an *expense report* needs to be created. Open the main "
"**Expenses** app dashboard, which displays the :guilabel:`My Expenses` "
"dashboard, by default. Alternatively, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> My Expenses --> My Expenses`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pengeluaran siap untuk dikirim (seperti di akhir perjalanan bisnis, "
"atau sebulan sekali), *laporan pengeluaran* perlu dibuat. Buka dashboard "
"utama aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, yang menampilkan "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya`, secara default. Atau, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> Pengeluaran "
"Saya`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:10
msgid ""
"All expenses are color-coded by status. Any expense with a status "
"of :guilabel:`To Report` (expenses that still need to be added to an expense "
"report) appears in blue text. For all other statuses (:guilabel:`To "
"Submit`, :guilabel:`Submitted`, and :guilabel:`Approved`) the text appears "
"in black."
msgstr ""
"Semua pengeluaran diberi kode warna berdasarkan status. Pengeluaran apa pun "
"dengan status :guilabel:`Untuk Dilaporkan` (pengeluaran yang masih perlu "
"ditambahkan ke laporan pengeluaran) muncul dalam teks biru. Untuk semua "
"status lainnya (:guilabel:`Untuk Dikirim`, :guilabel:`Dikirim`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Disetujui`), teksnya muncul dalam warna hitam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:17
msgid "Create expense reports"
msgstr "Buat laporan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:19
msgid ""
"First, select the desired expense to be added to the report on "
"the :guilabel:`My Expenses` dashboard by ticking the checkbox next to each "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pilih pengeluaran yang diinginkan untuk ditambahkan ke laporan pada "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya` dengan mencentang kotak centang di "
"sebelah setiap entri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:None
msgid "Select the expenses to submit, then create the report."
msgstr "Pilih pengeluaran yang akan dikirim, lalu buat laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:26
msgid ""
"Any expense can be selected from the :guilabel:`My Expenses` list, except "
"for expenses with a status of :guilabel:`Approved`."
msgstr ""
"Setiap pengeluaran dapat dipilih dari daftar :guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya`, "
"kecuali pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Disetujui`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:29
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Create Report` button is visible as long as there is a "
"minimum of one expense on the list with a status of either :guilabel:`To "
"Report` or :guilabel:`To Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Tombol :guilabel:`Buat Laporan` terlihat selama ada minimal satu pengeluaran "
"dalam daftar dengan status :guilabel:`Untuk Dilaporkan` "
"atau :guilabel:`Untuk Diajukan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:32
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Create Report` button is clicked, all expenses with a "
"status of :guilabel:`To Submit` that are *not* currently on another expense "
"report appear in the newly-created expense report."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tombol :guilabel:`Buat Laporan` diklik, semua pengeluaran dengan "
"status :guilabel:`Untuk Dikirim` yang *tidak* sedang berada di laporan "
"pengeluaran lain akan muncul di laporan pengeluaran yang baru dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:36
msgid ""
"If all expenses on the :guilabel:`My Expenses` report are already associated "
"with another expense report, an :guilabel:`Invalid Operation` pop-up window "
"appears, stating :guilabel:`You have no expenses to report.`"
msgstr ""
"Jika semua pengeluaran pada laporan :guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya` sudah "
"terkait dengan laporan pengeluaran lain, jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Operasi "
"Tidak Valid` muncul, yang menyatakan :guilabel:`Anda tidak memiliki "
"pengeluaran untuk dilaporkan.`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:40
msgid ""
"Once the expenses have been selected, click the :guilabel:`Create Report` "
"button."
msgstr "Setelah pengeluaran dipilih, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat Laporan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:43
msgid ""
"Another way to add *all* expenses that are not currently on an expense "
"report is to click the :guilabel:`Create Report` button, *without* selecting "
"any expenses, and Odoo automatically selects all expenses with a status "
"of :guilabel:`To Submit` that are not already on a report."
msgstr ""
"Cara lain untuk menambahkan *semua* pengeluaran yang saat ini tidak ada di "
"laporan pengeluaran adalah dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Buat Laporan`, "
"*tanpa* memilih pengeluaran apa pun, dan Odoo secara otomatis akan memilih "
"semua pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Untuk Dikirim` yang belum ada di "
"laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:47
msgid ""
"The new report loads with all the expenses listed in the :guilabel:`Expense` "
"tab. If there is a receipt attached to an individual expense, a :icon:`fa-"
"paperclip` :guilabel:`(paperclip)` icon appears on the expense line."
msgstr ""
"Laporan baru dimuat dengan semua pengeluaran yang terdaftar di "
"tab :guilabel:`Pengeluaran`. Jika ada tanda terima yang dilampirkan pada "
"pengeluaran individual, ikon :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(penjepit "
"kertas)` muncul pada baris pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:51
msgid ""
"When the report is created, the date range for the expenses appears as "
"the :guilabel:`Expense Report Summary`, by default. It is recommended to "
"edit this field with a brief summary for each report to help keep expenses "
"organized. Enter a description for the expense report, such as `Client Trip "
"NYC`, or `Office Supplies for Presentation`, in the :guilabel:`Expense "
"Report Summary` field."
msgstr ""
"Ketika laporan dibuat, rentang tanggal untuk pengeluaran muncul "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Ringkasan Laporan Pengeluaran`, secara default. "
"Disarankan untuk mengedit bidang ini dengan ringkasan singkat untuk setiap "
"laporan guna membantu menjaga pengeluaran tetap terorganisir. Masukkan "
"deskripsi untuk laporan pengeluaran, seperti `Perjalanan Klien NYC`, atau "
"`Perlengkapan Kantor untuk Presentasi`, di bidang :guilabel:`Ringkasan "
"Laporan Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:56
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Employee`, :guilabel:`Paid By`, and :guilabel:`Company` "
"fields are populated with the information listed on the individual expenses."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Karyawan`, :guilabel:`Dibayar Oleh`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Perusahaan` diisi dengan informasi yang tercantum pada "
"pengeluaran individual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:60
msgid "The :guilabel:`Company` field only appears in a multi-company database."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Perusahaan` hanya muncul di database multi-perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:62
msgid ""
"Next, select a :guilabel:`Manager` from the drop-down menu to assign a "
"manager to review the report. If needed, update the :guilabel:`Journal` "
"field using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pilih :guilabel:`Manajer` dari menu drop-down untuk menetapkan "
"manajer untuk meninjau laporan. Jika diperlukan, perbarui "
"bidang :guilabel:`Jurnal` menggunakan menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:None
msgid "Enter a short description and select a manager for the report."
msgstr "Masukkan deskripsi singkat dan pilih manajer untuk laporan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:68
msgid ""
"If some expenses are missing from the report, they can still be added from "
"this report form. To do so, click :guilabel:`Add a line` at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Expense` tab."
msgstr ""
"Jika beberapa pengeluaran tidak ada dalam laporan, pengeluaran tersebut "
"masih dapat ditambahkan dari formulir laporan ini. Untuk melakukannya, "
"klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` di bagian bawah tab :guilabel:`Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:71
msgid ""
"An :guilabel:`Add: Expense Lines` pop-up window appears, displaying all the "
"available expenses (with a :guilabel:`To Submit` status) that can be added "
"to the report. If a new expense needs to be added that does **not** appear "
"on the list, click :guilabel:`New` to :doc:`create a new expense <../"
"expenses/log_expenses>` and add it to the report."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Tambah: Baris Pengeluaran` muncul, menampilkan "
"semua pengeluaran yang tersedia (dengan status :guilabel:`Untuk Dikirim`) "
"yang dapat ditambahkan ke laporan. Jika pengeluaran baru perlu ditambahkan "
"yang **tidak** muncul di daftar, klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk :doc:`membuat "
"pengeluaran baru <../expenses/log_expenses>` dan menambahkannya ke laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:76
msgid ""
"Tick the checkbox next to each expense being added, then "
"click :guilabel:`Select`. Doing so closes the pop-up window, and the items "
"now appear on the report."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak centang di sebelah setiap pengeluaran yang ditambahkan, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Pilih`. Dengan melakukan ini, jendela pop-up akan tertutup, "
"dan item sekarang muncul di laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:80
msgid "Expense reports can be created in one of two ways:"
msgstr "Laporan pengeluaran dapat dibuat dengan salah satu dari dua cara:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:82
msgid ""
"Navigate to the main :menuselection:`Expenses app` dashboard (also "
"accessible, via :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> My "
"Expenses`) and click :guilabel:`Create Report`."
msgstr ""
"Navigasikan ke dashboard utama :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran` (juga "
"dapat diakses melalui :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran "
"Saya --> Pengeluaran Saya`) dan klik :guilabel:`Buat Laporan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:85
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> My Reports` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pengeluaran Saya --> "
"Laporan Saya` dan klik :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:91
msgid "Submit expense reports"
msgstr "Ajukan laporan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:93
msgid ""
"When an expense report is completed, the next step is to submit the report "
"to a manager for approval. To view all expense reports, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> My Reports`. Open the "
"specific report from the list of expense reports."
msgstr ""
"Ketika laporan pengeluaran selesai, langkah selanjutnya adalah mengajukan "
"laporan ke manajer untuk persetujuan. Untuk melihat semua laporan "
"pengeluaran, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> "
"Pengeluaran Saya --> Laporan Saya`. Buka laporan spesifik dari daftar "
"laporan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:98
msgid ""
"Reports must be individually submitted, and **cannot** be submitted in "
"batches."
msgstr ""
"Laporan harus diajukan satu per satu, dan **tidak dapat** diajukan secara "
"batch."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:100
msgid ""
"If the list is large, grouping the results by status may be helpful, since "
"only reports with a :guilabel:`To Submit` status need to be submitted; "
"reports with an :guilabel:`Approved` or :guilabel:`Submitted` status do not. "
"The :guilabel:`To Submit` expenses are identifiable by the :guilabel:`To "
"Submit` status, and by the blue text, while all other expense text appears "
"in black."
msgstr ""
"Jika daftarnya besar, mengelompokkan hasil berdasarkan status mungkin "
"bermanfaat, karena hanya laporan dengan status :guilabel:`Untuk Dikirim` "
"yang perlu dikirim; laporan dengan status :guilabel:`Disetujui` "
"atau :guilabel:`Dikirim` tidak perlu. Pengeluaran :guilabel:`Untuk Dikirim` "
"dapat diidentifikasi dengan status :guilabel:`Untuk Dikirim`, dan dengan "
"teks biru, sedangkan semua teks pengeluaran lainnya muncul dalam warna hitam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:None
msgid "Submit the report to the manager."
msgstr "Ajukan laporan ke manajer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:108
msgid ""
"Click on a report to open it, then click :guilabel:`Submit To Manager`. "
"After submitting a report, the next step is for management to review "
"and :doc:`approve it <approve_expenses>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada laporan untuk membukanya, lalu klik :guilabel:`Kirim ke Manajer`. "
"Setelah mengirimkan laporan, langkah berikutnya adalah bagi manajemen untuk "
"meninjau dan :doc:`menyetujuinya <approve_expenses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:112
msgid ""
"The status of each report is shown in the :guilabel:`Status` column. If "
"the :guilabel:`Status` column is not visible, click the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(additional options)` icon at the end of the row, and "
"tick the checkbox beside :guilabel:`Status` from the resulting drop-down "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"Status setiap laporan ditampilkan di kolom :guilabel:`Status`. Jika "
"kolom :guilabel:`Status` tidak terlihat, klik ikon :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(opsi tambahan)` di akhir baris, dan centang kotak "
"centang di samping :guilabel:`Status` dari menu drop-down yang muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:118
msgid ""
":doc:`Approving <../expenses/approve_expenses>` expenses, :doc:`posting <../"
"expenses/post_expenses>` expenses, and :doc:`reimbursing <../expenses/"
"reimburse>` expenses are **only** for users with the "
"appropriate :doc:`access rights </applications/general/users>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Menyetujui <../expenses/approve_expenses>` "
"pengeluaran, :doc:`memposting <../expenses/post_expenses>` pengeluaran, "
"dan :doc:`mengganti <../expenses/reimburse>` pengeluaran **hanya** untuk "
"pengguna dengan :doc:`hak akses </applications/general/users>` yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:3
msgid "Expenses analysis"
msgstr "Analisis pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:5
msgid ""
"It is important for companies to track expenses so they have an "
"understanding of their expenses and can identify trends. Expense reporting "
"allows for detailed information, such as which expense categories are "
"reimbursed the most, which employees incur the most expenses, and if there "
"are any periods of time that tend to incur more expenses than others."
msgstr ""
"Penting bagi perusahaan untuk melacak pengeluaran sehingga mereka memiliki "
"pemahaman tentang pengeluaran mereka dan dapat mengidentifikasi tren. "
"Pelaporan pengeluaran memungkinkan informasi terperinci, seperti kategori "
"pengeluaran mana yang paling banyak diganti, karyawan mana yang mengeluarkan "
"pengeluaran terbanyak, dan apakah ada periode waktu yang cenderung "
"mengeluarkan lebih banyak pengeluaran daripada yang lain."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:11
msgid "View expense analysis report"
msgstr "Lihat laporan analisis pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:13
msgid ""
"To view the default *Expenses Analysis* report, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Reporting --> Expenses Analysis`. "
"The :guilabel:`Expenses Analysis` report displays all expenses for the "
"current year, in a stacked bar chart, grouped by month."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat laporan *Analisis Pengeluaran* default, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pelaporan --> Analisis "
"Pengeluaran`. Laporan :guilabel:`Analisis Pengeluaran` menampilkan semua "
"pengeluaran untuk tahun berjalan, dalam bagan batang bertumpuk, "
"dikelompokkan berdasarkan bulan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:None
msgid "The default stacked bar chart for annual expenses, grouped by month."
msgstr ""
"Bagan batang bertumpuk default untuk pengeluaran tahunan, dikelompokkan "
"berdasarkan bulan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:21
msgid "View expenses by employee"
msgstr "Lihat pengeluaran berdasarkan karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:23
msgid ""
"It is possible to view the data so that the total cost of expenses *by "
"employee* is visible. To view the report in this way, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Reporting --> Expenses Analysis`. Next, "
"click the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` icon to view the data in "
"a pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk melihat data sehingga total biaya pengeluaran "
"*berdasarkan karyawan* terlihat. Untuk melihat laporan dengan cara ini, "
"navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pelaporan --> "
"Analisis Pengeluaran`. Selanjutnya, klik ikon :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` untuk melihat data dalam tabel pivot."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:28
msgid ""
"This presents the data with the *employees* populating the rows, and the "
"*total monthly expenses* populate the columns. Next, click :icon:`fa-minus-"
"square-o` :guilabel:`Total` at the top of the monthly columns to hide the "
"individual monthly totals, and present only the *total* amount for the year."
msgstr ""
"Ini menampilkan data dengan *karyawan* mengisi baris, dan *total pengeluaran "
"bulanan* mengisi kolom. Selanjutnya, klik :icon:`fa-minus-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Total` di bagian atas kolom bulanan untuk menyembunyikan total "
"bulanan individual, dan hanya menampilkan jumlah *total* untuk tahun "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:63
msgid ""
"To present the data in either ascending or descending total, click "
"the :guilabel:`Total In Currency` box, and the information is organized "
"first in ascending order, starting with the smallest amount. "
"Click :guilabel:`Total In Currency` again to reverse the order, and present "
"the highest amount first."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan data dalam urutan total menaik atau menurun, klik "
"kotak :guilabel:`Total In Currency`, dan informasi diatur pertama dalam "
"urutan menaik, dimulai dengan jumlah terkecil. Klik :guilabel:`Total In "
"Currency` lagi untuk membalikkan urutan, dan menampilkan jumlah tertinggi "
"terlebih dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:39
msgid ""
"In this example it can be determined that :guilabel:`Mike Smith` has the "
"highest amount of expenses, totaling :guilabel:`4,216.44`. This is almost "
"seven times higher than :guilabel:`Ronnie Hart`, who has the second highest "
"expenses, with a total of :guilabel:`644.74`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam contoh ini dapat ditentukan bahwa :guilabel:`Mike Smith` memiliki "
"jumlah pengeluaran tertinggi, dengan total :guilabel:`4,216.44`. Ini hampir "
"tujuh kali lebih tinggi dari :guilabel:`Ronnie Hart`, yang memiliki "
"pengeluaran tertinggi kedua, dengan total :guilabel:`644.74`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:0
msgid ""
"A pivot table with the information shown by employee, in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Tabel pivot dengan informasi yang ditampilkan berdasarkan karyawan, dalam "
"urutan menurun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:47
msgid "View expenses by category"
msgstr "Lihat pengeluaran berdasarkan kategori"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:49
msgid ""
"It is possible to view the data so that the total cost of expenses *by "
"category* is visible. To view the report in this way, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Reporting --> Expenses Analysis`. Next, "
"click the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` icon to view the data in "
"a pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk melihat data sehingga total biaya pengeluaran "
"*berdasarkan kategori* terlihat. Untuk melihat laporan dengan cara ini, "
"navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Pelaporan --> "
"Analisis Pengeluaran`. Selanjutnya, klik ikon :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` untuk melihat data dalam tabel pivot."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:54
msgid ""
"This presents the data with the *employees* populating the rows, and the "
"*total monthly expenses* populate the columns. Next, click :icon:`fa-minus-"
"square-o` :guilabel:`Total` at the top of the employees column. "
"Click :icon:`fa-plus-square` :guilabel:`Total` that appears in place "
"of :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` :guilabel:`Total`, revealing a drop-down menu "
"of options. Click :guilabel:`Category`, and the expense categories now "
"populate the rows."
msgstr ""
"Ini menampilkan data dengan *karyawan* mengisi baris, dan *total pengeluaran "
"bulanan* mengisi kolom. Selanjutnya, klik :icon:`fa-minus-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Total` di bagian atas kolom karyawan. Klik :icon:`fa-plus-"
"square` :guilabel:`Total` yang muncul menggantikan :icon:`fa-minus-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Total`, menampilkan menu drop-down pilihan. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Category`, dan kategori pengeluaran sekarang mengisi baris."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:60
msgid ""
"Next, click :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` :guilabel:`Total` at the top of the "
"months column to hide the individual months, and only show the annual total "
"for each category."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :icon:`fa-minus-square-o` :guilabel:`Total` di bagian atas "
"kolom bulan untuk menyembunyikan bulan individual, dan hanya menampilkan "
"total tahunan untuk setiap kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:69
msgid ""
"In this example, it can be determined that the company spent the most on "
"travel expenses, with the expense category :guilabel:`[TRANS & ACC] Travel & "
"Accommodation` incurring :guilabel:`2,940.00` of expenses for the year. The "
"company reimbursed mileage the least, with only :guilabel:`229.69` "
"in :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage` expenses."
msgstr ""
"Dalam contoh ini, dapat ditentukan bahwa perusahaan menghabiskan paling "
"banyak untuk biaya perjalanan, dengan kategori pengeluaran :guilabel:`[TRANS "
"& ACC] Travel & Accommodation` menimbulkan :guilabel:`2,940.00` pengeluaran "
"untuk tahun tersebut. Perusahaan mengganti jarak tempuh paling sedikit, "
"dengan hanya :guilabel:`229.69` dalam pengeluaran :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expenses_analysis.rst:0
msgid ""
"A pivot table with the information shown by catrgory in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Tabel pivot dengan informasi yang ditampilkan berdasarkan kategori dalam "
"urutan menurun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Log expenses"
msgstr "Catat pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"Before expenses can be reimbursed, each individual expense needs to be "
"logged in the database. Expense records can be created in four different "
"ways: :ref:`manually enter an expense record <expenses/"
"manual_expense>`, :ref:`upload a receipt <expenses/"
"upload_receipt>`, :ref:`drag and drop <expenses/drag_and_drop>` a receipt "
"onto the **Expenses** app dashboard, or :ref:`email a receipt <expenses/"
"email_expense>` to a preconfigured email address."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum pengeluaran dapat diganti, setiap pengeluaran individual perlu "
"dicatat dalam database. Catatan pengeluaran dapat dibuat dengan empat cara "
"berbeda: :ref:`memasukkan catatan pengeluaran secara manual <expenses/"
"manual_expense>`, :ref:`mengunggah tanda terima <expenses/"
"upload_receipt>`, :ref:`drag and drop <expenses/drag_and_drop>` tanda terima "
"ke dashboard aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, atau :ref:`mengirim email tanda "
"terima <expenses/email_expense>` ke alamat email yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:14
msgid "Manually enter expenses"
msgstr "Masukkan pengeluaran secara manual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:16
msgid ""
"To record a new expense, open the **Expenses** app, which displays "
"the :guilabel:`My Expenses` page, by default."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat pengeluaran baru, buka aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, yang "
"menampilkan halaman :guilabel:`My Expenses`, secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:20
msgid ""
"This view can also be accessed at any time by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> My Expenses`."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan ini juga dapat diakses kapan saja dengan menavigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> My Expenses --> My Expenses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:23
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button and fill out the following fields on the "
"blank expense form that loads:"
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`New` dan isi bidang berikut pada formulir pengeluaran "
"kosong yang dimuat:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description`: Enter a short description for the expense. This "
"should be concise and informative, such as `Lunch with client` or `Hotel for "
"trade show`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Description`: Masukkan deskripsi singkat untuk pengeluaran. Ini "
"harus ringkas dan informatif, seperti `Makan siang dengan klien` atau `Hotel "
"untuk pameran dagang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:28
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Category`: Using the drop-down menu, select the :doc:`expense "
"category <expense_categories>` that most closely corresponds to the expense."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Category`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih :doc:`kategori "
"pengeluaran <expense_categories>` yang paling sesuai dengan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Total`: Enter the total amount paid for the expense in one of two "
"ways:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Total`: Masukkan jumlah total yang dibayarkan untuk pengeluaran "
"dengan salah satu dari dua cara:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:32
msgid ""
"If the expense is for a single item/expense, and the category selected was "
"for a single item, enter the cost in the :guilabel:`Total` field "
"(the :guilabel:`Quantity` field is hidden)."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran untuk satu item/pengeluaran, dan kategori yang dipilih "
"adalah untuk satu item, masukkan biaya di kolom :guilabel:`Total` "
"(kolom :guilabel:`Quantity` disembunyikan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:34
msgid ""
"If the expense is for multiples of the same item/expense with a fixed price, "
"the :guilabel:`Unit Price` is displayed. Enter the number of units in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` field, and the total cost is automatically updated "
"with the correct total. The total cost appears below "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity`."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran adalah untuk beberapa item/pengeluaran yang sama dengan "
"harga tetap, :guilabel:`Unit Price` ditampilkan. Masukkan jumlah unit dalam "
"bidang :guilabel:`Quantity`, dan total biaya secara otomatis diperbarui "
"dengan total yang benar. Total biaya muncul di bawah :guilabel:`Quantity`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:40
msgid ""
"An employee received one dollar for each mile driven for work. "
"The :guilabel:`Category` is :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`. The :guilabel:`Unit "
"Price` is automatically populated with `$1.00`, which is the cost *per mile* "
"configured for the expense :guilabel:`Category` :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`. "
"The :guilabel:`Quantity` is set to `48`, which is the *number of miles "
"driven*, and the total is calculated to `$48.00`."
msgstr ""
"Seorang karyawan menerima satu dolar untuk setiap mil yang dikendarai untuk "
"pekerjaan. :guilabel:`Category` adalah :guilabel:`[MIL] "
"Mileage`. :guilabel:`Unit Price` secara otomatis diisi dengan `$1.00`, yang "
"merupakan biaya *per mil* yang dikonfigurasi untuk :guilabel:`Category` "
"pengeluaran :guilabel:`[MIL] Mileage`. :guilabel:`Quantity` diatur ke `48`, "
"yang merupakan *jumlah mil yang dikendarai*, dan totalnya dihitung menjadi "
"`$48.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Included Taxes`: If taxes were configured on the selected expense "
"category, the tax percentage and amount appear automatically after entering "
"either the :guilabel:`Total` or the :guilabel:`Quantity`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pajak yang Disertakan`: Jika pajak dikonfigurasi pada kategori "
"pengeluaran yang dipilih, persentase pajak dan jumlahnya muncul secara "
"otomatis setelah memasukkan :guilabel:`Total` atau :guilabel:`Kuantitas`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:51
msgid ""
"When a tax is configured on an expense category, the :guilabel:`Included "
"Taxes` value updates in real time, as the :guilabel:`Total` "
"or :guilabel:`Quantity` is updated."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pajak dikonfigurasi pada kategori pengeluaran, "
"nilai :guilabel:`Included Taxes` diperbarui secara real time, "
"saat :guilabel:`Total` atau :guilabel:`Quantity` diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee`: Using the drop-down menu, select the employee "
"associated with the expense."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Karyawan`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih karyawan yang "
"terkait dengan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paid By`: Click the radio button to indicate who paid for the "
"expense and should be reimbursed. Select either :guilabel:`Employee (to "
"reimburse)` or :guilabel:`Company`. Depending on the expense category "
"selected, this field may not appear."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dibayar Oleh`: Klik tombol radio untuk menunjukkan siapa yang "
"membayar pengeluaran dan harus diganti. Pilih :guilabel:`Karyawan (untuk "
"diganti)` atau :guilabel:`Perusahaan`. Tergantung pada kategori pengeluaran "
"yang dipilih, bidang ini mungkin tidak muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expense Date`: Using the calendar popover window that appears "
"when this field is clicked, enter the date the expense was incurred."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Expense Date`: Menggunakan jendela popover kalender yang muncul "
"saat kolom ini diklik, masukkan tanggal pengeluaran terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account`: If the selected expense :guilabel:`Category` has a "
"specific account linked to it, that account appears in "
"the :guilabel:`Account` field. If no account is specified, the default "
"`600000 Expenses` account populates this field. If a different account is "
"desired, select the account the expense should be logged in."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Akun`: Jika :guilabel:`Kategori` pengeluaran yang dipilih "
"memiliki akun tertentu yang terhubung dengannya, akun tersebut muncul di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Akun`. Jika tidak ada akun yang ditentukan, akun default "
"`600000 Expenses` mengisi bidang ini. Jika akun yang berbeda diinginkan, "
"pilih akun tempat pengeluaran harus dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice`: If the expense should be paid for by a "
"customer and the selected :guilabel:`Category` allows for reinvoicing of "
"expenses, select the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` and customer to be invoiced "
"for the expense using the drop-down menu. All sales orders in the drop-down "
"menu list both the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`, as well as the company the "
"sales order is written for. After the expense is saved, the customer name "
"disappears, and only the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is visible on the expense."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Ditagih Ulang`: Jika pengeluaran harus dibayar "
"oleh pelanggan dan :guilabel:`Kategori` yang dipilih memungkinkan penagihan "
"ulang pengeluaran, pilih :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` dan pelanggan yang akan "
"ditagih untuk pengeluaran menggunakan menu drop-down. Semua sales order "
"dalam menu drop-down mencantumkan :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`, serta perusahaan "
"tempat sales order ditulis. Setelah pengeluaran disimpan, nama pelanggan "
"hilang, dan hanya :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang terlihat pada pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:72
msgid ""
"A customer wishes to have an on-site meeting for the design and installation "
"of a custom building, and agrees to pay for all expenses associated with the "
"meeting, including travel, hotel, and meals for the traveling employees. All "
"expenses tied to that meeting would indicate the sales order for the custom "
"building (which also references the customer) as the :guilabel:`Customer to "
"Reinvoice`."
msgstr ""
"Seorang pelanggan ingin mengadakan pertemuan di lokasi untuk desain dan "
"instalasi bangunan khusus, dan setuju untuk membayar semua biaya yang "
"terkait dengan pertemuan, termasuk perjalanan, hotel, dan makan untuk "
"karyawan yang bepergian. Semua pengeluaran yang terkait dengan pertemuan "
"tersebut akan menunjukkan sales order untuk bangunan khusus (yang juga "
"mereferensikan pelanggan) sebagai :guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Ditagih Ulang`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`: Select the account the expense should be "
"written against from the drop-down menu for "
"either :guilabel:`Projects`, :guilabel:`Departments`, or both. Multiple "
"accounts can be listed for each category, if needed. Adjust the percentage "
"for each analytic account by typing in the percentage value next to each "
"account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`: Pilih akun yang harus ditulisi "
"pengeluaran dari menu drop-down "
"untuk :guilabel:`Projects`, :guilabel:`Departments`, atau keduanya. Beberapa "
"akun dapat didaftarkan untuk setiap kategori, jika diperlukan. Sesuaikan "
"persentase untuk setiap akun analitik dengan mengetik nilai persentase di "
"sebelah setiap akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If in a multi-company database, select the company the "
"expense should be filed for using the drop-down menu. The current company "
"automatically populates this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`: Jika dalam database multi-perusahaan, pilih "
"perusahaan tempat pengeluaran harus diajukan menggunakan menu drop-down. "
"Perusahaan saat ini secara otomatis mengisi bidang ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Notes...`: If any notes are needed to clarify the expense, enter "
"them in the notes field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Notes...`: Jika ada catatan yang diperlukan untuk menjelaskan "
"pengeluaran, masukkan di kolom catatan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:None
msgid "A filled in expense form for a client lunch."
msgstr "Formulir pengeluaran yang telah diisi untuk makan siang klien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:91
msgid "Attach receipts"
msgstr "Lampirkan tanda terima"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:93
msgid ""
"After the expense record is created, the next step is to attach a receipt. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and a file explorer appears. "
"Navigate to the receipt to be attached, and click :guilabel:`Open`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah catatan pengeluaran dibuat, langkah selanjutnya adalah melampirkan "
"tanda terima. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Attach Receipt`, dan file explorer akan "
"muncul. Navigasi ke tanda terima yang akan dilampirkan, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Open`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:97
msgid ""
"The new receipt is recorded in the *chatter*, and the number of receipts "
"appears next to the :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(paperclip)` icon. "
"Multiple receipts can be attached to an individual expense record, as needed."
msgstr ""
"Tanda terima baru dicatat di *chatter*, dan jumlah tanda terima muncul di "
"sebelah ikon :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(paperclip)`. Beberapa tanda "
"terima dapat dilampirkan ke catatan pengeluaran individual, sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:104
msgid "Upload expenses"
msgstr "Unggah pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:106
msgid ""
"It is possible to have expense records created automatically "
"by :ref:`uploading a PDF receipt <expenses/upload>`. To utilize this "
"feature, a setting must be enabled, and :abbr:`IAP (in-app purchases)` "
"credits must be purchased."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk membuat catatan pengeluaran secara otomatis "
"dengan :ref:`mengunggah tanda terima PDF <expenses/upload>`. Untuk "
"menggunakan fitur ini, pengaturan harus diaktifkan, dan kredit :abbr:`IAP "
"(in-app purchases)` harus dibeli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:113
msgid "Digitalization settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan digitalisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:115
msgid ""
"To enable receipt scanning, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and tick the checkbox beside "
"the :guilabel:`Expense Digitization (OCR)` option. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. When enabled, additional options appear. Click on "
"the corresponding radio button to select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan pemindaian tanda terima, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan "
"centang kotak di samping opsi :guilabel:`Digitalisasi Pengeluaran (OCR)`. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`. Ketika diaktifkan, opsi tambahan akan "
"muncul. Klik tombol radio yang sesuai untuk memilih salah satu opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Do not digitize`: Disables receipt digitization but does *not* "
"uninstall the related digitization module."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jangan digitalisasi`: Menonaktifkan digitalisasi tanda terima "
"tetapi *tidak* menghapus instalasi modul digitalisasi terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Digitize on demand only`: Only digitizes receipts when requested. "
"A :guilabel:`Digitize document` button appears on expense records. When "
"clicked, the receipt is scanned and the expense record is updated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Digitalisasi hanya sesuai permintaan`: Hanya mendigitalisasi "
"tanda terima saat diminta. Tombol :guilabel:`Digitalisasi dokumen` muncul "
"pada catatan pengeluaran. Saat diklik, tanda terima dipindai dan catatan "
"pengeluaran diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:125
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Digitize automatically`: Automatically digitizes all receipts "
"when they are uploaded."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Digitalisasi secara otomatis`: Secara otomatis mendigitalisasi "
"semua tanda terima saat diunggah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:127
msgid ""
"Beneath these options are two additional links. Click the :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Manage Service & Buy Credits` link to view account details "
"and settings, and purchase credits for receipt digitization. Click "
"the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`View My Services` link to view a list "
"of all current services, and their remaining credit balances."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah opsi ini terdapat dua tautan tambahan. Klik tautan :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Kelola Layanan & Beli Kredit` untuk melihat detail dan "
"pengaturan akun, dan membeli kredit untuk digitalisasi tanda terima. Klik "
"tautan :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Lihat Layanan Saya` untuk melihat "
"daftar semua layanan saat ini, dan saldo kredit yang tersisa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:132
msgid ""
"For more information on document digitization and :abbr:`IAPs (in-app "
"purchases)`, refer to the :doc:`In-app purchase (IAP) <../../essentials/"
"in_app_purchase>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang digitalisasi dokumen dan :abbr:`IAP "
"(pembelian dalam aplikasi)`, lihat dokumentasi :doc:`Pembelian dalam "
"aplikasi (IAP) <../../essentials/in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:136
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Expense Digitization (OCR)` option is enabled, a "
"necessary module is installed, so receipts can be scanned. Disabling this "
"option uninstalls the module."
msgstr ""
"Ketika opsi :guilabel:`Digitalisasi Pengeluaran (OCR)` diaktifkan, modul "
"yang diperlukan akan diinstal sehingga tanda terima dapat dipindai. "
"Menonaktifkan opsi ini akan menghapus instalasi modul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:139
msgid ""
"If, at some point, there is a desire to temporarily stop digitizing "
"receipts, select the :guilabel:`Do not digitize` option. The reason this "
"option is available is so the module is not uninstalled, allowing for "
"digitization to be enabled in the future by selecting one of the other two "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Jika, pada suatu saat, ada keinginan untuk sementara menghentikan "
"digitalisasi tanda terima, pilih opsi :guilabel:`Jangan digitalisasi`. "
"Alasan opsi ini tersedia adalah agar modul tidak dihapus instalasinya, "
"sehingga memungkinkan digitalisasi diaktifkan di masa mendatang dengan "
"memilih salah satu dari dua opsi lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:147
msgid "Upload receipts"
msgstr "Unggah tanda terima"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:149
msgid ""
"Open the :guilabel:`Expenses app`, and from the :guilabel:`My Expenses` "
"dashboard, click :guilabel:`Upload`, and a file explorer appears. Navigate "
"to the desired receipt, select it, then click :guilabel:`Open`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :guilabel:`aplikasi Pengeluaran`, dan dari "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Pengeluaran Saya`, klik :guilabel:`Unggah`, maka file "
"explorer akan muncul. Navigasikan ke tanda terima yang diinginkan, pilih, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`Buka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:153
msgid ""
"The receipt is scanned, and a new expense record is created. "
"The :guilabel:`Expense Date` field is populated with today's date, along "
"with any other fields based on the scanned data, such as "
"the :guilabel:`Total`."
msgstr ""
"Tanda terima dipindai, dan catatan pengeluaran baru dibuat. "
"Bidang :guilabel:`Tanggal Pengeluaran` diisi dengan tanggal hari ini, "
"bersama dengan bidang lainnya berdasarkan data yang dipindai, "
"seperti :guilabel:`Total`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:157
msgid ""
"Click on the new entry to open the individual expense form, and make any "
"changes, if needed. The scanned receipt appears in the *chatter*."
msgstr ""
"Klik entri baru untuk membuka formulir pengeluaran individual, dan lakukan "
"perubahan jika diperlukan. Tanda terima yang dipindai muncul di *chatter*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:163
msgid "Drag and drop an expense"
msgstr "Seret dan lepas pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:165
msgid ""
"If :ref:`digitalization is enabled <expenses/digitalization>`, drag and drop "
"a receipt onto the **Expenses** app dashboard. The receipt is scanned and "
"appears by itself on the :guilabel:`Generate Expenses` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Jika :ref:`digitalisasi diaktifkan <expenses/digitalization>`, seret dan "
"lepas tanda terima ke dashboard aplikasi **Pengeluaran**. Tanda terima "
"dipindai dan muncul sendiri di dashboard :guilabel:`Generate Expenses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:169
msgid ""
"Click on the expense record, and modify the details as needed. After changes "
"are made, return to the :guilabel:`My Expenses` dashboard, and the expense "
"now appears in the list."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada catatan pengeluaran, dan modifikasi detail sesuai kebutuhan. "
"Setelah perubahan dilakukan, kembali ke dashboard :guilabel:`My Expenses`, "
"dan pengeluaran sekarang muncul dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:175
msgid "Email expenses"
msgstr "Email pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:177
msgid ""
"Instead of individually creating each expense in the **Expenses** app, "
"expenses can be automatically created by sending an email to an email alias."
msgstr ""
"Alih-alih membuat setiap pengeluaran secara individual di aplikasi "
"**Pengeluaran**, pengeluaran dapat dibuat secara otomatis dengan mengirim "
"email ke alias email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:181
msgid ""
"For security purposes, only authenticated employee emails are accepted by "
"Odoo when creating an expense from an email. To confirm an authenticated "
"employee email address, go to the employee card in "
"the :menuselection:`Employees app`, and refer to the :guilabel:`Work Email` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk tujuan keamanan, hanya email karyawan yang terautentikasi yang "
"diterima oleh Odoo saat membuat pengeluaran dari email. Untuk mengonfirmasi "
"alamat email karyawan yang terautentikasi, buka kartu karyawan "
"di :menuselection:`aplikasi Karyawan`, dan lihat field :guilabel:`Email "
"Kerja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:0
msgid "Create the domain alias by clicking the link."
msgstr "Buat alias domain dengan mengklik tautan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:188
msgid ""
"To do so, an email alias must first be configured. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Ensure the "
"checkbox beside :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` is ticked. The default email "
"alias is *expense@(domain).com*. Change the email alias by entering the "
"desired email in the field to the right of :guilabel:`Alias`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, alias email harus dikonfigurasi terlebih dahulu. "
"Navigasikan ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`. Pastikan kotak di samping :guilabel:`Email Masuk` dicentang. "
"Alias email default adalah *expense@(domain).com*. Ubah alias email dengan "
"memasukkan email yang diinginkan di bidang di sebelah "
"kanan :guilabel:`Alias`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:194
msgid ""
"If the domain alias needs to be set up, :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Setup your domain alias` appears beneath "
"the :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` checkbox, instead of the email address field."
msgstr ""
"Jika alias domain perlu disiapkan, :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Siapkan "
"alias domain Anda` muncul di bawah kotak centang :guilabel:`Email Masuk`, "
"bukan bidang alamat email."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:198
msgid ""
"Refer to the :doc:`/applications/websites/website/configuration/"
"domain_names` documentation for setup instructions and more information."
msgstr ""
"Lihat dokumentasi :doc:`/applications/websites/website/configuration/"
"domain_names` untuk instruksi pengaturan dan informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:201
msgid ""
"Once the domain alias is configured, the email address field is visible "
"beneath the :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` feature on the :guilabel:`Settings` "
"page in the **Expenses** app."
msgstr ""
"Setelah alias domain dikonfigurasi, bidang alamat email terlihat di bawah "
"fitur :guilabel:`Email Masuk` pada halaman :guilabel:`Pengaturan` di "
"aplikasi **Pengeluaran**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:204
msgid ""
"Once the email address has been entered, emails can be sent to that alias to "
"create new expenses, without having to be in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Setelah alamat email dimasukkan, email dapat dikirim ke alias tersebut untuk "
"membuat pengeluaran baru, tanpa harus berada di database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:207
msgid ""
"To submit an expense via email, create a new email, and enter the product's "
"*reference* code (if available) and the amount of the expense as the subject "
"of the email. Next, attach the receipt to the email. Odoo creates the "
"expense by taking the information in the email subject, and combining it "
"with the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirimkan pengeluaran melalui email, buat email baru, dan masukkan "
"kode *referensi* produk (jika tersedia) dan jumlah pengeluaran sebagai "
"subjek email. Selanjutnya, lampirkan tanda terima ke email. Odoo membuat "
"pengeluaran dengan mengambil informasi dalam subjek email, dan "
"menggabungkannya dengan tanda terima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:213
msgid ""
"To check an expense category's reference code, go "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`. "
"Reference codes are listed in the :guilabel:`Reference` column."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa kode referensi kategori pengeluaran, "
"buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> Kategori "
"Pengeluaran`. Kode referensi terdaftar di kolom :guilabel:`Referensi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:217
msgid ""
"To add a reference code to an expense category, click on the category to "
"open the expense category form. Enter the reference code in "
"the :guilabel:`Reference` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan kode referensi ke kategori pengeluaran, klik pada kategori "
"untuk membuka formulir kategori pengeluaran. Masukkan kode referensi di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Referensi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:0
msgid "Reference categories displayed in the main Expense Categories view."
msgstr ""
"Kategori referensi ditampilkan dalam tampilan Kategori Pengeluaran utama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:224
msgid ""
"If submitting an expense, via email, for a $25.00 meal during a work trip, "
"the email subject would be `FOOD $25.00`."
msgstr ""
"Jika mengajukan pengeluaran, melalui email, untuk makanan senilai $25,00 "
"selama perjalanan kerja, subjek email akan menjadi `FOOD $25.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:227
msgid "Explanation:"
msgstr "Penjelasan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:229
msgid "The :guilabel:`Reference` for the expense category `Meals` is `FOOD`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Referensi` untuk kategori pengeluaran `Meals` adalah `FOOD`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:230
msgid "The :guilabel:`Cost` for the expense is `$25.00`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Biaya` untuk pengeluaran adalah `$25.00`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Post expenses"
msgstr "Post pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"Once an expense report is :doc:`approved <../expenses/approve_expenses>`, "
"the next step is to post the expenses to the proper accounting journal."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengeluaran :doc:`disetujui <../expenses/approve_expenses>`, "
"langkah selanjutnya adalah memposting pengeluaran ke jurnal akuntansi yang "
"sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:9
msgid ""
"To post expense reports to an accounting journal, the user **must** have the "
"following :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/access_rights>`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting laporan pengeluaran ke jurnal akuntansi, user **harus** "
"memiliki :doc:`hak akses <../../general/users/access_rights>` berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:12
msgid "Accounting: *Accountant* or *Adviser*"
msgstr "Akuntansi: *Akuntan* atau *Penasihat*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:13
msgid "Expenses: *Manager*"
msgstr "Pengeluaran: *Manajer*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:15
msgid ""
"Only expense reports with an *Approved* status can post the expenses to a "
"journal. To view all expense reports, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses "
"app --> Expense Reports`. Next, to view **only** approved expense reports "
"that need to be posted, adjust the filters on the left side so only "
"the :guilabel:`Approved` checkbox is ticked."
msgstr ""
"Hanya laporan pengeluaran dengan status *Disetujui* yang dapat memposting "
"pengeluaran ke jurnal. Untuk melihat semua laporan pengeluaran, navigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Laporan Pengeluaran`. "
"Selanjutnya, untuk melihat **hanya** laporan pengeluaran yang disetujui yang "
"perlu diposting, sesuaikan filter di sisi kiri sehingga hanya kotak "
"centang :guilabel:`Disetujui` yang dicentang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:None
msgid ""
"View reports to post by clicking on expense reports, then reports to post."
msgstr ""
"Lihat laporan untuk diposting dengan mengklik laporan pengeluaran, lalu "
"laporan untuk diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:24
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`All Reports` dashboard displays all expense reports "
"that are not :guilabel:`Refused`."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard :guilabel:`Semua Laporan` default menampilkan semua laporan "
"pengeluaran yang tidak :guilabel:`Ditolak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:27
msgid ""
"Expense reports can be posted to accounting journals in two "
"ways: :ref:`individually <expenses/post-individual>` or :ref:`in bulk "
"<expenses/post-multiple>`."
msgstr ""
"Laporan pengeluaran dapat diposting ke jurnal akuntansi dengan dua "
"cara: :ref:`secara individual <expenses/post-individual>` atau :ref:`secara "
"massal <expenses/post-multiple>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:33
msgid "Post individual reports"
msgstr "Posting laporan individual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:35
msgid ""
"To post an individual report, navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> "
"Expense Reports`, and click on an individual report with "
"a :guilabel:`Status` of :guilabel:`Approved`, to view the report form. In "
"this view, several options are presented: :guilabel:`Post Journal "
"Entries`, :guilabel:`Report In Next Payslip`, :guilabel:`Refuse`, "
"or :guilabel:`Reset to Draft`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting laporan individual, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Pengeluaran --> Laporan Pengeluaran`, dan klik laporan individual "
"dengan :guilabel:`Status` :guilabel:`Disetujui`, untuk melihat formulir "
"laporan. Dalam tampilan ini, beberapa opsi disajikan: :guilabel:`Posting "
"Entri Jurnal`, :guilabel:`Laporkan Dalam Slip Gaji "
"Berikutnya`, :guilabel:`Tolak`, atau :guilabel:`Reset ke Draft`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:40
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries` to post the report. The accounting "
"journal the expenses are posted to is listed in the :guilabel:`Journal` "
"field of the expense report."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Posting Entri Jurnal` untuk memposting laporan. Jurnal "
"akuntansi tempat pengeluaran diposting tercantum di field :guilabel:`Jurnal` "
"pada laporan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:43
msgid ""
"After posting the expenses to an accounting journal, a :guilabel:`Journal "
"Entry` smart button appears at the top of the screen. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Journal Entry` smart button, and the details for the journal "
"entry appear, with a status of :guilabel:`Posted`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memposting pengeluaran ke jurnal akuntansi, tombol "
"pintar :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal` muncul di bagian atas layar. Klik tombol "
"pintar :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal`, dan detail untuk entri jurnal muncul, "
"dengan status :guilabel:`Diposting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:None
msgid "A single expense report to be approved."
msgstr "Satu laporan pengeluaran untuk disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:53
msgid "Post multiple reports"
msgstr "Posting beberapa laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:55
msgid ""
"To post multiple expense reports at once, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense Reports` to view a list of "
"expense reports. Next, select the reports to approve by ticking the checkbox "
"next to each report being approved."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memposting beberapa laporan pengeluaran sekaligus, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Laporan Pengeluaran` untuk "
"melihat daftar laporan pengeluaran. Selanjutnya, pilih laporan yang akan "
"disetujui dengan mencentang kotak centang di sebelah setiap laporan yang "
"disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:60
msgid ""
"Only expense reports with a status of :guilabel:`Approved` are able to post "
"the expenses to an accounting journal. If an expense report is selected that "
"**cannot** be posted, such as an unapproved report, or the report has "
"already been posted to a journal, the :guilabel:`Post Entries` button is "
"**not** visible."
msgstr ""
"Hanya laporan pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Disetujui` yang dapat "
"memposting pengeluaran ke jurnal akuntansi. Jika laporan pengeluaran yang "
"dipilih **tidak dapat** diposting, seperti laporan yang belum disetujui, "
"atau laporan telah diposting ke jurnal, tombol :guilabel:`Posting Entri` "
"**tidak** terlihat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:66
msgid ""
"To select **only** approved expense reports, adjust the filters on the left "
"side, so that only the :guilabel:`Approved` checkbox is ticked. Next, tick "
"the checkbox next to the :guilabel:`Employee` column title to select **all** "
"the :guilabel:`Approved` reports in the list at once."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih **hanya** laporan pengeluaran yang disetujui, sesuaikan filter "
"di sisi kiri, sehingga hanya kotak centang :guilabel:`Disetujui` yang "
"dicentang. Selanjutnya, centang kotak centang di sebelah judul "
"kolom :guilabel:`Karyawan` untuk memilih **semua** "
"laporan :guilabel:`Disetujui` dalam daftar sekaligus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:71
msgid "Next, click the :guilabel:`Post Entries` button."
msgstr "Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Posting Entri`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/post_expenses.rst:None
msgid ""
"Post multiple reports at a time from the Expense Reports view, with the "
"Approved filter."
msgstr ""
"Posting beberapa laporan sekaligus dari tampilan Laporan Pengeluaran, dengan "
"filter Disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:3
msgid "Reimburse employees"
msgstr "Reimburse karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:5
msgid ""
"After an expense report is :doc:`posted to an accounting journal <../"
"expenses/post_expenses>`, the next step is to reimburse the employee. "
"Employees can be reimbursed via cash, check, or direct deposit in three ways:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengeluaran :doc:`diposting ke jurnal akuntansi <../expenses/"
"post_expenses>`, langkah selanjutnya adalah mengganti biaya karyawan. "
"Karyawan dapat diganti biayanya melalui uang tunai, cek, atau transfer "
"langsung dengan tiga cara:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`Individually <expenses/reimburse-single>`: Each individual expense "
"report is reimbursed separately."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Secara individual <expenses/reimburse-single>`: Setiap laporan "
"pengeluaran diganti biayanya secara terpisah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:11
msgid ""
":ref:`In bulk <expenses/reimburse-bulk>`: Multiple expense reports are "
"reimbursed in a single payment."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Secara massal <expenses/reimburse-bulk>`: Beberapa laporan pengeluaran "
"diganti biayanya dalam satu pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`In the employee's payslip <expenses/reimburse-payslip>`: Expense "
"reports are reimbursed directly in the employee's payslip."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dalam slip gaji karyawan <expenses/reimburse-payslip>`: Laporan "
"pengeluaran diganti biayanya langsung dalam slip gaji karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:19
msgid "Reimbursement settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan penggantian biaya"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:21
msgid ""
"Reimbursements can be paid via a paycheck, check, cash, or bank transfer "
"(usually referred to as direct deposit). To set up payment options, first "
"configure the various settings by navigating to :menuselection:`Expenses app "
"--> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Penggantian biaya dapat dibayar melalui gaji, cek, uang tunai, atau transfer "
"bank (biasanya disebut sebagai transfer langsung). Untuk mengatur opsi "
"pembayaran, pertama konfigurasikan berbagai pengaturan dengan menavigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:25
msgid ""
"To reimburse employees for expenses :ref:`in their paychecks <expenses/"
"reimburse-payslip>`, tick the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Reimburse in "
"Payslip` option in the :guilabel:`Expenses` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mereimburse karyawan atas pengeluaran :ref:`di slip gaji mereka "
"<expenses/reimburse-payslip>`, centang kotak di samping "
"opsi :guilabel:`Reimburse di Slip Gaji` di bagian :guilabel:`Pengeluaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:28
msgid ""
"Next, set how payments are made in the :guilabel:`Accounting` section. Click "
"the drop-down menu under :guilabel:`Payment Methods`, and select the desired "
"payment option. The default options include paying by :guilabel:`Manual "
"Payment (Cash)`, :guilabel:`Manual Payment (Bank)`, :guilabel:`Batch Deposit "
"(Bank)`, and :guilabel:`Checks (Bank)`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, atur cara pembayaran dilakukan di bagian :guilabel:`Akuntansi`. "
"Klik menu drop-down di bawah :guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran`, dan pilih opsi "
"pembayaran yang diinginkan. Opsi default termasuk membayar "
"dengan :guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual (Tunai)`, :guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual "
"(Bank)`, :guilabel:`Setoran Batch (Bank)`, dan :guilabel:`Cek (Bank)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:33
msgid ""
"Leaving this field blank allows for **all** available payment options to be "
"used."
msgstr ""
"Membiarkan bidang ini kosong memungkinkan **semua** opsi pembayaran yang "
"tersedia untuk digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:35
msgid ""
"When all desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save` to "
"activate the settings."
msgstr ""
"Ketika semua konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Simpan` "
"untuk mengaktifkan pengaturan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:40
msgid "Reimburse in payslips"
msgstr "Ganti dalam slip gaji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:42
msgid ""
"If the  *Reimburse in Payslip* option is activated on the :ref:`settings "
"<expenses/reimburse-settings>` page, payments can be added to the employee's "
"next payslip, instead of issuing separate payments."
msgstr ""
"Jika opsi *Reimburse in Payslip* diaktifkan pada halaman :ref:`pengaturan "
"<expenses/reimburse-settings>`, pembayaran dapat ditambahkan ke slip gaji "
"karyawan berikutnya, alih-alih mengeluarkan pembayaran terpisah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:47
msgid ""
"Reimbursing expenses on payslips can **only** be done individually for an "
"*approved* expense report. Once an expense report has a status of *Posted*, "
"the option to reimburse in the following payslip **is not available**."
msgstr ""
"Mengganti biaya pengeluaran pada slip gaji **hanya** dapat dilakukan secara "
"individual untuk laporan pengeluaran yang *disetujui*. Setelah laporan "
"pengeluaran memiliki status *Diposting*, opsi untuk mengganti biaya dalam "
"slip gaji berikutnya **tidak tersedia**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:51
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense Reports`, and click on "
"the individual expense report to reimburse on the following paycheck. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` button, and the expenses are added to "
"the next payslip issued for that employee."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Laporan Pengeluaran`, "
"dan klik laporan pengeluaran individual untuk diganti biayanya pada gaji "
"berikutnya. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Laporkan di Slip Gaji Berikutnya`, dan "
"pengeluaran akan ditambahkan ke slip gaji berikutnya yang diterbitkan untuk "
"karyawan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Report in Next Payslip button, visible with an expense report status of "
"Approved."
msgstr ""
"Tombol Laporkan dalam Slip Gaji Berikutnya, terlihat dengan status laporan "
"pengeluaran Disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:58
msgid ""
"Once the expense report is added to the following payslip, a message is "
"logged in the chatter stating `Expense report (expense report name) will be "
"added to the next payslip.` The status for the expense report "
"remains :guilabel:`Approved`. The status only changes to :guilabel:`Posted` "
"(and then :guilabel:`Done`), when the related payslip is processed."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengeluaran ditambahkan ke slip gaji berikutnya, pesan "
"dicatat dalam chatter yang menyatakan `Laporan pengeluaran (nama laporan "
"pengeluaran) akan ditambahkan ke slip gaji berikutnya.` Status untuk laporan "
"pengeluaran tetap :guilabel:`Disetujui`. Status hanya berubah "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Diposting` (dan kemudian :guilabel:`Selesai`), ketika "
"slip gaji terkait diproses."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:64
msgid ""
"Refer to the :doc:`Payslips <../../hr/payroll/payslips>` documentation for "
"more information about processing paychecks."
msgstr ""
"Rujuk ke dokumentasi :doc:`Slip Gaji <../../hr/payroll/payslips>` untuk "
"informasi lebih lanjut tentang pemrosesan slip gaji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:70
msgid "Reimburse individually"
msgstr "Reimburse secara individual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:72
msgid ""
"To reimburse an individual expense report, first navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense Reports`. All expense reports "
"are presented in a default list view. Click on the expense report being "
"reimbursed to view the report details."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengganti biaya laporan pengeluaran individu, pertama navigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Laporan Pengeluaran`. Semua "
"laporan pengeluaran ditampilkan dalam tampilan daftar default. Klik pada "
"laporan pengeluaran yang akan diganti untuk melihat detail laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:117
msgid ""
"**Only** expense reports with a status of :guilabel:`Posted` can be "
"reimbursed directly to the employee (not :ref:`via a payslip <expenses/"
"reimburse-payslip>`)."
msgstr ""
"**Hanya** laporan pengeluaran dengan status :guilabel:`Diposting` yang dapat "
"diganti biayanya langsung ke karyawan (bukan :ref:`melalui slip gaji "
"<expenses/reimburse-payslip>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:80
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Pay` button in the top-left corner of the expense "
"report, and a :guilabel:`Pay` pop-up window loads. Enter the following "
"information in the pop-up window:"
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`Bayar` di pojok kiri atas laporan pengeluaran, dan "
"jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Bayar` akan dimuat. Masukkan informasi berikut di "
"jendela pop-up:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:83
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select the accounting journal to post the payment using "
"the drop-down menu. The default options are :guilabel:`Bank` "
"or :guilabel:`Cash`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jurnal`: Pilih jurnal akuntansi untuk memposting pembayaran "
"menggunakan menu drop-down. Opsi default adalah :guilabel:`Bank` "
"atau :guilabel:`Tunai`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:85
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Method`: Select how the payment is made using the drop-"
"down menu. If :guilabel:`Cash` is selected for the :guilabel:`Journal`, the "
"only option available is :guilabel:`Manual Payment`. If :guilabel:`Bank` is "
"selected for the :guilabel:`Journal`, the default options "
"are :guilabel:`Manual Payment` or :guilabel:`Checks`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Metode Pembayaran`: Pilih cara pembayaran dilakukan menggunakan "
"menu drop-down. Jika :guilabel:`Tunai` dipilih untuk :guilabel:`Jurnal`, "
"satu-satunya opsi yang tersedia adalah :guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual`. "
"Jika :guilabel:`Bank` dipilih untuk :guilabel:`Jurnal`, opsi default "
"adalah :guilabel:`Pembayaran Manual` atau :guilabel:`Cek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recipient Bank Account`: This field only appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Journal` is set to :guilabel:`Bank`. The "
"employee's :ref:`bank account <employees/private-info>` populates this "
"field, by default. If the employee has more than one trusted bank account on "
"their employee profile, use the drop-down menu to select the desired bank "
"account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rekening Bank Penerima`: Field ini hanya muncul "
"jika :guilabel:`Jurnal` diatur ke :guilabel:`Bank`. :ref:`Rekening bank "
"<employees/private-info>` karyawan mengisi field ini, secara default. Jika "
"karyawan memiliki lebih dari satu rekening bank terpercaya pada profil "
"karyawannya, gunakan menu drop-down untuk memilih rekening bank yang "
"diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount`: The total amount being reimbursed populates this field, "
"by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jumlah`: Total jumlah yang diganti biayanya mengisi field ini, "
"secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Date`: Enter the date the payment is issued in this "
"field. The current date populates this field, by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Pembayaran`: Masukkan tanggal pembayaran diterbitkan di "
"field ini. Tanggal saat ini mengisi field ini, secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Memo`: The text entered in the :doc:`Expense Report Summary <../"
"expenses/expense_reports>` field of the expense report populates this field, "
"by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Memo`: Teks yang dimasukkan dalam field :doc:`Ringkasan Laporan "
"Pengeluaran <../expenses/expense_reports>` dari laporan pengeluaran mengisi "
"field ini secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Register Payment pop-up window filled out for an individual expense "
"report\n"
"reimbursement."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up Daftarkan Pembayaran yang diisi untuk reimbursement laporan "
"pengeluaran individual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:103
msgid ""
"When the fields of the pop-up window are completed, click "
"the :guilabel:`Create Payment` button to register the payment, and reimburse "
"the employee. A green :guilabel:`In Payment` banner now appears on the "
"expense report."
msgstr ""
"Ketika field pada jendela pop-up telah lengkap, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat "
"Pembayaran` untuk mendaftarkan pembayaran, dan mengganti biaya karyawan. "
"Banner hijau :guilabel:`Dalam Pembayaran` sekarang muncul pada laporan "
"pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:110
msgid "Reimburse in bulk"
msgstr "Reimburse dalam jumlah besar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:112
msgid ""
"To reimburse multiple expense reports at once, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense Reports` to view all expense "
"reports in a list view. Next, select the expense reports to be reimbursed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengganti beberapa laporan pengeluaran sekaligus, "
"buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Laporan Pengeluaran` untuk "
"melihat semua laporan pengeluaran dalam tampilan daftar. Selanjutnya, pilih "
"laporan pengeluaran yang akan diganti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:121
msgid ""
"Adjust the :guilabel:`STATUS` filter on the left side to only "
"show :guilabel:`Posted` expense reports. This displays **only** expense "
"reports that are able to be reimbursed."
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan filter :guilabel:`STATUS` di sisi kiri agar hanya menampilkan "
"laporan pengeluaran :guilabel:`Posted`. Ini menampilkan **hanya** laporan "
"pengeluaran yang dapat diganti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:124
msgid ""
"Tick the checkbox next to the expense reports being reimbursed, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Pay` button, and a :guilabel:`Pay` pop-up window loads. Enter "
"the following information in the pop-up window:"
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak di sebelah laporan pengeluaran yang akan diganti, lalu klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Bayar`, dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Bayar` akan muncul. "
"Masukkan informasi berikut di jendela pop-up:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Group Payments`: When multiple expense reports are selected for "
"the same employee, this option appears. Tick the checkbox to have only one "
"payment made per employee, rather than issuing multiple payments to the same "
"employee."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kelompokkan Pembayaran`: Ketika beberapa laporan pengeluaran "
"dipilih untuk karyawan yang sama, opsi ini muncul. Centang kotak untuk "
"melakukan hanya satu pembayaran per karyawan, daripada mengeluarkan beberapa "
"pembayaran kepada karyawan yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount`: The total amount being reimbursed for all the expense "
"reports populates this field, by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jumlah`: Total jumlah yang diganti untuk semua laporan "
"pengeluaran mengisi field ini secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Date`: Enter the date the payments are issued. The "
"current date populates this field, by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Pembayaran`: Masukkan tanggal pembayaran dikeluarkan. "
"Tanggal saat ini mengisi field ini secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:142
msgid ""
"When the fields on the :guilabel:`Pay` pop-up window are completed, click "
"the :guilabel:`Create Payments` button to register the payments, and "
"reimburse the employees."
msgstr ""
"Ketika field pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Bayar` telah dilengkapi, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Buat Pembayaran` untuk mencatat pembayaran dan mengganti "
"pengeluaran karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:None
msgid ""
"The pay pop-up window filled out for multiple reimbursements via checks."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up pembayaran yang diisi untuk beberapa penggantian melalui cek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Re-invoice expenses"
msgstr "Penagihan ulang pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"If expenses are tracked on customer projects, they can be automatically "
"charged back to the customer. This is done by :ref:`creating an expense "
"<expenses/reinvoice-create>`, referencing the sales order to which it is "
"added, then :ref:`creating an expense report <expenses/reinvoice-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengeluaran dilacak pada proyek pelanggan, pengeluaran tersebut dapat "
"secara otomatis ditagihkan kembali kepada pelanggan. Hal ini dilakukan "
"dengan :ref:`membuat pengeluaran <expenses/reinvoice-create>`, merujuk pada "
"Sales Order yang ditambahkan, kemudian :ref:`membuat laporan pengeluaran "
"<expenses/reinvoice-report>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:10
msgid ""
"Next, managers :ref:`approve the expense report <expenses/reinvoice-"
"approve>`, before the accounting department :ref:`posts the journal entries "
"<expenses/reinvoice-approve>`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, manajer :ref:`menyetujui laporan pengeluaran <expenses/"
"reinvoice-approve>`, sebelum Departemen Akuntansi :ref:`memposting entri "
"jurnal <expenses/reinvoice-approve>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:13
msgid ""
"Finally, once the expense report is posted to a journal, the expenses appear "
"on the specified :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`. The :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is "
"then :ref:`invoiced <expenses/reinvoice>`, thus charging the customer for "
"the expenses."
msgstr ""
"Akhirnya, setelah laporan pengeluaran diposting ke jurnal, pengeluaran "
"muncul pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang ditentukan. :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)` kemudian :ref:`ditagihkan <expenses/reinvoice>`, sehingga menagih "
"pelanggan untuk pengeluaran tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:18
msgid ""
"The **Sales** and **Accounting** apps must be installed for this "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Sales** dan **Akuntansi** harus diinstal untuk konfigurasi ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:20
msgid ""
"Approving expenses, posting expenses to accounting, and re-invoicing "
"expenses on :abbr:`SOs (Sales Orders)` are **only** possible for users with "
"the appropriate :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/access_rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Menyetujui pengeluaran, memposting pengeluaran ke Akuntansi, dan menagihkan "
"kembali pengeluaran pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` **hanya** dapat dilakukan "
"oleh pengguna dengan :doc:`hak akses <../../general/users/access_rights>` "
"yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:25
msgid ""
"This document provides lower-level instructions to create, submit, approve, "
"and post expenses. For fully-detailed instructions for any of these steps, "
"refer to the following documentation:"
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini menyediakan instruksi tingkat rendah untuk membuat, mengirimkan, "
"menyetujui, dan memposting pengeluaran. Untuk instruksi lengkap dari setiap "
"langkah ini, lihat dokumentasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:28
msgid ":doc:`Log expenses <log_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Mencatat pengeluaran <log_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:29
msgid ":doc:`Expense reports <expense_reports>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Laporan pengeluaran <expense_reports>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:30
msgid ":doc:`Approving expenses <approve_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Menyetujui pengeluaran <approve_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:31
msgid ":doc:`Posting expenses in accounting <post_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Memposting pengeluaran di Akuntansi <post_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:264
msgid "Setup"
msgstr "Setup"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:36
msgid ""
"In the **Expense** app, specify the invoicing policy for each expense "
"category. Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> "
"Expense Categories`. Click on the desired expense category or :doc:`create a "
"new one <expense_categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Pada aplikasi **Pengeluaran**, tentukan kebijakan Penagihan untuk setiap "
"kategori pengeluaran. Navigasikan ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --"
"> Konfigurasi --> Kategori Pengeluaran`. Klik pada kategori pengeluaran yang "
"diinginkan atau :doc:`buat yang baru <expense_categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:40
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section, click the radio button next to the "
"desired selection for :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Costs`:"
msgstr ""
"Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Penagihan`, klik tombol radio di sebelah pilihan "
"yang diinginkan untuk :guilabel:`Tagih Ulang Biaya`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:43
msgid ":guilabel:`No`\\: The expense category **cannot** be re-invoiced."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tidak`: Kategori pengeluaran **tidak dapat** ditagihkan ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At cost`\\: The expense category invoices expenses at "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` set on the expense category form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sesuai biaya`: Kategori pengeluaran menagihkan pengeluaran "
"pada :guilabel:`Biaya` yang ditetapkan pada formulir kategori pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales price`\\: The expense category invoices at "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Price` set on the expense form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Harga jual`: Kategori pengeluaran menagihkan "
"pada :guilabel:`Harga Jual` yang ditetapkan pada formulir pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:49
msgid ""
"The default expense categories have the following re-invoicing policies:"
msgstr ""
"Kategori pengeluaran default memiliki kebijakan penagihan ulang berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:52
msgid "**At cost**"
msgstr "**Sesuai biaya**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:52
msgid "**Sales price**"
msgstr "**Harga jual**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:52
msgid "**Not enabled**"
msgstr "**Tidak diaktifkan**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`COMM`\\: Communication expenses such as phone bills, postage, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`COMM`: Pengeluaran komunikasi seperti tagihan Telepon, pos, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`FOOD`\\: Meal expenses such as restaurants, business lunches, etc"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`FOOD`: Pengeluaran makan seperti restoran, makan siang bisnis, dll"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:54
msgid ":guilabel:`EXP_GEN`\\: Others."
msgstr ":guilabel:`EXP_GEN`: Lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`TRANS & ACCT`\\: Travel and accommodation expenses such as hotel, "
"plane ticket, taxi, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`TRANS & ACCT`: Pengeluaran perjalanan dan akomodasi seperti "
"hotel, tiket pesawat, taksi, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:56
msgid ":guilabel:`MIL`\\: Mileage."
msgstr ":guilabel:`MIL`: Jarak tempuh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:56
msgid ":guilabel:`GIFT`\\: Gifts to customers or vendors."
msgstr ":guilabel:`GIFT`: Hadiah untuk pelanggan atau vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Sample of the Expense Category form in the Expense app."
msgstr "Contoh formulir Kategori Pengeluaran di aplikasi Pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:65
msgid "Create an expense"
msgstr "Buat pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:67
msgid ""
"To re-invoice an expense, first :doc:`create an expense record "
"<log_expenses>`. In the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field, use the "
"drop-down menu to select the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` to add the expense to."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menagih ulang pengeluaran, pertama :doc:`buat catatan pengeluaran "
"<log_expenses>`. Di kolom :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice`, gunakan menu "
"drop-down untuk memilih :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` untuk menambahkan "
"pengeluaran tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:72
msgid ""
"Selecting the proper :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` in the :guilabel:`Customer to "
"Reinvoice` field is **critical**, since this is how expenses are "
"automatically invoiced after an expense report is approved."
msgstr ""
"Memilih :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang tepat di field :guilabel:`Pelanggan "
"untuk Diinvoice Ulang` sangat **penting**, karena ini adalah cara "
"pengeluaran diinvoice secara otomatis setelah laporan pengeluaran disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:77
msgid ":doc:`Detailed instructions on completing an expense <log_expenses>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Petunjuk lengkap untuk menyelesaikan pengeluaran <log_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:80
msgid "Analytic Distribution"
msgstr "Distribusi Analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:83
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field to be visible the "
"**Accounting** app must be installed, :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting`, "
"and :guilabel:`Analytic Plans` must be configured. Refer to :doc:`../"
"accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting` for more information."
msgstr ""
"Agar kolom :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` terlihat, aplikasi "
"**Akuntansi** harus diinstal, :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Analytic Plans` harus dikonfigurasi. Lihat :doc:`../"
"accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting` untuk informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:87
msgid ""
"As an optional step, select the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` the "
"expense is posted to. Multiple accounts can be selected, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai langkah opsional, pilih :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` tempat "
"pengeluaran diposting. Beberapa akun dapat dipilih jika diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Sample of a complete expense form in the Expense app."
msgstr "Contoh formulir pengeluaran lengkap di aplikasi Pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:93
msgid ""
"To add another :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, click on the line to "
"reveal the :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-over window. Click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`, then select the desired :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` from the "
"drop-down field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` lainnya, klik pada baris "
"untuk memunculkan jendela pop-over :guilabel:`Analytic`. Klik :guilabel:`Add "
"a line`, kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` yang diinginkan "
"dari kolom drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:97
msgid ""
"If selecting more than one :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, "
"the :guilabel:`Percentage` fields **must** be modified. By default, both "
"fields are populated with `100%`. Adjust the percentages for all the fields, "
"so the total of all selected accounts equals `100%`."
msgstr ""
"Jika memilih lebih dari satu :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, "
"kolom :guilabel:`Percentage` **harus** dimodifikasi. Secara default, kedua "
"kolom diisi dengan `100%`. Sesuaikan persentase untuk semua kolom, sehingga "
"total semua akun yang dipilih sama dengan `100%`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:102
msgid ""
"A painting company agrees to paint an office building that houses two "
"different companies. During the estimate, a meeting is held at the office "
"location to discuss the project."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan pengecatan setuju untuk mengecat gedung perkantoran yang "
"menampung dua perusahaan berbeda. Selama estimasi, pertemuan diadakan di "
"lokasi kantor untuk membahas proyek tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:105
msgid ""
"Both companies agree to pay for the travel expenses for the painting company "
"employees. When creating the expenses for the mileage and hotels, **both "
"companies** are listed in the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` line, for "
"50% each."
msgstr ""
"Kedua perusahaan setuju untuk membayar biaya perjalanan untuk karyawan "
"perusahaan pengecatan. Saat membuat pengeluaran untuk jarak tempuh dan "
"hotel, **kedua perusahaan** dicantumkan dalam baris :guilabel:`Analytic "
"Distribution`, masing-masing 50%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:112
msgid "Create an expense report"
msgstr "Buat laporan pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:114
msgid ""
"After the expenses are created, click :guilabel:`Create report`. Once the "
"expense report is submitted, the :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` "
"and :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Expenses` smart buttons appear at the "
"top of the expense report. The smart buttons will display the number "
"of :abbr:`SOs (Sales Orders)` and expenses linked to the expense report."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengeluaran dibuat, klik :guilabel:`Create report`. Setelah laporan "
"pengeluaran diajukan, tombol pintar :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales "
"Orders` dan :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Expenses` akan muncul di "
"bagian atas laporan pengeluaran. Tombol pintar akan menampilkan "
"jumlah :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` dan pengeluaran yang terhubung ke laporan "
"pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:119
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` to request approval from the "
"assigned Manager."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` untuk meminta persetujuan "
"dari Manager yang ditugaskan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:122
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field can be modified *only* until an "
"expense report is **approved**. After an expense report is approved, "
"the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field is no longer able to be modified."
msgstr ""
"Field :guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Diinvoice Ulang` dapat dimodifikasi *hanya* "
"sampai laporan pengeluaran **disetujui**. Setelah laporan pengeluaran "
"disetujui, field :guilabel:`Pelanggan untuk Diinvoice Ulang` tidak dapat "
"lagi dimodifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Sample of an expense report in the Expense app."
msgstr "Contoh laporan pengeluaran di aplikasi Pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:130
msgid ""
":doc:`Detailed instructions to create and submit an expense report "
"<expense_reports>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Instruksi terperinci untuk membuat dan mengajukan laporan pengeluaran "
"<expense_reports>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:135
msgid "Approve and post expenses"
msgstr "Setujui dan posting pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:137
msgid ""
"Before approving an expense report, ensure all the information for every "
"expense line is correct, then click :guilabel:`Approve`."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum menyetujui laporan pengeluaran, pastikan semua informasi untuk "
"setiap baris pengeluaran sudah benar, lalu klik :guilabel:`Approve`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "The expense report with all the Analytic Distribution lines populated."
msgstr "Laporan pengeluaran dengan semua baris Distribusi Analitik terisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:144
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Approve` button **only** appears after an expense report has "
"been :ref:`submitted <expenses/submit>`."
msgstr ""
"Tombol :guilabel:`Setujui` **hanya** muncul setelah laporan pengeluaran "
"telah :ref:`diajukan <expenses/submit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:147
msgid ""
"The accounting department is typically responsible for :doc:`posting journal "
"entries <post_expenses>`. To post expenses to an accounting journal, "
"click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`. Once an expense report is approved, "
"it can then be posted."
msgstr ""
"Departemen akuntansi biasanya bertanggung jawab untuk :doc:`memposting entri "
"jurnal <post_expenses>`. Untuk memposting pengeluaran ke jurnal akuntansi, "
"klik :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`. Setelah laporan pengeluaran "
"disetujui, laporan tersebut dapat diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:151
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is **only** updated *after* the journal entries "
"are posted. Once the journal entries are posted, the expenses now appear on "
"the referenced :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` **hanya** diperbarui *setelah* entri jurnal "
"diposting. Setelah entri jurnal diposting, pengeluaran sekarang muncul "
"pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang direferensikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:155
msgid ""
":doc:`Detailed instructions to approve an expense report <approve_expenses>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Instruksi terperinci untuk menyetujui laporan pengeluaran "
"<approve_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:160
msgid "Invoice expenses to the customer"
msgstr "Tagihkan pengeluaran kepada pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:162
msgid ""
"Once the expense report is approved and the corresponding journal entries "
"are posted, the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is automatically updated, allowing "
"the customer to be invoiced. The accounting department is typically "
"responsible for generating the final invoice."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan pengeluaran disetujui dan entri jurnal terkait "
"diposting, :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` secara otomatis diperbarui, memungkinkan "
"pelanggan untuk ditagih. Departemen akuntansi biasanya bertanggung jawab "
"untuk menghasilkan invoice akhir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:166
msgid ""
"Select the desired expense report, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button to open the :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`. The expenses to be re-invoiced now appear on the :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih laporan pengeluaran yang diinginkan, dan klik tombol pintar :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` untuk membuka :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`. "
"Pengeluaran yang akan ditagih ulang sekarang muncul di :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:171
msgid ""
"More than one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` can be referenced on an expense "
"report. If more than one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is referenced, clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button opens a list "
"displaying all the :abbr:`SOs (Sales Order)` associated with that expense "
"report. Click on a :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` to open the individual :abbr:`SO "
"(Sales Order)` details."
msgstr ""
"Lebih dari satu :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` dapat direferensikan pada laporan "
"pengeluaran. Jika lebih dari satu :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` direferensikan, "
"mengklik tombol pintar :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` akan "
"membuka daftar yang menampilkan semua :abbr:`SOs (Sales Order)` yang terkait "
"dengan laporan pengeluaran tersebut. Klik pada :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` "
"untuk membuka detail :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` individual."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:178
msgid ""
"A electronics repair company has a large customer base. Their service "
"charges vary depending on the product they service. A technician uses "
"different components depending on the product they service and services five "
"customers per day on average."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan perbaikan elektronik memiliki basis pelanggan yang besar. "
"Biaya layanan mereka bervariasi tergantung pada produk yang mereka layani. "
"Seorang teknisi menggunakan komponen yang berbeda tergantung pada produk "
"yang mereka layani dan melayani rata-rata lima pelanggan per hari."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:182
msgid ""
"After each job the technician submits an expense and associates the "
"appropriate :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` for each. At the end of the day, the "
"technician selects all of the expenses and creates an expense report for the "
"manager to review and approve."
msgstr ""
"Setelah setiap pekerjaan, teknisi mengajukan pengeluaran dan "
"mengaitkan :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang sesuai untuk masing-masing. Di "
"akhir hari, teknisi memilih semua pengeluaran dan membuat laporan "
"pengeluaran untuk ditinjau dan disetujui oleh manajer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:186
msgid ""
"When the expense report gets created, several :abbr:`SOs (Sales Order)` are "
"linked to it. The :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Expenses` and :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart buttons display the number of linked "
"records on the top of the expense report."
msgstr ""
"Ketika laporan pengeluaran dibuat, beberapa :abbr:`SOs (Sales Order)` "
"ditautkan padanya. Tombol pintar :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Expenses` "
"dan :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` menampilkan jumlah catatan "
"yang ditautkan di bagian atas laporan pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:0
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "See the expenses listed on the sales order after clicking into it."
msgstr "Lihat pengeluaran yang terdaftar pada sales order setelah mengkliknya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:193
msgid ""
"On the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` form, the expenses are now line items in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, with their :guilabel:`Delivered` column "
"filled in, and ready to be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`, pengeluaran sekarang menjadi item "
"baris di tab :guilabel:`Order Lines`, dengan kolom :guilabel:`Delivered` "
"terisi, dan siap untuk ditagih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:199
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, and a :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up "
"window appears."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Create "
"invoices` akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:201
msgid ""
"Select if the invoice is a :guilabel:`Regular invoice`, a :guilabel:`Down "
"payment (percentage)`, or a :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`. A customer invoice draft window "
"displays the products and expenses in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Pilih apakah invoice adalah :guilabel:`Regular invoice`, :guilabel:`Down "
"payment (percentage)`, atau :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)`, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`. Jendela draft invoice pelanggan "
"menampilkan produk dan pengeluaran di tab :guilabel:`Invoice Lines`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:206
msgid ""
"For an :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` with a product and a expense, if the product "
"has not been delivered to the customer, only the expense is listed in "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab of the invoice. Creating two invoices for "
"one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is possible."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` dengan produk dan pengeluaran, jika produk "
"belum dikirim ke pelanggan, hanya pengeluaran yang terdaftar di "
"tab :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` dari invoice. Membuat dua invoice untuk "
"satu :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` dimungkinkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:210
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to change the invoice status "
"from :guilabel:`Draft` to :guilabel:`Posted`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk mengubah status invoice "
"dari :guilabel:`Draft` menjadi :guilabel:`Posted`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:212
msgid ""
"To email the invoice to the customer, click :guilabel:`Send`. "
"A :guilabel:`Print & Send` pop-up window with a pre-configured email message "
"and a PDF invoice in its body is displayed. The message can be reviewed and "
"modified, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim email invoice kepada pelanggan, klik :guilabel:`Send`. "
"Jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Print & Send` dengan pesan email yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya dan invoice PDF di dalamnya akan ditampilkan. Pesan "
"dapat ditinjau dan dimodifikasi jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:216
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to email the invoice to the customer. The pop-up "
"window disappears, and a PDF of the invoice is automatically downloaded for "
"record-keeping and printing purposes."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Send` untuk mengirim email invoice kepada pelanggan. Jendela "
"pop-up akan hilang, dan PDF invoice secara otomatis diunduh untuk tujuan "
"penyimpanan catatan dan pencetakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:220
msgid "Invoice payment"
msgstr "Pembayaran invoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:222
msgid ""
"Depending on the payment configuration in the **Accounting** app, there are "
"several ways to process payment for an invoice. This workflow incorporates "
"the customer portal and manual verification. The customer is responsible for "
"submitting the invoice payment and the accounting department is responsible "
"for verification."
msgstr ""
"Bergantung pada konfigurasi pembayaran di aplikasi **Akuntansi**, ada "
"beberapa cara untuk memproses pembayaran faktur. Alur kerja ini "
"menggabungkan portal pelanggan dan verifikasi manual. Pelanggan bertanggung "
"jawab untuk mengirimkan pembayaran faktur dan departemen akuntansi "
"bertanggung jawab untuk verifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:228
msgid ""
"For online payments through the customer portal, the :doc:`Invoice Online "
"Payment <../../finance/payment_providers>` feature must be enabled on the "
"**Accounting** app. Also a payment method must be set up."
msgstr ""
"Untuk pembayaran online melalui portal pelanggan, fitur :doc:`Pembayaran "
"Faktur Online <../../finance/payment_providers>` harus diaktifkan di "
"aplikasi **Akuntansi**. Selain itu, metode pembayaran harus dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:232
msgid ""
"Navigate to the invoice by clicking :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense "
"Reports` and select the desired expense report."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke faktur dengan mengklik :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengeluaran --> "
"Laporan Pengeluaran` dan pilih laporan pengeluaran yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:235
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button, then "
"select the desired :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`. Click the :icon:`fa-pencil-"
"square-o` :guilabel:`Invoices` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol pintar :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Order`, lalu "
"pilih :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` yang diinginkan. Klik tombol pintar :icon:`fa-"
"pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Faktur`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:238
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Send`, the invoice is emailed to the customer and "
"published online on the customer portal. Click :guilabel:`Preview` to see "
"the customer's view of the invoice and payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik :guilabel:`Kirim`, faktur dikirim melalui email kepada "
"pelanggan dan dipublikasikan secara online di portal pelanggan. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Pratinjau` untuk melihat tampilan pelanggan terhadap faktur "
"dan metode pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:242
msgid ""
"Once the customer pays online, the invoice gets an :guilabel:`In Payment` "
"banner. The :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Payments` and :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Payment Transaction` smart buttons display at the top of "
"the invoice form."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pelanggan membayar secara online, faktur mendapatkan "
"banner :guilabel:`Dalam Pembayaran`. Tombol pintar :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`Pembayaran` dan :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Transaksi "
"Pembayaran` ditampilkan di bagian atas formulir faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:246
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Payments` smart button to go to "
"the :guilabel:`Pay` form. Click :guilabel:`Validate` to confirm that the "
"invoice payment has been received. The Pay form is automatically updated "
"to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol pintar :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Pembayaran` untuk membuka "
"formulir :guilabel:`Bayar`. Klik :guilabel:`Validasi` untuk mengonfirmasi "
"bahwa pembayaran faktur telah diterima. Formulir Bayar secara otomatis "
"diperbarui menjadi :guilabel:`Dibayar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:5
msgid "Fiscal localizations"
msgstr "Lokalisasi fiskal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:7
msgid ""
"Fiscal localizations are country-specific modules that allow you to be "
"compliant with a country's fiscal requirements. Most of these modules are "
"related to the Accounting app, but they can also be necessary for other apps "
"such as Point of Sale, eCommerce, etc., depending on a country's fiscal "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi fiskal adalah modul khusus negara yang memungkinkan Anda mematuhi "
"persyaratan fiskal suatu negara. Sebagian besar modul ini terkait dengan "
"aplikasi Akuntansi, tetapi juga dapat diperlukan untuk aplikasi lain seperti "
"POS, eCommerce, dll., tergantung pada persyaratan fiskal suatu negara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:13
msgid ":doc:`../hr/payroll/payroll_localizations` are documented separately."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../hr/payroll/payroll_localizations` didokumentasikan secara terpisah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:20
msgid ""
"Odoo should automatically install the fiscal localization's core modules "
"based on the company's country when the related app is installed. The rest "
"can be manually :ref:`installed <general/install>`. Refer to the :ref:`list "
"of countries <fiscal_localizations/countries-list>` to view the currently "
"supported countries and access their specific documentation."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis menginstal modul inti lokalisasi fiskal berdasarkan "
"negara perusahaan saat aplikasi terkait diinstal. Sisanya "
"dapat :ref:`diinstal <general/install>` secara manual. Lihat :ref:`daftar "
"negara <fiscal_localizations/countries-list>` untuk melihat negara yang saat "
"ini didukung dan mengakses dokumentasi spesifik mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:26
msgid ""
"In a :doc:`multi-company <../general/companies/multi_company>` environment, "
"each company can use different fiscal localization modules. "
"However, :ref:`branches <accounting/branches>` always follow the parent "
"company's localization. Therefore, entities operating in different countries "
"should be set up as companies, not branches."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:31
msgid ""
"Verify the right package of modules is installed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and checking "
"the :guilabel:`Package` field under the :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization` "
"section. Select another one if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi paket modul yang tepat telah diinstal dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan "
"memeriksa bidang :guilabel:`Paket` di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Lokalisasi "
"Fiskal`. Pilih yang lain jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:36
msgid "Selecting another package is only possible if no entry has been posted."
msgstr ""
"Memilih paket lain hanya dimungkinkan jika tidak ada entri yang telah "
"diposting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:38
msgid ""
"These packages require fine-tuning the chart of accounts, activating the "
"taxes to be used, configuring the country-specific statements and "
"certifications, and sometimes more."
msgstr ""
"Paket-paket ini memerlukan penyesuaian bagan akun, mengaktifkan pajak yang "
"akan digunakan, mengkonfigurasi laporan dan sertifikasi khusus negara, dan "
"terkadang lebih banyak lagi."

