#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:862
msgid "Enter check numbers manually"
msgstr "Memasukkan nomor cek secara manual"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:863
msgid "Adds a field to allocate the payment date of the check"
msgstr "Menambahkan bidang untuk mengalokasikan tanggal pembayaran cek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Bank journal configurations."
msgstr "Konfigurasi jurnal bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:870
msgid "Management of own checks"
msgstr "Manajemen cek sendiri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:872
msgid ""
"Own checks can be created directly from the vendor bill. For this process, "
"click on the :guilabel:`Register Payment` button."
msgstr ""
"Cek sendiri dapat dibuat langsung dari tagihan vendor. Untuk proses ini, "
"klik tombol :guilabel:`Daftarkan Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:875
msgid ""
"On the payment registration modal, select the bank journal from which the "
"payment is to be made and set the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Amount`."
msgstr ""
"Pada modal pendaftaran pembayaran, pilih jurnal bank dari mana pembayaran "
"akan dilakukan dan atur :guilabel:`Tanggal Pencairan Cek`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Jumlah`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment pop-up window with own check options enabled."
msgstr "Jendela pop-up pembayaran dengan opsi cek sendiri diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:883
msgid ""
"To manage current checks, the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date` field must be "
"left blank or filled in with the current date. To manage deferred checks, "
"the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date` must be set in the future."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola cek saat ini, bidang :guilabel:`Tanggal Pencairan Cek` harus "
"dibiarkan kosong atau diisi dengan tanggal saat ini. Untuk mengelola cek "
"tertunda, :guilabel:`Tanggal Pencairan Cek` harus diatur di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:887
msgid ""
"To manage your existing own checks, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Vendors --> Own Checks`. This window shows critical information such as "
"the dates when checks need to be paid, the total quantity of checks, and the "
"total amount paid in checks."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola cek sendiri Anda yang ada, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --"
"> Vendor --> Cek Sendiri`. Jendela ini menampilkan informasi penting seperti "
"tanggal kapan cek perlu dibayar, jumlah total cek, dan jumlah total yang "
"dibayarkan dalam cek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Own checks menu location."
msgstr "Lokasi menu cek sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:895
msgid ""
"It is important to note that the list is pre-filtered by checks that are "
"still *not reconciled* with a bank statement - that were not yet debited "
"from the bank - which can be verified with the :guilabel:`Is Matched with a "
"Bank Statement` field. If you want to see all of your own checks, delete "
"the :guilabel:`No Bank Matching` filter by clicking on the :guilabel:`X` "
"symbol."
msgstr ""
"Penting untuk dicatat bahwa daftar sudah disaring sebelumnya berdasarkan cek "
"yang masih *belum direkonsiliasi* dengan laporan bank - yang belum didebit "
"dari bank - yang dapat diverifikasi dengan bidang :guilabel:`Dicocokkan "
"dengan Laporan Bank`. Jika Anda ingin melihat semua cek sendiri Anda, hapus "
"filter :guilabel:`Tidak Ada Pencocokan Bank` dengan mengklik "
"simbol :guilabel:`X`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Own checks menu organization and filtering."
msgstr "Organisasi dan pemfilteran menu cek sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:905
msgid "Cancel an own check"
msgstr "Batalkan cek sendiri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:907
msgid ""
"To cancel an own check created in Odoo, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Own Checks` and select the "
"check to be cancelled, then click on the :guilabel:`Void Check` button. This "
"will break the reconciliation with the vendor bills and the bank statements "
"and leave the check in a **cancelled** state."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatalkan cek sendiri yang dibuat di Odoo, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Vendor --> Cek Sendiri` dan pilih cek "
"yang akan dibatalkan, kemudian klik tombol :guilabel:`Batalkan Cek`. Ini "
"akan memutuskan rekonsiliasi dengan tagihan vendor dan laporan bank serta "
"meninggalkan cek dalam status **dibatalkan**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Empty Check button to cancel Own Checks"
msgstr "Tombol Batalkan Cek untuk membatalkan Cek Sendiri"

