#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:68
msgid ""
"You can reach the :guilabel:`Chart of accounts` by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Accounting: Chart of "
"Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengakses :guilabel:`Bagan Akun` dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Akuntansi: Bagan Akun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:71
msgid ""
"The Belgian chart of accounts includes pre-configured accounts as described "
"in the :abbr:`PCMN(Plan Comptable Minimum Normalisé)`. To add a new account, "
"click :guilabel:`New`. A new line appears. Fill it in, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`, and then :guilabel:`Setup` to configure it further."
msgstr ""
"Bagan akun Belgia mencakup akun yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya seperti "
"yang dijelaskan dalam :abbr:`PCMN(Plan Comptable Minimum Normalisé)`. Untuk "
"menambahkan akun baru, klik :guilabel:`Baru`. Baris baru muncul. Isi, "
"klik :guilabel:`Simpan`, lalu :guilabel:`Atur` untuk mengonfigurasinya lebih "
"lanjut."

