msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/reporting`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:186
msgid "Disallowed expenses report"
msgstr "Laporan pengeluaran yang tidak diperbolehkan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:188
msgid ""
"**Disallowed expenses** are expenses that can be deducted from your "
"accounting result but not from your fiscal result."
msgstr ""
"**Pengeluaran yang tidak diperbolehkan** adalah pengeluaran yang dapat "
"dikurangkan dari hasil akuntansi Anda tetapi tidak dari hasil fiskal Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:191
msgid ""
"The **disallowed expenses report** is available by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Management: Disallowed "
"Expenses`. It allows financial results in real-time, and periodic changes. "
"This report is generated based on the **disallowed expenses categories** "
"that you can reach by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Management: Disallowed Expenses Categories`. Some categories already "
"exist by default but do not have any rates. Click on :guilabel:`Set Rates` "
"to update a specific category."
msgstr ""
"**Laporan pengeluaran yang tidak diperbolehkan** tersedia dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Manajemen: Pengeluaran "
"yang Tidak Diperbolehkan`. Ini memungkinkan hasil keuangan secara real-time "
"dan perubahan periodik. Laporan ini dibuat berdasarkan **kategori "
"pengeluaran yang tidak diperbolehkan** yang dapat Anda akses dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Manajemen: Kategori "
"Pengeluaran yang Tidak Diperbolehkan`. Beberapa kategori sudah ada secara "
"default tetapi tidak memiliki tarif. Klik :guilabel:`Atur Tarif` untuk "
"memperbarui kategori tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:199
msgid ""
"You can add multiple rates for various dates. In that case, the rate used to "
"calculate the expense depends on the date at which it is calculated, and the "
"rate set for that date."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menambahkan beberapa tarif untuk berbagai tanggal. Dalam hal ini, "
"tarif yang digunakan untuk menghitung pengeluaran tergantung pada tanggal "
"saat dihitung, dan tarif yang ditetapkan untuk tanggal tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:201
msgid ""
"If you have the **Fleet** app installed, tick the :guilabel:`Car Category` "
"box when applicable. This makes the vehicle mandatory while booking a vendor "
"bill."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda telah menginstal aplikasi **Armada**, centang "
"kotak :guilabel:`Kategori Mobil` jika berlaku. Ini membuat kendaraan wajib "
"saat membuat tagihan vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:204
msgid ""
"To link a disallowed expenses category with a specific account, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Accounting: Chart of "
"Accounts`. Find the account you want, and click on :guilabel:`Setup`. Add "
"the :guilabel:`Disallowed Expense category` in the :guilabel:`Disallowed "
"Expenses` field. From now, when an expense is created with this account, the "
"disallowed expense is calculated based on the rate mentioned in "
"the :guilabel:`Disallowed Expense category`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghubungkan kategori pengeluaran yang tidak diperbolehkan dengan "
"akun tertentu, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Akuntansi: "
"Bagan Akun`. Temukan akun yang Anda inginkan, dan klik :guilabel:`Atur`. "
"Tambahkan :guilabel:`Kategori Pengeluaran yang Tidak Diperbolehkan` di "
"field :guilabel:`Pengeluaran yang Tidak Diperbolehkan`. Mulai sekarang, "
"ketika pengeluaran dibuat dengan akun ini, pengeluaran yang tidak "
"diperbolehkan dihitung berdasarkan tarif yang disebutkan "
"dalam :guilabel:`Kategori Pengeluaran yang Tidak Diperbolehkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:210
msgid "Let's take an example reflecting **restaurant** and **car expenses**."
msgstr ""
"Mari kita ambil contoh yang mencerminkan pengeluaran **restoran** dan "
"**mobil**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:215
msgid "Restaurant expenses"
msgstr "Pengeluaran restoran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:217
msgid ""
"In Belgium, 31% of **restaurant** expenses are non-deductible. Create a new "
"**disallowed expenses category** and set both :guilabel:`Related Account(s)` "
"and :guilabel:`Current Rate`."
msgstr ""
"Di Belgia, 31% dari pengeluaran **restoran** tidak dapat dikurangkan. Buat "
"**kategori pengeluaran yang tidak diperbolehkan** baru dan "
"atur :guilabel:`Akun Terkait` dan :guilabel:`Tarif Saat Ini`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Disallowed expenses categories"
msgstr "Kategori pengeluaran yang tidak diperbolehkan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:226
msgid "Car expenses: vehicle split"
msgstr "Pengeluaran mobil: pembagian kendaraan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:228
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the deductible percentage varies from car to car and, therefore, "
"should be indicated for each vehicle. To do so, open :menuselection:`Fleet` "
"and select a vehicle. In the :guilabel:`Tax info` tab, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Disallowed Expenses Rate` section and click on :guilabel:`Add "
"a line`. Add a :guilabel:`Start Date` and a :guilabel:`%`. The amounts go in "
"the same account for all car expenses."
msgstr ""
"Di Belgia, persentase yang dapat dikurangkan bervariasi dari satu mobil ke "
"mobil lainnya dan, oleh karena itu, harus ditunjukkan untuk setiap "
"kendaraan. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Armada` dan pilih "
"kendaraan. Di tab :guilabel:`Info Pajak`, buka bagian :guilabel:`Tarif "
"Pengeluaran yang Tidak Diperbolehkan` dan klik :guilabel:`Tambah baris`. "
"Tambahkan :guilabel:`Tanggal Mulai` dan :guilabel:`%`. Jumlahnya masuk ke "
"akun yang sama untuk semua pengeluaran mobil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:234
msgid ""
"When you create a bill for car expenses, you can link each expense to a "
"specific car by filling the :guilabel:`Vehicle` column, so the right "
"percentage is applied."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda membuat tagihan untuk pengeluaran mobil, Anda dapat "
"menghubungkan setiap pengeluaran ke mobil tertentu dengan mengisi "
"kolom :guilabel:`Kendaraan`, sehingga persentase yang tepat diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:240
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`vehicle split` option available in the disallowed expenses "
"report allows you to see the rate and disallowed amount for each car."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`pembagian kendaraan` yang tersedia dalam laporan pengeluaran "
"yang tidak diperbolehkan memungkinkan Anda melihat tarif dan jumlah yang "
"tidak diperbolehkan untuk setiap mobil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:249
msgid "Fee form 281.50 and form 325"
msgstr "Formulir biaya 281.50 dan formulir 325"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:254
msgid "Fee form 281.50"
msgstr "Formulir biaya 281.50"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:256
msgid ""
"Annually, a **281.50 fee form** must be reported to the fiscal authorities. "
"To do so, the tag `281.50` must be added on the **contact form** of the "
"entities concerned by the **281.50** fee. To add the tag, "
"open :menuselection:`Contacts`, select the person or company you want to "
"create a **281.50 fee form** for, and add the `281.50` tag in "
"the :guilabel:`Tags` field."
msgstr ""
"Setiap tahun, **formulir biaya 281.50** harus dilaporkan kepada otoritas "
"fiskal. Untuk melakukannya, tag `281.50` harus ditambahkan pada **formulir "
"kontak** entitas yang terkait dengan biaya **281.50**. Untuk menambahkan "
"tag, buka :menuselection:`Kontak`, pilih orang atau perusahaan yang ingin "
"Anda buat **formulir biaya 281.50**, dan tambahkan tag `281.50` di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Tag`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "add the tag 281.50 on a contact form"
msgstr "tambahkan tag 281.50 pada formulir kontak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:265
msgid ""
"Make sure the **street, zip code, country**, and **VAT number** are also "
"informed on the **Contact form**."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan **jalan, kode pos, negara**, dan **nomor PPN** juga diinformasikan "
"pada **Formulir Kontak**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:268
msgid ""
"Then, depending on the nature of the expense, add the corresponding `281.50` "
"tag on the impact accounts. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Accounting: Chart of Accounts`, and click "
"on :guilabel:`Setup` to add the corresponding `281.50` tag on the impacted "
"accounts, i.e., :guilabel:`281.50 - Commissions`, depending on the nature of "
"the expense."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, tergantung pada sifat pengeluaran, tambahkan tag `281.50` yang "
"sesuai pada akun yang berdampak. Untuk melakukannya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Akuntansi: Bagan Akun`, "
"dan klik :guilabel:`Pengaturan` untuk menambahkan tag `281.50` yang sesuai "
"pada akun yang terdampak, yaitu :guilabel:`281.50 - Komisi`, tergantung pada "
"sifat pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:276
msgid "Form 325"
msgstr "Formulir 325"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:278
msgid ""
"You can create a **325 form** by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Belgium: Create 325 form`. A new page pops up: select the "
"right options and click :guilabel:`Generate 325 form`. To open an already "
"generated **325 form**, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Belgium: Open 325 forms`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membuat **formulir 325** dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi "
"--> Pelaporan --> Belgia: Buat formulir 325`. Halaman baru akan muncul: "
"pilih opsi yang sesuai dan klik :guilabel:`Buat formulir 325`. Untuk membuka "
"**formulir 325** yang sudah dibuat, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Pelaporan --> Belgia: Buka formulir 325`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Add the tag 281-50 on a contact form"
msgstr "Tambahkan tag 281-50 pada formulir kontak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:289
msgid "CODA and SODA statements"
msgstr "Rekening koran CODA dan SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:294
msgid "CODA"
msgstr "CODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:296
msgid ""
"**CODA** is an electronic XML format used to import Belgian bank statements. "
"You can download CODA files from your bank and import them directly into "
"Odoo by clicking :guilabel:`Import file` from your :guilabel:`Bank` journal "
"on your dashboard."
msgstr ""
"**CODA** adalah format XML elektronik yang digunakan untuk mengimpor "
"rekening koran bank Belgia. Anda dapat mengunduh file CODA dari bank Anda "
"dan mengimpornya langsung ke Odoo dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Impor file` "
"dari jurnal :guilabel:`Bank` Anda pada dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Import CODA files"
msgstr "Impor file CODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:304
msgid ":ref:`Import bank files <transactions/import>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Impor file bank <transactions/import>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:309
msgid "SODA"
msgstr "SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:311
msgid ""
"**SODA** is an electronic XML format used to import accounting entries "
"related to salaries. SODA files can be imported into the journal you use to "
"record salaries by going to your Accounting **dashboard** and "
"clicking :guilabel:`Upload` in the related journal card form."
msgstr ""
"**SODA** adalah format XML elektronik yang digunakan untuk mengimpor entri "
"akuntansi terkait gaji. File SODA dapat diimpor ke dalam jurnal yang Anda "
"gunakan untuk mencatat gaji dengan membuka **dashboard** Akuntansi Anda dan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Unggah` pada kartu formulir jurnal terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:315
msgid ""
"Once your **SODA** files are imported, the entries are created automatically "
"in your salary journal."
msgstr ""
"Setelah file **SODA** Anda diimpor, entri akan dibuat secara otomatis dalam "
"jurnal gaji Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Import SODA files"
msgstr "Impor file SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:323
msgid "CodaBox"
msgstr "CodaBox"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:325
msgid ""
"**CodaBox** is a service that allows Belgian companies and accounting firms "
"to access bank information and statements. Odoo provides a way to import "
"such statements automatically."
msgstr ""
"**CodaBox** adalah layanan yang memungkinkan perusahaan Belgia dan firma "
"akuntansi mengakses informasi dan rekening koran bank. Odoo menyediakan cara "
"untuk mengimpor rekening koran tersebut secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:331
msgid ""
"To configure and use Codabox, first :ref:`install <general/install>` "
"the :guilabel:`CodaBox` module."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengkonfigurasi dan menggunakan Codabox, pertama-tama :ref:`instal "
"<general/install>` modul :guilabel:`CodaBox`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:336
msgid "Configure the Connection"
msgstr "Konfigurasi Koneksi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:340
msgid "For companies"
msgstr "Untuk perusahaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:343
msgid ""
"Make sure the :doc:`company settings </applications/general/companies>` are "
"correctly configured, i.e., the country is set to :guilabel:`Belgium` and "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` or :guilabel:`Company ID` field is filled."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :doc:`pengaturan perusahaan </applications/general/companies>` "
"dikonfigurasi dengan benar, yaitu negara diatur ke :guilabel:`Belgia` dan "
"kolom :guilabel:`Tax ID` atau :guilabel:`ID Perusahaan` telah diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:347
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:376
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`CodaBox & SODA` section."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, lalu buka "
"bagian :guilabel:`CodaBox & SODA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:349
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, which "
"shows the :guilabel:`Company VAT/ID` number that will be used for the "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kelola Koneksi` untuk membuka wizard koneksi, yang "
"menampilkan nomor :guilabel:`VAT/ID Perusahaan` yang akan digunakan untuk "
"koneksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:351
msgid ""
"If this is your **first connection**, click on :guilabel:`Create "
"connection`. The wizard confirms that the connection has been created on "
"**Odoo's side**. Follow the steps to validate the connection on **CodaBox's "
"side** too."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini adalah **koneksi pertama** Anda, klik :guilabel:`Buat koneksi`. "
"Wizard mengonfirmasi bahwa koneksi telah dibuat di **sisi Odoo**. Ikuti "
"langkah-langkah untuk memvalidasi koneksi di **sisi CodaBox** juga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:355
msgid ""
"If this is **not your first connection**, the :guilabel:`Password` provided "
"by Odoo during the first connection will be requested to create a new "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini **bukan koneksi pertama** Anda, :guilabel:`Kata Sandi` yang "
"diberikan oleh Odoo selama koneksi pertama akan diminta untuk membuat "
"koneksi baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:359
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`Password` is unique to Odoo and must be stored securely on "
"your side."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kata Sandi` ini unik untuk Odoo dan harus disimpan dengan aman di "
"pihak Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:362
msgid "For accounting firms"
msgstr "Untuk kantor akuntan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:364
msgid ""
"Accounting firms must manage their clients on separate databases and "
"configure them individually to avoid mixing up their data. The connection "
"must be made by an accounting firm with valid CodaBox Connect credentials. "
"In the following instructions, we will refer to your client's company as "
"*Company* and to your accounting firm as *Accounting Firm*."
msgstr ""
"Kantor akuntan harus mengelola klien mereka pada database terpisah dan "
"mengonfigurasinya satu per satu untuk menghindari pencampuran data mereka. "
"Koneksi harus dibuat oleh kantor akuntan dengan kredensial CodaBox Connect "
"yang valid. Dalam instruksi berikut, kami akan menyebut perusahaan klien "
"Anda sebagai *Perusahaan* dan kantor akuntan Anda sebagai *Kantor Akuntan*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:371
msgid ""
"Make sure the :doc:`company settings </applications/general/companies>` are "
"correctly configured, i.e., the country is set to :guilabel:`Belgium`, "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` or :guilabel:`Company ID` and :guilabel:`Accounting "
"Firm` fields are filled, as well as the :guilabel:`Tax ID` of "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :doc:`pengaturan perusahaan </applications/general/companies>` "
"dikonfigurasi dengan benar, yaitu negara diatur ke :guilabel:`Belgia`, "
"kolom :guilabel:`ID Pajak` atau :guilabel:`ID Perusahaan` "
"dan :guilabel:`Kantor Akuntan` telah diisi, serta :guilabel:`ID Pajak` "
"dari :guilabel:`Kantor Akuntan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:378
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, which "
"shows the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` number and the :guilabel:`Company "
"VAT/ID` number that will be used for the connection."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kelola Koneksi` untuk membuka wizard koneksi, yang "
"menampilkan nomor :guilabel:`PPN Kantor Akuntan` dan nomor :guilabel:`PPN/ID "
"Perusahaan` yang akan digunakan untuk koneksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:381
msgid ""
"If this is your **first connection**, click on :guilabel:`Create "
"connection`. The wizard confirms that the connection has been created on "
"**Odoo's side**. Follow the steps to validate the connection on **CodaBox's "
"side**, too."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini adalah **koneksi pertama** Anda, klik :guilabel:`Buat koneksi`. "
"Wizard mengonfirmasi bahwa koneksi telah dibuat di **sisi Odoo**. Ikuti "
"langkah-langkah untuk memvalidasi koneksi di **sisi CodaBox** juga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:385
msgid ""
"If this is **not your first connection**, the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm "
"Password` provided by Odoo during the first connection will be requested to "
"create a new connection."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini **bukan koneksi pertama** Anda, :guilabel:`Kata Sandi Kantor "
"Akuntan` yang diberikan oleh Odoo selama koneksi pertama akan diminta untuk "
"membuat koneksi baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:389
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`Accounting Firm Password` is unique to Odoo and must be "
"stored securely on your side."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kata Sandi Kantor Akuntan` ini unik untuk Odoo dan harus disimpan "
"dengan aman di pihak Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:392
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Status` should have now switched to :guilabel:`Connected`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status` seharusnya sekarang telah berubah "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Terhubung`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:395
msgid "Configure the journals"
msgstr "Konfigurasi jurnal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:399
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:431
msgid "For CODA files"
msgstr "Untuk file CODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:401
msgid ":doc:`Create a new bank journal <../accounting/bank>`."
msgstr ":doc:`Buat jurnal bank baru <../accounting/bank>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:402
msgid "Set the right IBAN in the :guilabel:`Account Number` field."
msgstr "Atur IBAN yang tepat di kolom :guilabel:`Nomor Rekening`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:403
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`CodaBox synchronization` as the :guilabel:`Bank Feed`."
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`Sinkronisasi CodaBox` sebagai :guilabel:`Umpan Bank`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Configuration of a CODA journal."
msgstr "Konfigurasi jurnal CODA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:410
msgid ""
"When working with bank transactions that use different currencies, it is "
"recommended to create multiple journals with the same bank account but "
"different currencies."
msgstr ""
"Ketika bekerja dengan transaksi bank yang menggunakan mata uang berbeda, "
"disarankan untuk membuat beberapa jurnal dengan rekening bank yang sama "
"tetapi mata uang yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:413
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:437
msgid "For SODA files"
msgstr "Untuk file SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:415
msgid "Create a new miscellaneous journal."
msgstr "Buat jurnal lain-lain baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:416
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`CodaBox` section."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, lalu buka "
"bagian :guilabel:`CodaBox`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:418
msgid "Select the journal you just created in the SODA journal field."
msgstr "Pilih jurnal yang baru saja Anda buat di kolom jurnal SODA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Configuration of a SODA journal."
msgstr "Konfigurasi jurnal SODA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:425
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:569
msgid "Synchronization"
msgstr "Sinkronisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:427
msgid ""
"Once the connection is established, Odoo can be synchronized with CodaBox."
msgstr "Setelah koneksi terhubung, Odoo dapat disinkronkan dengan CodaBox."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:433
msgid ""
"CODA files are automatically imported from CodaBox every 12 hours. You do "
"not have to do anything. However, if you wish, it can also be done manually, "
"by clicking on :guilabel:`Fetch from CodaBox` in the Accounting Dashboard."
msgstr ""
"File CODA secara otomatis diimpor dari CodaBox setiap 12 jam. Anda tidak "
"perlu melakukan apa pun. Namun, jika Anda inginkan, ini juga dapat dilakukan "
"secara manual dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Ambil dari CodaBox` di Dashboard "
"Akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:439
msgid ""
"SODA files are automatically imported from CodaBox once a day as a draft. "
"You do not have to do anything. However, if you wish, it can also be done "
"manually by clicking on :guilabel:`Fetch from CodaBox` in the Accounting "
"Dashboard."
msgstr ""
"File SODA secara otomatis diimpor dari CodaBox sekali sehari sebagai draf. "
"Anda tidak perlu melakukan apa pun. Namun, jika Anda inginkan, ini juga "
"dapat dilakukan secara manual dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Ambil dari CodaBox` "
"di Dashboard Akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:443
msgid ""
"By default, if an account in the SODA file is not mapped to an account in "
"Odoo, the Suspense Account (499000) is used, and a note is added to the "
"created journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, jika akun dalam file SODA tidak dipetakan ke akun di Odoo, "
"Akun Suspensi (499000) digunakan, dan catatan ditambahkan ke entri jurnal "
"yang dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:447
msgid ""
"You can access the mapping between the SODA and Odoo accounts by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and clicking "
"on the :guilabel:`Open SODA Mapping` button in the :guilabel:`CodaBox` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengakses pemetaan antara akun SODA dan Odoo dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan "
"mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Buka Pemetaan SODA` di bagian :guilabel:`CodaBox`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:453
msgid "Potential issues"
msgstr "Masalah potensial"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:455
msgid "**CodaBox is not configured. Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr "**CodaBox tidak dikonfigurasi. Silakan periksa konfigurasi Anda.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:457
msgid ""
"Either the :guilabel:`Company VAT` or the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` is "
"not set."
msgstr ""
"Baik :guilabel:`PPN Perusahaan` atau :guilabel:`PPN Kantor Akuntan` tidak "
"ditetapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:459
msgid ""
"**No connection exists with these accounting firms and company VAT "
"numbers.** **Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr ""
"**Tidak ada koneksi dengan nomor PPN kantor akuntan dan perusahaan ini.** "
"**Silakan periksa konfigurasi Anda.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:462
msgid ""
"This can happen when checking the connection status, and "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` and :guilabel:`Company VAT` combination "
"still needs to be registered. This may happen if you have changed "
"the :guilabel:`Company VAT` after the connection was established. For "
"security reasons, you have to :ref:`recreate a connection <belgium/codabox-"
"configuration-connection>` for this :guilabel:`Company VAT`."
msgstr ""
"Ini dapat terjadi saat memeriksa status koneksi, dan "
"kombinasi :guilabel:`PPN Kantor Akuntan` dan :guilabel:`PPN Perusahaan` "
"masih perlu didaftarkan. Ini mungkin terjadi jika Anda telah "
"mengubah :guilabel:`PPN Perusahaan` setelah koneksi terhubung. Untuk alasan "
"keamanan, Anda harus :ref:`membuat ulang koneksi <belgium/codabox-"
"configuration-connection>` untuk :guilabel:`PPN Perusahaan` ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:468
msgid ""
"**It seems that your CodaBox connection is not valid anymore. Please connect "
"again.**"
msgstr ""
"**Sepertinya koneksi CodaBox Anda tidak lagi valid. Silakan hubungkan "
"kembali.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:470
msgid ""
"This can happen if you revoke Odoo's access to your CodaBox account or still "
"need to complete the configuration process. In this case, you must revoke "
"the connection and create a new one."
msgstr ""
"Ini dapat terjadi jika Anda mencabut akses Odoo ke akun CodaBox Anda atau "
"masih perlu menyelesaikan proses konfigurasi. Dalam hal ini, Anda harus "
"mencabut koneksi dan membuat yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:473
msgid ""
"**The provided password is not valid for this accounting firm.** **You must "
"reuse the password you received from Odoo during your first connection.**"
msgstr ""
"**Kata sandi yang diberikan tidak valid untuk kantor akuntan ini.** **Anda "
"harus menggunakan kembali kata sandi yang Anda terima dari Odoo saat koneksi "
"pertama Anda.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:476
msgid ""
"The password you provided is different from the one you received from Odoo "
"during your first connection. You must use the password you received from "
"Odoo during your first connection to create a new connection for this "
"accounting firm. If you have lost your password, you must first revoke the "
"Odoo connection on CodaBox's side (i.e., on your myCodaBox portal). Then, "
"you can revoke the connection on Odoo's side and :ref:`create a new one "
"<belgium/codabox-configuration-connection>`."
msgstr ""
"Kata sandi yang Anda berikan berbeda dari yang Anda terima dari Odoo saat "
"koneksi pertama Anda. Anda harus menggunakan kata sandi yang Anda terima "
"dari Odoo saat koneksi pertama Anda untuk membuat koneksi baru untuk kantor "
"akuntan ini. Jika Anda kehilangan kata sandi, Anda harus terlebih dahulu "
"mencabut koneksi Odoo di sisi CodaBox (yaitu, di portal myCodaBox Anda). "
"Kemudian, Anda dapat mencabut koneksi di sisi Odoo dan :ref:`membuat yang "
"baru <belgium/codabox-configuration-connection>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:483
msgid ""
"**It seems that the company or accounting firm VAT number you provided is "
"not valid.** **Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr ""
"**Sepertinya nomor PPN perusahaan atau kantor akuntan yang Anda berikan "
"tidak valid.** **Silakan periksa konfigurasi Anda.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:486
msgid ""
"Either the :guilabel:`Company VAT` or the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` is "
"not in a valid Belgian format."
msgstr ""
"Baik :guilabel:`PPN Perusahaan` atau :guilabel:`PPN Kantor Akuntan` tidak "
"dalam format Belgia yang valid."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:489
msgid ""
"**It seems that the accounting firm VAT number you provided does not exist "
"in CodaBox.** **Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr ""
"**Sepertinya nomor PPN kantor akuntan yang Anda berikan tidak ada di "
"CodaBox.** **Silakan periksa konfigurasi Anda.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:492
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` number you provided is not registered in "
"CodaBox. You may not have a valid CodaBox license linked to this VAT number."
msgstr ""
"Nomor :guilabel:`PPN Kantor Akuntan` yang Anda berikan tidak terdaftar di "
"CodaBox. Anda mungkin tidak memiliki lisensi CodaBox yang valid yang "
"terhubung dengan nomor PPN ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:495
msgid ""
"**It seems you have already created a connection to CodaBox with this "
"accounting firm.** **To create a new connection, you must first revoke the "
"old one on myCodaBox portal.**"
msgstr ""
"**Sepertinya Anda telah membuat koneksi ke CodaBox dengan kantor akuntan "
"ini.** **Untuk membuat koneksi baru, Anda harus terlebih dahulu mencabut "
"yang lama di portal myCodaBox.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:498
msgid ""
"You must go to your myCodaBox portal and revoke Odoo's access to your "
"CodaBox account. Then, you can :ref:`create a new connection <belgium/"
"codabox-configuration-connection>` on Odoo's side."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus membuka portal myCodaBox Anda dan mencabut akses Odoo ke akun "
"CodaBox Anda. Kemudian, Anda dapat :ref:`membuat koneksi baru <belgium/"
"codabox-configuration-connection>` di sisi Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:503
msgid ""
"To revoke the connection between Odoo and CodaBox, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`CodaBox` section, click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection`, "
"then click on :guilabel:`Revoke`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencabut koneksi antara Odoo dan CodaBox, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, gulir ke "
"bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`CodaBox`, klik :guilabel:`Kelola Koneksi`, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Cabut`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:511
msgid "Codaclean"
msgstr "Codaclean"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:513
msgid ""
"**Codaclean** is a service that allows Belgian companies and accounting "
"firms to access bank information and statements. Odoo provides a way to "
"import such statements and their transactions automatically."
msgstr ""
"**Codaclean** adalah layanan yang memungkinkan perusahaan Belgia dan firma "
"akuntansi mengakses informasi bank dan laporan mutasi. Odoo menyediakan cara "
"untuk mengimpor laporan tersebut dan transaksinya secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:523
msgid ""
"Make sure to :ref:`install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Codaclean` "
"(`l10n_be_codaclean`) module."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan untuk :ref:`menginstal <general/install>` "
"modul :guilabel:`Codaclean` (`l10n_be_codaclean`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:532
msgid "To connect Odoo with Codaclean, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghubungkan Odoo dengan Codaclean, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:534
msgid ""
"Open the Settings app, navigate to the :ref:`Companies <general/companies/"
"company>` section, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage "
"Companies` to make sure the company's :guilabel:`Country` is set "
"to :guilabel:`Belgium`."
msgstr ""
"Buka aplikasi Settings, navigasi ke bagian :ref:`Perusahaan <general/"
"companies/company>`, dan klik :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Kelola "
"Perusahaan` untuk memastikan :guilabel:`Negara` perusahaan diatur "
"ke :guilabel:`Belgium`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:537
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Codaclean` section."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan gulir ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Codaclean`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:539
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, enter the "
"Codaclean :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Password` and "
"click :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Kelola Koneksi` untuk membuka wizard koneksi, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Pengguna` dan :guilabel:`Kata Sandi` Codaclean, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`Hubungkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:542
msgid "The :guilabel:`Status` is updated to :guilabel:`Connected`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Status` diperbarui menjadi :guilabel:`Terhubung`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:545
msgid ""
"Once the connection is established, the :guilabel:`Manage Connection` wizard "
"provides two options:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah koneksi terbentuk, wizard :guilabel:`Kelola Koneksi` menyediakan dua "
"opsi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:547
msgid ""
"Update Codaclean credentials: Enter the new :guilabel:`Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Password`, then click :guilabel:`Change Credentials`."
msgstr ""
"Perbarui kredensial Codaclean: Masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Pengguna` "
"dan :guilabel:`Kata Sandi` baru, lalu klik :guilabel:`Ubah Kredensial`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:549
msgid ""
"Remove Codaclean connection: Click :guilabel:`Disconnect`; "
"no :guilabel:`Username` or :guilabel:`Password` is required."
msgstr ""
"Hapus koneksi Codaclean: Klik :guilabel:`Putuskan`; tidak "
"diperlukan :guilabel:`Nama Pengguna` atau :guilabel:`Kata Sandi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:555
msgid "Journal creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan jurnal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:557
msgid ""
"A specific bank journal must be created for Codaclean synchronization. To do "
"so, :doc:`create a new bank journal <../accounting/bank>`, make sure to "
"enter the correct IBAN in the :guilabel:`Bank Account Number` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`Codaclean Syncronization` in the :guilabel:`Bank Feeds` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Jurnal bank khusus harus dibuat untuk sinkronisasi Codaclean. Untuk "
"melakukannya, :doc:`buat jurnal bank baru <../accounting/bank>`, pastikan "
"memasukkan IBAN yang benar di kolom :guilabel:`Nomor Rekening Bank`, dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Sinkronisasi Codaclean` di kolom :guilabel:`Umpan Bank`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:563
msgid ""
"For bank transactions in different currencies, it is recommended to create a "
"separate journal for each currency, using the same bank account."
msgstr ""
"Untuk transaksi bank dalam mata uang berbeda, disarankan untuk membuat "
"jurnal terpisah untuk setiap mata uang, menggunakan rekening bank yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:571
msgid ""
"Once the connection is established, Odoo is synchronized with Codaclean, and "
"new CODA files received via Codaclean are checked every twelve hours."
msgstr ""
"Setelah koneksi terbentuk, Odoo disinkronkan dengan Codaclean, dan file CODA "
"baru yang diterima melalui Codaclean diperiksa setiap dua belas jam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:575
msgid ""
"To manually check for new CODA files, go to the Accounting Dashboard and "
"click :guilabel:`Fetch from Codaclean` on the relevant :ref:`journal "
"<belgium/codaclean-configuration-journal>` ."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa file CODA baru secara manual, buka Dashboard Akuntansi dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Ambil dari Codaclean` pada :ref:`jurnal <belgium/codaclean-"
"configuration-journal>` yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:581
msgid "Electronic invoicing with Peppol"
msgstr "Penagihan elektronik dengan Peppol"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:583
msgid ""
"As of 1 January 2026, all Belgian companies must be registered on the Peppol "
"network to send and receive electronic invoices."
msgstr ""
"Mulai 1 Januari 2026, semua perusahaan Belgia harus terdaftar di jaringan "
"Peppol untuk mengirim dan menerima faktur elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:586
msgid ""
"To activate Peppol, refer to the :ref:`Peppol documentation <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol>`, ensuring during :ref:`registration <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol-registration>` that:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan Peppol, lihat :ref:`dokumentasi Peppol <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol>`, pastikan selama :ref:`pendaftaran <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol-registration>` bahwa:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:589
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Peppol EAS` field is set to :guilabel:`0208 - Numero "
"d'entreprise / ondernemingsnummer / Unternehmensnummer`."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Peppol EAS` diatur ke :guilabel:`0208 - Numero "
"d'entreprise / ondernemingsnummer / Unternehmensnummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:591
msgid ""
"the :guilabel:`Peppol Endpoint` field is set to the company registry number."
msgstr ""
"bidang :guilabel:`Peppol Endpoint` diatur ke nomor registrasi perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:593
msgid ""
"In addition, when veryfing that a customer is :ref:`registered as a Peppol "
"participant <accounting/e-invoicing/contact-verification>`, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Format` field is set to :guilabel:`BIS Billing 3.0`."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, saat memverifikasi bahwa pelanggan :ref:`terdaftar sebagai "
"peserta Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/contact-verification>`, pastikan "
"bidang :guilabel:`Format` diatur ke :guilabel:`BIS Billing 3.0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:598
msgid ":ref:`Peppol documentation <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Dokumentasi Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:603
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:282
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:400
msgid "Cash discount"
msgstr "Diskon tunai"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:605
msgid ""
"In Belgium, if an early payment discount is offered on an invoice, the tax "
"is calculated based on the discounted total amount, whether the customer "
"benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"Di Belgia, jika diskon pembayaran awal ditawarkan pada faktur, pajak "
"dihitung berdasarkan jumlah total setelah diskon, baik pelanggan "
"memanfaatkan diskon tersebut maupun tidak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:608
msgid ""
"To apply the right tax amount and report it correctly in your VAT return, "
"set the tax reduction as :guilabel:`Always (upon invoice)`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menerapkan jumlah pajak yang tepat dan melaporkannya dengan benar "
"dalam pengembalian PPN Anda, atur pengurangan pajak "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Selalu (saat faktur)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:612
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:288
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:406
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:617
msgid "Fiscal certification: POS restaurant"
msgstr "Sertifikasi fiskal: POS restoran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:619
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the owner of a cooking business such as a restaurant or food "
"truck is required by law to use a government-certified **Cash Register "
"System** for their receipts. This applies if their yearly earnings "
"(excluding VAT, drinks, and take-away food) exceed 25,000 euros."
msgstr ""
"Di Belgia, pemilik usaha memasak seperti restoran atau truk makanan "
"diwajibkan oleh hukum untuk menggunakan **Sistem Kasir** yang disertifikasi "
"pemerintah untuk tanda terima mereka. Ini berlaku jika pendapatan tahunan "
"mereka (tidak termasuk PPN, minuman, dan makanan bawa pulang) melebihi "
"25.000 euro."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:623
msgid ""
"This government-certified system entails the use of a :ref:`certified POS "
"system <belgium/certified-pos>`, along with a device called a :ref:`Fiscal "
"Data Module <belgium/fdm>` (or **black box**) and a :ref:`VAT Signing Card "
"<belgium/vat>`."
msgstr ""
"Sistem bersertifikat pemerintah ini memerlukan penggunaan :ref:`sistem POS "
"bersertifikat <belgium/certified-pos>`, bersama dengan perangkat yang "
"disebut :ref:`Modul Data Fiskal <belgium/fdm>` (atau **kotak hitam**) "
"dan :ref:`Kartu Tanda Tangan PPN <belgium/vat>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:628
msgid ""
"Do not forget to register as *foodservice industry manager* on the `Federal "
"Public Service Finance registration form <https://"
"www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/enregistrement>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jangan lupa untuk mendaftar sebagai *manajer industri layanan makanan* pada "
"`formulir pendaftaran Federal Public Service Finance <https://"
"www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/enregistrement>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:634
msgid "Certified POS system"
msgstr "Sistem POS bersertifikat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:636
msgid ""
"The Odoo POS system is certified for databases hosted on **Odoo Online**, "
"**Odoo.sh**, and **On-Premise**."
msgstr ""
"Sistem POS Odoo disertifikasi untuk basis data yang dihosting di **Odoo "
"Online**, **Odoo.sh**, dan **On-Premise**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:640
msgid ":doc:`/administration/standard_extended_support`"
msgstr ":doc:`/administration/standard_extended_support`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:642
msgid ""
"A `certified POS system <https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/"
"systemes-certifies>`_ must adhere to rigorous government regulations, which "
"means it operates differently from a non-certified POS."
msgstr ""
"`Sistem POS bersertifikat <https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/"
"systemes-certifies>`_ harus mematuhi peraturan pemerintah yang ketat, yang "
"berarti sistem ini beroperasi secara berbeda dari POS yang tidak "
"bersertifikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:646
msgid "On a certified POS, you cannot:"
msgstr "Pada POS bersertifikat, Anda tidak dapat:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:648
msgid ""
"Set up and use the **global discounts** feature (the `pos_discount` module "
"is blacklisted and cannot be activated)."
msgstr ""
"Mengatur dan menggunakan fitur **diskon global** (modul `pos_discount` masuk "
"daftar hitam dan tidak dapat diaktifkan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:650
msgid ""
"Set up and use the **loyalty programs** feature (the `pos_loyalty` module is "
"blacklisted and cannot be activated)."
msgstr ""
"Mengatur dan menggunakan fitur **program loyalitas** (modul `pos_loyalty` "
"masuk daftar hitam dan tidak dapat diaktifkan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:652
msgid ""
"Reprint receipts (the `pos_reprint` module is blacklisted and cannot be "
"activated)."
msgstr ""
"Mencetak ulang tanda terima (modul `pos_reprint` masuk daftar hitam dan "
"tidak dapat diaktifkan)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:653
msgid "Modify prices in order lines."
msgstr "Mengubah harga dalam baris pesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:654
msgid "Modify or delete order lines in POS orders."
msgstr "Mengubah atau menghapus baris pesanan dalam pesanan POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:655
msgid "Sell products without a valid VAT number."
msgstr "Menjual produk tanpa nomor PPN yang valid."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:656
msgid "Use a POS that is not connected to an IoT box."
msgstr "Menggunakan POS yang tidak terhubung ke kotak IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:658
msgid ""
"The :doc:`cash rounding <../../sales/point_of_sale/pricing/cash_rounding>` "
"feature must be activated and set to a :guilabel:`Rounding Precision` of "
"`0,05` and a :guilabel:`Rounding Method` set as :guilabel:`Half-Up`."
msgstr ""
"Fitur :doc:`pembulatan tunai <../../sales/point_of_sale/pricing/"
"cash_rounding>` harus diaktifkan dan diatur ke :guilabel:`Presisi "
"Pembulatan` sebesar `0,05` dan :guilabel:`Metode Pembulatan` diatur "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Half-Up`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:661
msgid ""
"Taxes must be set as included in the price. To set it up, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`, and from "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` section, open the :guilabel:`Default Sales Tax` "
"form by clicking the arrow next to the default sales tax field. There, "
"click :guilabel:`Advanced Options` and enable :guilabel:`Included in Price`."
msgstr ""
"Pajak harus diatur sebagai sudah termasuk dalam harga. Untuk mengaturnya, "
"buka :menuselection:`POS --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan dari "
"bagian :guilabel:`Akuntansi`, buka formulir :guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan "
"Default` dengan mengklik panah di sebelah bidang pajak penjualan default. Di "
"sana, klik :guilabel:`Opsi Lanjutan` dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Termasuk dalam "
"Harga`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:665
msgid ""
"At the start of a POS session, users must click :guilabel:`Work in` to clock "
"in. Doing so allows the registration of POS orders. If users are not clocked "
"in, they cannot make POS orders. Likewise, they must click :guilabel:`Work "
"Out` to clock out at the end of the session."
msgstr ""
"Pada awal sesi POS, pengguna harus mengklik :guilabel:`Masuk Kerja` untuk "
"clock in. Melakukannya memungkinkan pendaftaran pesanan POS. Jika pengguna "
"tidak clock in, mereka tidak dapat membuat pesanan POS. Demikian pula, "
"mereka harus mengklik :guilabel:`Keluar Kerja` untuk clock out di akhir sesi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:670
msgid ""
"If you configure a POS to work with a :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)`, you "
"cannot use it again without it."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda mengonfigurasi POS untuk bekerja dengan :abbr:`FDM (Modul Data "
"Fiskal)`, Anda tidak dapat menggunakannya lagi tanpa FDM tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:676
msgid "Fiscal Data Module (FDM)"
msgstr "Modul Data Fiskal (FDM)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:678
msgid ""
"An FDM, or **black box**, is a government-certified device that works "
"together with the Point of Sale application and saves your POS orders "
"information. Concretely, a **hash** (:dfn:`unique code`) is generated for "
"each POS order and added to its receipt. This allows the government to "
"verify that all revenue is declared."
msgstr ""
"FDM, atau **black box**, adalah perangkat bersertifikasi pemerintah yang "
"bekerja bersama dengan aplikasi Point of Sale dan menyimpan informasi "
"pesanan POS Anda. Secara konkret, sebuah **hash** (:dfn:`kode unik`) "
"dihasilkan untuk setiap pesanan POS dan ditambahkan ke tanda terimanya. Ini "
"memungkinkan pemerintah untuk memverifikasi bahwa semua pendapatan "
"dinyatakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:684
msgid ""
"Only the FDM from **Boîtenoire.be** with the `FDM certificate number BMC04 "
"<https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/systemes-"
"certifies#FDM%20certifiés>`_ is supported by Odoo. `Contact the manufacturer "
"(GCV BMC) <https://www.boîtenoire.be/contact>`_ to order one."
msgstr ""
"Hanya FDM dari **Boîtenoire.be** dengan `nomor sertifikat FDM BMC04 <https://"
"www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/systemes-certifies#FDM%20certifiés>`_ "
"yang didukung oleh Odoo. `Hubungi produsen (GCV BMC) <https://"
"www.boîtenoire.be/contact>`_ untuk memesannya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:692
msgid ""
"Before setting up your database to work with an FDM, ensure you have the "
"following hardware:"
msgstr ""
"Sebelum menyiapkan database Anda untuk bekerja dengan FDM, pastikan Anda "
"memiliki perangkat keras berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:694
msgid "a **Boîtenoire.be** (certificate number BMC04) FDM;"
msgstr "FDM **Boîtenoire.be** (nomor sertifikat BMC04);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:695
msgid "an RS-232 serial null modem cable per FDM;"
msgstr "kabel null modem serial RS-232 per FDM;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:696
msgid "an RS-232 serial-to-USB adapter per FDM;"
msgstr "adaptor serial-ke-USB RS-232 per FDM;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:697
msgid "an :ref:`IoT Box <belgium/iotbox>` (one IoT box per FDM); and"
msgstr ":ref:`IoT Box <belgium/iotbox>` (satu IoT box per FDM); dan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:698
msgid "a receipt printer."
msgstr "printer tanda terima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:703
msgid "Black box module"
msgstr "Modul black box"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:705
msgid ""
"As a pre-requisite, :ref:`activate <general/install>` the `Belgian "
"Registered Cash Register` module (technical name: `pos_blackbox_be`)."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai prasyarat, :ref:`aktifkan <general/install>` modul `Belgian "
"Registered Cash Register` (nama teknis: `pos_blackbox_be`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "black box modules for belgian fiscal certification"
msgstr "modul black box untuk sertifikasi fiskal belgia"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:711
msgid ""
"Once the module is activated, add your VAT number to your company "
"information. To set it up, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Companies --> "
"Update Info`, and fill in the :guilabel:`VAT` field. Then, enter a national "
"registration number for every staff member who operates the POS system. To "
"do so, go to the :guilabel:`Employees` app and open an employee form. There, "
"go to :menuselection:`HR settings tab --> Attendance/Point of Sale`, and "
"fill in the :guilabel:`INSZ or BIS number` field."
msgstr ""
"Setelah modul diaktifkan, tambahkan nomor PPN Anda ke informasi perusahaan "
"Anda. Untuk menyiapkannya, buka :menuselection:`Settings --> Companies --> "
"Update Info`, dan isi kolom :guilabel:`VAT`. Kemudian, masukkan nomor "
"registrasi nasional untuk setiap anggota staf yang mengoperasikan sistem "
"POS. Untuk melakukannya, buka aplikasi :guilabel:`Karyawan` dan buka "
"formulir karyawan. Di sana, buka :menuselection:`HR settings tab --> "
"Attendance/Point of Sale`, dan isi kolom :guilabel:`INSZ or BIS number`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "ISNZ or BIS number field on employee form"
msgstr "Kolom nomor ISNZ atau BIS pada formulir karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:721
msgid ""
"To input your information, click on your avatar, go to :menuselection:`My "
"Profile --> Preference tab`, and enter your INSZ or BIS number in the "
"designated field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memasukkan informasi Anda, klik avatar Anda, buka :menuselection:`My "
"Profile --> Preference tab`, dan masukkan nomor INSZ atau BIS Anda di kolom "
"yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:725
msgid ""
"You must configure the :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)` directly in the "
"production database. Utilizing it in a testing environment may result in "
"incorrect data being stored within the FDM."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus mengonfigurasi :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)` langsung di "
"database produksi. Menggunakannya di lingkungan pengujian dapat "
"mengakibatkan data yang salah disimpan di dalam FDM."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:731
msgid "IoT Box"
msgstr "IoT Box"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:733
msgid ""
"In order to use an :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)`, you need a registered "
"IoT Box. To register your IoT box, you must contact us through our `support "
"contact form <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ and provide the following "
"information:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)`, Anda memerlukan IoT Box "
"yang terdaftar. Untuk mendaftarkan IoT box Anda, Anda harus menghubungi kami "
"melalui `formulir kontak dukungan kami <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ dan "
"memberikan informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:737
msgid "your VAT number;"
msgstr "nomor PPN Anda;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:738
msgid "your company's name, address, and legal structure; and"
msgstr "nama perusahaan Anda, alamat, dan struktur hukum; dan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:739
msgid "the Mac address of your IoT Box."
msgstr "alamat Mac dari IoT Box Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:741
msgid ""
"Once your IoT box is certified, :doc:`connect <../../general/iot/connect>` "
"it to your database. To verify that the IoT Box recognizes the FDM, go to "
"the IoT homepage and scroll down the :guilabel:`IOT Device` section, which "
"should display the FDM."
msgstr ""
"Setelah IoT box Anda tersertifikasi, :doc:`hubungkan <../../general/iot/"
"connect>` ke database Anda. Untuk memverifikasi bahwa IoT Box mengenali FDM, "
"buka halaman beranda IoT dan gulir ke bawah pada bagian :guilabel:`IOT "
"Device`, yang seharusnya menampilkan FDM."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Hardware status page on a registered IoT Box"
msgstr "Halaman status perangkat keras pada IoT Box yang terdaftar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:748
msgid ""
"Then, add the IoT to your POS. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale "
"--> Configuration --> Point of Sale`, select your POS, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Connected Device` section, and enable :guilabel:`IoT Box`. "
"Lastly, add the FMD in the :guilabel:`Fiscal Data Module` field."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, tambahkan IoT ke POS Anda. Untuk melakukannya, "
"buka :menuselection:`POS --> Configuration --> POS`, pilih POS Anda, gulir "
"ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Connected Device`, dan aktifkan :guilabel:`IoT "
"Box`. Terakhir, tambahkan FMD pada kolom :guilabel:`Fiscal Data Module`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:753
msgid ""
"To be able to use an FDM, you must at least connect one :guilabel:`Receipt "
"Printer`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk dapat menggunakan FDM, Anda harus menghubungkan setidaknya "
"satu :guilabel:`Receipt Printer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:758
msgid "VAT signing card"
msgstr "Kartu penandatanganan PPN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:760
msgid ""
"When you open a POS session and make your initial transaction, you are "
"prompted to enter the PIN provided with your :abbr:`VSC (VAT signing card)`. "
"The card is delivered by the :abbr:`FPS (Service Public Federal Finances)` "
"upon `registration <https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/"
"enregistrement>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda membuka sesi POS dan melakukan transaksi awal, Anda diminta "
"untuk memasukkan PIN yang diberikan dengan :abbr:`VSC (kartu penandatanganan "
"PPN)` Anda. Kartu tersebut dikirimkan oleh :abbr:`FPS (Service Public "
"Federal Finances)` setelah `pendaftaran <https://"
"www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/enregistrement>`_."

