#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:100
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>`, the accounts are mapped automatically to their "
"corresponding taxes, and the default account payable and account receivable "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"Dalam :doc:`Bagan Akun <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>`, akun "
"secara otomatis dipetakan ke pajak yang sesuai dan field default hutang "
"usaha dan piutang usaha."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:105
msgid ""
"The Brazil chart of accounts is based on the SPED CoA, which provides a "
"baseline of the necessary accounts."
msgstr ""
"Bagan Akun Brasil didasarkan pada SPED CoA, yang menyediakan basis akun-akun "
"yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:113
msgid ""
":doc:`Taxes <../accounting/taxes>` are automatically created and configured "
"when installing the Brazilian localization. Avalara uses some to compute "
"taxes on sales orders or invoices."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Pajak <../accounting/taxes>` secara otomatis dibuat dan dikonfigurasi "
"saat menginstal lokalisasi Brasil. Avalara menggunakan beberapa untuk "
"menghitung pajak pada sales order atau faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:116
msgid ""
"Taxes used for services must be manually added and configured, as the rate "
"may differ depending on the city where the service is offered."
msgstr ""
"Pajak yang digunakan untuk layanan harus ditambahkan dan dikonfigurasi "
"secara manual, karena tarifnya dapat berbeda tergantung pada kota tempat "
"layanan ditawarkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:120
msgid ""
"NFS-e can't be issued for service taxes created manually. "
"To :ref:`electronically send an NFS-e <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-"
"services>`, compute taxes using Avalara."
msgstr ""
"NFS-e tidak dapat diterbitkan untuk pajak layanan yang dibuat secara manual. "
"Untuk :ref:`mengirim NFS-e secara elektronik <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-"
"services>`, hitung pajak menggunakan Avalara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:124
msgid ""
"Do not delete taxes, as they are used for the AvaTax tax computation. If "
"deleted, Odoo creates them again when used in an |SO| or invoice, computing "
"taxes with AvaTax. However, the account used to register the tax must be "
"reconfigured in the tax's :guilabel:`Definition` tab, under "
"the :guilabel:`Distribution for invoices` and :guilabel:`Distribution for "
"refunds` sections."
msgstr ""
"Jangan hapus pajak, karena digunakan untuk penghitungan pajak AvaTax. Jika "
"dihapus, Odoo akan membuatnya lagi saat digunakan dalam |SO| atau faktur, "
"menghitung pajak dengan AvaTax. Namun, akun yang digunakan untuk mencatat "
"pajak harus dikonfigurasi ulang di tab :guilabel:`Definition` pajak, di "
"bawah bagian :guilabel:`Distribution for invoices` "
"dan :guilabel:`Distribution for refunds`."

