msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Transporter Brasil` menentukan siapa yang melakukan pengangkutan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:515
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Send`. In the pop-up window, click :guilabel:`Process "
"e-invoice` and any other options, such as :guilabel:`Download` "
"or :guilabel:`Email`. Finally, click :guilabel:`Send` to process the invoice "
"with the government."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Di jendela pop-up, klik :guilabel:`Proses "
"e-faktur` dan opsi lain seperti :guilabel:`Unduh` atau :guilabel:`Email`. "
"Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Kirim` untuk memproses faktur dengan pemerintah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:520
msgid ""
"All fields available on the invoice used to issue an electronic invoice are "
"also available on the sales order, if needed. When creating the first "
"invoice, the :guilabel:`Document Number` field is displayed and allocated as "
"the first number to be used sequentially for subsequent invoices."
msgstr ""
"Semua bidang yang tersedia pada faktur yang digunakan untuk menerbitkan "
"faktur elektronik juga tersedia pada Sales Order, jika diperlukan. Saat "
"membuat faktur pertama, bidang :guilabel:`Nomor Dokumen` ditampilkan dan "
"dialokasikan sebagai nomor pertama yang akan digunakan secara berurutan "
"untuk faktur berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:527
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:589
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:395
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:367
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:376
msgid "Credit notes"
msgstr "Nota kredit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:529
msgid ""
"If a sales return needs to be registered, a :ref:`credit note can be created "
"in Odoo <accounting/credit_notes/issue-credit-note>` and sent to the "
"government for validation."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengembalian penjualan perlu didaftarkan, :ref:`nota kredit dapat "
"dibuat di Odoo <accounting/credit_notes/issue-credit-note>` dan dikirim ke "
"pemerintah untuk validasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:533
msgid ""
"Credit notes are only available for electronic invoices for goods (NF-e)."
msgstr "Nota kredit hanya tersedia untuk faktur elektronik barang (NF-e)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:538
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:646
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:421
msgid "Debit notes"
msgstr "Nota debit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:540
msgid ""
"If additional information needs to be included or values that were not "
"accurately provided in the original invoice need to be corrected, "
"a :ref:`debit note can be issued <accounting/credit_notes/issue-debit-note>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika informasi tambahan perlu disertakan atau nilai yang tidak akurat dalam "
"faktur asli perlu diperbaiki, :ref:`nota debit dapat diterbitkan <accounting/"
"credit_notes/issue-debit-note>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:545
msgid ""
"Debit notes are only available for electronic invoices for goods (NF-e)."
msgstr "Nota debit hanya tersedia untuk faktur elektronik barang (NF-e)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:546
msgid ""
"Only the products included in the original invoice can be included in the "
"debit note. While changes can be made to the product's unit price or "
"quantity, products **cannot** be added to the debit note. The purpose of "
"this document is only to declare the amount to be added to the original "
"invoice for the same or fewer products."
msgstr ""
"Hanya produk yang tercantum dalam faktur asli yang dapat disertakan dalam "
"nota debit. Meskipun perubahan dapat dilakukan pada harga satuan atau "
"kuantitas produk, produk **tidak dapat** ditambahkan ke nota debit. Tujuan "
"dokumen ini hanya untuk menyatakan jumlah yang akan ditambahkan ke faktur "
"asli untuk produk yang sama atau lebih sedikit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:554
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:279
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:221
msgid "Invoice cancellation"
msgstr "Pembatalan faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:556
msgid ""
"It is possible to cancel an electronic invoice that the government validated."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk membatalkan faktur elektronik yang telah divalidasi oleh "
"pemerintah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:559
msgid ""
"Check whether the electronic invoice is still within the cancellation "
"deadline, which may vary according to each state's legislation."
msgstr ""
"Periksa apakah faktur elektronik masih dalam batas waktu pembatalan, yang "
"dapat bervariasi sesuai dengan peraturan masing-masing negara bagian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:567
msgid ""
"To cancel an e-invoice for goods (NF-e) in Odoo, click :guilabel:`Request "
"Cancel` and add a cancellation :guilabel:`Reason` on the pop-up that "
"appears. To send this cancellation reason to the customer via email, enable "
"the :guilabel:`E-mail` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatalkan e-faktur barang (NF-e) di Odoo, klik :guilabel:`Request "
"Cancel` dan tambahkan :guilabel:`Reason` pembatalan pada pop-up yang muncul. "
"Untuk mengirim alasan pembatalan ini ke pelanggan melalui email, aktifkan "
"kotak centang :guilabel:`E-mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:572
msgid ""
"This is an electronic cancellation, which means that Odoo will send a "
"request to the government to cancel the NF-e. It will then consume one |IAP| "
"credit, as an |API| call occurs."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah pembatalan elektronik, yang berarti Odoo akan mengirim permintaan "
"ke pemerintah untuk membatalkan NF-e. Ini akan menggunakan satu kredit |"
"IAP|, karena terjadi panggilan |API|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:580
msgid ""
"To cancel an e-invoice for services (NFS-e) in Odoo, "
"click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. There is no electronic cancellation "
"process in this case, as not every city has this service available. The user "
"needs to cancel this NFS-e on the city portal manually. Once that step is "
"completed, they can request the cancellation in Odoo, which will cancel the "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatalkan e-faktur layanan (NFS-e) di Odoo, klik :guilabel:`Request "
"Cancel`. Tidak ada proses pembatalan elektronik dalam kasus ini, karena "
"tidak setiap kota memiliki layanan ini. User perlu membatalkan NFS-e ini "
"secara manual di portal kota. Setelah langkah tersebut selesai, mereka dapat "
"meminta pembatalan di Odoo, yang akan membatalkan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:588
msgid "Correction letter"
msgstr "Surat koreksi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:590
msgid ""
"A correction letter can be created and linked to an electronic invoice for "
"goods (NF-e) that the government validated."
msgstr ""
"Surat koreksi dapat dibuat dan ditautkan ke faktur elektronik barang (NF-e) "
"yang telah divalidasi oleh pemerintah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:593
msgid ""
"To do so in Odoo, click :guilabel:`Correction Letter` and add a "
"correction :guilabel:`Reason` to the pop-up. To send the correction reason "
"to a customer via email, enable the :guilabel:`E-mail` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya di Odoo, klik :guilabel:`Correction Letter` dan "
"tambahkan :guilabel:`Reason` koreksi pada pop-up. Untuk mengirim alasan "
"koreksi ke pelanggan melalui email, aktifkan kotak centang :guilabel:`E-"
"mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:598
msgid ""
"Correction letters are only available for electronic invoices for goods (NF-"
"e)."
msgstr "Surat koreksi hanya tersedia untuk faktur elektronik barang (NF-e)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:603
msgid "Invoice number range invalidation"
msgstr "Pembatalan rentang nomor faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:605
msgid ""
"A range of sequences that are assigned to sales journals can be invalidated "
"by the government if they are not currently used **and** will not be used in "
"the future. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Journals`, open the journal, click the :icon:`fa-cog` (gear) icon, and "
"select :guilabel:`Invalidate Number Range (BR)`. On "
"the :guilabel:`Invalidate Number Range (BR)` wizard, add "
"the :guilabel:`Initial Number` and :guilabel:`End Number` of the range that "
"should be cancelled, and enter an invalidation :guilabel:`Reason`."
msgstr ""
"Rentang urutan yang ditetapkan untuk jurnal penjualan dapat dibatalkan oleh "
"pemerintah jika saat ini tidak digunakan **dan** tidak akan digunakan di "
"masa mendatang. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Configuration --> Journals`, buka jurnal, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog`, dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Invalidate Number Range (BR)`. Pada "
"wizard :guilabel:`Invalidate Number Range (BR)`, "
"tambahkan :guilabel:`Initial Number` dan :guilabel:`End Number` rentang yang "
"harus dibatalkan, dan masukkan :guilabel:`Reason` pembatalan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:614
msgid ""
"Invoice number range invalidation is only available for electronic invoices "
"for goods (NF-e)."
msgstr ""
"Pembatalan rentang nomor faktur hanya tersedia untuk faktur elektronik "
"barang (NF-e)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:615
msgid ""
"The journal's chatter records the log of the cancelled numbers, along with "
"the XML file."
msgstr "Chatter jurnal mencatat log nomor yang dibatalkan, beserta file XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:622
msgid ""
"When receiving an invoice from a supplier, encode the bill in Odoo by adding "
"all the commercial information and the same Brazilian-specific information "
"recorded on the :ref:`customer invoices <localizations/brazil/electronic-"
"documents>`."
msgstr ""
"Saat menerima faktur dari pemasok, encode tagihan di Odoo dengan menambahkan "
"semua informasi komersial dan informasi khusus Brasil yang sama seperti yang "
"tercatat pada :ref:`faktur pelanggan <localizations/brazil/electronic-"
"documents>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:626
msgid "These Brazilian-specific fields are:"
msgstr "Bidang-bidang khusus Brasil ini adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:629
msgid ":guilabel:`Document Type`: used by the vendor"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen`: digunakan oleh vendor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:630
msgid ":guilabel:`Document Number`: the invoice number from the supplier"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nomor Dokumen`: nomor faktur dari pemasok"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:631
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Freight Model`: **NF-e specific** how goods are planned to be "
"transported - domestic"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Model Pengiriman`: **khusus NF-e** bagaimana barang direncanakan "
"untuk ditransportasikan - domestik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:632
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Transporter Brazil`: **NF-e specific** who is doing the "
"transportation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pengangkut Brasil`: **khusus NF-e** siapa yang melakukan "
"transportasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:637
msgid "Point of sale NFC-e"
msgstr "POS NFC-e"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:639
msgid ""
"The NFC-e is a legal document that supports selling goods or merchandise to "
"the final customer. Like the :ref:`NF-e <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-"
"goods-nf-e>`, the electronic customer invoice is also issued in XML file "
"format and has an auxiliary document (DANFC-e) known as the *NFC-e Summary*. "
"This electronic document can be issued through **Odoo Point of Sale**."
msgstr ""
"NFC-e adalah dokumen legal yang mendukung penjualan barang atau merchandise "
"kepada pelanggan akhir. Seperti :ref:`NF-e <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-"
"goods-nf-e>`, faktur pelanggan elektronik juga diterbitkan dalam format file "
"XML dan memiliki dokumen tambahan (DANFC-e) yang dikenal sebagai *Ringkasan "
"NFC-e*. Dokumen elektronik ini dapat diterbitkan melalui **Odoo Point of "
"Sale**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:644
msgid ""
"Its legal validity is guaranteed by the digital signature and by each "
"Brazilian state's SEFAZ (Secretaria da Fazenda)."
msgstr ""
"Keabsahan legalnya dijamin oleh tanda tangan digital dan oleh SEFAZ "
"(Secretaria da Fazenda) setiap negara bagian Brasil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:648
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Avalara integration <localizations/brazil/avatax-account>` "
"operates on a credit-based system. Each operation that involves "
"communication with Avalara consumes one credit. The following operations "
"within the **Point of Sale** (POS) application are subject to credit "
"consumption:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Integrasi Avalara <localizations/brazil/avatax-account>` beroperasi "
"pada sistem berbasis kredit. Setiap operasi yang melibatkan komunikasi "
"dengan Avalara mengonsumsi satu kredit. Operasi berikut dalam aplikasi "
"**Point of Sale** (POS) dikenakan konsumsi kredit:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:653
msgid "Tax calculation at the time of sale"
msgstr "Perhitungan pajak pada saat penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:654
msgid "Electronic invoice issuance (NFC-e)"
msgstr "Penerbitan faktur elektronik (NFC-e)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:657
msgid ""
"Each step is billed separately. For example, calculating taxes and issuing "
"an invoice for the same POS transaction consumes two credits."
msgstr ""
"Setiap langkah ditagih secara terpisah. Misalnya, menghitung pajak dan "
"menerbitkan faktur untuk transaksi POS yang sama mengonsumsi dua kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:661
msgid ":doc:`Point of Sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Point of Sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:668
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Brazilian Accounting EDI for "
"POS` (`l10nbr_edi_pos`) module and make sure to activate :doc:`AvaTax <../"
"accounting/taxes/avatax>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Instal <general/install>` modul :guilabel:`Brazilian Accounting EDI "
"for POS` (`l10nbr_edi_pos`) dan pastikan untuk mengaktifkan :doc:`AvaTax <../"
"accounting/taxes/avatax>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:674
msgid "CSC details"
msgstr "Detail CSC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:676
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Taxes` section. In the :guilabel:`NFC-e configuration` "
"section, complete the following CSC (Taxpayer Security Code) fields:"
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan gulir ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Pajak`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Konfigurasi NFC-e`, lengkapi "
"bidang CSC (Kode Keamanan Wajib Pajak) berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:680
msgid ""
":guilabel:`CSC ID`: The *CSC ID* or *CSC Token* is an identification of the "
"taxpayer security code, which can have 1 to 6 digits and is available on the "
"official website of your state’s Department of Finance (SEFAZ)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID CSC`: *ID CSC* atau *Token CSC* adalah identifikasi kode "
"keamanan wajib pajak, yang dapat memiliki 1 hingga 6 digit dan tersedia di "
"situs web resmi Departemen Keuangan (SEFAZ) negara bagian Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:683
msgid ""
":guilabel:`CSC Number`: The *CSC Number* is a code of up to 36 characters "
"that only you and the Department of Finance know. It is used to generate the "
"QR Code of the NFC-e and ensure the authenticity of the DANFE."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nomor CSC`: *Nomor CSC* adalah kode hingga 36 karakter yang hanya "
"Anda dan Departemen Keuangan yang tahu. Ini digunakan untuk menghasilkan QR "
"Code NFC-e dan memastikan keaslian DANFE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:688
msgid ""
"The information required for these fields can be generated through the SEFAZ "
"website of each Brazilian State by the company's accountant."
msgstr ""
"Informasi yang diperlukan untuk bidang ini dapat dihasilkan melalui situs "
"web SEFAZ setiap negara bagian Brasil oleh akuntan perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:696
msgid ""
"Access the relevant :doc:`product form in POS <../../sales/point_of_sale/"
"configuration>`, then configure the :ref:`product <localizations/brazil/"
"products>`'s :guilabel:`Brazil Accounting` fields."
msgstr ""
"Akses :doc:`formulir produk yang relevan di POS <../../sales/point_of_sale/"
"configuration>`, kemudian konfigurasikan kolom :guilabel:`Akuntansi Brasil` "
"dari :ref:`produk <localizations/brazil/products>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:703
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:889
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1132
msgid "Point of sale"
msgstr "Point of sale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:705
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings` and make "
"sure that the relevant Point of Sale is :doc:`selected at the top of the "
"screen <../../sales/point_of_sale/configuration>`. Then, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` section and configure the :guilabel:`Brazilian "
"EDI` fields:"
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`POS --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan pastikan bahwa "
"POS yang relevan :doc:`dipilih di bagian atas layar <../../sales/"
"point_of_sale/configuration>`. Kemudian, gulir ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Akuntansi` dan konfigurasikan kolom :guilabel:`EDI Brasil`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:710
msgid ":guilabel:`Series`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Seri`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:711
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Next number`: the next NFC-e number in the sequence to be issued, "
"for instance, if the last number issued in SEFAZ is `100`, the *Next number* "
"will be `101`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nomor berikutnya`: nomor NFC-e berikutnya dalam urutan yang akan "
"diterbitkan, misalnya, jika nomor terakhir yang diterbitkan di SEFAZ adalah "
"`100`, *Nomor berikutnya* akan menjadi `101`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:717
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1213
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:136
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:314
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:230
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:141
msgid "Workflow"
msgstr "Workflow"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:722
msgid "Generating an NFC-e"
msgstr "Membuat NFC-e"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:724
msgid "To generate an NFC-e, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk membuat NFC-e, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:726
msgid ""
":ref:`Open the relevant point of sale shop and make a sale <pos/session-"
"start>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Buka toko point of sale yang relevan dan lakukan penjualan <pos/"
"session-start>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:727
msgid ""
"Validate the payment to calculate taxes and issue an NFC-e. The valid NFC-e "
"appears on the right side of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Validasi pembayaran untuk menghitung pajak dan menerbitkan NFC-e. NFC-e yang "
"valid muncul di sisi kanan layar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:None
msgid "NFC-e Success in a POS session."
msgstr "Keberhasilan NFC-e dalam sesi POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:734
msgid ""
"It is also possible to issue an NFC-e that identifies the customer by their "
"CPF/CNPJ. To do so, click :icon:`fa-user` :guilabel:`Customer`, search for "
"the customer, or create a new one."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk menerbitkan NFC-e yang mengidentifikasi pelanggan "
"berdasarkan CPF/CNPJ mereka. Untuk melakukannya, klik :icon:`fa-"
"user` :guilabel:`Pelanggan`, cari pelanggan, atau buat yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:737
msgid ""
"The following are mandatory fields to issue a CPF/CNPJ identified NFC-e:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut ini adalah bidang wajib untuk menerbitkan NFC-e yang teridentifikasi "
"CPF/CNPJ:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:740
msgid ""
":guilabel:`City` and :guilabel:`State` where the invoice is being issued"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kota` dan :guilabel:`Negara Bagian` tempat faktur diterbitkan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:741
msgid ":guilabel:`CPF/CNPJ`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`CPF/CNPJ`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:743
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Validate`. The NFC-e appears, highlighting the customer's "
"CPF on the print."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Validasi`. NFC-e muncul, menyoroti CPF pelanggan pada "
"cetakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:744
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Print` or :guilabel:`Send via e-mail` to deliver the "
"invoice to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Cetak` atau :guilabel:`Kirim via email` untuk mengirimkan "
"faktur kepada pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:749
msgid "NFC-e ticket print"
msgstr "Cetakan tiket NFC-e"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:751
msgid ""
"After :ref:`generating and validating the NFC-e <localizations/brazil/"
"generate-nfc-e>`, click :guilabel:`Print` to deliver the invoice."
msgstr ""
