#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:311
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: select :guilabel:`Sale` from the drop-down menu for "
"customer invoice journals."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipe`: pilih :guilabel:`Penjualan` dari menu drop-down untuk "
"jurnal faktur pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:312
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Point of sale type`: if the sales journal will be used for "
"electronic documents, the option :guilabel:`Online` must be selected. "
"Otherwise, if the journal is used for invoices imported from a previous "
"system or if you are using the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` "
"portal *Facturación MiPyme*, you can use the option :guilabel:`Manual`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipe point of sale`: jika jurnal penjualan akan digunakan untuk "
"dokumen elektronik, opsi :guilabel:`Online` harus dipilih. Jika tidak, jika "
"jurnal digunakan untuk faktur yang diimpor dari sistem sebelumnya atau jika "
"Anda menggunakan portal :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` "
"*Facturación MiPyme*, Anda dapat menggunakan opsi :guilabel:`Manual`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:316
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Documents`: check this field if the journal will use document "
"types. This field is only applicable to purchase and sales journals that can "
"be related to the different sets of document types available in Chile. By "
"default, all the sales journals created will use documents."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gunakan Dokumen`: centang field ini jika jurnal akan menggunakan "
"tipe dokumen. Field ini hanya berlaku untuk jurnal pembelian dan penjualan "
"yang dapat dihubungkan dengan berbagai set tipe dokumen yang tersedia di "
"Chili. Secara default, semua jurnal penjualan yang dibuat akan menggunakan "
"dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:320
msgid ""
"Next, from the :guilabel:`Jounal Entries` tab, define the :guilabel:`Default "
"Income Account` and :guilabel:`Dedicated Credit Note Squence` in "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Information` section. Configuring these fields is "
"required for one of the debit notes :ref:`use cases <chile/use-cases>`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, dari tab :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal`, tentukan :guilabel:`Akun "
"Pendapatan Default` dan :guilabel:`Urutan Nota Kredit Khusus` di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Informasi Akuntansi`. Mengkonfigurasi field ini diperlukan "
"untuk salah satu :ref:`kasus penggunaan <chile/use-cases>` nota debit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:327
msgid "CAF"
msgstr "CAF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:329
msgid ""
"A *folio authorization code* (CAF) is required for each document type that "
"will be issued electronically. The :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` is "
"a file the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` provides to the "
"issuer with the folios/sequences authorized for the electronic invoice "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"*Kode otorisasi folio* (CAF) diperlukan untuk setiap tipe dokumen yang akan "
"diterbitkan secara elektronik. :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` adalah "
"file yang disediakan oleh :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` "
"kepada penerbit dengan folio/urutan yang diotorisasi untuk dokumen faktur "
"elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:334
msgid ""
"Your company can request multiple folios and obtain several :abbr:`CAFs "
"(Folio Authorization Codes)` linked to different folio ranges. "
"These :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)` are shared within all "
"journals, so you only need one active :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` "
"per document type, and it will be applied to all journals."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan Anda dapat meminta beberapa folio dan mendapatkan "
"beberapa :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Codes)` yang terkait dengan rentang "
"folio yang berbeda. :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` ini dibagikan di "
"semua jurnal, jadi Anda hanya memerlukan satu :abbr:`CAF (Folio "
"Authorization Code)` aktif per tipe dokumen, dan akan diterapkan ke semua "
"jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:339
msgid ""
"Please refer to the `SII documentation <https://palena.sii.cl/dte/"
"mn_timbraje.html>`_ to check the details on how to acquire the :abbr:`CAF "
"(Folio Authorization Code)` files."
msgstr ""
"Silakan merujuk ke `dokumentasi SII <https://palena.sii.cl/dte/"
"mn_timbraje.html>`_ untuk memeriksa detail tentang cara memperoleh "
"file :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:343
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)` required by the :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` are different from production to test "
"(certification mode). Make sure you have the correct :abbr:`CAF (Folio "
"Authorization Code)` set depending on your environment."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` yang diperlukan oleh :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` berbeda dari produksi ke tes (mode "
"sertifikasi). Pastikan Anda memiliki :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` "
"yang benar yang diatur tergantung pada lingkungan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:348
msgid "Upload CAF files"
msgstr "Unggah file CAF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:350
msgid ""
"Once the :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` files have been acquired "
"from the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` portal, they need to "
"be uploaded in the database by navigating to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration: Chilean SII --> CAFs`. Then, click the :guilabel:`New` begin "
"the configuration. On the :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` form, "
"upload your :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` file by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Upload your file` button and then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah file :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` diperoleh dari "
"portal :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, file tersebut perlu "
"diunggah ke database dengan navigasi ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi: Chilean SII --> CAF`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk "
"memulai konfigurasi. Pada formulir :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)`, "
"unggah file :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` Anda dengan mengklik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Unggah file Anda` lalu klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:357
msgid ""
"Once uploaded, the status changes to :guilabel:`In Use`. At this moment, "
"when a transaction is used for this document type, the invoice number takes "
"the first folio in the sequence."
msgstr ""
"Setelah diunggah, status berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Digunakan`. Pada saat "
"ini, ketika transaksi digunakan untuk tipe dokumen ini, nomor faktur "
"mengambil folio pertama dalam urutan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:361
msgid ""
"The document types have to be active before uploading the :abbr:`CAF (Folio "
"Authorization Code)` files. In case some folios have been used in the "
"previous system, the next valid folio has to be set when the first "
"transaction is created."
msgstr ""
"Tipe dokumen harus aktif sebelum mengunggah file :abbr:`CAF (Folio "
"Authorization Code)`. Jika beberapa folio telah digunakan di sistem "
"sebelumnya, folio valid berikutnya harus diatur ketika transaksi pertama "
"dibuat."

