#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:195
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Identification Number` (VAT): Select the identification number "
"type and enter the identification number. If the identification number type "
"is :guilabel:`NIT`, the identification number must include the verification "
"digit at the end, prefixed by a hyphen (`-`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nomor Identifikasi` (VAT): Pilih jenis nomor identifikasi dan "
"masukkan nomor identifikasi. Jika jenis nomor identifikasi "
"adalah :guilabel:`NIT`, nomor identifikasi harus menyertakan digit "
"verifikasi di akhir, diawali dengan tanda hubung (`-`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:198
msgid ""
":ref:`Fiscal Information fields <localization/colombia/configuration/"
"company>` in the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Kolom Informasi Fiskal <localization/colombia/configuration/company>` "
"di tab :guilabel:`Penjualan & Pembelian`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:206
msgid ""
"Access the product's form via :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Products` and ensure that either the :guilabel:`UNSPSC Category` field "
"(found in the :guilabel:`Accounting tab`) or the :guilabel:`Internal "
"Reference` field (in the :guilabel:`General Information` tab) is configured."
msgstr ""
"Akses formulir produk melalui :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> "
"Produk` dan pastikan bahwa kolom :guilabel:`Kategori UNSPSC` (ditemukan "
"di :guilabel:`tab Akuntansi`) atau kolom :guilabel:`Referensi Internal` (di "
"tab :guilabel:`Informasi Umum`) telah dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:215
msgid ""
"To create or modify taxes, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, and select the related tax."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat atau mengubah pajak, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, dan pilih pajak yang terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:218
msgid ""
"If sales transactions include products with taxes, configure "
"the :guilabel:`Value Type` field in the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab. "
"Retention tax types (:guilabel:`ICA`, :guilabel:`IVA`, :guilabel:`Fuente`) "
"are also included. This configuration is used to display taxes correctly on "
"the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Jika transaksi penjualan menyertakan produk dengan pajak, konfigurasikan "
"bidang :guilabel:`Jenis Nilai` di tab :guilabel:`Opsi Lanjutan`. Jenis pajak "
"retensi (:guilabel:`ICA`, :guilabel:`IVA`, :guilabel:`Fuente`) juga "
"disertakan. Konfigurasi ini digunakan untuk menampilkan pajak dengan benar "
"pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Specific tax configurations per DIAN regulations."
msgstr "Konfigurasi pajak khusus sesuai peraturan DIAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:229
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:275
msgid "Sales journals"
msgstr "Jurnal penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:231
msgid ""
"Once the |DIAN| has assigned the official sequence and prefix for the "
"electronic invoice resolution, the sales journals related to the invoices "
"**must** be updated in Odoo. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and select an "
"existing sales journal or create a new one with the :guilabel:`Create` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Setelah |DIAN| menetapkan urutan dan prefix resmi untuk resolusi faktur "
"elektronik, jurnal penjualan yang terkait dengan faktur **harus** diperbarui "
"di Odoo. Untuk melakukannya, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Jurnal` dan pilih jurnal penjualan yang ada atau buat yang "
"baru dengan tombol :guilabel:`Buat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:236
msgid ""
"On the sales journal form, enter the :guilabel:`Journal Name` "
"and :guilabel:`Type`, then set a unique :guilabel:`Short Code` in "
"the :guilabel:`Journals Entries` tab. Then, configure the following data in "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab:"
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir jurnal penjualan, masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Jurnal` "
"dan :guilabel:`Jenis`, kemudian tetapkan :guilabel:`Kode Singkat` yang unik "
"di tab :guilabel:`Entri Jurnal`. Kemudian, konfigurasikan data berikut di "
"tab :guilabel:`Pengaturan Lanjutan`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:240
msgid ":guilabel:`Electronic invoicing`: enable UBL 2.1 (Colombia)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Faktur elektronik`: aktifkan UBL 2.1 (Kolombia)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:241
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Resolution`: resolution number issued by |DIAN| to the "
"company via their test set."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Resolusi Faktur`: nomor resolusi yang dikeluarkan oleh |DIAN| "
"kepada perusahaan melalui test set mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:243
msgid ":guilabel:`Resolution Date`: initial effective date of the resolution."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal Resolusi`: tanggal efektif awal resolusi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:244
msgid ":guilabel:`Resolution End Date`: end date of the resolution's validity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Akhir Resolusi`: tanggal akhir masa berlaku resolusi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:245
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Range of Numbering (minimum)`: first authorized invoice number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rentang Penomoran (minimum)`: nomor faktur pertama yang "
"diotorisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:246
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Range of Numbering (maximum)`: last authorized invoice number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rentang Penomoran (maksimum)`: nomor faktur terakhir yang "
"diotorisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Technical Key`: control key received from the |DIAN| portal test "
"set or from their web service in case of the production environment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kunci Teknis`: kunci kontrol yang diterima dari test set portal |"
"DIAN| atau dari layanan web mereka dalam kasus lingkungan produksi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:250
msgid ""
"When the database is configured for the :ref:`production environment "
"<localization/colombia/einvoice-configuration>`, instead of configuring "
"these fields manually, click the :guilabel:`Reload DIAN configuration` "
"button to obtain the |DIAN| resolution information from the |DIAN| web "
"service."
msgstr ""
"Ketika database dikonfigurasi untuk :ref:`lingkungan produksi <localization/"
"colombia/einvoice-configuration>`, alih-alih mengonfigurasi bidang ini "
"secara manual, klik tombol :guilabel:`Muat ulang konfigurasi DIAN` untuk "
"mendapatkan informasi resolusi |DIAN| dari layanan web |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Reload DIAN configuration button in sale journals."
msgstr "Tombol Muat ulang konfigurasi DIAN di jurnal penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:259
msgid ""
"The short code and resolution of the journal **must** match the ones "
"received in the |DIAN| portal test set or from the MUISCA portal."
msgstr ""
"Kode singkat dan resolusi jurnal **harus** sesuai dengan yang diterima di "
"test set portal |DIAN| atau dari portal MUISCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:261
msgid ""
"The :ref:`invoice sequence and prefix <localization/colombia/invoice-"
"creation>` **must** be correctly configured when the first invoice is "
"created. Odoo automatically assigns a prefix and sequence to the following "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Urutan dan prefix faktur <localization/colombia/invoice-creation>` "
"**harus** dikonfigurasi dengan benar saat faktur pertama dibuat. Odoo secara "
"otomatis menetapkan prefix dan urutan ke faktur berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:268
msgid "Purchase journals"
msgstr "Jurnal pembelian"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:270
msgid ""
"Once the |DIAN| has assigned the official sequence and prefix for the "
"*support document* related to vendor bills, the purchase journals related to "
"their supporting documents need to be updated in Odoo. The process is "
"similar to the configuration of the :ref:`sales journals <localization/"
"colombia/co-journals>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah |DIAN| menetapkan urutan dan prefix resmi untuk *dokumen pendukung* "
"yang terkait dengan tagihan vendor, jurnal pembelian yang terkait dengan "
"dokumen pendukung mereka perlu diperbarui di Odoo. Prosesnya mirip dengan "
"konfigurasi :ref:`jurnal penjualan <localization/colombia/co-journals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:276
msgid ""
"For more information on support document journals using the Carvajal "
"solution, review the `Documento Soporte - Localización de Colombia video "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmYsFcD7xzE&list=PL1-"
"aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=8>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang jurnal dokumen pendukung menggunakan "
"solusi Carvajal, tinjau `video Documento Soporte - Localización de Colombia "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmYsFcD7xzE&list=PL1-"
"aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=8>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:285
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chart of accounts </applications/finance/accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` is installed by default as part of the localization "
"module. The accounts are mapped automatically in taxes, default account "
"payable, and default account receivable. The chart of accounts for Colombia "
"is based on the PUC (Plan Unico de Cuentas)."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Bagan akun </applications/finance/accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` diinstal secara default sebagai bagian dari modul "
"lokalisasi. Akun dipetakan secara otomatis dalam pajak, akun hutang default, "
"dan akun piutang default. Bagan akun untuk Kolombia didasarkan pada PUC "
"(Plan Unico de Cuentas)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:295
msgid ""
"The official exchange rate for Colombia is provided by the `Banco de la "
"República <https://suameca.banrep.gov.co/estadisticas-economicas/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Nilai tukar resmi untuk Kolombia disediakan oleh `Banco de la República "
"<https://suameca.banrep.gov.co/estadisticas-economicas/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:298
msgid "To enable automatic exchange rate updates, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan pembaruan nilai tukar otomatis, ikuti langkah-langkah "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:301
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Currencies` section and "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates`."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke bagian :guilabel:`Mata Uang` dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Nilai Tukar "
"Mata Uang Otomatis`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:302
msgid ""
"Ensure that :guilabel:`[CO] Bank of the Republic` is selected as "
"the :guilabel:`Service`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :guilabel:`[CO] Bank of the Republic` dipilih "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Layanan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:303
msgid ""
"Select an :guilabel:`Interval` for how frequently the currency rate should "
"be automatically updated."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Interval` untuk seberapa sering nilai tukar mata uang harus "
"diperbarui secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:307
msgid "Main workflows"
msgstr "Alur kerja utama"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:314
msgid ""
"The following is a breakdown of the main workflow for electronic invoices "
"with the Colombian localization:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut adalah rincian alur kerja utama untuk faktur elektronik dengan "
"lokalisasi Kolombia:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:317
msgid "The user creates an invoice."
msgstr "User membuat faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:318
msgid "Odoo generates the legal XML file."
msgstr "Odoo menghasilkan file XML legal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:319
msgid ""
"Odoo generates the CUFE (Invoice Electronic Code) with the electronic "
"signature."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menghasilkan CUFE (Invoice Electronic Code) dengan tanda tangan "
"elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:320
msgid "Odoo sends a notification to DIAN."
msgstr "Odoo mengirimkan notifikasi ke DIAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:321
msgid "|DIAN| validates the invoice."
msgstr "|DIAN| memvalidasi faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:322
msgid "|DIAN| accepts or rejects the invoice."
msgstr "|DIAN| menerima atau menolak faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:323
msgid "Odoo generates the PDF invoice with a QR code."
msgstr "Odoo menghasilkan faktur PDF dengan kode QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:324
msgid ""
"Odoo compresses the attached document (containing the sent XML file and the "
"DIAN validation response) and the fiscal valid PDF into a :file:`.zip` file."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengompresi dokumen terlampir (berisi file XML yang dikirim dan respons "
"validasi DIAN) dan PDF yang valid secara fiskal menjadi file :file:`.zip`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:326
msgid ""
"The user sends the invoice (:file:`.zip` file) via Odoo to the acquirer."
msgstr "User mengirimkan faktur (file :file:`.zip`) melalui Odoo ke penerima."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:334
msgid ""
"The functional workflow taking place before an invoice validation does "
"**not** alter the main changes introduced with the electronic invoice."
msgstr ""
"Alur kerja fungsional yang terjadi sebelum validasi faktur **tidak** "
"mengubah perubahan utama yang diperkenalkan dengan faktur elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:337
msgid ""
"Electronic invoices are generated and sent to both the |DIAN| and the "
"customer. These documents can be created from the sales order or manually "
"generated. To create a new invoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Costumers --> Invoices`, and select :guilabel:`Create`. On the invoice form, "
"configure the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Faktur elektronik dibuat dan dikirim ke |DIAN| dan pelanggan. Dokumen-"
"dokumen ini dapat dibuat dari sales order atau dibuat secara manual. Untuk "
"membuat faktur baru, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> "
"Faktur`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Buat`. Pada formulir faktur, konfigurasikan "
"kolom-kolom berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:342
msgid ":guilabel:`Customer`: customer's information."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pelanggan`: informasi pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:343
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`: journal used for electronic invoices."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jurnal`: jurnal yang digunakan untuk faktur elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:344
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Electronic Invoice Type`: Select the type of document. By "
"default, :guilabel:`Factura de Venta` is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Faktur Elektronik`: Pilih jenis dokumen. Secara "
"default, :guilabel:`Factura de Venta` dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:346
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Lines`: Specify the products with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Baris Faktur`: Tentukan produk dengan pajak yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:349
msgid ""
"When creating the first invoice related to an electronic invoicing journal, "
"it is required to manually change the *sequence* of the invoice to the |"
"DIAN| format: `Prefix + Sequence`."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat faktur pertama yang terkait dengan jurnal penagihan elektronik, "
"diperlukan untuk mengubah *urutan* faktur secara manual ke format |DIAN|: "
"`Prefix + Sequence`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:352
msgid "For example, format the sequence from `SETP/2024/00001` to `SETP1`."
msgstr "Misalnya, format urutan dari `SETP/2024/00001` menjadi `SETP1`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:354
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:221
msgid "When done, click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr "Setelah selesai, klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:359
msgid "Electronic invoice sending"
msgstr "Pengiriman faktur elektronik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:361
msgid ""
"After the :ref:`invoice confirmation <localization/colombia/invoice-"
"creation>`, click :guilabel:`Send`. In the wizard that appears, make sure to "
"enable the :guilabel:`DIAN` and :guilabel:`Email` checkboxes to send an XML "
"to the |DIAN| web service and the validated invoice to the client fiscal "
"email and click :guilabel:`Send`. Then:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah :ref:`konfirmasi faktur <localization/colombia/invoice-creation>`, "
"klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Di wizard yang muncul, pastikan untuk mengaktifkan "
"kotak centang :guilabel:`DIAN` dan :guilabel:`Email` untuk mengirim XML ke "
"layanan web |DIAN| dan faktur yang divalidasi ke email fiskal klien, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Kirim`. Kemudian:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:366
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:238
msgid "The XML document is created."
msgstr "Dokumen XML dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:367
msgid "The CUFE is generated."
msgstr "CUFE dihasilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:368
