msgstr ""
"Invoice B2C atau invoice B2B lintas negara tidak dapat dikirim melalui "
"jaringan e-invoicing. Namun, setelah dikonfirmasi di Odoo, invoice ini "
"diajukan ke otoritas pajak melalui :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-"
"invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:255
msgid ""
"Domestic B2B invoices that are paid in cash are also submitted to the tax "
"authorities via :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-"
