msgstr ""
"Invoice B2B domestik yang dibayar tunai juga diajukan ke otoritas pajak "
"melalui :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-"
"reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:261
