#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:273
msgid ""
"In the Accounting dashboard, click :guilabel:`E-invoicing ready invoices` on "
"the relevant sales journal."
msgstr ""
"Di Dashboard Akuntansi, klik :guilabel:`E-invoicing ready invoices` pada "
"jurnal penjualan yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:276
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is :ref:`created <accounting/invoice/creation>` "
