msgid ""
"The account type is then flagged as :guilabel:`payable` "
"and :guilabel:`reconcilable` based on the account template."
msgstr ""
"Jenis akun kemudian ditandai sebagai :guilabel:`hutang` dan :guilabel:`dapat "
"direkonsiliasi` berdasarkan templat akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:639
msgid ""
"Journals are checked against the existing ones in Odoo to avoid duplicates, "
"even when importing multiple FEC files."
msgstr ""
"Jurnal diperiksa terhadap jurnal yang sudah ada di Odoo untuk menghindari "
"duplikasi, bahkan saat mengimpor beberapa file FEC."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:642
msgid ""
"If a journal with the same code already exists, the existing journal is used "
"instead of creating a new one."
msgstr ""
"Jika jurnal dengan kode yang sama sudah ada, jurnal yang ada digunakan alih-"
"alih membuat yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:645
msgid ""
"New journals have the prefix :guilabel:`FEC-` added to their name. For "
"example, :guilabel:`ACHATS` becomes :guilabel:`FEC-ACHATS`."
msgstr ""
"Jurnal baru memiliki awalan :guilabel:`FEC-` yang ditambahkan ke namanya. "
"Misalnya, :guilabel:`ACHATS` menjadi :guilabel:`FEC-ACHATS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:649
msgid ""
"Journals are *not* archived, allowing the user to manage them as desired."
msgstr ""
"Jurnal *tidak* diarsipkan, memungkinkan pengguna untuk mengelolanya sesuai "
"keinginan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:654
msgid "Journal type determination"
msgstr "Penentuan jenis jurnal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:656
msgid ""
"The journal type is not specified in the format (similar to the accounts) "
"and is initially created with the default type :guilabel:`general`."
msgstr ""
"Jenis jurnal tidak ditentukan dalam format (mirip dengan akun) dan pada "
"awalnya dibuat dengan jenis default :guilabel:`umum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:659
msgid ""
"At the end of the import process, the journal type is determined based on "
"the following rules regarding related moves and accounts:"
msgstr ""
"Pada akhir proses impor, tipe jurnal ditentukan berdasarkan aturan berikut "
"terkait pergerakan dan akun yang terkait:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`bank`: Moves in these journals always include a line (debit or "
"credit) impacting a liquidity account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`bank`: Pergerakan dalam jurnal ini selalu menyertakan baris "
"(debit atau kredit) yang memengaruhi akun likuiditas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`cash` / :guilabel:`bank` can be interchanged, so :guilabel:`bank` "
"is assigned when this condition is met."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`kas` / :guilabel:`bank` dapat dipertukarkan, "
"jadi :guilabel:`bank` ditetapkan ketika kondisi ini terpenuhi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`sale`: Moves in these journals mostly have debit lines on "
"receivable accounts and credit lines on tax income accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`penjualan`: Pergerakan dalam jurnal ini sebagian besar memiliki "
"baris debit pada akun piutang dan baris kredit pada akun pendapatan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid "Sale refund journal items are debit/credit inverted."
msgstr "Item jurnal pengembalian penjualan dibalik debit/kreditnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`purchase`: Moves in these journals mostly have credit lines on "
"payable accounts and debit lines on expense accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`pembelian`: Pergerakan dalam jurnal ini sebagian besar memiliki "
"baris kredit pada akun utang dan baris debit pada akun beban."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid "Purchase refund journal items are debit/credit inverted."
msgstr "Item jurnal pengembalian pembelian dibalik debit/kreditnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`general`: Used for everything else."
msgstr ":guilabel:`umum`: Digunakan untuk yang lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:675
msgid "A minimum of three moves is required to identify the journal type."
msgstr "Minimal tiga pergerakan diperlukan untuk mengidentifikasi tipe jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:676
msgid ""
"A threshold of 70% of the moves must meet the criteria for a journal type to "
"be determined."
msgstr ""
"Ambang batas 70% dari pergerakan harus memenuhi kriteria agar tipe jurnal "
"dapat ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:679
msgid ""
"Suppose we are analyzing the moves that share a "
"certain :guilabel:`journal_id`."
msgstr ""
"Misalkan kita menganalisis pergerakan yang memiliki :guilabel:`journal_id` "
"tertentu yang sama."

