#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:787
msgid "Liasse fiscale"
msgstr "Liasse fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:789
msgid ""
"The *liasse fiscale* (tax returns) is a collection of standardized financial "
"documents that businesses must submit annually to the tax authorities. It "
"comprehensively summarizes the company’s financial activities and determines "
"corporate taxes."
msgstr ""
"*Liasse fiscale* (laporan pajak) adalah kumpulan dokumen keuangan standar "
"yang harus diajukan oleh perusahaan setiap tahun kepada otoritas pajak. Ini "
"merangkum aktivitas keuangan perusahaan secara komprehensif dan menentukan "
"pajak perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:793
msgid ""
"`Teledec <https://www.teledec.fr>`_ is a platform used to prepare and submit "
"tax returns using data from accounting records. To synchronize your "
"accounting data stored in Odoo with Teledec and electronically send your "
"company's *liasse fiscale* to |DGFiP|, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""

