msgid ""
":guilabel:`GT Status`: Status result obtained in the |SAT| response. If the "
"file contains errors, a warning message displays the reason(s) and the email "
"is not sent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status GT`: Hasil status yang diperoleh dalam respons |SAT|. Jika "
"file mengandung kesalahan, pesan peringatan menampilkan alasan dan email "
