msgstr "Sistem e-Invoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:74
msgid ""
"Odoo is compliant with the **Indian Goods and Services Tax (GST) e-Invoice "
"system** requirements."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mematuhi persyaratan **sistem e-Invoice Pajak Barang dan Jasa (GST) "
"India**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:82
msgid "NIC e-Invoice registration"
msgstr "Pendaftaran e-Invoice NIC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:84
msgid ""
"You must register on the :abbr:`NIC (National Informatics Centre)` e-Invoice "
"portal to get your **API credentials**. You need these credentials "
"to :ref:`configure your Odoo Accounting app <india/e-invoicing-"
"configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus mendaftar di portal e-Invoice :abbr:`NIC (National Informatics "
"Centre)` untuk mendapatkan **kredensial API** Anda. Anda memerlukan "
"kredensial ini untuk :ref:`mengonfigurasi aplikasi Odoo Accounting Anda "
"<india/e-invoicing-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:88
msgid ""
"Log in to the `NIC e-Invoice portal <https://einvoice1.gst.gov.in/>`_ by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Login` and entering your :guilabel:`Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Password`;"
msgstr ""
"Masuk ke `portal e-Invoice NIC <https://einvoice1.gst.gov.in/>`_ dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Login` dan memasukkan :guilabel:`Username` "
"dan :guilabel:`Password` Anda;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:92
msgid ""
"If you are already registered on the NIC portal, you can use the same login "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda sudah terdaftar di portal NIC, Anda dapat menggunakan kredensial "
"login yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Register Odoo ERP system on e-invoice web portal"
msgstr "Mendaftarkan sistem ERP Odoo di portal web e-invoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:97
msgid ""
"From the dashboard, go to :menuselection:`API Registration --> User "
"Credentials --> Create API User`;"
msgstr ""
"Dari dashboard, buka :menuselection:`API Registration --> User Credentials --"
"> Create API User`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:99
msgid ""
"After that, you should receive an :abbr:`OTP (one-time password)` code on "
"your registered mobile number. Enter the OTP code and "
"click :guilabel:`Verify OTP`;"
msgstr ""
"Setelah itu, Anda akan menerima kode :abbr:`OTP (one-time password)` di "
"nomor ponsel terdaftar Anda. Masukkan kode OTP dan klik :guilabel:`Verify "
"OTP`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:101
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Through GSP` for the API interface, set :guilabel:`BVM IT "
"Consulting Services India Private Limited` as GSP, and type in "
"a :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Password` for your API. Once it is "
"done, click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Through GSP` untuk antarmuka API, atur :guilabel:`BVM IT "
"Consulting Services India Private Limited` sebagai GSP, dan "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Username` dan :guilabel:`Password` untuk API Anda. "
"Setelah selesai, klik :guilabel:`Submit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Submit API specific Username and Password"
msgstr "Kirim Username dan Password khusus API"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:299
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:142
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:126
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal.rst:42
msgid "Configuration in Odoo"
msgstr "Konfigurasi di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:113
msgid ""
"To enable the e-Invoice service in Odoo, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Configuration --> Settings --> Indian Electronic Invoicing`, and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Password` previously set for the API."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan layanan e-Invoice di Odoo, "
"buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> Indian "
"Electronic Invoicing`, dan masukkan :guilabel:`Username` "
"dan :guilabel:`Password` yang telah ditetapkan sebelumnya untuk API."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "Setup e-invoice service"
msgstr "Menyiapkan layanan e-invoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:120
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:308
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:475
msgid ""
"Additionally, make sure the :ref:`GSP field is configured <india/"
"gsp_configuration>` in the Accounting settings."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, pastikan :ref:`kolom GSP dikonfigurasi <india/"
"gsp_configuration>` di pengaturan Akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:128
msgid ""
"To automatically send e-Invoices to the NIC e-Invoice portal, you must first "
"configure your *sales* journal by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals`, opening your *sales* journal, and in "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab, under :guilabel:`Electronic Data "
"Interchange`, enable :guilabel:`E-Invoice (IN)` and save."
msgstr ""
"Untuk secara otomatis mengirim e-Invoice ke portal e-Invoice NIC, Anda harus "
"terlebih dahulu mengonfigurasi jurnal *sales* Anda dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, membuka "
"jurnal *sales* Anda, dan di tab :guilabel:`Advanced Settings`, di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Electronic Data Interchange`, aktifkan :guilabel:`E-Invoice "
"(IN)` dan simpan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:141
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:330
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:447
msgid "Invoice validation"
msgstr "Validasi faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:143
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is validated, a confirmation message is displayed at the "
"top. Odoo automatically uploads the JSON-signed file of validated invoices "
"to the NIC e-Invoice portal after some time. If you want to process the "
"invoice immediately, click :guilabel:`Process now`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah faktur divalidasi, pesan konfirmasi ditampilkan di bagian atas. Odoo "
"secara otomatis mengunggah file JSON yang ditandatangani dari faktur yang "
"divalidasi ke portal e-Invoice NIC setelah beberapa waktu. Jika Anda ingin "
"memproses faktur segera, klik :guilabel:`Process now`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "Indian e-invoicing confirmation message"
msgstr "Pesan konfirmasi e-invoicing India"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:151
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:339
msgid "You can find the JSON-signed file in the attached files in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menemukan file yang ditandatangani JSON di file terlampir dalam "
"chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:152
msgid ""
"You can check the document's :abbr:`EDI (electronic data interchange)` "
"status under the :guilabel:`EDI Document` tab or the :guilabel:`Electronic "
"invoicing` field of the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memeriksa status :abbr:`EDI (electronic data interchange)` "
"dokumen di bawah tab :guilabel:`EDI Document` atau "
"bidang :guilabel:`Electronic invoicing` pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:160
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is validated and submitted, the invoice PDF report can be "
"printed. The report includes the :abbr:`IRN (Invoice Reference "
"Number)`, :guilabel:`Ack. No` (acknowledgment number) and :guilabel:`Ack. "
"Date` (acknowledgment date), and QR code. These certify that the invoice is "
"a valid fiscal document."
msgstr ""
"Setelah faktur divalidasi dan dikirim, laporan PDF faktur dapat dicetak. "
"Laporan tersebut mencakup :abbr:`IRN (Invoice Reference "
"Number)`, :guilabel:`Ack. No` (nomor pengakuan) dan :guilabel:`Ack. Date` "
"(tanggal pengakuan), serta kode QR. Ini membuktikan bahwa faktur adalah "
"dokumen fiskal yang sah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "IRN and QR code"
msgstr "IRN dan kode QR"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:171
msgid "e-Invoice cancellation"
msgstr "Pembatalan e-Invoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:173
msgid ""
"If you want to cancel an e-Invoice, go to the :guilabel:`Other info` tab of "
"the invoice and fill out the :guilabel:`Cancel reason` and :guilabel:`Cancel "
"remarks` fields. Then, click :guilabel:`Request EDI cancellation`. The "
"status of the :guilabel:`Electronic invoicing` field changes "
"to :guilabel:`To Cancel`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda ingin membatalkan e-Invoice, buka tab :guilabel:`Other info` pada "
"faktur dan isi bidang :guilabel:`Cancel reason` dan :guilabel:`Cancel "
"remarks`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Request EDI cancellation`. Status "
"bidang :guilabel:`Electronic invoicing` berubah menjadi :guilabel:`To "
"Cancel`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:179
msgid ""
"Doing so cancels both the :ref:`e-Invoice <india/e-invoicing>` and "
"the :ref:`E-Way bill <india/e-waybill>`."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan ini akan membatalkan :ref:`e-Invoice <india/e-invoicing>` "
"dan :ref:`E-Way bill <india/e-waybill>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "cancel reason and remarks"
msgstr "alasan dan keterangan pembatalan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:186
msgid ""
"If you want to abort the cancellation before processing the invoice, then "
"click :guilabel:`Call Off EDI Cancellation`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda ingin membatalkan permintaan pembatalan sebelum memproses faktur, "
"klik :guilabel:`Call Off EDI Cancellation`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:188
msgid ""
"Once you request to cancel the e-Invoice, Odoo automatically submits the "
"JSON-signed file to the NIC e-Invoice portal. You can "
"click :guilabel:`Process now` if you want to process the invoice immediately."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda meminta untuk membatalkan e-Invoice, Odoo secara otomatis "
"mengirimkan file JSON yang ditandatangani ke portal e-Invoice NIC. Anda "
"dapat mengklik :guilabel:`Process now` jika ingin memproses faktur segera."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:195
msgid "Management of negative lines in e-Invoices"
msgstr "Pengelolaan baris negatif dalam e-Invoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:197
msgid ""
"Negative lines are typically used to represent discounts or adjustments "
"associated with specific products or global discounts. The government portal "
"prohibits the submission of data with negative lines, which means they need "
"to be converted based on the HSN code and GST rate. This is done "
"automatically by Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Baris negatif biasanya digunakan untuk mewakili diskon atau penyesuaian yang "
"terkait dengan produk tertentu atau diskon global. Portal pemerintah "
"melarang pengiriman data dengan baris negatif, yang berarti baris tersebut "
"perlu dikonversi berdasarkan kode HSN dan tarif GST. Hal ini dilakukan "
"secara otomatis oleh Odoo."

