#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:90
msgid ""
"Many of the e-invoicing features are implemented using Odoo's tax system. As "
"such, taxes must be properly configured to generate invoices correctly and "
"handle other billing use cases."
msgstr ""
"Banyak fitur e-invoicing diimplementasikan menggunakan sistem pajak Odoo. "
"Oleh karena itu, pajak harus dikonfigurasi dengan benar untuk menghasilkan "
"invoice dengan benar dan menangani kasus penagihan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:93
msgid ""
"The **Italian** localization contains predefined **examples** of taxes for "
"various purposes."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi **Italia** berisi **contoh** pajak yang telah ditentukan "
"sebelumnya untuk berbagai tujuan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:98
msgid "Tax exemption"
msgstr "Pembebasan pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:100
msgid ""
"The use of sale taxes that amount to **zero percent** (0%) is required by "
"Italian authorities to keep track of the exact :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Kind "
"(Natura)` and :guilabel:`Law Reference` that justify the exemption operated "
"on an invoice line."
msgstr ""
"Penggunaan pajak penjualan yang berjumlah **nol persen** (0%) diperlukan "
"oleh otoritas Italia untuk melacak :guilabel:`Jenis Pembebasan Pajak "
"(Natura)` dan :guilabel:`Referensi Hukum` yang tepat yang membenarkan "
"pembebasan yang dilakukan pada baris invoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:105
msgid ""
"The export tax in the EU can be used as reference (`0% EU`, invoice label "
"`00eu`). It can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Taxes`. Exports are exempt from VAT, and therefore, they "
"require :guilabel:`Exoneration` kind and :guilabel:`Law Reference` filled in."
msgstr ""
"Pajak ekspor di UE dapat digunakan sebagai referensi (`0% EU`, label invoice "
"`00eu`). Ini dapat ditemukan di :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --"
"> Pajak`. Ekspor bebas dari PPN, dan oleh karena itu, "
"memerlukan :guilabel:`Pembebasan` jenis dan :guilabel:`Referensi Hukum` yang "
"diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Tax Exemption Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Pembebasan Pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:113
msgid ""
"There are many :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Kind (Natura)` and :guilabel:`Law "
"Reference` codes. Make sure you check the latest version available to get "
"the latest information on:"
msgstr ""
"Ada banyak kode :guilabel:`Jenis Pembebasan Pajak (Natura)` "
"dan :guilabel:`Referensi Hukum`. Pastikan Anda memeriksa versi terbaru yang "
"tersedia untuk mendapatkan informasi terbaru tentang:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:116
msgid ""
"`Italian authorities documentation <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale/web/guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentasi otoritas Italia <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/web/"
"guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:117
msgid ""
"`Official guide on Tax exemption <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/"
"documents/20143/451259/Guida_compilazione-FE-Esterometro-"
"V_1.9_2024-03-05.pdf/67fe4c2d-1174-e8de-f1ee-cea77b7f5203>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Panduan resmi tentang pembebasan pajak <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale/documents/20143/451259/Guida_compilazione-FE-Esterometro-"
"V_1.9_2024-03-05.pdf/67fe4c2d-1174-e8de-f1ee-cea77b7f5203>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:120
msgid ""
"If you need to use a different kind of exoneration, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes`, select a similar "
"tax, then click on the cog icon and select :guilabel:`Duplicate`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, add the :guilabel:`Exoneration` "
"and :guilabel:`Law Reference`. To confirm click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda perlu menggunakan jenis pembebasan yang berbeda, "
"buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pajak`, pilih pajak "
"serupa, lalu klik ikon roda gigi dan pilih :guilabel:`Duplikasi`. Di "
"tab :guilabel:`Opsi Lanjutan`, tambahkan :guilabel:`Pembebasan` "
"dan :guilabel:`Referensi Hukum`. Untuk mengonfirmasi, "
"klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:126
msgid ""
"**Rename** your taxes in the :guilabel:`Name` field according to "
"their :guilabel:`Exoneration` to differentiate them easily."
msgstr ""
"**Ubah nama** pajak Anda di kolom :guilabel:`Nama` sesuai "
"dengan :guilabel:`Pembebasan` mereka untuk membedakannya dengan mudah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:132
msgid "Reverse charge"
msgstr "Reverse charge"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:134
msgid ""
"The **reverse charge** mechanism is a VAT rule that shifts the liability to "
"pay VAT from the supplier to the customer. The customers pay the VAT "
"*themselves* to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` instead. There are "
"different types:"
msgstr ""
"Mekanisme **reverse charge** adalah aturan PPN yang mengalihkan kewajiban "
"membayar PPN dari pemasok ke pelanggan. Pelanggan membayar PPN *sendiri* "
"ke :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Ada berbagai jenis:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Internal Reverse Charge` (for domestic sales)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reverse Charge Internal` (untuk penjualan domestik)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"The VAT responsibility is shifted to the buyer for certain categories of "
"products and services."
msgstr ""
"Tanggung jawab PPN dialihkan kepada pembeli untuk kategori produk dan "
"layanan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`External Reverse Charge` (for intra-EU sales)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reverse Charge Eksternal` (untuk penjualan intra-EU)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"VAT is due in the country of the delivery or in the country where the "
"service is performed. When the buyer is itself an Italian business, then the "
"EU offers a mechanism that allows the seller to transfer his responsibility "
"to the buyer."
msgstr ""
"PPN jatuh tempo di negara pengiriman atau di negara tempat layanan "
"dilakukan. Ketika pembeli itu sendiri adalah bisnis Italia, maka EU "
"menawarkan mekanisme yang memungkinkan penjual untuk mengalihkan tanggung "
"jawabnya kepada pembeli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:586
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:230
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:204
msgid "Invoices"
msgstr "Faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:150
msgid ""
"**Reverse-charged** customer invoices show no VAT amount, but the :abbr:`AdE "
"(Agenzia delle Entrate)` requires the seller to specify the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Exemption` reason and the :guilabel:`Law Reference` that enable the reverse-"
"charge mechanism. Odoo provides a set of special 0% taxes that can be "
"assigned to each reverse-charged invoice lines, representing the most "
"commonly used configurations."
msgstr ""
"Faktur pelanggan **reverse-charged** tidak menunjukkan jumlah PPN, "
"tetapi :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` mewajibkan penjual untuk "
"menentukan alasan :guilabel:`Tax Exemption` dan :guilabel:`Law Reference` "
"yang memungkinkan mekanisme reverse-charge. Odoo menyediakan serangkaian "
"pajak khusus 0% yang dapat ditetapkan ke setiap baris faktur reverse-"
"charged, mewakili konfigurasi yang paling umum digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:161
msgid ""
"Italian companies subjected to Reverse Charge must send the information in "
"the bill received to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan Italia yang dikenakan Reverse Charge harus mengirimkan informasi "
"dalam tagihan yang diterima ke :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:165
msgid ""
"Self-reported VAT XML files must be issued and sent to the :abbr:`AdE "
"(Agenzia Delle Entrate)` for reverse charged bills."
msgstr ""
"File XML PPN yang dilaporkan sendiri harus diterbitkan dan dikirim "
"ke :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` untuk tagihan reverse charge."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:168
msgid ""
"When creating a vendor bill, **reverse charge** taxes are available to be "
"added in the :guilabel:`Taxes` field. You can check which taxes are "
"available by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Taxes`, you can see that the 10% Goods and 22% Services taxes are activated, "
"among others. Due to the automated configuration of the Italian fiscal "
"position, these are automatically activated in the tax list."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat tagihan vendor, pajak **reverse charge** tersedia untuk "
"ditambahkan di kolom :guilabel:`Pajak`. Anda dapat memeriksa pajak mana yang "
"tersedia dengan membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pajak`, Anda dapat melihat bahwa pajak Barang 10% dan Layanan 22% "
"diaktifkan, di antara yang lainnya. Karena konfigurasi otomatis posisi "
"fiskal Italia, pajak ini secara otomatis diaktifkan dalam daftar pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:177
msgid "Tax grids"
msgstr "Grid pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:179
msgid ""
"The Italian localization has a specific :ref:`tax grid <tax-returns/tax-"
"grids>` section for **reverse charge** taxes. These tax grids are "
"identifiable by the :guilabel:`VJ` tag, and can be found by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Return`."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi Italia memiliki bagian :ref:`kisi pajak <tax-returns/tax-grids>` "
"khusus untuk pajak **reverse charge**. Kisi pajak ini dapat diidentifikasi "
"dengan tag :guilabel:`VJ`, dan dapat ditemukan dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelaporan --> Pengembalian Pajak`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Reverse charge tax grid from the VJ section of the Tax Declaration"
msgstr "Grid pajak reverse charge dari bagian VJ Deklarasi Pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:192
msgid ""
"Make sure all the Italian-specific e-invoicing modules are :ref:`installed "
"<general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan semua modul e-invoicing khusus Italia telah :ref:`diinstal <general/"
"install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:194
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` is the :doc:`electronic invoicing "
"<../accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing>` system used in "
"Italy. It enables the sending and receiving of electronic invoices to and "
"from customers. The documents must be in an XML :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data "
"Interchange)` format called **FatturaPA** and formally validated by the "
"system before being delivered."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` adalah sistem :doc:`faktur elektronik "
"<../accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing>` yang digunakan di "
"Italia. Sistem ini memungkinkan pengiriman dan penerimaan faktur elektronik "
"ke dan dari pelanggan. Dokumen harus dalam format XML :abbr:`EDI (Electronic "
"Data Interchange)` yang disebut **FatturaPA** dan divalidasi secara formal "
"oleh sistem sebelum dikirimkan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:200
msgid ""
"To be able to receive invoices and notifications, the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)` service must be notified that the user's files need to be "
"sent to Odoo and processed on their behalf. To do so, you must set up "
"Odoo's :guilabel:`Destination Code` on the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle "
"Entrate)` portal."
msgstr ""
"Untuk dapat menerima faktur dan notifikasi, layanan :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)` harus diberitahu bahwa file user perlu dikirim ke Odoo dan "
"diproses atas nama mereka. Untuk melakukannya, Anda harus "
"mengatur :guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` Odoo di portal :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle "
"Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:205
msgid ""
"Go to `Italian authorities portal <https://ivaservizi.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale>`_ and authenticate;"
msgstr ""
"Buka `portal otoritas Italia <https://ivaservizi.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale>`_ dan lakukan autentikasi;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:207
msgid "Go to section :guilabel:`Fatture e Corrispettivi`;"
msgstr "Buka bagian :guilabel:`Fatture e Corrispettivi`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:208
msgid ""
"Set the user as Legal Party for the VAT number you wish to configure the "
"electronic address;"
msgstr ""
"Tetapkan user sebagai Pihak Legal untuk nomor PPN yang ingin Anda "
"konfigurasikan alamat elektroniknya;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:209
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Servizi Disponibili --> Fatturazione Elettronica --> "
"Registrazione dell’indirizzo telematico dove ricevere tutte le fatture "
"elettroniche`, insert Odoo's :guilabel:`Destination Code` `K95IV18`, and "
"confirm."
msgstr ""
"Di :menuselection:`Servizi Disponibili --> Fatturazione Elettronica --> "
"Registrazione dell'indirizzo telematico dove ricevere tutte le fatture "
"elettroniche`, masukkan :guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` Odoo `K95IV18`, dan "
"konfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:216
msgid "EDI Mode and authorization"
msgstr "Mode EDI dan otorisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:218
msgid ""
"Since the files are transmitted through Odoo's server before being sent to "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` or received by your database, you "
"need to authorize Odoo to process your files from your database. To do so, "
"go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Italian Electronic Invoicing` section."
msgstr ""
"Karena file ditransmisikan melalui server Odoo sebelum dikirim ke :abbr:`SdI "
"(Sistema di Interscambio)` atau diterima oleh database Anda, Anda perlu "
"mengotorisasi Odoo untuk memproses file Anda dari database Anda. Untuk "
"melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` "
"dan gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Faktur Elektronik Italia`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:223
msgid "There are three modes available:"
msgstr "Tersedia tiga mode:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Demo`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Demo`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"This mode simulates an environment in which invoices are sent to the "
"government. In this mode, invoices need to be *manually* downloaded as XML "
"files and uploaded to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`'s website."
msgstr ""
"Mode ini mensimulasikan lingkungan di mana faktur dikirim ke pemerintah. "
"Dalam mode ini, faktur perlu diunduh *secara manual* sebagai file XML dan "
"diunggah ke situs web :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Test (experimental)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Test (eksperimental)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"This mode sends invoices to a non-production (i.e., test) service made "
"available by the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Saving this change "
"directs all companies on the database to use this configuration."
msgstr ""
"Mode ini mengirim faktur ke layanan non-produksi (yaitu, pengujian) yang "
"disediakan oleh :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Menyimpan perubahan ini "
"mengarahkan semua perusahaan di database untuk menggunakan konfigurasi ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Official`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Resmi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"This is a production mode that sends your invoices directly to "
"the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah mode produksi yang mengirim faktur Anda langsung ke :abbr:`AdE "
"(Agenzia delle Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:237
msgid ""
"Once a mode is selected, you need to accept the **terms and conditions** by "
"ticking :guilabel:`Allow Odoo to process invoices`, and "
"then :guilabel:`Save`. You can now record your transactions in Odoo "
"Accounting."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mode dipilih, Anda perlu menerima **syarat dan ketentuan** dengan "
"mencentang :guilabel:`Izinkan Odoo memproses faktur`, "
"lalu :guilabel:`Simpan`. Anda sekarang dapat mencatat transaksi Anda di Odoo "
"Akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:242
msgid ""
"Selecting either :guilabel:`Test (experimental)` or :guilabel:`Official` is "
"**irreversible**. For example, once in :guilabel:`Official` mode, it is not "
"possible to select :guilabel:`Test (experimental)` or :guilabel:`Demo`. We "
"recommend creating a **separate database** for testing purposes only."
msgstr ""
"Memilih :guilabel:`Test (eksperimental)` atau :guilabel:`Resmi` bersifat "
"**tidak dapat dibatalkan**. Misalnya, setelah berada dalam "
"mode :guilabel:`Resmi`, tidak mungkin memilih :guilabel:`Test "
"(eksperimental)` atau :guilabel:`Demo`. Kami menyarankan untuk membuat "
"**database terpisah** hanya untuk tujuan pengujian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:248
msgid ""
"When in :guilabel:`Test (Experimental)` mode, all invoices sent *must* have "
"a partner using one of the following fake :guilabel:`Destination Code` given "
"by the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)`: `0803HR0` - `N8MIMM9` - "
"`X9XX79Z`. Any real production :guilabel:`Codice Destinario` of your "
"customers will not be recognized as valid by the test service."
msgstr ""
"Saat dalam mode :guilabel:`Test (Eksperimental)`, semua faktur yang dikirim "
"*harus* memiliki partner yang menggunakan salah satu :guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` "
"palsu berikut yang diberikan oleh :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)`: "
"`0803HR0` - `N8MIMM9` - `X9XX79Z`. Setiap :guilabel:`Codice Destinario` "
"produksi nyata dari pelanggan Anda tidak akan dikenali sebagai valid oleh "
"layanan pengujian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Electronic document invoicing settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan faktur dokumen elektronik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:677
msgid "Process"
msgstr "Proses :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:261
msgid ""
"The submission of invoices to the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` for "
"Italy is an electronic process used for the mandatory transmission of tax "
"documents in XML format between companies and the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle "
"Entrate)` to reduce errors and verify the correctness of operations."
msgstr ""
"Pengiriman faktur ke :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` untuk Italia "
"adalah proses elektronik yang digunakan untuk transmisi wajib dokumen pajak "
"dalam format XML antara perusahaan dan :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` "
"untuk mengurangi kesalahan dan memverifikasi kebenaran operasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:266
msgid ""
"You can check the current status of an invoice by the :guilabel:`SdI State` "
"field. The XML file is attached to the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memeriksa status faktur saat ini di kolom :guilabel:`Status SdI`. "
"File XML dilampirkan pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI system architecture"
msgstr "Arsitektur sistem EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:275
msgid "XML Documents creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan dokumen XML"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:277
msgid ""
"Odoo generates the required XML files as attachments to invoices in the "
"`FatturaPA` format required by the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Once "
"the invoices needed are selected, click the :guilabel:`Send` button."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menghasilkan file XML yang diperlukan sebagai lampiran pada faktur "
"dalam format `FatturaPA` yang diperlukan oleh :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle "
"Entrate)`. Setelah faktur yang diperlukan dipilih, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:281
msgid ""
"When the pop-up window opens there is a selection of actions that can be "
"taken. :guilabel:`Generate XML File` generates the attachments."
msgstr ""
"Ketika jendela pop-up terbuka, ada pilihan tindakan yang dapat "
"diambil. :guilabel:`Hasilkan File XML` menghasilkan lampiran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:284
msgid ""
"The XML file as well as the PDF once can be found attached to the invoice."
msgstr "File XML serta PDF dapat ditemukan dilampirkan pada faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI Attachments"
msgstr "Lampiran EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:289
msgid "After choosing the desired actions, click :guilabel:`send`."
msgstr "Setelah memilih tindakan yang diinginkan, klik :guilabel:`kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:294
msgid "Submission to SDI"
msgstr "Pengiriman ke SDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:296
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Send to Tax Agency` sends the attachment to "
"the :guilabel:`Proxy Server`, which gathers all requests and then forwards "
"them via a WebServices channel to the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. "
"Check the sending status of the invoice through the :guilabel:`Check "
"Sending` button at the top of the invoice's view."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kirim ke Badan Pajak` mengirimkan lampiran ke :guilabel:`Server "
"Proxy`, yang mengumpulkan semua permintaan dan kemudian meneruskannya "
"melalui saluran WebServices ke :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. "
"Periksa status pengiriman faktur melalui tombol :guilabel:`Periksa "
"Pengiriman` di bagian atas tampilan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:304
msgid "Processing by SDI"
msgstr "Pemrosesan oleh SDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:306
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` receives the document and verifies "
"for any errors. At this stage, the invoice is in the :guilabel:`SdI "
"Processing` state, as shown on the invoice. The invoice also gets assigned "
"a :guilabel:`FatturaPA Transaction` number that is shown in "
"the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing` tab. The checks may take variable time, "
"ranging from a few seconds up to a day, depending on the queue of invoices "
"sent throughout Italy."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` menerima dokumen dan memverifikasi "
"kesalahan. Pada tahap ini, faktur berada dalam status :guilabel:`SdI "
"Processing`, seperti yang ditampilkan pada faktur. Faktur juga mendapatkan "
"nomor :guilabel:`FatturaPA Transaction` yang ditampilkan di "
"tab :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing`. Pemeriksaan dapat memakan waktu yang "
"bervariasi, mulai dari beberapa detik hingga satu hari, tergantung pada "
"antrian faktur yang dikirim di seluruh Italia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Check Sending button and Sdi Processing state"
msgstr "Periksa tombol Kirim dan status Pemrosesan SdI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:318
msgid "Acceptance"
msgstr "Penerimaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:320
msgid ""
"If the document is valid, it is recorded and considered fiscally valid by "
"the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`, which will proceed with archiving "
"in :guilabel:`Substitute Storage (Conservazione Sostitutiva)` if explicitly "
"requested on the Agency's portal."
msgstr ""
"Jika dokumen valid, dokumen tersebut dicatat dan dianggap sah secara fiskal "
"oleh :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`, yang akan melanjutkan dengan "
"pengarsipan dalam :guilabel:`Substitute Storage (Conservazione Sostitutiva)` "
"jika secara eksplisit diminta di portal Agensi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:325
msgid ""
"Odoo does not offer the `Conservazione Sostitutiva <https://www.agid.gov.it/"
"index.php/it/piattaforme/conservazione>`_ requirements. Other providers "
"and :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` supply free and certified storage to "
"meet the specifications requested by law."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tidak menawarkan persyaratan `Conservazione Sostitutiva <https://"
"www.agid.gov.it/index.php/it/piattaforme/conservazione>`_. Penyedia lain "
"dan :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` menyediakan penyimpanan gratis dan "
"bersertifikat untuk memenuhi spesifikasi yang diminta oleh hukum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:330
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination Code` "
"attempts to forward the invoice to the customer at the provided address, "
"whether it is a `PEC` email address or a :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination Code` for their ERP's WebServices "
"channels. A maximum of 6 attempts are made every 12 hours, so even if "
"unsuccessful, this process can take up to three days. The invoice status "
"is :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Forwarding to Partner`."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination Code` mencoba "
"meneruskan faktur kepada pelanggan di alamat yang diberikan, baik itu alamat "
"email `PEC` atau :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination Code` untuk saluran WebServices ERP "
"mereka. Maksimal 6 kali percobaan dilakukan setiap 12 jam, sehingga meskipun "
"tidak berhasil, proses ini dapat memakan waktu hingga tiga hari. Status "
"faktur adalah :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Forwarding to Partner`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:339
msgid "Possible Rejection"
msgstr "Kemungkinan Penolakan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:341
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` may find inaccuracies in the "
"compilation, possibly even formal ones. In this case, the invoice is in "
"the :guilabel:`SDI Rejected` state. The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`'s observations are inserted at the top of the Invoice tab. To "
"resolve the issue, it is sufficient to delete the attachments of the "
"invoice, return the invoice to :guilabel:`Draft`, and fix the errors. Once "
"the invoice is ready, it can be resent."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` mungkin menemukan ketidakakuratan "
"dalam kompilasi, bahkan mungkin yang bersifat formal. Dalam hal ini, faktur "
"berada dalam status :guilabel:`SDI Rejected`. Catatan :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)` disisipkan di bagian atas tab Invoice. Untuk mengatasi "
"masalah, cukup hapus lampiran faktur, kembalikan faktur "
"ke :guilabel:`Draft`, dan perbaiki kesalahan. Setelah faktur siap, faktur "
"dapat dikirim ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:348
msgid ""
"To regenerate the XML, both the XML attachment and the PDF report must be "
"deleted, so that they are then regenerated together. This ensures that both "
"always contain the same data."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat ulang XML, lampiran XML dan laporan PDF harus dihapus, "
"sehingga keduanya kemudian dibuat ulang bersama-sama. Ini memastikan bahwa "
"keduanya selalu berisi data yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI Rejected State"
msgstr "Status Ditolak EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:357
msgid "Forwarding Completed"
msgstr "Penerusan Selesai"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:359
msgid ""
"The invoice has been delivered to the customer; however, you can still send "
"a copy to the customer in PDF via email or post. Its status "
"is :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Delivered to Partner`."
msgstr ""
"Faktur telah dikirim ke pelanggan; namun, Anda masih dapat mengirim salinan "
"ke pelanggan dalam format PDF melalui email atau pos. Statusnya "
"adalah :guilabel:`Diterima oleh SDI, Dikirim ke Mitra`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:362
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` cannot contact your customer, "
"they may not be registered on the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` "
"portal. In this case, just make sure to send the invoice in PDF via email or "
"by mail. The invoice is then in the :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Partner "
"Delivery Failed` state."
msgstr ""
"Jika :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` tidak dapat menghubungi pelanggan "
"Anda, mereka mungkin tidak terdaftar di portal :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle "
"Entrate)`. Dalam hal ini, pastikan saja untuk mengirim faktur dalam PDF "
"melalui email atau pos. Faktur kemudian berada dalam "
"status :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Partner Delivery Failed`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:370
msgid "Tax Integration"
msgstr "Integrasi Pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:372
msgid ""
"When you receive a vendor bill, either from :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, from paper or from an imported XML file, the Tax Agency "
"might request that you send some tax information integration back to "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. It happens when a transaction "
"that was tax exempt becomes taxable for any reason."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda menerima tagihan vendor, baik dari :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, dari kertas atau dari file XML yang diimpor, Badan Pajak "
"mungkin meminta Anda untuk mengirim kembali beberapa integrasi informasi "
"pajak ke :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Ini terjadi ketika transaksi "
"yang bebas pajak menjadi kena pajak karena alasan apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:378
msgid "Here is a non-exhaustive list:"
msgstr "Berikut adalah daftar yang tidak lengkap:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`"
msgstr ":ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"As a buyer, you have to pay taxes on what you buy and integrate tax "
"information. :guilabel:`Reverse Charge` taxes."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai pembeli, Anda harus membayar pajak atas apa yang Anda beli dan "
"mengintegrasikan informasi pajak. Pajak :guilabel:`Reverse Charge`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`localizations/italy/split-payment`"
msgstr ":ref:`localizations/italy/split-payment`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"As a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business buyer, you have to pay "
"taxes and integrate tax information. Be sure that you replace "
"the :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` on the vendor bill you received with the "
"correct :guilabel:`Split Payment` taxes."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai pembeli bisnis :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)`, Anda harus "
"membayar pajak dan mengintegrasikan informasi pajak. Pastikan Anda "
"mengganti :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` pada tagihan vendor yang Anda terima "
"dengan pajak :guilabel:`Split Payment` yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Self Consumption`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Self Consumption`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"When, as a business owner, you use an asset that you bought for business for "
"personal reasons instead, you have to pay those taxes you originally "
"deducted as a business cost for it."
msgstr ""
"Ketika, sebagai pemilik bisnis, Anda menggunakan aset yang Anda beli untuk "
"bisnis untuk keperluan pribadi, Anda harus membayar pajak yang awalnya Anda "
"deduksi sebagai biaya bisnis untuk aset tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:391
msgid ""
"Odoo may detect that your vendor bill can be interpreted as a document of a "
"type that needs tax integration, as detailed in the :ref:`localizations/"
"italy/document-types` section."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat mendeteksi bahwa tagihan vendor Anda dapat ditafsirkan sebagai "
"dokumen jenis yang memerlukan integrasi pajak, seperti dijelaskan dalam "
"bagian :ref:`localizations/italy/document-types`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:395
msgid ""
"Be sure that you replace the :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` on the vendor bill "
"you received with the ones you're supposed to pay to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia "
"delle Entrate)`. A button then appears on the top of the single vendor bill "
"form to send them."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan Anda mengganti :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` pada tagihan vendor yang "
"Anda terima dengan yang seharusnya Anda bayarkan ke :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia "
"delle Entrate)`. Sebuah tombol kemudian muncul di bagian atas formulir "
"tagihan vendor tunggal untuk mengirimnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:399
msgid ""
"When clicking on the :guilabel:`Send Tax Integration` button, an XML file of "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Document Type` is generated, attached to the "
"bill, and sent as for invoices."
msgstr ""
"Ketika mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Send Tax Integration`, file XML "
"dengan :guilabel:`Document Type` yang sesuai akan dihasilkan, dilampirkan ke "
"tagihan, dan dikirim seperti untuk faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid "EDI Send Tax Integration button"
msgstr "Tombol EDI Send Tax Integration"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:408
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:344
msgid "Document Types"
msgstr "Jenis Dokumen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:410
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` requires businesses to send "
"customer invoices and other documents through the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic "
"Data Interchange)`."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` mengharuskan bisnis untuk mengirim "
"faktur pelanggan dan dokumen lainnya melalui :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data "
"Interchange)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:413
msgid ""
"The following :guilabel:`Document Type` codes all technically identify "
"different business use cases."
msgstr ""
"Kode :guilabel:`Document Type` berikut secara teknis mengidentifikasi kasus "
"penggunaan bisnis yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:418
msgid "TD01 - Invoices"
msgstr "TD01 - Faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:420
msgid ""
"This represents the standard **domestic** scenario for all invoices "
"exchanged through the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Any invoice "
"that doesn't fall into one of the specific special cases is categorized as a "
"regular invoice, identified by the :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD01`."
msgstr ""
"Ini mewakili skenario **domestik** standar untuk semua faktur yang "
"dipertukarkan melalui :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Setiap faktur "
"yang tidak termasuk dalam salah satu kasus khusus tertentu dikategorikan "
"sebagai faktur reguler, diidentifikasi dengan :guilabel:`Document Type` "
"`TD01`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:427
msgid "TD02 - Down payments"
msgstr "TD02 - Uang Muka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:429
msgid ""
"**Down payment** invoices are imported/exported with a "
"different :guilabel:`Document Type` code `TDO2` than regular invoices. Upon "
"import of the invoice, a regular vendor bill is created."
msgstr ""
"Faktur **uang muka** diimpor/diekspor dengan kode :guilabel:`Document Type` "
"`TDO2` yang berbeda dari faktur biasa. Saat mengimpor faktur, tagihan vendor "
"biasa akan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:432
msgid ""
"Odoo exports transactions as `TD02` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengekspor transaksi sebagai `TD02` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:434
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:574
msgid "It is an invoice;"
msgstr "Ini adalah faktur;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:435
msgid "All invoice lines are related to down payment sales order lines."
msgstr "Semua baris faktur terkait dengan baris sales order uang muka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:440
msgid "TD04 - Credit notes"
msgstr "TD04 - Nota Kredit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:442
msgid ""
"It is the standard scenario for all **credit notes** issued to **domestic** "
"clients, when we need to formally acknowledge that the seller is reducing or "
"cancelling a previously issued invoice, for example, in case of overbilling, "
"incorrect items, or overpayment. Just like invoices, they must be sent to "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`, their :guilabel:`Document Type` "
"`TD04`"
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah skenario standar untuk semua **nota kredit** yang dikeluarkan "
"kepada klien **domestik**, ketika kita perlu secara formal mengakui bahwa "
"penjual mengurangi atau membatalkan faktur yang diterbitkan sebelumnya, "
"misalnya, dalam kasus penagihan berlebih, barang yang salah, atau pembayaran "
"berlebih. Sama seperti faktur, nota kredit harus dikirim ke :abbr:`SdI "
"(Sistema di Interscambio)`, :guilabel:`Document Type` mereka `TD04`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:450
msgid "TD07, TD08, TD09 - Simplified Invoicing"
msgstr "TD07, TD08, TD09 - Penagihan yang Disederhanakan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:452
msgid ""
"Simplified invoices (`TD07`), credit notes (`TD08`), and debit notes "
"(`TD09`) can be used to certify domestic transactions under 400 EUR (VAT "
"included). Its status is the same as that of a regular invoice, but with "
"fewer information requirements."
msgstr ""
"Faktur sederhana (`TD07`), nota kredit (`TD08`), dan nota debit (`TD09`) "
"dapat digunakan untuk mengesahkan transaksi domestik di bawah 400 EUR "
"(termasuk PPN). Statusnya sama dengan faktur biasa, tetapi dengan "
"persyaratan informasi yang lebih sedikit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:456
msgid "For a simplified invoice to be established, it must include:"
msgstr "Agar faktur sederhana dapat dibuat, faktur harus mencakup:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:458
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Invoice` reference: **unique** numbering sequence with "
"**no gaps**;"
msgstr ""
"Referensi :guilabel:`Faktur Pelanggan`: urutan penomoran **unik** **tanpa "
"celah**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:459
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Date`: issue **date** of the invoice;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal Faktur`: **tanggal** penerbitan faktur;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:460
msgid ""
":ref:`Company Info <general/companies/company>`: the **seller**'s full "
"credentials (VAT/TIN number, name, full address);"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Info Perusahaan <general/companies/company>`: kredensial lengkap "
"**penjual** (nomor VAT/TIN, nama, alamat lengkap);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:462
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`: the **buyer**'s VAT/TIN number (on the partner form);"
msgstr ":guilabel:`VAT`: nomor VAT/TIN **pembeli** (pada formulir mitra);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:463
msgid ":guilabel:`Total`: the total **amount** (VAT included) of the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Total`: **jumlah** total (termasuk PPN) dari faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:465
msgid ""
"In the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo exports invoices as "
"simplified if:"
msgstr ""
"Dalam :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo mengekspor faktur "
"sebagai sederhana jika:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:467
msgid "It is a domestic transaction (i.e., the partner is from Italy);"
msgstr "Ini adalah transaksi domestik (yaitu, mitra berasal dari Italia);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:468
msgid ""
"Your company's **required fields** (:guilabel:`VAT Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime`, and full "
"**address**) are provided;"
msgstr ""
"**Bidang wajib** perusahaan Anda (:guilabel:`Nomor VAT` "
"atau :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Rezim Fiskal`, dan **alamat** "
"lengkap) telah disediakan;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:470
msgid ""
"The partner's address is not fully specified (i.e., it misses the City or "
"the ZipCode);"
msgstr ""
"Alamat mitra tidak sepenuhnya ditentukan (yaitu, tidak ada Kota atau Kode "
"Pos);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:471
msgid "The total amount of VAT included is **less** than **400 EUR**."
msgstr "Jumlah total PPN yang termasuk **kurang** dari **400 EUR**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:474
msgid ""
"The 400 EUR threshold was defined in `the decree of the 10th of May 2019 in "
"the Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/"
"2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. We advise you to check the current official value."
msgstr ""
"Ambang batas 400 EUR ditetapkan dalam `keputusan 10 Mei 2019 di Gazzetta "
"Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/2019/05/24/19A03271/"
"sg>`_. Kami menyarankan Anda untuk memeriksa nilai resmi saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:481
msgid "TD16 - Internal Reverse Charge"
msgstr "TD16 - Reverse Charge Internal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:483
msgid ""
"Internal reverse charge transactions (see :ref:`localizations/italy/tax-"
"exemption` and :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`) are exported as "
"`TD16` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Transaksi reverse charge internal (lihat :ref:`localizations/italy/tax-"
"exemption` dan :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`) diekspor sebagai "
"`TD16` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:487
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:506
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:522
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:543
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:609
msgid "It is a vendor bill;"
msgstr "Ini adalah tagihan vendor;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:488
msgid ""
"It has at least **one tax** on the invoice lines that targets one of "
"these :ref:`tax grids <localizations/italy/grids>`: `VJ6`, `VJ7`, `VJ8`, "
"`VJ12`, `VJ13`, `VJ14`, `VJ15`, `VJ16`, `VJ17`"
msgstr ""
"Memiliki setidaknya **satu pajak** pada baris faktur yang menargetkan salah "
"satu :ref:`kisi pajak <localizations/italy/grids>` berikut: `VJ6`, `VJ7`, "
"`VJ8`, `VJ12`, `VJ13`, `VJ14`, `VJ15`, `VJ16`, `VJ17`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:494
msgid "TD17 - Buying services from abroad"
msgstr "TD17 - Pembelian jasa dari luar negeri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:496
msgid ""
"When buying **services** from **EU** and **non-EU** countries, the foreign "
"*seller* invoices a service with a **VAT-excluded** price, as it is not "
"taxable in Italy. The VAT is paid by the *buyer* in Italy."
msgstr ""
"Ketika membeli **layanan** dari negara-negara **UE** dan **non-UE**, "
"*penjual* asing menagih layanan dengan harga **tidak termasuk PPN**, karena "
"tidak kena pajak di Italia. PPN dibayar oleh *pembeli* di Italia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:500
msgid ""
"Within the EU: the *buyer* integrates the invoice received with the **VAT "
"information** due in Italy (i.e., **vendor bill tax integration**);"
msgstr ""
"Dalam UE: *pembeli* mengintegrasikan faktur yang diterima dengan **informasi "
"PPN** yang berlaku di Italia (yaitu, **integrasi pajak tagihan vendor**);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:502
msgid ""
"Non-EU: the *buyer* sends themselves an invoice (i.e., **self-billing**)."
msgstr ""
"Non-UE: *pembeli* mengirim faktur kepada diri mereka sendiri (yaitu, **self-"
"billing**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:504
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as `TD17` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengekspor transaksi sebagai `TD17` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:507
msgid ""
"It has at least **one tax** on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grid :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Memiliki setidaknya **satu pajak** pada baris faktur yang menargetkan kisi "
"pajak :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:509
msgid ""
"All invoice lines either have :guilabel:`Services` as **products**, or a tax "
"with the :guilabel:`Services` as **tax scope**."
msgstr ""
"Semua baris faktur memiliki :guilabel:`Services` sebagai **produk**, atau "
"pajak dengan :guilabel:`Services` sebagai **cakupan pajak**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:515
msgid "TD18 - Buying goods from EU"
msgstr "TD18 - Pembelian barang dari UE"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:517
msgid ""
"Invoices issued within the EU follow a **standard format**, therefore only "
"an integration of the existing invoice is required."
msgstr ""
"Faktur yang diterbitkan dalam UE mengikuti **format standar**, oleh karena "
"itu hanya diperlukan integrasi dari faktur yang ada."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:520
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as `TD18` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengekspor transaksi sebagai `TD18` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:523
msgid "The **partner** is from an **EU** country;"
msgstr "**Mitra** berasal dari negara **UE**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:524
msgid ""
"It has at least one tax on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grid :ref:`VJ9 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Memiliki setidaknya satu pajak pada baris faktur yang menargetkan kisi "
"pajak :ref:`VJ9 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:526
msgid ""
"All invoice lines either have :guilabel:`Consumable` as **products**, or a "
"tax with :guilabel:`Goods` as **tax scope**."
msgstr ""
"Semua baris faktur memiliki :guilabel:`Consumable` sebagai **produk**, atau "
"pajak dengan :guilabel:`Goods` sebagai **cakupan pajak**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:532
msgid "TD19 - Buying goods from VAT deposit"
msgstr "TD19 - Pembelian barang dari depot PPN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:534
msgid ""
"Buying **goods** from a **foreign** vendor, but the **goods** are already in "
"**Italy** in a **VAT deposit**."
msgstr ""
"Membeli **barang** dari vendor **luar negeri**, tetapi **barang** tersebut "
"sudah berada di **Italia** dalam **gudang PPN**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:537
msgid ""
"From the EU: the *buyer* integrates the invoice received with the **VAT "
"information** due in Italy (i.e., **vendor bill tax integration**);"
msgstr ""
"Dari UE: *pembeli* mengintegrasikan faktur yang diterima dengan **informasi "
"PPN** yang berlaku di Italia (yaitu, **integrasi pajak tagihan vendor**);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:539
msgid ""
"Non-EU: the *buyer* sends an invoice to *themselves* (i.e., **self-"
"billing**)."
msgstr ""
"Non-UE: *pembeli* mengirim faktur ke *diri mereka sendiri* (yaitu, "
"**penagihan sendiri**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:541
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as a `TD19` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengekspor transaksi sebagai `TD19` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:544
msgid ""
"It has at least one tax on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grid :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Memiliki setidaknya satu pajak pada baris faktur yang menargetkan kisi "
"pajak :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:546
msgid ""
"All invoice lines either have :guilabel:`Consumables` as products, or a tax "
"with :guilabel:`Goods` as **tax scope**."
msgstr ""
"Semua baris faktur memiliki :guilabel:`Consumables` sebagai produk, atau "
"pajak dengan :guilabel:`Goods` sebagai **cakupan pajak**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:552
msgid "TD24 - Deferred invoices"
msgstr "TD24 - Faktur tertunda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:554
msgid ""
"The **deferred invoice** is an invoice that is **issued at a later time** "
"than the sale of goods or the provision of services. A **deferred invoice** "
"has to be issued at the latest within the **15th day** of the month "
"following the delivery covered by the document."
msgstr ""
"**Faktur ditangguhkan** adalah faktur yang **diterbitkan di waktu yang lebih "
"lambat** daripada penjualan barang atau penyediaan jasa. **Faktur "
"ditangguhkan** harus diterbitkan paling lambat pada **hari ke-15** bulan "
"berikutnya setelah pengiriman yang tercakup dalam dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:558
msgid ""
"It usually is a **summary invoice** containing a list of multiple sales of "
"goods or services carried out in the month. The business is allowed to "
"**group** the sales into **one invoice**, generally issued at the **end of "
"the month** for accounting purposes. Deferred invoices are default for "
"**wholesalers** having recurrent clients."
msgstr ""
"Biasanya merupakan **faktur ringkasan** yang berisi daftar beberapa "
"penjualan barang atau jasa yang dilakukan dalam bulan tersebut. Bisnis "
"diizinkan untuk **mengelompokkan** penjualan menjadi **satu faktur**, "
"umumnya diterbitkan pada **akhir bulan** untuk tujuan akuntansi. Faktur "
"ditangguhkan adalah default untuk **pedagang grosir** yang memiliki klien "
"berulang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:563
msgid ""
"If the goods are transported by a **carrier**, every delivery has an "
"associated **Documento di Transporto (DDT)**, or **Transport Document**. The "
"deferred invoice **must** indicate the details of all the **DDTs** "
"information for better tracing."
msgstr ""
"Jika barang diangkut oleh **pengangkut**, setiap pengiriman memiliki "
"**Documento di Transporto (DDT)** terkait, atau **Dokumen Transportasi**. "
"Faktur ditangguhkan **harus** mencantumkan detail semua informasi **DDT** "
"untuk pelacakan yang lebih baik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:568
msgid ""
"E-invoicing of deferred invoices requires the "
"`l10n_it_stock_ddt` :ref:`module <localizations/italy/modules>`. In this "
"case, a dedicated :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD24` is used in the e-invoice."
msgstr ""
"E-invoicing faktur tertunda memerlukan :ref:`modul <localizations/italy/"
"modules>` `l10n_it_stock_ddt`. Dalam hal ini, :guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen` "
"khusus `TD24` digunakan dalam e-invoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:572
msgid ""
"Odoo exports transactions as `TD24` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengekspor transaksi sebagai `TD24` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:575
msgid ""
"It is associated with deliveries whose **DDTs** have a **different** date "
"than the issue date of the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Terkait dengan pengiriman yang **DDT**-nya memiliki tanggal **berbeda** dari "
"tanggal penerbitan faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:581
msgid "TD28 - San Marino"
msgstr "TD28 - San Marino"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:588
msgid ""
"San Marino and Italy have special agreements on e-invoicing operations. As "
"such, **invoices** follow the regular **reverse charge** rules. You can use "
"the proper :guilabel:`Document Type` depending on the invoice type: `TD01`, "
"`TD04`, `TD05`, `TD24`, `TD25`. Additional requirements are not enforced by "
"Odoo. However, the user is requested by the **State** to:"
msgstr ""
"San Marino dan Italia memiliki perjanjian khusus tentang operasi faktur "
"elektronik. Dengan demikian, **faktur** mengikuti aturan **reverse charge** "
"biasa. Anda dapat menggunakan :guilabel:`Document Type` yang sesuai "
"tergantung pada jenis faktur: `TD01`, `TD04`, `TD05`, `TD24`, `TD25`. "
"Persyaratan tambahan tidak diberlakukan oleh Odoo. Namun, user diminta oleh "
"**Negara** untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:593
msgid "Select a tax with the :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Kind` set to `N3.3`;"
msgstr ""
"Pilih pajak dengan :guilabel:`Jenis Pembebasan Pajak` diatur ke `N3.3`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:594
msgid ""
"Use the generic :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination "
"Code` `2R4GTO8`."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` "
"generik `2R4GTO8`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:596
msgid ""
"The invoice is then routed by a dedicated office in San Marino to the "
"correct business."
msgstr ""
"Faktur kemudian diarahkan oleh kantor khusus di San Marino ke bisnis yang "
"benar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:601
msgid "Vendor Bills"
msgstr "Tagihan Vendor"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:603
msgid ""
"When a **paper bill** is received from San Marino, any Italian company "
"**must** submit that invoice to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` by "
"indicating the e-invoice's :guilabel:`Document Type` field with the special "
"value `TD28`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika **tagihan kertas** diterima dari San Marino, setiap perusahaan Italia "
"**wajib** mengirimkan faktur tersebut ke :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` "
"dengan menunjukkan bidang :guilabel:`Jenis Dokumen` e-faktur dengan nilai "
"khusus `TD28`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:607
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as `TD28` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengekspor transaksi sebagai `TD28` jika kondisi berikut terpenuhi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:610
msgid ""
"It has at least one tax on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grids :ref:`VJ <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Memiliki setidaknya satu pajak pada baris faktur yang menargetkan kisi "
"pajak :ref:`VJ <localizations/italy/grids>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:612
msgid "The **country** of the partner is **San Marino**."
msgstr "**Negara** mitra adalah **San Marino**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:617
msgid "Public Administration Businesses (B2G)"
msgstr "Bisnis Administrasi Publik (B2G)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:619
msgid ""
":abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses are subjected to more control "
"than private businesses as they handle public money coming from taxpayers. "
"The :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)` process adds some steps to "
"the :ref:`regular one <localizations/italy/e-invoicing-process>`, "
"as :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses can **accept** or "
"**refuse** invoices."
msgstr ""
"Bisnis :abbr:`PA (Administrasi Publik)` tunduk pada kontrol yang lebih ketat "
"daripada bisnis swasta karena mereka menangani uang publik yang berasal dari "
"wajib pajak. Proses :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)` menambahkan "
"beberapa langkah pada :ref:`proses reguler <localizations/italy/e-invoicing-"
"process>`, karena bisnis :abbr:`PA (Administrasi Publik)` dapat **menerima** "
"atau **menolak** faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:625
msgid ""
":abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses have a 6-digit "
"long :guilabel:`Destination Code`, also called :abbr:`CUU (Codice Univoco "
"Ufficio)`, that is **mandatory**, **PEC** address cannot be used in this "
"case."
msgstr ""
"Bisnis :abbr:`PA (Administrasi Publik)` memiliki :guilabel:`Kode Tujuan` "
"sepanjang 6 digit, juga disebut :abbr:`CUU (Codice Univoco Ufficio)`, yang "
"**wajib**, alamat **PEC** tidak dapat digunakan dalam kasus ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:630
msgid ""
"`Complete list of businesses that belong to the Public Administration along "
"with their Destination Code <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/web/"
"guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Daftar lengkap bisnis yang termasuk dalam Administrasi Publik beserta Kode "
"Tujuan mereka <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/web/guest/aree-"
"tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:636
msgid "CIG, CUP, DatiOrdineAcquisto"
msgstr "CIG, CUP, DatiOrdineAcquisto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:638
msgid ""
"To ensure the effective traceability of payments by public administrations, "
"electronic invoices issued to public administrations must contain:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memastikan ketertelusuran pembayaran yang efektif oleh administrasi "
"publik, faktur elektronik yang diterbitkan ke administrasi publik harus "
"berisi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:641
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)`, except in cases of exclusion "
"from traceability obligations provided by law n. 136 of August 13, 2010;"
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)`, kecuali dalam kasus pengecualian "
"dari kewajiban penelusuran yang diatur oleh undang-undang no. 136 tanggal 13 "
"Agustus 2010;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:643
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)`, in case of invoices related to "
"public works."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)`, dalam kasus faktur yang terkait "
"dengan pekerjaan umum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:645
msgid ""
"If the XML file requires it, the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` can "
"*only* proceed payments of electronic invoices when the XML file contains "
"a :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)` and :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di "
"Progetto)`."
msgstr ""
"Jika file XML memerlukannya, :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` *hanya* "
"dapat memproses pembayaran faktur elektronik ketika file XML "
"berisi :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)` dan :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico "
"di Progetto)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:650
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)` and the :abbr:`CIG (Codice "
"Identificativo Gara)` must be included in one of the `DatiOrdineAcquisto`, "
"`DatiContratto`, `DatiConvenzione`, `DateRicezione`, or "
"`DatiFattureCollegate` XML tags."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)` dan :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo "
"Gara)` harus disertakan dalam salah satu tag XML `DatiOrdineAcquisto`, "
"`DatiContratto`, `DatiConvenzione`, `DateRicezione`, atau "
"`DatiFattureCollegate`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:654
msgid ""
"These correspond to the elements named :guilabel:`CodiceCUP` "
"and :guilabel:`CodiceCIG` of the electronic invoice XML file, whose table "
"can be found on the government `website <http://www.fatturapa.gov.it/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ini sesuai dengan elemen bernama :guilabel:`CodiceCUP` "
"dan :guilabel:`CodiceCIG` dari file XML faktur elektronik, yang tabelnya "
"dapat ditemukan di `website <http://www.fatturapa.gov.it/>`_ pemerintah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:661
msgid "Split Payment"
msgstr "Pemisahan Pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:663
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Split Payment` mechanism behaves much "
"like :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`."
msgstr ""
"Mekanisme :guilabel:`Split Payment` berfungsi mirip "
"dengan :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:666
msgid ""
"When an Italian company bills a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business "
"- for example, cleaning services for a public building - the :abbr:`PA "
"(Public Administration)` business self-reports the VAT to the Tax Agency "
"themselves, and the vendor just has to select the appropriate tax with the "
"right :guilabel:`Tax Exemption` for their invoice lines."
msgstr ""
"Ketika perusahaan Italia menagih bisnis :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` - "
"misalnya, layanan kebersihan untuk gedung publik - bisnis :abbr:`PA (Public "
"Administration)` melaporkan sendiri PPN kepada Badan Pajak, dan vendor hanya "
"perlu memilih pajak yang sesuai dengan :guilabel:`Pengecualian Pajak` yang "
"tepat untuk baris faktur mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:671
msgid ""
"The specific :guilabel:`Scissione dei Pagamenti` fiscal position is "
"available to deal with partners belonging to the :abbr:`PA (Public "
"Administration)`."
msgstr ""
"Posisi fiskal :guilabel:`Scissione dei Pagamenti` khusus tersedia untuk "
"menangani mitra yang termasuk dalam :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:682
msgid "Qualified electronic signature"
msgstr "Tanda tangan elektronik berkualifikasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:684
msgid ""
"Invoices and bills intended for the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` must "
"include a **qualified electronic signature** when submitted through "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. This signature is automatically "
"applied in the :abbr:`XAdES (XML Advanced Electronic Signature)` format when "
"the invoice's partner has a 6-digit long :guilabel:`Destination Code` (which "
"indicates a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business)."
msgstr ""
"Faktur dan tagihan yang ditujukan untuk :abbr:`PA (Administrasi Publik)` "
"harus menyertakan **tanda tangan elektronik yang memenuhi syarat** saat "
"dikirimkan melalui :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Tanda tangan ini "
"secara otomatis diterapkan dalam format :abbr:`XAdES (XML Advanced "
"Electronic Signature)` ketika mitra faktur memiliki :guilabel:`Destination "
"Code` sepanjang 6 digit (yang menunjukkan bisnis :abbr:`PA (Administrasi "
"Publik)`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:691
msgid ""
"When such an invoice is transmitted to the Tax Agency, the generated `.xml` "
"file is signed on the Odoo servers, returned to the database, and attached "
"to the invoice automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ketika faktur tersebut dikirimkan ke Badan Pajak, file `.xml` yang "
"dihasilkan ditandatangani di server Odoo, dikembalikan ke database, dan "
"dilampirkan ke faktur secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:697
msgid "Acceptance or Refusal"
msgstr "Penerimaan atau Penolakan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:699
msgid ""
"After receiving the invoice through the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business has 15 days "
"to accept the invoice. If it does, then the process ends here. If "
"the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business refuses the invoice, it is "
"still considered valid once it is accepted by the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`. You then have to issue a credit note to compensate and send "
"it to the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menerima faktur melalui :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`, "
"bisnis :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` memiliki waktu 15 hari untuk "
"menerima faktur. Jika diterima, maka prosesnya berakhir di sini. Jika "
"bisnis :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` menolak faktur, faktur tersebut "
"masih dianggap valid setelah diterima oleh :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`. Anda kemudian harus menerbitkan nota kredit untuk "
"mengompensasi dan mengirimkannya ke :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:708
msgid "Expired Terms"
msgstr "Batas Waktu Terlewati"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:710
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business doesn't reply within 15 "
"days, you need to contact the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business "
"directly, sending them both the invoice and the received deadline "
"notification by email. You can make an arrangement with them and manually "
"set the correct :guilabel:`SdI State` on your invoice."
msgstr ""
"Jika bisnis :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` tidak membalas dalam 15 hari, "
"Anda perlu menghubungi bisnis :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` secara "
"langsung, mengirimkan kepada mereka faktur dan notifikasi tenggat waktu yang "
"diterima melalui email. Anda dapat membuat kesepakatan dengan mereka dan "
"secara manual mengatur :guilabel:`Status SdI` yang benar pada faktur Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:718
msgid "Point of Sale fiscal printers"
msgstr "Printer fiskal POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:721
msgid ""
"Fiscal printers are distinct from :doc:`ePOS printers </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale/configuration/epos_printers>`. The IP address for a fiscal "
"printer should not be entered in the ePOS IP address settings."
msgstr ""
"Printer fiskal berbeda dari :doc:`printer ePOS </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale/configuration/epos_printers>`. Alamat IP untuk printer fiskal "
"tidak boleh dimasukkan di pengaturan alamat IP ePOS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:725
msgid ""
"Fiscal regulations mandate using certified RT devices, such as RT printers "
"or RT servers, to ensure compliant sales receipts and secure communication "
"with the Tax Authority. These devices automatically transmit fiscal data "
"daily. RT printers, designed for individual POS terminals, handle "
"transactions, print receipts, and report to the authorities, ensuring data "
"integrity and compliance."
msgstr ""
"Peraturan fiskal mewajibkan penggunaan perangkat RT bersertifikat, seperti "
"printer RT atau server RT, untuk memastikan tanda terima penjualan yang "
"sesuai dan komunikasi aman dengan Otoritas Pajak. Perangkat ini secara "
"otomatis mengirimkan data fiskal setiap hari. Printer RT, yang dirancang "
"untuk terminal POS individual, menangani transaksi, mencetak tanda terima, "
"dan melaporkan ke otoritas, memastikan integritas data dan kepatuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:733
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:57
msgid "Simulation mode"
msgstr "Mode simulasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:736
msgid ""
"Since the simulation mode sends data to the authorities, it should only be "
"enabled at the very start of the printer's configuration process. Once the "
"printer is switched to the production mode, it cannot be reverted to the "
"simulation mode."
msgstr ""
"Karena mode simulasi mengirimkan data ke otoritas, mode ini hanya boleh "
"diaktifkan pada awal proses konfigurasi printer. Setelah printer dialihkan "
"ke mode produksi, printer tidak dapat dikembalikan ke mode simulasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:740
msgid ""
"To test the fiscal printer setup with Odoo, configure the fiscal printer in "
"the simulation mode as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menguji pengaturan printer fiskal dengan Odoo, konfigurasikan printer "
"fiskal dalam mode simulasi sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:743
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:774
msgid ""
"Make sure the fiscal printer is set to its default state: printer on, start-"
"up cycle complete, and no transaction in progress."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan printer fiskal disetel ke keadaan default: printer hidup, siklus "
"start-up selesai, dan tidak ada transaksi yang sedang berlangsung."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:745
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:776
msgid "Type `3333`."
msgstr "Ketik `3333`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:746
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:777
msgid ""
"Press :guilabel:`Chiave`. The screen displays :guilabel:`Scelta Funzione`."
msgstr ""
"Tekan :guilabel:`Chiave`. Layar menampilkan :guilabel:`Scelta Funzione`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:747
msgid "Type `14`. The screen displays :guilabel:`Apprendimento`."
msgstr "Ketik `14`. Layar menampilkan :guilabel:`Apprendimento`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:748
msgid "Type `62`. The screen displays :guilabel:`Simulazione`."
msgstr "Ketik `62`. Layar menampilkan :guilabel:`Simulazione`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:749
msgid "To turn the :guilabel:`no` into a :guilabel:`si`, press :guilabel:`X`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah :guilabel:`no` menjadi :guilabel:`si`, tekan :guilabel:`X`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:750
msgid "To confirm, press :guilabel:`Contante`."
msgstr "Untuk mengonfirmasi, tekan :guilabel:`Contante`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:751
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:782
msgid "Press :guilabel:`Chiave`."
msgstr "Tekan :guilabel:`Chiave`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:753
msgid "To configure the printer for production, repeat the steps above."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengkonfigurasi printer untuk produksi, ulangi langkah-langkah di atas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:756
msgid ""
"To test the printer configuration, the physical device must first be "
"obtained and registered with the relevant authorities."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menguji konfigurasi printer, perangkat fisik harus terlebih dahulu "
"diperoleh dan didaftarkan ke otoritas terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:762
msgid "Setting up the printer to work with Odoo"
msgstr "Mengatur printer untuk bekerja dengan Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:764
msgid ""
"Fiscal printers are meant to work only in the local network. This means the "
"printer and the device running :doc:`Odoo Point of Sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` must be connected to the same network."
msgstr ""
"Printer fiskal dimaksudkan untuk bekerja hanya dalam jaringan lokal. Ini "
"berarti printer dan perangkat yang menjalankan :doc:`Odoo Point of Sale </"
"applications/sales/point_of_sale>` harus terhubung ke jaringan yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:768
msgid ""
"Fiscal printers are typically configured to use HTTP by default. To ensure "
"compatibility with Odoo, the settings must be updated to enable HTTPS "
"support on the printer. This can be done using either the EpsonFPWizard "
"configuration software or the keyboard connected to the printer."
msgstr ""
"Printer fiskal biasanya dikonfigurasi untuk menggunakan HTTP secara default. "
"Untuk memastikan kompatibilitas dengan Odoo, pengaturan harus diperbarui "
"untuk mengaktifkan dukungan HTTPS pada printer. Ini dapat dilakukan "
"menggunakan perangkat lunak konfigurasi EpsonFPWizard atau keyboard yang "
"terhubung ke printer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:772
msgid "To set up the fiscal printer using the keyboard, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur printer fiskal menggunakan keyboard, ikuti langkah-langkah "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:778
msgid "Type `34`. The screen displays :guilabel:`Web Server`."
msgstr "Ketik `34`. Layar menampilkan :guilabel:`Web Server`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:779
msgid ""
"Press :guilabel:`Contante` 3 times until the screen displays :guilabel:`Web "
"Server: SSL`."
msgstr ""
"Tekan :guilabel:`Contante` 3 kali hingga layar menampilkan :guilabel:`Web "
"Server: SSL`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:780
msgid "To turn the value `0` into a `1`, press :guilabel:`X`."
msgstr "Untuk mengubah nilai `0` menjadi `1`, tekan :guilabel:`X`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:781
msgid "To confirm, press :guilabel:`Contante` 3 times."
msgstr "Untuk mengonfirmasi, tekan :guilabel:`Contante` 3 kali."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:784
msgid ""
"Then, log in to the printer with the device that runs :doc:`Odoo Point of "
"Sale </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` so it recognizes the printer's "
"certificate."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, masuk ke printer dengan perangkat yang menjalankan :doc:`Odoo "
"Point of Sale </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` agar mengenali sertifikat "
"printer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:787
msgid "To approve and install the printer's certificate, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyetujui dan menginstal sertifikat printer, ikuti langkah-langkah "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:789
msgid ""
"Access the printer by opening a web browser and entering `https://<ip-of-"
"your-printer>` in the address bar. A :guilabel:`Warning: Potential Security "
"Risk Ahead` security message appears."
msgstr ""
"Akses printer dengan membuka browser web dan memasukkan `https://<ip-of-your-"
"printer>` di bilah alamat. Pesan keamanan :guilabel:`Warning: Potential "
"Security Risk Ahead` muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:791
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Advanced` to show the certificate approval options."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Advanced` untuk menampilkan opsi persetujuan sertifikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:792
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Proceed` to validate the certificate."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Proceed` untuk memvalidasi sertifikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:794
msgid ""
"Then, to ensure :doc:`Odoo Point of Sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` is configured with the fiscal printer, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Connected Devices` section, add the IP address in "
"the :guilabel:`Italian Fiscal Printer IP address` and enable :guilabel:`Use "
"HTTPS`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, untuk memastikan :doc:`Odoo Point of Sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` dikonfigurasi dengan printer fiskal, "
"buka :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`. Di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Connected Devices`, tambahkan alamat IP "
"di :guilabel:`Italian Fiscal Printer IP address` dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Use "
"HTTPS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:802
msgid "Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)"
msgstr "Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:804
msgid ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` is a payment method widely used in Italy "
"where vendors request payments through their bank, which forwards the "
"request to the customer's own bank and takes responsibility for the "
"collection. This enables payment automation and reduces risks for the vendor."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` adalah metode pembayaran yang banyak "
"digunakan di Italia di mana vendor meminta pembayaran melalui bank mereka, "
"yang meneruskan permintaan ke bank pelanggan sendiri dan bertanggung jawab "
"atas penagihan. Ini memungkinkan otomatisasi pembayaran dan mengurangi "
"risiko bagi vendor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:808
msgid ""
"The vendor generally uploads a fixed-format text file with the list of "
"payments to the bank's web portal."
msgstr ""
"Vendor umumnya mengunggah file teks format tetap dengan daftar pembayaran ke "
"portal web bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:812
msgid ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute Bancarie)` are exclusively for **domestic payments** "
"in Italy. For recurring international payments, please use `SEPA Direct Debt "
"(SDD) <../accounting/payments/batch_sdd>`_"
msgstr ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute Bancarie)` secara eksklusif untuk **pembayaran "
"domestik** di Italia. Untuk pembayaran internasional berulang, silakan "
"gunakan `SEPA Direct Debt (SDD) <../accounting/payments/batch_sdd>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:820
msgid ""
"Check that the `l10n_it_riba` module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Periksa bahwa modul `l10n_it_riba` telah :ref:`diinstal <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:821
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies` and "
"select the company that will use :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute Bancarie)`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Pengaturan --> Pengguna & Perusahaan --> Perusahaan` "
"dan pilih perusahaan yang akan menggunakan :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute "
"Bancarie)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:823
msgid "Fill out the required :guilabel:`SIA Code`."
msgstr "Isi :guilabel:`SIA Code` yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid "The company's SIA code"
msgstr "Kode SIA perusahaan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:829
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SIA Code` identifies businesses within the Italian banking "
"network and is used to receive money through specific payment methods. It "
"consists of one letter and four digits (e.g., T1234) and can usually be "
"found on the bank's portal or obtained by contacting the bank."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SIA Code` mengidentifikasi bisnis dalam jaringan perbankan Italia "
"dan digunakan untuk menerima uang melalui metode pembayaran tertentu. Kode "
"ini terdiri dari satu huruf dan empat digit (misalnya, T1234) dan biasanya "
"dapat ditemukan di portal bank atau diperoleh dengan menghubungi bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:834
msgid "Ensure the Company's bank account has an Italian IBAN."
msgstr "Pastikan rekening bank Perusahaan memiliki IBAN Italia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:837
msgid "How to configure :doc:`Bank Accounts <../accounting/bank>`"
msgstr "Cara mengonfigurasi :doc:`Rekening Bank <../accounting/bank>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:842
msgid "Accept Ri.Ba. for your invoices"
msgstr "Terima Ri.Ba. untuk faktur Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:844
msgid ""
"Payments of type :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` can be registered from "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` (:menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Invoices`)."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran jenis :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` dapat dicatat "
"dari :guilabel:`Faktur` (:menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> "
"Faktur`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:848
msgid ""
"Make sure that your invoice involves a Partner that has a bank account with "
"an Italian IBAN."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan bahwa faktur Anda melibatkan Mitra yang memiliki rekening bank "
"dengan IBAN Italia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:850
msgid "Then, all Payments must be grouped in a **Batch Payment**."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, semua Pembayaran harus dikelompokkan dalam **Pembayaran Batch**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:853
msgid ":doc:`Batch Payments <../accounting/payments>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Pembayaran Batch <../accounting/payments>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:854
msgid ":doc:`Create a Batch Payment <../accounting/payments/batch>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Buat Pembayaran Batch <../accounting/payments/batch>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:856
msgid ""
"Once you press the :guilabel:`Validate` button for the Batch Payment, "
"the :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` file is generated and attached to the "
"Batch Payment, so you can download it and upload it through your bank's web "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda menekan tombol :guilabel:`Validasi` untuk Pembayaran Batch, "
"file :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` dihasilkan dan dilampirkan ke "
"Pembayaran Batch, sehingga Anda dapat mengunduhnya dan mengunggahnya melalui "
"portal web bank Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "The Ri.Ba. file attached"
msgstr "File Ri.Ba. yang dilampirkan"

