#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:40
msgid ""
"The Jordanian localization package ensures compliance with Jordanian fiscal "
"and accounting regulations. It includes tools for managing taxes, fiscal "
"positions, reporting, and a predefined chart of accounts tailored to "
"Jordan's standards."
msgstr ""
"Paket lokalisasi Yordania memastikan kepatuhan terhadap peraturan fiskal dan "
"akuntansi Yordania. Paket ini mencakup alat untuk mengelola pajak, posisi "
"fiskal, pelaporan, dan bagan akun yang telah ditentukan sebelumnya yang "
"disesuaikan dengan standar Yordania."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:44
msgid ""
"The Jordanian localization package provides the following key features to "
"ensure compliance with local fiscal and accounting regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Paket lokalisasi Yordania menyediakan fitur-fitur utama berikut untuk "
"memastikan kepatuhan terhadap peraturan fiskal dan akuntansi lokal:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:47
msgid ""
":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`: a predefined structure "
"tailored to Jordanian accounting standards"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`: struktur yang telah "
"ditentukan sebelumnya yang disesuaikan dengan standar akuntansi Yordania"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:49
msgid ""
":ref:`localizations/jordan/taxes`: pre-configured tax rates, including "
"standard VAT, zero-rated, and exempt options"
msgstr ""
":ref:`localizations/jordan/taxes`: tarif pajak yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya, termasuk PPN standar, tarif nol, dan opsi bebas pajak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:53
msgid ""
":ref:`localizations/jordan/tax-reporting`: detailed overview of your net tax "
"liability"
msgstr ""
":ref:`localizations/jordan/tax-reporting`: ikhtisar terperinci tentang "
"kewajiban pajak bersih Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:54
msgid ""
":ref:`E-invoicing (JoFotara)<localizations/jordan/jofotara>`: integration "
"for electronic invoicing in line with Jordanian government requirements"
msgstr ""
":ref:`E-invoicing (JoFotara)<localizations/jordan/jofotara>`: integrasi "
"untuk penagihan elektronik sesuai dengan persyaratan pemerintah Yordania"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:62
msgid ""
"The following :doc:`taxes <../accounting/taxes>` are available by default "
"with the Jordanian localization package:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Pajak <../accounting/taxes>` berikut tersedia secara default dengan "
"paket lokalisasi Yordania:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:65
msgid ""
"standard sales tax (16%): applied to most goods and services within Jordan."
msgstr ""
"pajak penjualan standar (16%): diterapkan pada sebagian besar barang dan "
"jasa di Yordania."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:66
msgid ""
"exempt transactions: for sales and services not subject to VAT, such as "
"financial services or healthcare."
msgstr ""
"transaksi bebas pajak: untuk penjualan dan jasa yang tidak dikenakan PPN, "
"seperti jasa keuangan atau layanan kesehatan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:68
msgid ""
"export tax (0%): zero-rated tax applied to goods and services exported "
"outside Jordan."
msgstr ""
"pajak ekspor (0%): pajak tarif nol yang diterapkan pada barang dan jasa yang "
"diekspor ke luar Yordania."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:75
msgid ""
"The :doc:`VAT summary <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` provides a "
"detailed breakdown of taxable, zero-rated, and exempt transactions. Like "
"other :doc:`financial reports <../accounting/reporting>`, the VAT summary "
"can be filtered by period, compared against other periods, and exported in "
"Excel and PDF formats, ensuring compliance with Jordanian tax laws."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Ringkasan PPN <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` menyediakan "
"rincian terperinci tentang transaksi yang dikenakan pajak, tarif nol, dan "
"bebas pajak. Seperti :doc:`laporan keuangan <../accounting/reporting>` "
"lainnya, ringkasan PPN dapat difilter berdasarkan periode, dibandingkan "
"dengan periode lain, dan diekspor dalam format Excel dan PDF, memastikan "
"kepatuhan terhadap undang-undang perpajakan Yordania."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:83
msgid "E-invoicing with JoFotara"
msgstr "E-invoicing dengan JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:85
msgid ""
"E-invoicing with JoFotara is integrated with Odoo, ensuring compliance with "
"Jordanian government's technical and legal requirements for electronic "
"invoicing. The JoFotara integration in Odoo directly connects with the "
"Jordanian e-invoicing platform, allowing companies to:"
msgstr ""
"E-invoicing dengan JoFotara terintegrasi dengan Odoo, memastikan kepatuhan "
"terhadap persyaratan teknis dan hukum pemerintah Yordania untuk penagihan "
"elektronik. Integrasi JoFotara di Odoo terhubung langsung dengan platform e-"
"invoicing Yordania, memungkinkan perusahaan untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:89
msgid "generate compliant electronic invoices"
msgstr "membuat faktur elektronik yang sesuai"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:90
msgid "submit invoices in real time for validation"
msgstr "mengirimkan faktur secara real time untuk validasi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:91
msgid "track invoice statuses directly within Odoo"
msgstr "melacak status faktur langsung di dalam Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:93
msgid ""
"The integration requires first creating an account with JoFotara, then "
"generating API credentials, and finally entering those credentials in your "
"Odoo database to link the two."
msgstr ""
"Integrasi ini memerlukan pembuatan akun dengan JoFotara terlebih dahulu, "
"kemudian membuat kredensial API, dan akhirnya memasukkan kredensial tersebut "
"ke dalam database Odoo Anda untuk menghubungkan keduanya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:98
msgid ""
"`Government manuals <manuals_>`_ provide instructions for creating an "
"account and generating the API credentials."
msgstr ""
"`Panduan pemerintah <manuals_>`_ menyediakan instruksi untuk membuat akun "
"dan menghasilkan kredensial API."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:109
msgid "Link Odoo to JoFotara"
msgstr "Hubungkan Odoo ke JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:111
msgid ""
"If you don't already have an account, create one by going to the `government "
"manuals <manuals_>`_ page and following the steps in the **Procedure Manual "
"for Joining the Jordanian National Electronic Invoicing System**."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda belum memiliki akun, buat akun dengan mengunjungi halaman `panduan "
"pemerintah <manuals_>`_ dan ikuti langkah-langkah dalam **Panduan Prosedur "
"untuk Bergabung dengan Sistem Penagihan Elektronik Nasional Yordania**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:114
msgid ""
"Generate API credentials (Activity Number, Secret Key, and Client ID) by "
"going to the `government manuals <manuals_>`_ page and following the steps "
"in **Procedure Manual for Linking to the Jordanian National Electronic "
"Invoicing System**."
msgstr ""
"Hasilkan kredensial API (Nomor Aktivitas, Kunci Rahasia, dan ID Klien) "
"dengan mengunjungi halaman `panduan pemerintah <manuals_>`_ dan ikuti "
"langkah-langkah dalam **Panduan Prosedur untuk Menghubungkan ke Sistem "
"Penagihan Elektronik Nasional Yordania**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:117
msgid ""
"In your Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing (Jordan)` section, enter "
"the API credentials generated previously:"
msgstr ""
"Di database Odoo Anda, buka :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Penagihan Elektronik (Yordania)`, masukkan "
"kredensial API yang dihasilkan sebelumnya:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Activity Number` (income source sequence)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nomor Aktivitas` (urutan sumber pendapatan)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:122
msgid ":guilabel:`JoFotara Secret Key`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kunci Rahasia JoFotara`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:123
msgid ":guilabel:`JoFotara Client ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID Klien JoFotara`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:125
msgid "Enter the :guilabel:`Taxpayer type`:"
msgstr "Masukkan :guilabel:`Jenis Wajib Pajak`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unregistered in the sales tax`: for businesses not registered for "
"sales tax. No tax on the invoice line is required."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tidak terdaftar dalam pajak penjualan`: untuk bisnis yang tidak "
"terdaftar untuk pajak penjualan. Tidak ada pajak pada baris faktur yang "
"diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Registered in the sales tax`: for businesses registered under the "
"standard sales tax system. One tax computed as a percentage is required per "
"invoice line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Terdaftar dalam pajak penjualan`: untuk bisnis yang terdaftar "
"dalam sistem pajak penjualan standar. Satu pajak yang dihitung sebagai "
"persentase diperlukan per baris faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Registered in the special sales tax`: for businesses subject to "
"special sales tax regulations. One tax computed as a percentage and one "
"fixed tax per invoice line are required per invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Terdaftar dalam pajak penjualan khusus`: untuk bisnis yang tunduk "
"pada peraturan pajak penjualan khusus. Satu pajak yang dihitung sebagai "
"persentase dan satu pajak tetap per baris faktur diperlukan per faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:138
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing (Jordan)` section is missing from "
"the :guilabel:`Settings`, make sure the :guilabel:`Jordan E-Invoicing` "
"module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika bagian :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing (Jordan)` hilang "
