#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:195
msgid ""
"In the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`adjust settings`) menu, add "
"the :guilabel:`JoFotara State` and :guilabel:`JoFotara Error` fields to see "
"the sending state and any errors in the list view, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Di menu :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`sesuaikan pengaturan`), "
"tambahkan bidang :guilabel:`Status JoFotara` dan :guilabel:`Kesalahan "
"JoFotara` untuk melihat status pengiriman dan kesalahan apa pun dalam "
"tampilan daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:200
msgid ""
"There is an inherent difference in how values are approximated in Odoo and "
"ISTD due to the differing system architectures. JOD values in Odoo are "
"stored and approximated to three decimals, whereas ISTD expects values to "
"have nine decimals. As a result, an insignificant difference is inevitable "
"and arises between the values stores in Odoo and the values reported to "
"ISTD, which can have an error margin of <0.001."
msgstr ""
"Ada perbedaan yang melekat dalam cara nilai diperkirakan di Odoo dan ISTD "
"karena perbedaan arsitektur sistem. Nilai JOD di Odoo disimpan dan "
"diperkirakan hingga tiga desimal, sedangkan ISTD mengharapkan nilai memiliki "
"sembilan desimal. Akibatnya, perbedaan yang tidak signifikan tidak dapat "
"dihindari dan muncul antara nilai yang disimpan di Odoo dan nilai yang "
"dilaporkan ke ISTD, yang dapat memiliki margin kesalahan <0.001."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:209
msgid "JoFotara State"
msgstr "Status JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:211
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`JoFotara State` field in the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab of "
"confirmed invoices reflects the current state of the document in JoFotara. "
"It can be changed manually to reflect the actual state of the invoices in "
"cases where a technical error or timeout prevents Odoo from updating it "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Status JoFotara` di tab :guilabel:`Info Lainnya` dari "
"faktur yang dikonfirmasi mencerminkan status dokumen saat ini di JoFotara. "
"Ini dapat diubah secara manual untuk mencerminkan status faktur yang "
"sebenarnya dalam kasus di mana kesalahan teknis atau timeout mencegah Odoo "
"memperbaruinya secara otomatis."

