msgstr ""
"Instal paket :ref:`lokalisasi fiskal <fiscal_localizations/packages>` 🇰🇪 "
"**Kenya** untuk mendapatkan semua fitur lokalisasi Kenya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:14
msgid "eTIMS"
msgstr "eTIMS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:16
msgid ""
"The `Kenya Revenue Authority (KRA) <https://www.kra.go.ke/>`_ has "
"implemented the `electronic Tax Invoice Management System (eTIMS) <https://"
"www.kra.go.ke/online-services/etims>`_ for tax collection."
msgstr ""
"`Otoritas Pendapatan Kenya (KRA) <https://www.kra.go.ke/>`_ telah menerapkan "
"`Sistem Manajemen Faktur Pajak Elektronik (eTIMS) <https://www.kra.go.ke/"
"online-services/etims>`_ untuk pengumpulan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:20
msgid ""
"To submit documents through eTIMS, you must use an :abbr:`OSCU (Online Sales "
"Control Unit)` that integrates with the existing **Trader Invoicing System "
"(TIS)**, such as the one provided by Odoo. The OSCU is used to validate, "
"encrypt, sign, transmit, and store tax invoices."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirimkan dokumen melalui eTIMS, Anda harus menggunakan :abbr:`OSCU "
"(Unit Kontrol Penjualan Online)` yang terintegrasi dengan **Sistem Penagihan "
"Pedagang (TIS)** yang ada, seperti yang disediakan oleh Odoo. OSCU digunakan "
"untuk memvalidasi, mengenkripsi, menandatangani, mengirimkan, dan menyimpan "
"faktur pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:25
msgid ""
"Make sure to :ref:`install <general/install>` the **Kenya eTIMS EDI** "
"modules to use the OSCU device fully."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan untuk :ref:`menginstal <general/install>` modul **Kenya eTIMS EDI** "
"untuk menggunakan perangkat OSCU sepenuhnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:31
msgid "OSCU device initialization"
msgstr "Inisialisasi perangkat OSCU"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:33
msgid ""
"The OSCU must be initialized before use. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings`, click :guilabel:`Update "
"Info` in the :guilabel:`Companies` section, and enter your :guilabel:`Tax "
"ID`."
msgstr ""
"OSCU harus diinisialisasi sebelum digunakan. Untuk melakukannya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings`, klik :guilabel:`Update "
"Info` di bagian :guilabel:`Companies`, dan masukkan :guilabel:`Tax ID` Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:37
msgid "To initialize the OSCU:"
msgstr "Untuk menginisialisasi OSCU:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:39
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` and scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Kenya eTIMS Integration` section."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` dan gulir ke bawah ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Kenya eTIMS Integration`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:41
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`eTIMS Server Mode` to :guilabel:`Test` for the "
"initialization."
msgstr ""
"Atur :guilabel:`eTIMS Server Mode` ke :guilabel:`Test` untuk inisialisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:42
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Serial Number` of the device and tick the two check "
"boxes."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan :guilabel:`Serial Number` perangkat dan centang kedua kotak centang."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:43
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Initialize OSCU`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Initialize OSCU`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:46
msgid "Three server modes are available:"
msgstr "Tiga mode server tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Demo`: Designed for demo purposes; it uses mock data and does not "
"require an initialized OSCU;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Demo`: Dirancang untuk tujuan demo; menggunakan data tiruan dan "
"tidak memerlukan OSCU yang diinisialisasi;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Test`: Used to test the connection to eTIMS;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Test`: Digunakan untuk menguji koneksi ke eTIMS;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Production`: Used for live databases that are ready to send data."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Production`: Digunakan untuk database aktif yang siap mengirim "
"data."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:54
msgid ""
"If your device has **already been initialized** (through another ERP, for "
"example), enable the :doc:`../../general/developer_mode`. Then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Kenya eTIMS Integration` section, enter the ID of the unit in "
"the :guilabel:`Unit ID` field and the key obtained through a previous "
"initialization in the :guilabel:`CMC Key` field. Click :guilabel:`Save` when "
"done."
msgstr ""
"Jika perangkat Anda **sudah diinisialisasi** (melalui ERP lain, misalnya), "
"aktifkan :doc:`../../general/developer_mode`. Kemudian, di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Kenya eTIMS Integration`, masukkan ID unit di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Unit ID` dan kunci yang diperoleh melalui inisialisasi "
"sebelumnya di kolom :guilabel:`CMC Key`. Klik :guilabel:`Save` setelah "
"selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:59
msgid ""
"Once the **OSCU module** has been :ref:`initialized <kenya/initialization>`, "
"an OSCU serial number is generated for each company on that database with "
"its **country** set to :guilabel:`Kenya`. The serial number is generated "
"based on the VAT number of the company (regardless of its validity). It is a "
"unique and sequential serial number starting with the prefix `ODOO` followed "
"by the company's **VAT number** and a sequence of numbers."
msgstr ""
"Setelah **modul OSCU** telah :ref:`diinisialisasi <kenya/initialization>`, "
"nomor seri OSCU dihasilkan untuk setiap perusahaan di database tersebut "
"dengan **negara** diatur ke :guilabel:`Kenya`. Nomor seri dihasilkan "
"berdasarkan nomor PPN perusahaan (terlepas dari validitasnya). Ini adalah "
"nomor seri unik dan berurutan yang dimulai dengan awalan `ODOO` diikuti oleh "
"**nomor PPN** perusahaan dan urutan angka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:66
msgid "Registering on eTIMS"
msgstr "Mendaftar di eTIMS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:68
msgid ""
"Taxpayers *must* sign up and create an account on the `KRA portal <https://"
"etims.kra.go.ke/basic/login/indexLogin>`_. If you do not have an account yet:"
msgstr ""
"Wajib pajak *harus* mendaftar dan membuat akun di `portal KRA <https://"
"etims.kra.go.ke/basic/login/indexLogin>`_. Jika Anda belum memiliki akun:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:71
msgid ""
"Sign up, enter your **PIN**, and verify that all information is correct, "
"including your phone number, email address, and postal address. Correct any "
"errors on the `iTax page <https://itax.kra.go.ke/KRA-Portal/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Sign up, masukkan **PIN** Anda, dan verifikasi bahwa semua informasi sudah "
"benar, termasuk nomor telepon, alamat email, dan alamat pos Anda. Perbaiki "
"kesalahan apa pun di `halaman iTax <https://itax.kra.go.ke/KRA-Portal/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:74
msgid ""
"An :abbr:`OTP (One-time Password)` is sent to the phone number provided. "
"Unblock promotional messages if you do not receive it."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`OTP (One-time Password)` dikirim ke nomor telepon yang diberikan. "
"Buka blokir pesan promosi jika Anda tidak menerimanya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:76
msgid ""
"Upload the **business owner ID** *or* **director's ID** (as listed on iTax), "
"along with the filled-out and signed **commitment form** ."
msgstr ""
"Unggah **ID pemilik bisnis** *atau* **ID direktur** (seperti yang tercantum "
"di iTax), beserta **formulir komitmen** yang telah diisi dan ditandatangani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:78
msgid ""
"On the **eTIMS dashboard**, click :guilabel:`Service request` at the top of "
"the page. Select :guilabel:`OSCU` as the **eTIMS type**, enter `Odoo KE LTD` "
"as the third-party integrator, and enter your company's OSCU serial number "
"retrieved earlier."
msgstr ""
"Di **dashboard eTIMS**, klik :guilabel:`Service request` di bagian atas "
"halaman. Pilih :guilabel:`OSCU` sebagai **tipe eTIMS**, masukkan `Odoo KE "
"LTD` sebagai integrator pihak ketiga, dan masukkan nomor seri OSCU "
"perusahaan Anda yang diambil sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:83
msgid ""
"Service request approvals are usually quick. If there's a delay, contact the "
"eTIMS operation or KRA office."
msgstr ""
"Persetujuan permintaan layanan biasanya cepat. Jika ada penundaan, hubungi "
"operasi eTIMS atau kantor KRA."

