#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:92
msgid ""
"To send electronic invoices to MyInvois, you first need to register and log "
"in to the MyInvois portal to grant Odoo the **right to invoice** as an "
"intermediary for your company."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim faktur elektronik ke MyInvois, Anda harus terlebih dahulu "
"mendaftar dan masuk ke portal MyInvois untuk memberikan Odoo **hak untuk "
"membuat faktur** sebagai perantara untuk perusahaan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:96
msgid ""
"If this is the first time you log into the MyInvois portal, "
"click :guilabel:`User Manual` on MyTax_ to learn more about the registration "
"process. Both the **pre-production** (:dfn:`testing environment to try the "
"functions before using the actual (production) environment`) and "
"**production** (:dfn:`actual environment to submit e-invoices with accurate "
"information`) environments are supported."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini adalah pertama kalinya Anda login ke portal MyInvois, "
"klik :guilabel:`User Manual` di MyTax_ untuk mempelajari lebih lanjut "
"tentang proses pendaftaran. Baik lingkungan **pre-production** "
"(:dfn:`lingkungan pengujian untuk mencoba fungsi-fungsi sebelum menggunakan "
"lingkungan aktual (production)`) maupun **production** (:dfn:`lingkungan "
"aktual untuk mengirimkan e-invoice dengan informasi yang akurat`) didukung."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:102
msgid ""
"Log into MyTax_. Choose the :guilabel:`ID Type` and the "
"corresponding :guilabel:`identification number` used to register for the "
