#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:118
msgid ""
"The **Goods and Services Tax (GST) report** is a critical tax reporting "
"requirement for businesses registered for GST. The GST return is used to "
"report and remit GST to the **Inland Revenue Department (IRD)**."
msgstr ""
"**Laporan Pajak Barang dan Jasa (GST)** adalah persyaratan pelaporan pajak "
"penting bagi bisnis yang terdaftar untuk GST. Pengembalian GST digunakan "
"untuk melaporkan dan menyetor GST ke **Departemen Pendapatan Dalam Negeri "
"(IRD)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:None
msgid "GST Report."
msgstr "Laporan GST."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:125
msgid ""
"The base and tax amounts are collected from the **GST**, which is pre-"
"configured in Odoo to align with GST Return requirements (Boxes 1-15). The "
"**GST** can also be manually configured for special use cases, such as "
"specific GST treatments (e.g., zero-rating for exported agricultural goods). "
"Once the **GST** setup for each account is complete, Odoo automatically "
"categorizes journal items into the appropriate boxes. This ensures the "
"**GST** return is accurate and fully reflects the business's financial "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah dasar dan pajak dikumpulkan dari **GST**, yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya di Odoo agar selaras dengan persyaratan Pengembalian GST (Kotak "
"1-15). **GST** juga dapat dikonfigurasi secara manual untuk kasus penggunaan "
"khusus, seperti perlakuan GST tertentu (misalnya, tarif nol untuk barang "
"pertanian yang diekspor). Setelah pengaturan **GST** untuk setiap akun "
"selesai, Odoo secara otomatis mengkategorikan item jurnal ke dalam kotak "
"yang sesuai. Hal ini memastikan pengembalian **GST** akurat dan sepenuhnya "
"mencerminkan aktivitas keuangan bisnis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:138
msgid "Closing the GST report"
msgstr "Menutup laporan GST"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:140
msgid ""
"The :ref:`tax return periodicity <tax-returns/periodicity>` must be set up "
"before submitting the :ref:`tax return <tax-returns/report>` (**GST "
"report**) to the **IRD**."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Periodisitas pengembalian pajak <tax-returns/periodicity>` harus "
"diatur sebelum mengirimkan :ref:`pengembalian pajak <tax-returns/report>` "
"(**laporan GST**) ke **IRD**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:144
msgid ""
":doc:`Year-end closing documentation <../../../applications/finance/"
"accounting/reporting/year_end>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentasi penutupan akhir tahun <../../../applications/finance/"
"accounting/reporting/year_end>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:147
msgid ""
"Before closing the entry for the first time, enable the :doc:`developer mode "
"<../../../applications/general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Tax Groups` to set the "
"default **GST payable account** and **GST receivable account**."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum menutup entri untuk pertama kalinya, aktifkan :doc:`mode pengembang "
"<../../../applications/general/developer_mode>` dan "
"buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Tax Groups` untuk "
"mengatur **akun hutang GST** dan **akun piutang GST** default."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:152
msgid ""
"Once the **GST payable** and **GST receivable** accounts are set up, the "
"**Tax Return** report generates an accurate journal closing entry "
"automatically, balancing the GST balance with the GST clearing account."
msgstr ""
"Setelah akun **hutang GST** dan **piutang GST** diatur, laporan **Tax "
"Return** menghasilkan entri penutupan jurnal yang akurat secara otomatis, "
"menyeimbangkan saldo GST dengan akun kliring GST."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:156
msgid ""
"The balance between **GST receivable** and **payable** is set against the "
"tax clearing account defined on the tax group. The amount to be paid to or "
"received from **IRD** can then be reconciled with a bank transaction."
msgstr ""
"Saldo antara **piutang GST** dan **hutang** diatur terhadap akun kliring "
"pajak yang ditentukan pada grup pajak. Jumlah yang harus dibayarkan kepada "
"atau diterima dari **IRD** kemudian dapat direkonsiliasi dengan transaksi "
"bank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:161
msgid ""
"The **GST** report is not submitted directly to the **IRD**. Instead, Odoo "
"automatically calculates the required values for each section, providing "
"options to audit and review the data for a clearer understanding of its "
"history. Businesses can then submit these values to the `IRD portal <https://"
"myir.ird.govt.nz/_/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Laporan **GST** tidak dikirimkan langsung ke **IRD**. Sebaliknya, Odoo "
"secara otomatis menghitung nilai yang diperlukan untuk setiap bagian, "
"menyediakan opsi untuk mengaudit dan meninjau data untuk pemahaman yang "
"lebih jelas tentang riwayatnya. Bisnis kemudian dapat mengirimkan nilai-"
"nilai ini ke `portal IRD <https://myir.ird.govt.nz/_/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:171
msgid ""
"A remittance advice is a document used as proof of payment to a business. To "
"access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments` and "
"select the payment(s). Then click :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Print` and "
"select :guilabel:`Payment Receipt`."
msgstr ""
"Surat pemberitahuan pengiriman adalah dokumen yang digunakan sebagai bukti "
"pembayaran kepada bisnis. Untuk mengaksesnya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments` dan pilih "
"pembayaran. Kemudian klik :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Print` dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Payment Receipt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:None
msgid "Remittance Advice."
msgstr "Remittance Advice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:188
msgid ""
"Odoo allows :ref:`electronic invoicing <accounting/e-invoicing/"
"configuration>` settings to be configured per contact."
msgstr ""
"Odoo memungkinkan pengaturan :ref:`faktur elektronik <accounting/e-invoicing/"
"configuration>` dikonfigurasi per kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:None
msgid "Peppol Contact."
msgstr "Peppol Contact."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:195
msgid ""
"Validating an invoice or credit note for a contact on the PEPPOL network "
"will download a compliant XML file that can be manually uploaded to the "
"PEPPOL network. Odoo is currently in the process of becoming an access point "
"for the ANZ region."
msgstr ""
"Memvalidasi faktur atau nota kredit untuk kontak di jaringan PEPPOL akan "
"mengunduh file XML yang sesuai yang dapat diunggah secara manual ke jaringan "
"PEPPOL. Odoo saat ini sedang dalam proses menjadi titik akses untuk wilayah "
"ANZ."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:200
msgid ""
"`PEPPOL requirements <https://peppol.org/learn-more/country-profiles/new-"
"zealand/>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Persyaratan PEPPOL <https://peppol.org/learn-more/country-profiles/new-"
"zealand/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:205
msgid "EFT batch payments"
msgstr "Pembayaran batch EFT"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:207
msgid ""
"An :abbr:`EFT (electronic funds transfer)` batch file is a digital format "
"used to facilitate bulk payment processing for businesses. It allows "
"companies to consolidate multiple inbound and outbound payments into a "
"single electronic file. This process is commonly used by businesses handling "
"multiple payments at once, such as payroll or payments to multiple suppliers."
msgstr ""
"File batch :abbr:`EFT (electronic funds transfer)` adalah format digital "
"yang digunakan untuk memfasilitasi pemrosesan pembayaran massal untuk "
"bisnis. Ini memungkinkan perusahaan untuk mengonsolidasikan beberapa "
"pembayaran masuk dan keluar ke dalam satu file elektronik. Proses ini "
"umumnya digunakan oleh bisnis yang menangani beberapa pembayaran sekaligus, "
"seperti payroll atau pembayaran kepada beberapa pemasok."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:219
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`EFT Batch Payment` module "
"(`l10n_nz_eft`)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Instal <general/install>` modul :guilabel:`EFT Batch Payment` "
"(`l10n_nz_eft`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:220
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` section, enable :guilabel:`Batch Payments`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. Di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Customer Payments`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Batch Payments`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:224
msgid ":doc:`../../../applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:231
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` to "
"configure the bank **journal**. In the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, "
"enter the :guilabel:`Account Number` and click :guilabel:`Create and "
"edit...`. In the :guilabel:`Create Account Number` window, fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` and enable :guilabel:`Send Money` to set the bank "
"account as trusted. The :guilabel:`Currency` field is optional."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` untuk "
"mengonfigurasi **jurnal** bank. Di tab :guilabel:`Journal Entries`, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Account Number` dan klik :guilabel:`Create and edit...`. "
"Di jendela :guilabel:`Create Account Number`, isi :guilabel:`Bank` dan "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Send Money` untuk mengatur akun bank sebagai tepercaya. "
"Bidang :guilabel:`Currency` bersifat opsional."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:240
msgid "Contacts' bank accounts"
msgstr "Akun bank kontak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:242
msgid ""
"To add banking information for a contact, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Customers`, :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors`, or access "
"the contact directly through the **Contacts** app. Select the relevant "
"contact, then open the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. Under the :guilabel:`Bank "
"Accounts` section, click :guilabel:`Add a line` to enter the required "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan informasi perbankan untuk kontak, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Pelanggan --> "
"Pelanggan`, :menuselection:`Akuntansi --> Vendor --> Vendor`, atau akses "
"kontak secara langsung melalui aplikasi **Kontak**. Pilih kontak yang "
"relevan, kemudian buka tab :guilabel:`Akuntansi`. Di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Rekening Bank`, klik :guilabel:`Tambah baris` untuk "
"memasukkan detail yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:250
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account Holder` (it will automatically be selected for that "
"contact)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pemegang Rekening` (akan otomatis dipilih untuk kontak tersebut)"

