"for **New Zealand**, use the following value as :guilabel:`Payroll URL`: "
"`https://api.nzpayroll.co.nz/`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :ref:`mengkonfigurasi API Employment Hero <employment_hero/"
"configuration>` untuk **Selandia Baru**, gunakan nilai berikut "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Payroll URL`: `https://api.nzpayroll.co.nz/`."

