"metode pembayaran di Amerika Latin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:977
msgid ""
"Make sure to define a :guilabel:`Sales Price` on the :guilabel:`Delivery "
"Product` of the shipping method to prevent errors when validating the "
"invoice with |SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan untuk menentukan :guilabel:`Sales Price` pada :guilabel:`Delivery "
"Product` dari metode pengiriman untuk mencegah kesalahan saat memvalidasi "
"faktur dengan |SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:979
msgid ""
"To offer free delivery, manually remove the :guilabel:`Delivery Product`, or "
"at least use `$0.01` (one cent) for the invoice to be validated with SUNAT."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menawarkan pengiriman gratis, hapus secara manual :guilabel:`Delivery "
"Product`, atau setidaknya gunakan `$0.01` (satu sen) agar faktur dapat "
"divalidasi dengan SUNAT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:983
