#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:54
msgid "E-invoicing with KSeF"
msgstr "E-invoicing dengan KSeF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:56
msgid ""
"`KSeF <https://ksef.podatki.gov.pl/>`_ is Poland's mandatory, centralized "
"electronic invoicing system used to issue, transmit, and store electronic "
"invoices according to national regulations."
msgstr ""
"`KSeF <https://ksef.podatki.gov.pl/>`_ adalah sistem e-invoicing terpusat "
"wajib Polandia yang digunakan untuk menerbitkan, mengirimkan, dan menyimpan "
"faktur elektronik sesuai dengan peraturan nasional."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:62
msgid ""
"`KSeF platform video tutorials of the Polish Ministry of Finance <https://"
"www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=V6E1fGUFPw4&list=PLGj5OAFBHLKX0cEVGjcGplnbX6LpDFF38&index=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Tutorial video platform KSeF dari Kementerian Keuangan Polandia <https://"
"www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=V6E1fGUFPw4&list=PLGj5OAFBHLKX0cEVGjcGplnbX6LpDFF38&index=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:67
msgid ""
"To use KSeF e-Invoicing with Odoo, first `create a KSeF account <https://"
"ap.ksef.mf.gov.pl/web/>`_ or log in using your company's NIP if you already "
"have credentials. Next, request a certificate and ensure you save the "
"password created during this process, as it will be required later."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan E-Invoicing KSeF dengan Odoo, pertama `buat akun KSeF "
"<https://ap.ksef.mf.gov.pl/web/>`_ atau masuk menggunakan NIP perusahaan "
"Anda jika Anda sudah memiliki kredensial. Selanjutnya, minta sertifikat dan "
"pastikan Anda menyimpan kata sandi yang dibuat selama proses ini, karena "
"akan diperlukan nanti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:71
msgid ""
"Once the certificate request is complete, download the `.pem` **certificate "
"file** and save the **private key** issued by KSeF. You will need both to "
"complete the Odoo integration."
msgstr ""
"Setelah permintaan sertifikat selesai, unduh **file sertifikat** `.pem` dan "
"simpan **kunci pribadi** yang diterbitkan oleh KSeF. Anda akan memerlukan "
"keduanya untuk menyelesaikan integrasi Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:77
msgid "Link Odoo to KSeF"
msgstr "Hubungkan Odoo ke KSeF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:80
msgid ""
"`KSeF test and pre-production environments <https://ksef.podatki.gov.pl/"
"aplikacja-podatnika-ksef-20/>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Lingkungan pengujian dan pra-produksi KSeF <https://ksef.podatki.gov.pl/"
"aplikacja-podatnika-ksef-20/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:83
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Polish Localization` section and "
"enable :guilabel:`Allow KSeF integration`."
msgstr ""
"Gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Polish Localization` dan "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Allow KSeF integration`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:85
msgid ""
"Enter a name for your KSeF certificate in the newly enabled field, then "
"select :guilabel:`Create and edit...` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan nama untuk sertifikat KSeF Anda di bidang yang baru diaktifkan, "
"kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Create and edit...` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:87
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, click :guilabel:`Upload your file` and select your "
"**certificate** (`.pem`). In the :guilabel:`Certificate Password` field, "
"enter the password created during the certificate application on the KSeF "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela pop-up, klik :guilabel:`Upload your file` dan pilih "
"**sertifikat** Anda (`.pem`). Di bidang :guilabel:`Certificate Password`, "
"masukkan kata sandi yang dibuat selama aplikasi sertifikat di platform KSeF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once the certificate is uploaded, the :guilabel:`Private Key` field appears. "
"Click the empty field, select :guilabel:`Create` from the drop-down menu, "
"and enter your **private key**. The **public key** is embedded within the "
"`.pem` file and is automatically filled in."
msgstr ""
"Setelah sertifikat diunggah, bidang :guilabel:`Private Key` muncul. Klik "
"bidang kosong, pilih :guilabel:`Create` dari menu drop-down, dan masukkan "
"**kunci pribadi** Anda. **Kunci publik** tertanam dalam file `.pem` dan "
"diisi secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:93
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:100
msgid ""
"The KSeF invoicing workflow requires address information related to the "
"company that sends the invoices and the customers who receive them:"
msgstr ""
"Alur kerja penagihan KSeF memerlukan informasi alamat terkait dengan "
"perusahaan yang mengirim faktur dan pelanggan yang menerimanya:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:103
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies` and "
"select the company that will use KSeF."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies` dan pilih "
"perusahaan yang akan menggunakan KSeF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:105
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Company Name`, :guilabel:`VAT` (Tax ID), "
"and :guilabel:`Country`. If desired, fill in additional optional fields such "
"as :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
"and :guilabel:`ZIP`."
msgstr ""
"Isi :guilabel:`Company Name`, :guilabel:`VAT` (Tax ID), "
"dan :guilabel:`Country`. Jika diinginkan, isi bidang opsional tambahan "
"seperti :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
"dan :guilabel:`ZIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:110
msgid "The :guilabel:`Country` must be set to :guilabel:`Poland`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Country` harus diatur ke :guilabel:`Poland`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:111
msgid "The company must have a valid Polish VAT (**NIP**) number."
msgstr "Perusahaan harus memiliki nomor VAT Polandia (**NIP**) yang valid."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:113
msgid ""
"Open the **Accounting** app, and go to :menuselection:`Customers --> "
"Customers`."
msgstr ""
"Buka aplikasi **Akuntansi**, dan buka :menuselection:`Customers --> "
"Customers`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:114
msgid ""
"For each customer whose invoices will be sent to KSeF, click on the customer "
"to open the form view, and complete the :guilabel:`Country` "
"and :guilabel:`VAT`. If desired, fill in additional optional fields such "
"as :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
