"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Companies`, "
"click :guilabel:`Update info`, and ensure the following company information "
"is complete and up-to-date."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Companies`, "
"klik :guilabel:`Update info`, dan pastikan informasi perusahaan berikut "
"lengkap dan terkini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:43
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Company Name`, limited to a maximum of 63 characters to "
"comply with ZATCA requirements."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nama Perusahaan`, dibatasi maksimal 63 karakter untuk mematuhi "
"persyaratan ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:45
msgid ""
"All relevant :guilabel:`Address` fields, including the :guilabel:`Building "
"Number` and :guilabel:`Plot Identification` (four digits each)."
msgstr ""
"Semua kolom :guilabel:`Address` yang relevan, termasuk :guilabel:`Building "
"Number` dan :guilabel:`Plot Identification` (masing-masing empat digit)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:47
msgid ""
"Select an enterprise :guilabel:`Identification Scheme`. It is recommended to "
"use the :guilabel:`Commercial Registration Number`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Identification Scheme` perusahaan. Disarankan untuk "
"menggunakan :guilabel:`Commercial Registration Number`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:49
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Identification Number` for the "
"selected :guilabel:`Identification Scheme`."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan :guilabel:`Identification Number` untuk :guilabel:`Identification "
"Scheme` yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:50
msgid "The :guilabel:`VAT` number."
msgstr "Nomor :guilabel:`VAT`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:51
msgid "Ensure the :guilabel:`Currency` is set to :guilabel:`SAR`."
msgstr "Pastikan :guilabel:`Currency` diatur ke :guilabel:`SAR`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:54
msgid ""
"It is also necessary to fill out similar information for partner companies."
msgstr "Perlu juga mengisi informasi serupa untuk perusahaan mitra."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:60
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended to thoroughly test all invoicing workflows using "
"the Fatoora **simulation** portal first, as **any** invoice submitted to the "
"regular Fatoora portal will be accounted for, which could lead to fines and "
"penalties."
msgstr ""
"Sangat disarankan untuk menguji secara menyeluruh semua alur kerja penagihan "
"menggunakan portal **simulasi** Fatoora terlebih dahulu, karena **setiap** "
"invoice yang dikirimkan ke portal Fatoora reguler akan diperhitungkan, yang "
"dapat menyebabkan denda dan penalti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:65
msgid "Fatoora simulation portal"
msgstr "Portal simulasi Fatoora"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:67
msgid ""
"Log in on the `Fatoora portal <https://fatoora.zatca.gov.sa/>`_ using the "
"company's ZATCA credentials. Then, click the :guilabel:`Fatoora Simulation "
"Portal` button to switch to the simulation portal."
msgstr ""
"Masuk ke `portal Fatoora <https://fatoora.zatca.gov.sa/>`_ menggunakan "
"kredensial ZATCA perusahaan. Kemudian, klik tombol :guilabel:`Fatoora "
"Simulation Portal` untuk beralih ke portal simulasi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:72
msgid ""
"`ZACTA Fatoora portal user manual version 3 (May 2023) <https://zatca.gov.sa/"
"en/E-Invoicing/Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/"
"Fatoora_Portal_User_Manual_English.pdf>`_"
msgstr ""
"Manual pengguna portal `ZACTA Fatoora versi 3 (Mei 2023) <https://"
"zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/"
"Fatoora_Portal_User_Manual_English.pdf>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:77
msgid "ZATCA API integration"
msgstr "Integrasi API ZATCA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:79
msgid ""
"On Odoo, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Under :guilabel:`ZATCA API Integration`, select the :guilabel:`Simulation "
"(Pre-Production)` :guilabel:`API mode` and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. Di "
"bawah :guilabel:`ZATCA API Integration`, pilih :guilabel:`Simulation (Pre-"
"Production)` :guilabel:`API mode` dan klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:88
msgid ""
"Each sales journal on Odoo needs to be configured. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, open any "
"sales journal (e.g., Customer Invoices), and go to the :guilabel:`ZATCA` "
"tab. Once there, enter any :guilabel:`Serial Number` to identify the journal."
msgstr ""
"Setiap jurnal penjualan di Odoo perlu dikonfigurasi. Untuk melakukannya, "
"buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, buka jurnal "
"penjualan apa pun (misalnya, Customer Invoices), dan buka "
"tab :guilabel:`ZATCA`. Setelah itu, masukkan :guilabel:`Serial Number` apa "
"pun untuk mengidentifikasi jurnal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:93
msgid ""
"The same serial number can be used for all of the company's sales journals."
msgstr ""
"Nomor seri yang sama dapat digunakan untuk semua jurnal penjualan perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:95
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Onboard Journal`. In the dialog box, providing "
"an :abbr:`OTP (one-time password)` code is required. To retrieve it, open "
"the `Fatoora simulation portal <https://fatoora.zatca.gov.sa/>`_, "
"click :guilabel:`Onboard New Solution Unit/Device`, choose the number of OTP "
"codes to generate (one per journal to configure), and "
"click :guilabel:`Generate OTP Code`. Copy an OTP code, it into the dialog "
"box on Odoo, and click :guilabel:`Request`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Onboard Journal`. Dalam kotak dialog, "
"diperlukan kode :abbr:`OTP (one-time password)`. Untuk mendapatkannya, buka "
"`portal simulasi Fatoora <https://fatoora.zatca.gov.sa/>`_, "
"klik :guilabel:`Onboard New Solution Unit/Device`, pilih jumlah kode OTP "
"yang akan dibuat (satu per jurnal yang akan dikonfigurasi), dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Generate OTP Code`. Salin kode OTP, masukkan ke dalam kotak "
"dialog di Odoo, dan klik :guilabel:`Request`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:102
msgid "OTP codes expire after one hour."
msgstr "Kode OTP akan kedaluwarsa setelah satu jam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:105
msgid ""
"If any issue occurs during onboarding, click :guilabel:`Regenerate CSR` to "
"start again."
msgstr ""
"Jika terjadi masalah selama onboarding, klik :guilabel:`Regenerate CSR` "
"untuk memulai lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:110
msgid ""
"When confirming an invoice, there is now an option to process the invoice, "
"sending it directly the Fatoora simulation portal. Odoo displays the "
"portal's response after each submission. Only rejected invoices can be reset "
"to draft and edited on Odoo. Furthermore, at the end of each day, Odoo sends "
"all unprocessed invoices to the portal."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengonfirmasi invoice, sekarang ada opsi untuk memproses invoice, "
"mengirimkannya langsung ke portal simulasi Fatoora. Odoo menampilkan respons "
"portal setelah setiap pengiriman. Hanya invoice yang ditolak yang dapat "
"direset ke draft dan diedit di Odoo. Selain itu, di akhir setiap hari, Odoo "
"mengirimkan semua invoice yang belum diproses ke portal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:116
msgid ""
"Testing all invoicing workflows, preferably with real invoices and for a "
"reasonable amount of time, is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Disarankan untuk menguji semua alur kerja penagihan, sebaiknya dengan "
"invoice nyata dan untuk jangka waktu yang wajar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:118
msgid ""
"Compare the invoices received statistics page on the Fatoora simulation "
"portal with the list of invoices on Odoo to ensure both align."
msgstr ""
"Bandingkan halaman statistik invoice yang diterima di portal simulasi "
"Fatoora dengan daftar invoice di Odoo untuk memastikan keduanya selaras."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:124
msgid ""
"When using a **0% tax** in a customer invoice, it is necessary to specify "
"the reason behind such a rate. To configure taxes, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> Taxes`, and "
"open the tax to edit. Under the :guilabel:`Advanced Options`, select "
"an :guilabel:`Exemption Reason Code` and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan **pajak 0%** dalam invoice pelanggan, perlu menentukan "
"alasan di balik tarif tersebut. Untuk mengonfigurasi pajak, "
"buka :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> Taxes`, "
"dan buka pajak yang akan diedit. Di bawah :guilabel:`Advanced Options`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Exemption Reason Code` dan klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:129
msgid ""
"When using **retention** or **withholding an amount** in a customer invoice, "
"the tax used to retain the amount needs to be specified."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan **retensi** atau **pemotongan jumlah** dalam invoice "
"pelanggan, pajak yang digunakan untuk menahan jumlah tersebut perlu "
"ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:133
msgid "Production mode"
msgstr "Mode produksi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:135
msgid ""
"When ready for production, change the :ref:`API mode <saudi-arabia/api-"
"mode>` to :guilabel:`Production` and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Saat siap untuk produksi, ubah :ref:`API mode <saudi-arabia/api-mode>` "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Production` dan klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:139
msgid ""
"Setting the :guilabel:`API mode` to :guilabel:`Production` is "
"**irreversible**."
msgstr ""
"Mengatur :guilabel:`API mode` ke :guilabel:`Production` bersifat **tidak "
"dapat diubah**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:141
msgid ""
"The sales journals initially linked to the simulation portal now needs to be "
"linked to the regular portal. To do so, :ref:`onboard the journals <saudi-"
"arabia/journals>` again, ensuring to use the regular `Fatoora portal "
"<https://fatoora.zatca.gov.sa/>`_ this time."
msgstr ""
"Jurnal penjualan yang awalnya terhubung ke portal simulasi sekarang perlu "
"dihubungkan ke portal reguler. Untuk melakukannya, :ref:`onboard jurnal "
"<saudi-arabia/journals>` lagi, pastikan untuk menggunakan `portal Fatoora "
"<https://fatoora.zatca.gov.sa/>`_ reguler kali ini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:3
