"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` section of the vendor bill and select the "
"appropriate |CIS| tax rate in the :guilabel:`Taxes` column of the **labor** "
"items."
msgstr ""
"Pajak |CIS| yang sesuai harus diterapkan pada **item tenaga kerja** pada "
"tagihan vendor berdasarkan :guilabel:`Deduction Rate` "
"subkontraktor: :guilabel:`0% CIS`, :guilabel:`20% CIS` atau :guilabel:`30% "
"CIS`. Untuk menerapkan tarif, buka bagian :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` dari "
"tagihan vendor dan pilih tarif pajak |CIS| yang sesuai di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Taxes` dari item **tenaga kerja**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:358
