#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:189
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Chart of Accounts` dashboard, create new accounts by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`New` button in the top-left corner of the dashboard "
"and :ref:`filling in the corresponding form <chart-of-account/create>`. "
"Search and sort through existing accounts by using "
"specific :guilabel:`Filters` and :guilabel:`Group By` criteria, which are "
"available in the search drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Dari dashboard :guilabel:`Bagan Akun`, buat akun baru dengan mengklik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Baru` di pojok kiri atas dashboard dan :ref:`mengisi "
"formulir yang sesuai <chart-of-account/create>`. Cari dan urutkan akun yang "
"ada dengan menggunakan :guilabel:`Filter` dan "
"kriteria :guilabel:`Kelompokkan Berdasarkan` tertentu, yang tersedia di menu "
"drop-down pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:195
msgid ""
"To filter accounts by category, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(caret down)` icon to access the drop-down menu and look "
"under the :guilabel:`Filters` column for individual selections. Clicking on "
"a specific category will only show accounts that match that particular "
"filter."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memfilter akun berdasarkan kategori, klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(caret down)` untuk mengakses menu drop-down dan lihat di "
"bawah kolom :guilabel:`Filters` untuk pilihan individual. Mengklik kategori "
"tertentu hanya akan menampilkan akun yang sesuai dengan filter tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:199
msgid ""
"To view all the available account types, remove all of the filters in the "
"search bar, and then click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(caret "
"down)` icon to access the drop-down menu. From there, "
"select :guilabel:`Account Type` under the :guilabel:`Group By` column "
"heading to list all of the account types in the table."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua jenis akun yang tersedia, hapus semua filter di bilah "
"pencarian, kemudian klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(caret down)` "
"untuk mengakses menu drop-down. Dari sana, pilih :guilabel:`Account Type` di "
"bawah judul kolom :guilabel:`Group By` untuk membuat daftar semua jenis akun "
"dalam tabel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "Chart of Accounts grouped by Account Type."
msgstr "Bagan Akun dikelompokkan berdasarkan Tipe Akun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:208
msgid ""
"Besides structure, there are other key differences in the chart of accounts "
"in the United States, compared to other countries:"
msgstr ""
"Selain struktur, ada perbedaan utama lainnya dalam bagan akun di Amerika "
"Serikat, dibandingkan dengan negara lain:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:211
msgid ""
"**Specificity**: US |GAAP| often requires more detailed accounts compared to "
"some other countries. This can include separate accounts for various types "
"of revenue, expenses, and assets, providing more granular information in "
"financial reports."
msgstr ""
"**Kekhususan**: |GAAP| AS sering memerlukan akun yang lebih detail "
"dibandingkan dengan beberapa negara lain. Ini dapat mencakup akun terpisah "
"untuk berbagai jenis pendapatan, pengeluaran, dan aset, memberikan informasi "
"yang lebih rinci dalam laporan keuangan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:214
msgid ""
"**Regulatory Requirements**: In the United States, there are specific "
"regulatory requirements set by bodies such as the |SEC| for publicly traded "
"companies. These requirements may influence the structure and content of the "
"|COA| to ensure compliance with reporting standards."
msgstr ""
"**Persyaratan Regulasi**: Di Amerika Serikat, ada persyaratan regulasi "
"khusus yang ditetapkan oleh badan seperti |SEC| untuk perusahaan yang "
"diperdagangkan secara publik. Persyaratan ini dapat memengaruhi struktur dan "
"konten |COA| untuk memastikan kepatuhan terhadap standar pelaporan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:217
msgid ""
"**Industry Practices**: Certain industries in the United States may have "
"unique accounting requirements or specialized |COA| structures. For example, "
"financial institutions often have specific accounts related to loans, "
"investments, and interest income."
msgstr ""
"**Praktik Industri**: Industri tertentu di Amerika Serikat mungkin memiliki "
"persyaratan akuntansi unik atau struktur |COA| khusus. Misalnya, lembaga "
"keuangan sering memiliki akun khusus yang berkaitan dengan pinjaman, "
"investasi, dan pendapatan bunga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:220
msgid ""
"**Tax Considerations**: The |COA| may also reflect tax considerations, such "
"as accounts for deductible expenses, deferred tax assets, and liabilities, "
"to ensure compliance with tax laws and facilitate tax reporting."
msgstr ""
"**Pertimbangan Pajak**: |COA| juga dapat mencerminkan pertimbangan pajak, "
"seperti akun untuk pengeluaran yang dapat dikurangkan, aset pajak tangguhan, "
"dan kewajiban, untuk memastikan kepatuhan terhadap undang-undang pajak dan "
"memfasilitasi pelaporan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:224
msgid ""
"These differences, ultimately, should be reflected in the |COA| structure "
"itself, with the addition of new accounts, as needed, in order to meet the "
"demands of US accounting reporting requirements."
msgstr ""
"Perbedaan ini, pada akhirnya, harus tercermin dalam struktur |COA| itu "
"sendiri, dengan penambahan akun baru, sesuai kebutuhan, untuk memenuhi "
"tuntutan persyaratan pelaporan akuntansi AS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:228
msgid ":ref:`Create a new account <chart-of-account/create>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Buat akun baru <chart-of-account/create>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:236
msgid ""
"In the United States, tax rates and what is considered taxable vary by "
"jurisdiction. Default *Sales* and *Purchase* taxes are created automatically "
"when the Odoo *Accounting* application is installed. To manage existing or "
"configure additional taxes, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Di Amerika Serikat, tarif pajak dan apa yang dianggap kena pajak bervariasi "
"menurut yurisdiksi. Pajak *Sales* dan *Purchase* default dibuat secara "
"otomatis ketika aplikasi *Akuntansi* Odoo diinstal. Untuk mengelola pajak "
"yang ada atau mengonfigurasi pajak tambahan, buka :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Configuration --> Taxes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:246
msgid ""
"**Avalara AvaTax** is a cloud-based tax calculation and compliance software "
"that integrates with Odoo for several localizations. Integrating AvaTax with "
"Odoo provides real-time and region-specific tax calculations when items are "
"sold, purchased, and invoiced in the database."
msgstr ""
"**Avalara AvaTax** adalah perangkat lunak perhitungan dan kepatuhan pajak "
"berbasis cloud yang terintegrasi dengan Odoo untuk beberapa lokalisasi. "
"Mengintegrasikan AvaTax dengan Odoo menyediakan perhitungan pajak real-time "
"dan khusus wilayah ketika item dijual, dibeli, dan ditagih dalam database."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:251
msgid ""
"AvaTax is available for integration with databases/companies that have "
"locations in the United States and Canada. Reference the :ref:`accounting/"
"avatax/fiscal_country` documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"AvaTax tersedia untuk integrasi dengan database/perusahaan yang memiliki "
"lokasi di Kanada dan/atau Amerika Serikat. Rujuk "
"dokumentasi :ref:`accounting/avatax/fiscal_country` untuk informasi lebih "
"lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:262
msgid ""
"`US Tax Compliance: AvaTax elearning video <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/us-tax-compliance-avatax-2858?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Video eLearning Kepatuhan Pajak AS: Avatax <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/us-tax-compliance-avatax-2858?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:272
msgid ""
"A number of :doc:`report selections <../accounting/reporting>` are readily "
"available for the US localization, under the :menuselection:`Accounting app "
