#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:147
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice type`: The invoice type on which to declare an issuance "
"notice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis faktur`: Jenis faktur yang akan dideklarasikan dalam "
"pemberitahuan penerbitan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice template`: Select from the list of templates available "
"based on the invoice type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Template faktur`: Pilih dari daftar template yang tersedia "
"berdasarkan jenis faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Symbol`: Select from the list of symbols available based on the "
"invoice type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Simbol`: Pilih dari daftar simbol yang tersedia berdasarkan jenis "
"faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quantity`: Total number of invoices to issue for the selected "
"type. Based on the type and template selected, this field is filled in "
"automatically. It can be changed if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jumlah`: Total jumlah faktur yang akan diterbitkan untuk jenis "
"yang dipilih. Berdasarkan jenis dan template yang dipilih, kolom ini terisi "
"otomatis. Dapat diubah jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start date of use`: The date from which the invoice template, "
"range, and quantity are used for the issuance notice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal mulai penggunaan`: Tanggal mulai template faktur, "
"rentang, dan jumlah digunakan untuk pemberitahuan penerbitan."

