"masukkan :guilabel:`Alasan` pembatalan, :guilabel:`Nama Perjanjian`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Tanggal Perjanjian`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Minta Pembatalan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:228
