"the :guilabel:`Website` dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
"Buka :guilabel:`Settings` di sidebar kiri, pilih :guilabel:`My Integration "
"Settings`, lalu pilih halaman pembayaran Anda di menu "
"dropdown :guilabel:`Website`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/nuvei.rst:21
