"for :ref:`later <payment_providers/nuvei/odoo>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Reveal`, lalu salin :guilabel:`Secret Key` dan simpan "
"untuk :ref:`nanti <payment_providers/nuvei/odoo>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/nuvei.rst:27
msgid ""
"Nuvei supports additional functionality relating to error handling from the "
"same page as above. For example, the following options are available for "
"handling failed transactions: Enable :guilabel:`User Trap` to redirect users "
"back to the payment page and allow them to attempt another deposit "
"or :guilabel:`Decline Recovery` to display a popup suggesting alternative or "
"similar payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Nuvei mendukung fungsionalitas tambahan terkait penanganan kesalahan dari "
"halaman yang sama seperti di atas. Misalnya, opsi berikut tersedia untuk "
"menangani transaksi yang gagal: Aktifkan :guilabel:`User Trap` untuk "
"mengarahkan user kembali ke halaman pembayaran dan memungkinkan mereka untuk "
"mencoba deposit lain atau :guilabel:`Decline Recovery` untuk menampilkan "
"popup yang menyarankan metode pembayaran alternatif atau serupa."

