"The :guilabel:`Bank Account` defined for the :guilabel:`Payment Journal` "
"must be a valid IBAN."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bank Account` yang didefinisikan untuk :guilabel:`Payment "
"Journal` harus berupa IBAN yang valid."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:55
msgid ""
"You can also test SEPA direct debit payments using "
"the :ref:`payment_providers/test-mode`."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menguji pembayaran SEPA direct debit "
"menggunakan :ref:`payment_providers/test-mode`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:61
msgid "Online payments with |sdd|"
msgstr "Pembayaran online dengan |sdd|"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:63
msgid ""
"Customers selecting |sdd| as a payment method are prompted to enter their "
"IBAN to complete the :ref:`SEPA Direct Debit mandate <accounting/"
"sepa_payments/sdd_mandates>`."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan yang memilih |sdd| sebagai metode pembayaran akan diminta untuk "
"memasukkan IBAN mereka untuk menyelesaikan :ref:`mandat SEPA Direct Debit "
"<accounting/sepa_payments/sdd_mandates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:66
msgid ""
"The |sdd| mandate is then automatically created in :guilabel:`Draft` based "
"on the provided IBAN. To validate the information, customers must confirm "
"each new mandate with a successful bank transfer of the expected amount "
"**using the specified payment reference (communication)** defined in "
"the :ref:`SEPA Direct Debit payment provider's form <sdd/configuration>`. "
"Once this initial payment is received and :doc:`reconciled <../accounting/"
"bank/reconciliation>`, the mandate is automatically validated and updated to "
"the :guilabel:`Active` status. Once a mandate is active, it is reused for "
"all subsequent payments made with the |sdd| payment method. You can then "
"collect them by :ref:`uploading them to your online banking interface "
"<accounting/sepa_payments/XML>`."
msgstr ""
"Mandat |sdd| kemudian secara otomatis dibuat dalam status :guilabel:`Draft` "
"berdasarkan IBAN yang diberikan. Untuk memvalidasi informasi, pelanggan "
"harus mengkonfirmasi setiap mandat baru dengan transfer bank yang berhasil "
"sejumlah yang diharapkan **menggunakan referensi pembayaran (komunikasi) "
"yang ditentukan** yang didefinisikan dalam :ref:`formulir penyedia "
"pembayaran SEPA Direct Debit <sdd/configuration>`. Setelah pembayaran awal "
"ini diterima dan :doc:`direkonsiliasi <../accounting/bank/reconciliation>`, "
"mandat secara otomatis divalidasi dan diperbarui ke "
"status :guilabel:`Active`. Setelah mandat aktif, mandat tersebut digunakan "
"kembali untuk semua pembayaran berikutnya yang dilakukan dengan metode "
"pembayaran |sdd|. Anda kemudian dapat mengumpulkannya "
"dengan :ref:`mengunggahnya ke antarmuka online banking Anda <accounting/"
"sepa_payments/XML>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:76
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/payments/sepa_payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/payments/sepa_payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:79
msgid ""
"Mandates are automatically :ref:`closed <accounting/sepa_payments/close-"
"revoke-mandate>` 36 months after the date of the last collection."
msgstr ""
"Mandat secara otomatis :ref:`ditutup <accounting/sepa_payments/close-revoke-"
"mandate>` 36 bulan setelah tanggal penagihan terakhir."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:81
msgid ""
"|sdd| is also available as a payment method through other providers, such "
"as :doc:`adyen`, :doc:`buckaroo`, and :doc:`stripe`. In these cases, |sdd| "
"mandates are handled externally by the payment provider."
msgstr ""
"|sdd| juga tersedia sebagai metode pembayaran melalui penyedia lain, "
"seperti :doc:`adyen`, :doc:`buckaroo`, dan :doc:`stripe`. Dalam kasus ini, "
"mandat |sdd| ditangani secara eksternal oleh penyedia pembayaran."

