"Go to `the API keys page on Stripe <https://dashboard.stripe.com/account/"
"apikeys>`_, or log into your Stripe dashboard and go "
"to :menuselection:`Developers --> API Keys`."
msgstr ""
"Buka `halaman API keys di Stripe <https://dashboard.stripe.com/account/"
"apikeys>`_, atau login ke dashboard Stripe Anda dan "
"buka :menuselection:`Developers --> API Keys`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:68
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Standard keys` section, copy the :guilabel:`Publishable "
"key` and the :guilabel:`Secret key` and save them for "
"the :ref:`payment_providers/stripe/odoo-configuration` step."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian :guilabel:`Standard keys`, salin :guilabel:`Publishable key` "
"dan :guilabel:`Secret key` dan simpan untuk langkah :ref:`payment_providers/"
"stripe/odoo-configuration`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:77
msgid ":ref:`Enable the developer mode <developer-mode>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Aktifkan mode pengembang <developer-mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:78
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the Stripe payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Navigasi ke penyedia pembayaran Stripe <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:79
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab, fill in the :guilabel:`Publishable Key` "
"and :guilabel:`Secret Key` fields with the values you :ref:`previously saved "
"<payment_providers/stripe/stripe-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Pada tab :guilabel:`Credentials`, isi field :guilabel:`Publishable Key` "
"dan :guilabel:`Secret Key` dengan nilai yang :ref:`sebelumnya disimpan "
"<payment_providers/stripe/stripe-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:82
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Generate your webhook`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Generate your webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:87
msgid ""
"You can also test Stripe without affecting live transactions using "
"the :ref:`test mode <payment_providers/test-mode>` and the :ref:`API keys "
"<payment_providers/stripe/stripe-configuration>` of your `Stripe account's "
"Test Mode or a sandbox environment <https://docs.stripe.com/testing-use-"
"cases>`_."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menguji Stripe tanpa mempengaruhi transaksi langsung "
"menggunakan :ref:`test mode <payment_providers/test-mode>` dan :ref:`API "
"keys <payment_providers/stripe/stripe-configuration>` dari `Stripe account's "
"Test Mode atau sandbox environment <https://docs.stripe.com/testing-use-"
"cases>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:91
msgid ""
"To link the same Stripe account to :doc:`multiple companies </applications/"
"general/companies/multi_company>` in a database, :ref:`create an account "
"<payment_providers/stripe/create_account>` and :ref:`fill in the credentials "
"<payment_providers/stripe/manual_input>` for one company, then reuse the "
"same credentials and webhook for the others. To view the webhook, go to the "
"`Webhooks page on Stripe <https://dashboard.stripe.com/webhooks>`_, or log "
"into your Stripe dashboard and go to :menuselection:`Developers --> "
"Webhooks`. Click the destination in the list, then click the :icon:`fa-eye` "
"(:guilabel:`Reveal secret`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Signing secret` "
"field and copy the value."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghubungkan akun Stripe yang sama ke :doc:`multiple companies </"
"applications/general/companies/multi_company>` dalam database, :ref:`buat "
"akun <payment_providers/stripe/create_account>` dan :ref:`isi kredensial "
"<payment_providers/stripe/manual_input>` untuk satu perusahaan, lalu gunakan "
"kembali kredensial dan webhook yang sama untuk yang lain. Untuk melihat "
"webhook, buka `Webhooks page on Stripe <https://dashboard.stripe.com/"
"webhooks>`_, atau masuk ke Stripe dashboard Anda dan "
"buka :menuselection:`Developers --> Webhooks`. Klik tujuan dalam daftar, "
"lalu klik ikon :icon:`fa-eye` (:guilabel:`Reveal secret`) di sebelah "
"field :guilabel:`Signing secret` dan salin nilainya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:102
msgid "Enable Apple Pay"
msgstr "Aktifkan Apple Pay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:104
msgid ""
"To allow customers to use the Apple Pay button to pay for their eCommerce "
"orders, :ref:`navigate to the Stripe payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`, then go to the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab, "
"enable :guilabel:`Allow Express Checkout`, and click :guilabel:`Enable Apple "
"Pay`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memungkinkan pelanggan menggunakan tombol Apple Pay untuk membayar "
"pesanan eCommerce mereka, :ref:`navigasi ke penyedia pembayaran Stripe "
"<payment_providers/supported_providers>`, lalu buka "
"tab :guilabel:`Configuration`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Allow Express Checkout`, "
"dan klik :guilabel:`Enable Apple Pay`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:110
msgid ""
":ref:`Express checkout and Google Pay <payment_providers/express_checkout>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Express checkout dan Google Pay <payment_providers/express_checkout>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:113
msgid ""
"Stripe allows to :ref:`manually capture <payment_providers/manual_capture>` "
"and :ref:`refund <payment_providers/refunds>` payments either from Odoo or "
"directly from the Stripe dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Stripe memungkinkan untuk :ref:`menangkap secara manual <payment_providers/"
"manual_capture>` dan :ref:`mengembalikan dana <payment_providers/refunds>` "
"pembayaran baik dari Odoo maupun langsung dari Stripe dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:3
msgid "Wire transfers"
msgstr "Transfer bank"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **Wire Transfer** payment method allows you to provide payment "
"instructions to your customers, such as your bank details and a reference to "
"include with the payment. These instructions are displayed after the "
"customer selects :guilabel:`Wire Transfer` as the payment method and clicks "
"the :guilabel:`Pay now` button at the end of the checkout process on your "
"ecommerce website or on the customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Metode pembayaran **Transfer Bank** memungkinkan Anda memberikan instruksi "
"pembayaran kepada pelanggan, seperti detail bank Anda dan referensi yang "
"harus disertakan dengan pembayaran. Instruksi ini ditampilkan setelah "
"pelanggan memilih :guilabel:`Wire Transfer` sebagai metode pembayaran dan "
"mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Pay now` di akhir proses checkout di website "
"eCommerce Anda atau di portal pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:None
msgid "Payment instructions on the customer portal"
msgstr "Instruksi pembayaran di portal pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:16
msgid ""
"While this method is widely accessible and requires minimal setup, it is not "
"efficient process-wise. It is recommended to set up a :doc:`payment provider "
"<../payment_providers>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun metode ini mudah diakses dan memerlukan pengaturan minimal, ini "
"tidak efisien dari sisi proses. Disarankan untuk menyiapkan :doc:`penyedia "
"pembayaran <../payment_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:19
msgid ""
"Online orders remain in the :guilabel:`Quotation sent` (i.e., unpaid order) "
"stage until you receive the payment and manually :guilabel:`Confirm` the "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Pesanan online tetap berada di tahap :guilabel:`Quotation sent` (yaitu "
"pesanan yang belum dibayar) hingga Anda menerima pembayaran dan secara "
"manual :guilabel:`Confirm` pesanan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Wire transfer** can be used as a template for other payment methods that "
"are processed manually, such as checks, by renaming or duplicating it."
msgstr ""
"**Transfer bank** dapat digunakan sebagai templat untuk metode pembayaran "
"lain yang diproses secara manual, seperti cek, dengan mengganti nama atau "
"menduplikasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:29
msgid "To configure **Wire Transfer**:"
msgstr "Untuk mengonfigurasi **Transfer Bank**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:31
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the Wire Transfer payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Navigasi ke penyedia pembayaran Wire Transfer <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:38
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Enable QR codes` to activate QR code payments."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan :guilabel:`Enable QR codes` untuk mengaktifkan pembayaran kode QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:44
msgid ""
"Define the payment instructions in the :guilabel:`Messages` tab. If :doc:`a "
"bank account <../accounting/bank>` has already been defined, the account "
"number is automatically added to the default message generated by Odoo. You "
"can also add it afterward and update the message by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Reload pending message`."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan instruksi pembayaran di tab :guilabel:`Messages`. Jika :doc:`akun "
"bank <../accounting/bank>` telah didefinisikan, nomor rekening akan secara "
"otomatis ditambahkan ke pesan default yang dibuat oleh Odoo. Anda juga dapat "
"menambahkannya kemudian dan memperbarui pesan dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Reload pending message`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:0
msgid "Define payment instructions"
msgstr "Tentukan instruksi pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:55
msgid ""
"You can also test wire transfers using the :ref:`payment_providers/test-"
"mode`."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menguji transfer bank menggunakan :ref:`payment_providers/"
"test-mode`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:3
msgid "Worldline"
msgstr "Worldline"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Worldline <https://worldline.com/>`_ is a France-based company and the "
"world's fourth largest payment provider."
msgstr ""
"`Worldline <https://worldline.com/>`_ adalah perusahaan yang berbasis di "
"Prancis dan merupakan penyedia pembayaran terbesar keempat di dunia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:9
msgid "Settings in Worldline"
msgstr "Pengaturan di Worldline"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:14
msgid "Create an API user"
msgstr "Buat API user"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:16
msgid ""
"It is recommended to set up an **API user** to create transactions from Odoo "
"to ensure that your Worldline configuration remains safe even if credentials "
"are compromised. Additionally, API users do not require frequent password "
"updates like regular accounts."
msgstr ""
"Disarankan untuk menyiapkan **API user** untuk membuat transaksi dari Odoo "
"guna memastikan konfigurasi Worldline Anda tetap aman meskipun kredensial "
"dikompromikan. Selain itu, API user tidak memerlukan pembaruan kata sandi "
"yang sering seperti akun reguler."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:20
msgid "To create an **API user**, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "Untuk membuat **API user**, lakukan langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:22
msgid ""
"Log into your `Worldline Merchant Portal <https://merchant-portal.worldline-"
"solutions.com/>`_, click the :icon:`fa-th` (:guilabel:`menu`) icon, and "
"select :guilabel:`Back Office`."
msgstr ""
"Login ke `Worldline Merchant Portal <https://merchant-portal.worldline-"
"solutions.com/>`_, klik ikon :icon:`fa-th` (:guilabel:`menu`), dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Back Office`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:24
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` and click on :guilabel:`New "
"User`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` dan klik :guilabel:`New User`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:25
msgid "Configure the following fields:"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan kolom berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:27
msgid ""
"Specify a :guilabel:`UserID`, :guilabel:`User's name`, :guilabel:`E-mail "
"address`, and :guilabel:`Timezone` of your choice."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan :guilabel:`UserID`, :guilabel:`User's name`, :guilabel:`E-mail "
"address`, dan :guilabel:`Timezone` pilihan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:29
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Profile` field to :guilabel:`Admin`."
msgstr "Atur kolom :guilabel:`Profile` ke :guilabel:`Admin`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:30
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Special user for API`."
msgstr "Aktifkan :guilabel:`Special user for API`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:33
msgid ""
"If you have already set up a user, make sure it is activated without any "
"error."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda sudah menyiapkan user, pastikan user tersebut diaktifkan tanpa "
"kesalahan apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:34
msgid ""
"To test the payment flow with Worldline, use their `test environment "
"<https://merchant-portal.preprod.worldline-solutions.com/>`_ together with "
"the :ref:`test mode <payment_providers/test-mode>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menguji alur pembayaran dengan Worldline, gunakan `test environment "
"<https://merchant-portal.preprod.worldline-solutions.com/>`_ mereka bersama "
"dengan :ref:`test mode <payment_providers/test-mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:41
msgid "Set up Worldline for Odoo"
msgstr "Siapkan Worldline untuk Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:43
msgid "Worldline must now be configured to accept payments from Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Worldline sekarang harus dikonfigurasi untuk menerima pembayaran dari Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:45
msgid ""
"From your merchant portal, go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Payment API` "
"and click on :guilabel:`Generate API key`. Copy the :guilabel:`API key ID` "
"and the :guilabel:`Secret API key` and save them for :ref:`later <wordline/"
"odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Dari portal pedagang Anda, buka :menuselection:`Developer --> Payment API` "
"dan klik :guilabel:`Generate API key`. Salin :guilabel:`API key ID` "
"dan :guilabel:`Secret API key` lalu simpan untuk :ref:`nanti <wordline/odoo-"
"configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:48
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Webhooks` and click "
"on :guilabel:`Generate webhook keys`. Copy the :guilabel:`Webhook ID` and "
"the associated :guilabel:`Secret webhook key` and save them for :ref:`later "
"<wordline/odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Developer --> Webhooks` dan klik :guilabel:`Generate "
"webhook keys`. Salin :guilabel:`Webhook ID` dan :guilabel:`Secret webhook "
"key` terkait lalu simpan untuk :ref:`nanti <wordline/odoo-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add webhook endpoint`, enter your Odoo database's URL "
"followed by `/payment/worldline/webhook` in the :guilabel:`Endpoint url` "
"field, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Add webhook endpoint`, masukkan URL database Odoo Anda "
"diikuti dengan `/payment/worldline/webhook` di kolom :guilabel:`Endpoint "
"url`, dan :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid "For example: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."
msgstr "Misalnya: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:58
msgid "Settings in Odoo"
msgstr "Pengaturan di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:60
msgid "To set up Worldline in Odoo:"
msgstr "Untuk menyiapkan Worldline di Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:62
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Worldline <payment_providers/"
"add_new>` and change its state to :guilabel:`Enabled`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Navigasikan ke payment provider Worldline <payment_providers/add_new>` "
"dan ubah statusnya menjadi :guilabel:`Enabled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:64
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab, enter the :guilabel:`PSPID` of your "
"Worldline account and fill in the :guilabel:`API Key`, :guilabel:`API "
"Secret`, :guilabel:`Webhook Key`, and :guilabel:`Webhook Secret` with the "
"values you saved at the step :ref:`Set up Worldline for Odoo <worldline/set-"
"up>`."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Credentials`, masukkan :guilabel:`PSPID` akun Worldline "
"Anda dan isi :guilabel:`API Key`, :guilabel:`API Secret`, :guilabel:`Webhook "
"Key`, dan :guilabel:`Webhook Secret` dengan nilai yang Anda simpan pada "
"langkah :ref:`Set up Worldline for Odoo <worldline/set-up>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:3
msgid "Xendit"
msgstr "Xendit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Xendit <https://www.xendit.co>`_ is an Indonesian-based payment solution "
"provider that covers several Southeast Asian countries. It allows businesses "
"to accept credit cards as well as several local payment methods."
msgstr ""
"`Xendit <https://www.xendit.co>`_ adalah penyedia solusi pembayaran berbasis "
"Indonesia yang mencakup beberapa negara Asia Tenggara. Platform ini "
"memungkinkan bisnis untuk menerima kartu kredit serta beberapa metode "
"pembayaran lokal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:10
msgid ""
"Credit card payments are processed through Odoo, while all other payment "
"methods are handled via Xendit's website."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran kartu kredit diproses melalui Odoo, sementara semua metode "
"pembayaran lainnya ditangani melalui situs web Xendit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:12
msgid ""
"Xendit supports card payment tokenization, provided the customer has "
"requested Merchant Initiated Transaction (MIT) from `Xendit Support <https://"
"www.xendit.co/en/contact/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Xendit mendukung tokenisasi pembayaran kartu, asalkan pelanggan telah "
"meminta Merchant Initiated Transaction (MIT) dari `Xendit Support <https://"
"www.xendit.co/en/contact/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:18
msgid "Configuration on the Xendit Dashboard"
msgstr "Konfigurasi di Xendit Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Create a Xendit account <https://dashboard.xendit.co/register/1?"
"referral_code=odooid&countr_code=ID>`_ if necessary and log in to the "
"`Xendit Dashboard <https://dashboard.xendit.co>`_."
msgstr ""
"Buat `akun Xendit <https://dashboard.xendit.co/register/1?"
"referral_code=odooid&countr_code=ID>`_ jika diperlukan dan masuk ke "
"`Dashboard Xendit <https://dashboard.xendit.co>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:23
msgid ""
"Check your account mode in the top left corner of the page. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Test Mode` to try the integration without charging your "
"customers. Switch to :guilabel:`Live Mode` once you are ready to accept "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Periksa mode akun Anda di sudut kiri atas halaman. Gunakan :guilabel:`Test "
"Mode` untuk mencoba integrasi tanpa menagih pelanggan Anda. Beralih "
"ke :guilabel:`Live Mode` setelah Anda siap menerima pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:26
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration: Settings` in the left part of the "
"application page. In the :guilabel:`Developers` section, click `API Keys "
"<https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#api-keys>`_."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings` di bagian kiri halaman "
"aplikasi. Di bagian :guilabel:`Developers`, klik `API Keys <https://"
"dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#api-keys>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Generate Secret Key`. In the popup box, enter "
"any :guilabel:`API key name`, select :guilabel:`Write` for "
"the :guilabel:`Money-in Products` permission and :guilabel:`None` for all "
"other permissions then click :guilabel:`Generate key`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Generate Secret Key`. Di kotak popup, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`API key name` apa pun, pilih :guilabel:`Write` untuk "
"izin :guilabel:`Money-in Products` dan :guilabel:`None` untuk semua izin "
"lainnya lalu klik :guilabel:`Generate key`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:32
msgid ""
"Confirm your password to display your API key. Copy or download the key and "
"**save this information securely for later**. This is the only time the API "
"key can be viewed or downloaded."
msgstr ""
"Konfirmasi kata sandi Anda untuk menampilkan kunci API Anda. Salin atau "
"unduh kunci tersebut dan **simpan informasi ini dengan aman untuk nanti**. "
"Ini adalah satu-satunya waktu kunci API dapat dilihat atau diunduh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:35
msgid ""
"Once completed, scroll down the page to the `Webhooks <https://"
"dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks>`_ section to generate the "
"webhook token."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, gulir ke bawah halaman ke bagian `Webhooks <https://"
"dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks>`_ untuk membuat token "
"webhook."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:38
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Webhook verification token`, click :guilabel:`View Webhook "
"Verification Token`, then confirm your password to display the token. Save "
"it for later."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah :guilabel:`Webhook verification token`, klik :guilabel:`View "
"Webhook Verification Token`, lalu konfirmasi kata sandi Anda untuk "
"menampilkan token. Simpan untuk nanti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Webhook URL` section, enter your Odoo database's URL, "
"followed by `/payment/xendit/webhook` (e.g., `https://example.odoo.com/"
"payment/xendit/webhook`) in the field :guilabel:`Invoices paid` and click "
"the :guilabel:`Test and save` button next to it."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian :guilabel:`Webhook URL`, masukkan URL database Odoo Anda, diikuti "
"dengan `/payment/xendit/webhook` (mis., `https://example.odoo.com/payment/"
"xendit/webhook`) di bidang :guilabel:`Invoices paid` dan klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Test and save` di sebelahnya."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:43
msgid ""
"To allow recurring payments for credit cards, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration: Payment Channels` in the left part of the "
"application page. Then, hover your mouse over the :guilabel:`Visa, "
"Mastercard, JCB, Amex` channel, click :guilabel:`View Details`, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Recurring Payments` by toggling the related switch."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengizinkan pembayaran berulang untuk kartu kredit, "
"buka :menuselection:`Configuration --> Payment Channels` di bagian kiri "
"halaman aplikasi. Kemudian, arahkan mouse Anda ke channel :guilabel:`Visa, "
"Mastercard, JCB, Amex`, klik :guilabel:`View Details`, dan "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Recurring Payments` dengan mengaktifkan sakelar terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Xendit <payment_providers/add_new>` "
"and change its state to :guilabel:`Enabled`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Buka penyedia pembayaran Xendit <payment_providers/add_new>` dan ubah "
"statusnya menjadi :guilabel:`Enabled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:53
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Secret Key` and :guilabel:`Webhook Token` fields with "
"the information saved at the step :ref:`payment_providers/xendit/"
"configure_dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Isi bidang :guilabel:`Secret Key` dan :guilabel:`Webhook Token` dengan "
"informasi yang disimpan pada langkah :ref:`payment_providers/xendit/"
"configure_dashboard`."

