#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can register any vendor payments made with SEPA. To do so, go "
#~ "to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments`. When creating "
#~ "your payment, select :guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer` as "
